# game/script_marion.rpy:33
translate Spanish ch2m_01_3599ebae:

    # "A week passes, but not a day goes by without me seeing Marion. I feel a responsibility to check in on her regularly, now that her sister has left town."
    "Transcurrio una semana, pero no pasa un día que no vea a Marion. Siento la responsabilidad de ir a verla con regularidad ahora que su hermana ha dejado la ciudad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:34
translate Spanish ch2m_01_168628fc:

    # "In the mornings I stop by with breakfast biscuits or a daily newspaper, or just about anything I can think of that she or Grace might need."
    "Por las mañanas paso por allí con galletas para el desayuno, el periódico del dia o cualquier cosa que se me ocurra que ella o Grace podrían necesitar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:35
translate Spanish ch2m_01_bd14c9bd:

    # "Sometimes Marion and I only speak briefly, a hello or thank you. Other times she has longer moments to spare to chat about her day and mine. But mostly, we keep busy with work at home."
    "A veces, Marion y yo solo hablamos brevemente para saludar o agradecer. Otras veces ella tiene mucho más tiempo libre para charlar sobre su día y el mío. Pero sobre todo, nos mantenemos ocupados con el trabajo en casa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:36
translate Spanish ch2m_01_35daa40a:

    # "While she seems to have recovered from the initial shock of Jessie's departure, times are still tough. Marion has redoubled her efforts on the farm."
    "Si bien ella parece haberse recuperado del shock inicial por la partida de Jessie, los tiempos siguen siendo difíciles. Marion ha redoblado sus esfuerzos en la granja"

# game/script_marion.rpy:37
translate Spanish ch2m_01_23fbef77:

    # "Whether the extra hard work is a necessity or simply a necessary distraction, I cannot say."
    "Si el trabajo extra es una necesidad o simplemente una distracción necesaria, no puedo decirlo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:38
translate Spanish ch2m_01_c559400e:

    # "All I know is that I miss those evenings when we could simply talk, free from all responsibilities. Oh, how I'd love to share another meal together soon."
    "Todo lo que se, es que extraño esas tardes en las que simplemente podíamos hablar, libres de toda responsabilidad. Oh, como me encantaría compartir otra comida juntos pronto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:40
translate Spanish ch2m_01_a20cefa7:

    # "..."
    "..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:41
translate Spanish ch2m_01_efb1a434:

    # "I suppose I could just ask, but I'd hate to pressure her to take time away from her routine."
    "Aunque supongo que podría solo preguntar, pero odiaría presionarla para que se tome un tiempo de su rutina."

# game/script_marion.rpy:42
translate Spanish ch2m_01_a5fda4a1:

    # "At least, that is what I tell myself. Otherwise, I would have to face the truth that... perhaps we're now more than just neighbors. More than just friends."
    "Al menos, eso es lo que lo me digo a mí mismo, tendría que afrontar la verdad de que… quizás ahora seamos mas que simples vecinos. Más que solo amigos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:43
translate Spanish ch2m_01_cf58fd33:

    # "That after every visit, I think more fondly of Marion. What if I get hurt, or worse, hurt this woman who is becoming dear to my heart?"
    "Que después de cada visita, pienso con mas cariño en Marion. ¿Y si salgo herido,  o peor aún, lastimo a esta mujer que se esta volviendo querida en mi corazón?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:57
translate Spanish ch2m_01_da62fc9f:

    # "Eventually, my grandmother takes notice of my strange behavior. At lunch one day, she voices her thoughts."
    "Eventualmente, mi abuela se percataría de mi extraño comportamiento. Un día, durante el almuerzo, ella expreso sus pensamientos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:59
translate Spanish ch2m_01_5732b098:

    # s "You've seemed nervous these past few days, Malcolm. Is everything all right?"
    s "Pareces bastante nervioso estos días, Malcolm, ¿Todo está bien?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:60
translate Spanish ch2m_01_f6f16163:

    # c "Uh, yes."
    c "Uh, claro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:61
translate Spanish ch2m_01_ad9a6273:

    # "I shift in my seat, knowing I'm terrible at lying. Gran saves me the trouble of having to need a cover story."
    "Me muevo en mi asiento, sabiendo que soy terrible mintiendo. Abue me ahorra la molestia de tener que necesitar una tapadera."

# game/script_marion.rpy:63
translate Spanish ch2m_01_5bc6c7c7:

    # s "You two are sweet together."
    s "Ustedes dos se ven lindos juntos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:64
translate Spanish ch2m_01_df72d121:

    # c "What's that?"
    c "¿Que?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:66
translate Spanish ch2m_01_8ee0d5a4:

    # s "You and Marion. I see you dote on her. You make a dear couple."
    s "Tu y Marion. Veo que la adoras. Hacen una linda pareja."

# game/script_marion.rpy:67
translate Spanish ch2m_01_82db23ac:

    # "Leave it to Gran to be a dining table matchmaker."
    "Deja que abue sea la casamentera de la mesa del comedor"

# game/script_marion.rpy:68
translate Spanish ch2m_01_79b2c915:

    # c "I—I'm not entirely sure that's, uh... what we are?"
    c "Y-Yo.. no estoy completamente seguro de que... uh…. ¿Qué somos nosotros?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:70
translate Spanish ch2m_01_22960f8a:

    # s "Then you ought to try harder. To become a dear couple."
    s "Entonces, deberías esforzarte más. Para que se conviertan en una querida pareja."

# game/script_marion.rpy:71
translate Spanish ch2m_01_9971f65f:

    # c "Ha! I imagine some of that would be her decision, Gran."
    c "¡Ja!, Me imagino que parte de eso sería su decisión, abue."

# game/script_marion.rpy:73
translate Spanish ch2m_01_4092afd0:

    # s "No need. Most times a woman makes her mind up first. Then the man realizes what the woman has decided. And he accepts it."
    s "No hay necesidad. La mayoría de las veces es la mujer la que toma la primera decisión. Entonces el hombre se da cuenta de lo que ha decidido la mujer y lo acepta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:74
translate Spanish ch2m_01_d1c20ddd:

    # c "And Marion has made up her mind?"
    c "¿Y Marion ha tomado una decisión?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:76
translate Spanish ch2m_01_9c727c8a:

    # s "And yours. I've seen the way you look at her. More importantly, I see the way she looks at you. She's keen on you. Taken to your heart and kindness."
    s "Y tú. He visto la forma en la que la miras. Más importante aún, veo la forma en la que ella te mira. Ella esta interesada en ti. Llévalo a tu corazón y bondad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:77
translate Spanish ch2m_01_681f59e5:

    # s "I see strength in you both! You ought to make sure she is happy."
    s "¡Veo fuerza en ustedes dos!, Deberías asegurarte de que ella sea feliz."

# game/script_marion.rpy:78
translate Spanish ch2m_01_7f272f06:

    # c "I trust that you're offering sage advice, and not giving me undue hope."
    c "Confío en que estés ofreciendome sabios consejos y no falsas esperanzas"

# game/script_marion.rpy:80
translate Spanish ch2m_01_a7c769d8:

    # s "Oh, Malcolm. Your Gran is wont to give only wisdom, gathered from lifelong experience. I've not enough time left on God's green Earth to give spurious counsel."
    s "Ay, Malcolm. Tu abue solo quiere darte algo de sabiduría acumulada durante toda una vida. No me queda suficiente tiempo en la gran Tierra verde de Dios para dar consejos en vano."

# game/script_marion.rpy:82
translate Spanish ch2m_01_b080ec19:

    # s "Anyway, I speak from personal experience. When your grandfather was but a young lad, even younger than yourself, my eye took a fancy to him."
    s "De todos modos, hablando por experiencia personal. Cuando tu abuelo era sólo un muchacho, incluso más joven que tú, mis ojos se enamoraron de él."

# game/script_marion.rpy:83
translate Spanish ch2m_01_071211b5:

    # s "Every time I saw him at the Stag & Nanny—"
    s "Cada vez que lo lo veia en el Stag & Nanny-"

# game/script_marion.rpy:84
translate Spanish ch2m_01_ad594949:

    # c "You? At the Stag & Nanny?"
    c "Tu? en el Stag & Nanny?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:91
translate Spanish ch2m_01_ce58b5dd:

    # s "Of course! I was a barmaid there until I turned nineteen and got married."
    s "Claro!, era una mesera allí hasta que cumplí diecinueve años y me casé."

# game/script_marion.rpy:92
translate Spanish ch2m_01_f5476988:

    # c "The things we learn about our grandparents..."
    c "las cosas que uno aprende sobre sus abuelos..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:94
translate Spanish ch2m_01_71ebe84b:

    # s "That's where I met your grandfather. Every night he'd come in, and I'd pour him a fresh draught."
    s "Ahi fue donde conocí a tu abuelo. Todas las noches él venía y yo le servía un trago. "

# game/script_marion.rpy:96
translate Spanish ch2m_01_46ae9274:

    # s "As soon as I set my sights on him, I had a bugger of a time getting him to realize it. But sure as the sun sets in the west, that fella was going to be all mine."
    s "Tan pronto como puse mi mirada en él, me costó muchísimo lograr que se diera cuenta. Pero tan seguro como que el sol se pone por el oeste, ese tipo iba a ser todo mío."

# game/script_marion.rpy:97
translate Spanish ch2m_01_a6958177:

    # c "It surely couldn't have taken much convincing. A beauty like you!"
    c "Seguramente no habría sido necesario mucho para convencerlo. ¡Una belleza como tú!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:99
translate Spanish ch2m_01_6f48382f:

    # s "Not convincing, just a bit of attention-grabbing... wearing a low-cut blouse, winking a bit too often..."
    s "No es convencerlo, sólo un poco para llamar la atención... usar una blusa escotada, guiñar un ojo con demasiada frecuencia..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:100
translate Spanish ch2m_01_f6a57779:

    # c "Oh, Gran. That's plenty of description."
    c "Ay, abue. Esa es mucha descripción."

# game/script_marion.rpy:102
translate Spanish ch2m_01_9a518f1d:

    # s "My point is... I found a good, honest, kind, and hard-working man. I wasn't going to let him slip away. Now you need to let Marion make your mind up for {i}you{/i}."
    s "Mi punto es... encontré a un buen, honesto, amable y trabajador hombre. No iba a dejar que se me escapara. Ahora debes dejar que Marion decida por {i}tí{/i}."

# game/script_marion.rpy:103
translate Spanish ch2m_01_ce22cc33:

    # "I mull for a moment. Admittedly, sometimes it takes the perspective of another to see more clearly what's right in front of you."
    "Reflexionando por un momento. Es cierto que a veces se necesita la perspectiva de otra persona para ver más claramente lo que está frente de uno."

# game/script_marion.rpy:104
translate Spanish ch2m_01_9cdcbc12:

    # "If nothing else, Gran's encouragement helps allay my worries."
    "Al menos, los animos de mi abue me ayudan a disipar mis preocupaciones."

# game/script_marion.rpy:105
translate Spanish ch2m_01_89a57b40:

    # c "All right. I shall."
    c "Está bien. Lo haré."

# game/script_marion.rpy:106
translate Spanish ch2m_01_5dbb0993:

    # s "She'll thank ye for it, and be ever grateful. No woman wants a man lollygagging around with her feelings."
    s "Ella te lo agradecerá y siempre estara agradecida. Ninguna mujer quiere que un hombre se divierta con sus sentimientos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:107
translate Spanish ch2m_01_1888123c:

    # c "And we make a cute couple?"
    c "Y nosotros hacemos una linda pareja?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:109
translate Spanish ch2m_01_7103bd86:

    # s "You do, my dear boy. Your Gran certainly wouldn't ramble idly about such things."
    s "Sí, mi querido muchacho. Tu abue ciertamente no divagaría ociosamente sobre tales cosas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:112
translate Spanish ch2m_01_ccf41905:

    # "She moves onto gossip and stories after that, giving me slight glances and smirks as she chitters from behind her teacup, laced with whisky."
    "Luego pasa a los chismes y las historias, lanzándome miradas leves y sonrisas mientras parlotea detrás de su taza de té, mezclada con whisky."

# game/script_marion.rpy:113
translate Spanish ch2m_01_56c3cbaa:

    # s "You know my good friend, Maggie Tyte? She's up in arms about the neon sign Balgair wants to put outside the pub. Can y'imagine? That blazing glare! What a tacky sight."
    s "¿Conoces a mi buena amiga, Maggie Tyte? Está en pie de guerra por el cartel de neón que Balgair quiere poner fuera del la taberna. ¿Te lo imaginas? ¡Ese resplandor ardiente! Qué espectáculo de mal gusto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:119
translate Spanish ch2m_01_7842ffa2:

    # c "Gran... there's not even electricity in town."
    c "Abue... ni siquiera hay electricidad en la ciudad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:121
translate Spanish ch2m_01_12fff218:

    # s "And they best keep it that way. The Whist club ladies are starting a petition to ban neon from the town. How's he ever going to haul the gaudy mass over from Glasgow, anyhow?"
    s "Y más vale que siga siendo así. Las señoras del club de Whist están iniciando una petición para prohibir el neón en la ciudad. ¿Cómo va a transportar esa masa llamativa desde Glasgow?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:123
translate Spanish ch2m_01_c0c353b0:

    # s "Now Robina, she's been going on about having the devil's time putting together everything for the church picnic. Y'know, if not for these old bones, I'd help out and attend."
    s "Ahora Robina, ella ha estado hablando de tener el tiempo del diablo organizando todo para el picnic de la iglesia. Sabes, si no fuera por estos viejos huesos, ayudaría y asistiría."

# game/script_marion.rpy:125
translate Spanish ch2m_01_7554e8d7:

    # s "But, 'tis hard enough on my back to sit in the pews for the length of the pastor's services, much less out on a bonny bare hillside—{i}Malcolm{/i}, ye listening?"
    s "Pero ya es bastante duro para mi espalda sentarme en los bancos durante los servicios del pastor, y mucho menos en una hermosa ladera desnuda... Malcolm, ¿me estás escuchando?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:126
translate Spanish ch2m_01_cbbd962d:

    # "About half. I nod lazily."
    "Más o menos la mitad. Asiento con pereza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:128
translate Spanish ch2m_01_0a7f4acd:

    # s "That {i}means{/i} if you were planning on going, you'll just have to find someone else to take with you. The girl next door, perhaps...?"
    s "Eso {i}significa{/i} que si estabas planeando ir, tendrás que encontrar a alguien más a quien llevar contigo. ¿La chica de al lado, tal vez...?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:129
translate Spanish ch2m_01_8e684aee:

    # "I laugh. A sly, matchmaking rascal is who I live with now, I see. Not that I complain about her intentions; I only hope they aren't a pipe dream."
    "Me río. Veo que ahora vivo con una granuja astuta y casamentera. No es que me queje de sus intenciones; sólo espero que no sean un sueño imposible."

# game/script_marion.rpy:144
translate Spanish ch2m_01_e7446963:

    # "That evening, as I tend to Hazel, my mind swirls. One thing, however, cuts through my musings to grab my attention. My nose twitches."
    "Esa noche, como suelo hacer con Hazel, mi mente da vueltas. Sin embargo, una cosa se abre paso entre mis pensamientos y capta mi atención. Me tiembla la nariz."

# game/script_marion.rpy:145
translate Spanish ch2m_01_5cdd5237:

    # c "How long's it been since you last had a good bath, girl?"
    c "¿Cuánto hace que no te das un buen baño, chica?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:148
translate Spanish ch2m_01_9d860df1:

    # "Hazel huffs. I take that to mean \"ages.\" The musty odor of hay and... well, not hay, are becoming as overwhelming to my senses as anything I'm carrying around internally."
    "Hazel resopla. Tomo eso como que \"años.\". El olor rancio del heno y... bueno, no del heno, se está volviendo tan abrumador para mis sentidos como todo lo que llevo dentro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:149
translate Spanish ch2m_01_838d883d:

    # c "Come, little lady. Let's get to scrubbing."
    c "Vamos, señorita. Vamos a lavarte."

# game/script_marion.rpy:156
translate Spanish ch2m_01_48ab5ad4:

    # "I tote out a full pail of water, a dense bristled brush, and a tablet of lye. The water foams quickly, and I tackle Hazel's fur and mane, starting with her haunches."
    "Saco un cubo lleno de agua, un cepillo de cerdas densas y una pastilla de jabón. El agua hace espuma rápidamente y empiezo a cepillar el pelo y la melena de Hazel, empezando por las ancas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:160
translate Spanish ch2m_01_6937e7c7:

    # c "Hey, now! Don't buck at me. Settle. You'll smell fresh as a daisy, or at least as pleasant as the bluebells you adore."
    c "¡Eh, ya! No me pegues. Tranquilízate. Olerás fresca como una lechuga, o al menos tan agradable como las campanillas que adoras."

# game/script_marion.rpy:162
translate Spanish ch2m_01_a2ba2aa7:

    # "Circling the brush in her thick undercoat, I try hard to think of anything other than Marion, her smile, her eyes, her sweet figure."
    "Dando vueltas con el cepillo en su espeso subpelo, me esfuerzo por pensar en otra cosa que no sea Marion, su sonrisa, sus ojos, su dulce figura."

# game/script_marion.rpy:163
translate Spanish ch2m_01_8da52d0a:

    # "Should I say something to her? I promised Gran I would... but, what? How? Maybe my confidante de rigeur, Miss Hazel, has some advice."
    "¿Debería decirle algo? Le prometí a la abuela que lo haría... pero, ¿qué? ¿Cómo se lo diría? Tal vez mi confidente de rigeur, Miss Hazel, tenga algún consejo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:164
translate Spanish ch2m_01_d4fdda32:

    # c "Hazel, my heart but melts when I picture her. That Marion. It's like a ringing in my head, a constant tug... a pull at my brain."
    c "Hazel, mi corazón se derrite cuando me la imagino. Esa Marion. Es como un zumbido en mi cabeza, un tirón constante... un tirón en mi cerebro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:165
translate Spanish ch2m_01_69e6b301:

    # c "There's not much else to keep my attention. Even your fine visage."
    c "No hay mucho más para mantener mi atención. Ni siquiera tu hermoso rostro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:167
translate Spanish ch2m_01_3fe382a3:

    # "The horse's head whips back, and I do believe an evil eye is cast my way. All right, perhaps I was laying it on a bit thick."
    "La cabeza del caballo da un latigazo hacia atrás y creo que me echa un mal de ojo. Muy bien, tal vez yo estaba poniendo en un poco pesado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:168
translate Spanish ch2m_01_8473845c:

    # c "Don't fret, Hazel. You're still the apple of my eye. But... I dare say Marion is the whole orchard."
    c "No te preocupes, Hazel. Sigues siendo la niña de mis ojos. Pero... Me atrevo a decir que Marion es todo el huerto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:169
translate Spanish ch2m_01_459e74eb:

    # "I smile to myself, knowing that my heart has probably doubled in size in the brief time I've gotten reacquainted with my kind and beautiful neighbor."
    "Sonrío para mi mismo, sabiendo que mi corazón probablemente ha duplicado su tamaño en el breve tiempo que llevo reencontrándome con mi amable y hermosa vecina."

# game/script_marion.rpy:170
translate Spanish ch2m_01_4c88492e:

    # c "I'm guessing you've not a lick of advice for me, eh?"
    c "Supongo que no tienes ni un consejo para mí, ¿eh?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:178
translate Spanish ch2m_01_12885f33:

    # "As if on cue, Hazel knocks her head back and gives my jaw a fair slurp with her wet tongue. I drop the brush and consider dunking my head into the lye."
    "Hazel echa la cabeza hacia atrás y me sorbe la mandíbula con su lengua húmeda. Dejo caer el cepillo y me planteo sumergir la cabeza en el jabon."

# game/script_marion.rpy:179
translate Spanish ch2m_01_51533af5:

    # c "Thanks... I think. Alas, I'm not sure Marion would respond so favourably to a big ol' slurp."
    c "Gracias... Creo. Por desgracia, no estoy seguro de Marion respondería tan favorablemente a un buen trago"

# game/script_marion.rpy:180
translate Spanish ch2m_01_cfbbcfb5:

    # "As I scrub and rinse my obstinate beauty, I look over my work. She positively glows."
    "Mientras friego y enjuago a mi obstinada belleza, repaso mi trabajo. Está radiante."

# game/script_marion.rpy:181
translate Spanish ch2m_01_78d18444:

    # c "You're a good dame, Hazel, and an even better listener. Remind me to consult you for advice more frequently."
    c "Eres una buena dama, Hazel, y aún mejor oyente. Recuérdame que te pida consejo más a menudo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:183
translate Spanish ch2m_01_bed30809:

    # "Hazel glares, letting me know that she would prefer I do no such thing."
    "Hazel me fulmina con la mirada, haciéndome saber que preferiría que no hiciera tal cosa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:195
translate Spanish ch2m_01_5afd0f28:

    # "It's another struggle to get my horse back into the stable for the evening, and I reward myself with a tumbler of Scotch back inside the home."
    "Vuelvo a tener que esforzarme para que mi caballo vuelva al establo y me recompenso con un vaso de whisky en casa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:196
translate Spanish ch2m_01_1231d681:

    # "I can hear Gran's snores, and decide to retire for the night, as well. It's an evening of dreams."
    "Oigo los ronquidos de la abuela y decido retirarme también a dormir. Es una noche de sueños."

# game/script_marion.rpy:200
translate Spanish ch2m_01_a3e01304:

    # "Dreams of summer wildflowers, of the wind on my face, of Marion's hair blowing in the breeze like a window curtain. Every imagined movement feels closer to becoming a reality."
    "Sueño con flores silvestres de verano, con el viento en mi cara, con el pelo de Marion ondeando con la brisa como una cortina de ventana. Cada movimiento imaginado parece más cerca de convertirse en realidad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:201
translate Spanish ch2m_01_ab4c10c5:

    # "I sleep well, knowing that soon, I may be able to make at least one dream come true."
    "Duermo bien, sabiendo que pronto podré hacer realidad al menos un sueño."

# game/script_marion.rpy:230
translate Spanish ch2m_02_1ae61813:

    # "The next morning, I wake to Gran's broad grin facing me at the breakfast table."
    "A la mañana siguiente, me despierto con la amplia sonrisa de la abuela frente a mí en la mesa del desayuno."

# game/script_marion.rpy:231
translate Spanish ch2m_02_1e5a8c8c:

    # c "That's a smile wider than the loch, Gran. What have you got up yer sleeve?"
    c "Esa es una sonrisa más ancha que el lago, abuela. Qué tienes en la manga?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:233
translate Spanish ch2m_02_6ca2099e:

    # s "Not a thing, Malcolm. Not one! I just need you to pick up a few things from the market today."
    s "Nada, Malcolm. ¡Ni una! Sólo necesito que recojas algunas cosas del mercado hoy."

# game/script_marion.rpy:234
translate Spanish ch2m_02_e471f30b:

    # "The smile widens as she slides a silver coin across the table."
    "La sonrisa se ensancha cuando desliza una moneda de plata por la mesa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:235
translate Spanish ch2m_02_90c8f3a3:

    # c "Gran, I've plenty of money. Fret not."
    c "Abue, tengo mucho dinero. No te preocupes."

# game/script_marion.rpy:237
translate Spanish ch2m_02_c90e5f7a:

    # s "This is for something else. I've seen the spring in your step. It's been keeping you nearly a foot aloft all week."
    s "Esto es por otra cosa. He visto el brinco en tu paso. Te ha estado manteniendo casi un pie de altura toda la semana."

# game/script_marion.rpy:238
translate Spanish ch2m_02_3d74e95b:

    # s "Take this shilling and get a nice gift for Marion. A present to make her smile as broadly as I am."
    s "Toma este chelín y compra un buen regalo para Marion. Un regalo que la haga sonreír tan ampliamente como yo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:239
translate Spanish ch2m_02_9e319c81:

    # c "Gran! Matchmaking is one thing, but subsidizing your grandson's relationships?"
    c "¡Abue! Buscar pareja es una cosa, ¿pero financiar las relaciones de tu nieto?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:241
translate Spanish ch2m_02_f57318b6:

    # s "Think of it as an investment in our future. I've only so many years left on this earthly plane, and still no great grandchildren to dote on!"
    s "Piensa en ello como una inversión en tu futuro. Me quedan pocos años en este plano terrenal, ¡y aún no tengo bisnietos a los que adorar!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:242
translate Spanish ch2m_02_e4703b23:

    # "I just about choke on my morning tea."
    "Casi me atraganto con mi té matutino."

# game/script_marion.rpy:243
translate Spanish ch2m_02_34a1e771:

    # c "G-grandchildren!? Goodness, let's not get ahead of ourselves!"
    c "¿¡Ni-Nietos!? ¡Dios mío, no nos adelantemos!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:245
translate Spanish ch2m_02_53330f91:

    # s "Of course not, dear. I'm only suggesting you get our dear neighbor a little gift."
    s "Claro que no, querido. Sólo sugiero que le des un regalito a nuestra querida vecina."

# game/script_marion.rpy:246
translate Spanish ch2m_02_cd1cba5d:

    # "Her smile is far more innocent than her intentions, of that I am sure."
    "Su sonrisa es mucho más inocente que sus intenciones, de eso estoy seguro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:247
translate Spanish ch2m_02_054db1ad:

    # c "All right. Of that, we are of a same mind. Any suggestions?"
    c "De acuerdo. pensamos lo mismo. ¿Alguna sugerencia?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:248
translate Spanish ch2m_02_283bd8fc:

    # s "Something small and memorable. A treasure with which she will never want to part."
    s "Algo pequeño y memorable. Un tesoro del que nunca querrá separarse."

# game/script_marion.rpy:249
translate Spanish ch2m_02_67df7eef:

    # c "That's a lot of pressure, finding the perfect gift!"
    c "Encontrar el regalo perfecto es mucha presión!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:251
translate Spanish ch2m_02_86e670e1:

    # s "Jewelry, dear. A charm. Bright, shiny, small. Something befitting of her sparkling nature. She will love it."
    s "Una joya, querido. Un amuleto. Brillante, reluciente, pequeño. Algo acorde con su naturaleza chispeante. Le encantará."

# game/script_marion.rpy:252
translate Spanish ch2m_02_f5c54d4c:

    # "Gran likely has a point. While I take her advice, I don't take her shilling, sliding it back across the table."
    "La abuela tiene razón. Aunque acepto su consejo, no acepto su moneda, que vuelvo a deslizar sobre la mesa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:253
translate Spanish ch2m_02_4b79525a:

    # c "Very well. And to you, I return this small, shiny thing. No buts!"
    c "Muy bien. Y a ti, te devuelvo esta pequeña y brillante cosa. ¡Sin peros!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:255
translate Spanish ch2m_02_e623afff:

    # "Gran pouts, but I stand my ground. After I clean up the morning dishes, I kiss Gran atop the head, saddle up Hazel, and head to town to shop."
    "La abue pone mala cara, pero yo me mantengo firme. Después de fregar los platos de la mañana, le doy un beso en la cabeza a la abuela, ensillo a Hazel y me voy de compras al pueblo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:272
translate Spanish ch2m_02_64561afd:

    # "The market is crowded as usual. While most stalls are geared toward produce and household goods, a few dabble in things for the missus."
    "El mercado está abarrotado, como de costumbre. Aunque la mayoría de los puestos están orientados a productos y artículos para el hogar, unos pocos ofrecen artículos para la señora."

# game/script_marion.rpy:273
translate Spanish ch2m_02_eeb57f9f:

    # "I keep an eye out for a small token or trinket to pass along to Marion, if only to thank her for her kindness and warmth, and to cheer her up."
    "No pierdo de vista algún pequeño detalle o baratija para dárselo a Marion, aunque sólo sea para agradecerle su amabilidad y su calidez, y para animarla."

# game/script_marion.rpy:274
translate Spanish ch2m_02_297a0301:

    # "She still misses Jessie something terrible, and Grace has been little help to ease the concern."
    "Sigue echando terriblemente de menos a Jessie, y Grace ha sido de poca ayuda para aliviar la preocupación."

# game/script_marion.rpy:275
translate Spanish ch2m_02_8f4c811c:

    # "Mind, it couldn't hurt if the gift impressed Marion a wee bit, too. I do truly want her to know I think of her constantly."
    "Eso sí, no estaría de más que el regalo también impresionara un poco a Marion. De verdad quiero que sepa que pienso en ella constantemente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:276
translate Spanish ch2m_02_fd5892d2:

    # "It's a tall order. I wonder if the market has something that fits the bill? The gift must remind her both of me and my fondness for her."
    "Es mucho pedir. Me pregunto si el mercado tiene algo que se ajuste a la situación. El regalo debe recordarle tanto a mí como mi cariño por ella."

# game/script_marion.rpy:279
translate Spanish ch2m_02_36627455:

    # "Among stalls of breads, fruits, nuts, and sundries, a small row of charms catches my eye."
    "Entre puestos de pan, fruta, frutos secos y otros artículos, me llama la atención una pequeña hilera de amuletos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:280
translate Spanish ch2m_02_40bf0bf6:

    # c "Hmm... Ah!"
    c "Hmm... Ah!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:282
translate Spanish ch2m_02_d31fe045:

    # "It shines brightly, like Marion when she smiles. A tiny silver cowbell, just small enough to fit in my palm."
    "Brilla intensamente, como Marion cuando sonríe. Un minúsculo cencerro de plata, lo bastante pequeño para caber en la palma de mi mano."

# game/script_marion.rpy:283
translate Spanish ch2m_02_db93ed72:

    # "A hand reaches out for the trinket just as mine does. It pulls away when I pick up the bell."
    "Una mano tiende la mano hacia la baratija igual que la mía. Se aparta cuando recojo la campanilla."

# game/script_marion.rpy:284
translate Spanish ch2m_02_0df44191:

    # e "I was just going to recommend that one for you, Malcolm. Looks to have a bit of magic to it."
    e "Iba a recomendarte ese, Malcolm. Parece tener un poco de magia."

# game/script_marion.rpy:300
translate Spanish ch2m_02_116eaf1c:

    # "I look up when I realize it is Effie's voice. She is staring at me, plain-faced."
    "Levanto la vista cuando me doy cuenta de que es la voz de Effie. Me mira fijamente, con la cara desencajada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:301
translate Spanish ch2m_02_805b0d8c:

    # c "Effie! How nice to see you again. How've you been?"
    c "¡Effie! Qué alegría volver a verte. Cómo has estado?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:302
translate Spanish ch2m_02_ce62045d:

    # e "Fairly well, Malcolm. It's always a pleasure to see you, too."
    e "Bastante bien, Malcolm. Siempre es un placer verte, también."

# game/script_marion.rpy:303
translate Spanish ch2m_02_fc4d6b7c:

    # c "You took off so quickly last week after church. I was hoping to run into you again. To catch up."
    c "Te fuiste tan rápido la semana pasada después de la iglesia. Esperaba encontrarme contigo otra vez. Para ponernos al día."

# game/script_marion.rpy:305
translate Spanish ch2m_02_78e5b738:

    # e "You were?"
    e "¿En serio?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:306
translate Spanish ch2m_02_78c04284:

    # "She squints, as if in disbelief.."
    "Entrecierra los ojos, como incrédula.."

# game/script_marion.rpy:307
translate Spanish ch2m_02_e62ccc47:

    # c "Naturally. Your friendly face is always a welcome sight."
    c "Naturalmente. Tu cara amable siempre es bienvenida."

# game/script_marion.rpy:317
translate Spanish ch2m_02_53ccd82f:

    # "Effie does a quick curtsy."
    "Effie hace una rápida reverencia."

# game/script_marion.rpy:318
translate Spanish ch2m_02_c79a192d:

    # e "Thank ye, Mr. Campbell."
    e "Gracias, Sr. Campbell."

# game/script_marion.rpy:321
translate Spanish ch2m_02_abd4c6f0:

    # "I cling to the miniature cowbell, rolling it around in my hand, letting my thumb brush across the sharper corners. It jingles whimsically."
    "Me aferro al cencerro en miniatura, dándole vueltas en la mano y dejando que el pulgar roce las esquinas más afiladas. Tintinea caprichosamente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:322
translate Spanish ch2m_02_c63baa9e:

    # c "So... I thought you worked for the milliner first time I saw you in the market stalls. Now I see you here with the ephemera. You get around, don't you?"
    c "Así que... pensé que trabajabas para el sombrerero la primera vez que te vi en los puestos del mercado. Ahora te veo aquí con las efemérides. Te mueves mucho, no?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:324
translate Spanish ch2m_02_88d79943:

    # "She laughs and nods."
    "Se ríe y asiente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:326
translate Spanish ch2m_02_8e916953:

    # e "I float from place to place... go where the wind takes me."
    e "Floto de un lugar a otro... voy donde me lleva el viento."

# game/script_marion.rpy:327
translate Spanish ch2m_02_e2a19c3f:

    # c "I don't doubt you. You have a smile that could sell a broken oar to a fisherman."
    c "No dudo de ti. Tienes una sonrisa que podría vender un remo roto a un pescador."

# game/script_marion.rpy:329
translate Spanish ch2m_02_67a11187:

    # e "My word! You don't think I'm unscrupulous, do you?"
    e "¡Vaya! No creerás que no tengo escrúpulos, ¿verdad?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:330
translate Spanish ch2m_02_3386796b:

    # c "Not at all! Just, gently persuasive."
    c "En absoluto. Sólo, suavemente persuasivo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:332
translate Spanish ch2m_02_7a056249:

    # "As we talk, I look over the other baubles and trinkets. I still can't get past the one in my hand. It feels meant to be."
    "Mientras hablamos, miro las demás chucherías y baratijas. No puedo dejar de mirar el que tengo en la mano. Parece destinado a ser."

# game/script_marion.rpy:333
translate Spanish ch2m_02_d8e7ca6f:

    # "Effie watches me closely."
    "Effie me observa atentamente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:335
translate Spanish ch2m_02_0611a091:

    # e "And the cowbell charm... You're going to get it?"
    e "Y el amuleto del cencerro... ¿Vas a conseguirlo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:336
translate Spanish ch2m_02_dc4400bc:

    # c "I love it. I'm definitely going to purchase it."
    c "Me encanta. Definitivamente voy a comprarlo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:338
translate Spanish ch2m_02_f33509c2:

    # "Effie pauses and wrings her hands."
    "Effie hace una pausa y se retuerce las manos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:340
translate Spanish ch2m_02_aefd3e62:

    # e "It reminds you of someone special, doesn't it?"
    e "Te recuerda a alguien especial, ¿verdad?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:341
translate Spanish ch2m_02_5d287746:

    # c "Am I such an open book? Yes. Very much so."
    c "¿Soy un libro abierto? Sí. Mucho."

# game/script_marion.rpy:343
translate Spanish ch2m_02_a0b5f38d:

    # e "She will like it."
    e "Le gustará."

# game/script_marion.rpy:344
translate Spanish ch2m_02_3079022a:

    # c "You think so?"
    c "Tú crees?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:346
translate Spanish ch2m_02_08ee414c:

    # e "Well... I certainly would. A gift from a gentleman ought always be appreciated and welcomed, that's for sure."
    e "Bueno... Ciertamente lo haría. Un regalo de un caballero siempre debe ser apreciado y bienvenido, eso es seguro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:347
translate Spanish ch2m_02_77b885f3:

    # c "How much for the cowbell? Five shillings?"
    c "¿Cuánto por el cencerro? ¿Cinco chelines?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:349
translate Spanish ch2m_02_80526a8a:

    # "She gives me a knowing look. I root around in my pocket for the coins, but Effie shakes her head."
    "Me mira con complicidad. Busco las monedas en el bolsillo, pero Effie niega con la cabeza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:350
translate Spanish ch2m_02_913cf5af:

    # e "No need, Malcolm. It's on me. May the new owner be delighted to receive it. Perhaps even as delighted as you are speaking of her."
    e "No es necesario, Malcolm. Yo invito. Que la nueva dueña esté encantada de recibirla. Tal vez incluso tan encantado como usted está hablando de ella."

# game/script_marion.rpy:351
translate Spanish ch2m_02_815407fb:

    # "The girl smiles but has a wistful look in her eyes. I nod and set down the money just in case."
    "La chica sonríe, pero tiene una mirada melancólica. Asiento con la cabeza y dejo el dinero por si acaso."

# game/script_marion.rpy:352
translate Spanish ch2m_02_e109ce06:

    # c "I can't walk off without leaving something. Take care, Effie. Good to see you once again."
    c "No puedo irme sin dejar algo. Cuídate, Effie. Me alegro de volver a verte."

# game/script_marion.rpy:369
translate Spanish ch2m_02_d1fa39d2:

    # "I take off through the market stalls, and glance back. Another merchant at the booth pockets the coins before Effie can, and seems to ignore her in the process."
    "Atravieso los puestos del mercado y miro hacia atrás. Otro comerciante del puesto se embolsa las monedas antes de que Effie pueda hacerlo, y parece ignorarla en el proceso."

# game/script_marion.rpy:370
translate Spanish ch2m_02_62e4c6a8:

    # "She looks up at him and shrugs. Then she adjusts her hat, brushes down her attire, and walks out into the crowd, disappearing as swiftly as she appeared."
    "Le mira y se encoge de hombros. Luego se ajusta el sombrero, se cepilla el traje y sale entre la multitud, desapareciendo tan rápidamente como apareció."

# game/script_marion.rpy:371
translate Spanish ch2m_02_c4eb5cf3:

    # "I can't figure that girl out. As much as that friendly face, with that oversized hat and those charming glasses, puts me at ease... deep down, something feels off."
    "No puedo entender a esa chica. Por mucho que esa cara amable, con ese sombrero de gran tamaño y esas encantadoras gafas, me tranquilice... en el fondo, algo no encaja."

# game/script_marion.rpy:372
translate Spanish ch2m_02_28d0b2fe:

    # "Something I can't quite put my finger on. But I don't dwell on it. Instead, I stock up on other needed goods while keeping an eye out for an auburn head of hair."
    "Algo que no puedo identificar. Pero no pienso en ello. En lugar de eso, me abastezco de otros artículos necesarios mientras vigilo que no se me caiga el pelo castaño."

# game/script_marion.rpy:373
translate Spanish ch2m_02_b00b274d:

    # "No sign of Marion. I wonder when I will next see her."
    "Ni rastro de Marion. Me pregunto cuándo la volveré a ver."

# game/script_marion.rpy:374
translate Spanish ch2m_02_9982ae9c:

    # "My hand nervously fumbles with the tiny gift in my waistcoat pocket. What if I'm being too forward? Or worse, what if she thinks I'm calling {i}her{/i} a cow?"
    "Mi mano tantea nerviosa el pequeño regalo que llevo en el bolsillo del chaleco. ¿Y si estoy siendo demasiado atrevido? O peor, ¿y si cree que {i}la{/i} estoy llamando vaca?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:375
translate Spanish ch2m_02_a20cefa7:

    # "..."
    "..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:376
translate Spanish ch2m_02_5bd860a5:

    # "Don't be ridiculous, Malcolm. Marion's an understanding lass. She'll accept it for what it's meant to be."
    "No seas ridículo, Malcolm. Marion es una chica comprensiva. Ella lo aceptará tal como debe ser."

# game/script_marion.rpy:377
translate Spanish ch2m_02_9e7b2dce:

    # "...I hope."
    "...Espero."

# game/script_marion.rpy:401
translate Spanish ch2m_03_d8405cdc:

    # "My fingers are still fiddling with the trinket in my pocket when the MacLeods' homestead comes into view."
    "Mis dedos siguen jugueteando con la baratija que llevo en el bolsillo cuando la granja de los MacLeods aparece a la vista."

# game/script_marion.rpy:402
translate Spanish ch2m_03_4271e8b3:

    # "I came straight from home, after dropping off the day's groceries. Crivens. I've not felt butterflies like these since the war."
    "Vine directamente de casa, después de dejar la compra del día. Crivens. No he sentido mariposas como estas desde la guerra."

# game/script_marion.rpy:403
translate Spanish ch2m_03_b60647ca:

    # "All right, Malcolm. Keep the head and carry on. Best get this done, before I get cold feet."
    "Muy bien, Malcolm. Mantén la cabeza y continúa. Mejor terminar esto, antes de que me acobarde."

# game/script_marion.rpy:432
translate Spanish ch2m_03_10de9990:

    # "Marching on, I find Marion scrubbing laundry outside. I duck in and around hanging linens and bed sheets until I get closer to her."
    "Sigo mi camino y encuentro a Marion fregando la ropa. Me escabullo entre las sábanas colgadas hasta acercarme a ella."

# game/script_marion.rpy:433
translate Spanish ch2m_03_b37badd4:

    # "Her cheeks are flush from work and being out in the sun. Those freckles are painfully cute."
    "Tiene las mejillas sonrosadas por el trabajo y por estar al sol. Esas pecas son dolorosamente bonitas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:434
translate Spanish ch2m_03_de87617a:

    # "Suddenly, I am struck with a case of the jitters. What if she doesn't like the gift? I can't just hand it to her... it'll look like I'm not even trying."
    "De repente, me entra un ataque de nervios. ¿Y si no le gusta el regalo? No puedo dárselo sin más... parecerá que ni siquiera lo intento."

# game/script_marion.rpy:435
translate Spanish ch2m_03_aa4efb87:

    # "I want to make it a surprise. Oh, why didn't I think this through earlier?"
    "Quiero que sea una sorpresa. Por qué no lo pensé antes?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:436
translate Spanish ch2m_03_14c5c3ca:

    # "A laundry basket sits on the ground, full to the brim with cotton sheets. I could easily drop the necklace inside and wait for her to discover it."
    "En el suelo hay un cesto lleno de sábanas de algodón. Podría dejar el collar dentro y esperar a que ella lo descubriera."

# game/script_marion.rpy:437
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a30d96b0:

    # "It's the best idea I can muster for a last-second plan."
    "Es la mejor idea que se me ocurre para un plan de último momento."

# game/script_marion.rpy:439
translate Spanish ch2m_03_23ceae5e:

    # m "Oh! Hello, Malcolm! Forgive me, I didn't even see you there."
    m "¡Oh! Hola, Malcolm! Perdóname, no te había visto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:440
translate Spanish ch2m_03_c19d495d:

    # c "Hello, Miss Marion! Such a fine day to be outside."
    c "¡Hola, Señorita Marion! Qué buen día para estar afuera."

# game/script_marion.rpy:441
translate Spanish ch2m_03_fa145183:

    # m "It is! What brings you by?"
    m "¡Así es! Qué te trae por aquí?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:442
translate Spanish ch2m_03_ccb43caa:

    # c "I didn't see you in town, and just wanted to check in. And..."
    c "No te vi en la ciudad, y sólo quería comprobarlo. Y..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:444
translate Spanish ch2m_03_41764376:

    # "Marion looks away to clip a sheet to the line. Swifter than a hare, I slip the pendant underneath the first layer of cotton in the basket."
    "Marion aparta la mirada para enganchar una sábana al tendedero. Más rápido que una liebre, deslizo el colgante bajo la primera capa de algodón de la cesta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:445
translate Spanish ch2m_03_488d140f:

    # c "...Thought I could help any way you see fit. Perhaps hang a few linens to dry?"
    c "...pensé que podría ayudar de la forma que creas conveniente. Quizás colgar algunas sábanas para que se sequen?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:447
translate Spanish ch2m_03_1c926605:

    # "I gesture towards the basket, but she shakes her head."
    "Hago un gesto hacia la cesta, pero ella niega con la cabeza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:449
translate Spanish ch2m_03_351a7012:

    # m "Those are clean, and already dry... but there's another basket of wet laundry by the door if you don't mind getting it!"
    m "Esos están limpios, y ya secos... pero hay otro cesto de ropa mojada junto a la puerta, si no te importaria tomarla!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:450
translate Spanish ch2m_03_e099ec9c:

    # c "Oh! Of course... um... I'll go get it for you!"
    c "¡Oh! Por supuesto... um... ¡Iré a buscarlo por ti!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:451
translate Spanish ch2m_03_8e36df6a:

    # "Marion doesn't notice the contents of her basket at all as she hefts it my way and passes it off."
    "Marion no se da cuenta del contenido de su cesta mientras me la arrebata y me la pasa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:453
translate Spanish ch2m_03_2936c6d6:

    # m "This one is full. Can you leave it inside?"
    m "Este está lleno. Puedes dejarlo dentro?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:454
translate Spanish ch2m_03_e631bc97:

    # c "Sure thing."
    c "Claro"

# game/script_marion.rpy:456
translate Spanish ch2m_03_40c25a62:

    # m "Thank you!"
    m "Gracias!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:461
translate Spanish ch2m_03_c742632d:

    # "That didn't work. I drop the basket inside the doorway, and rifle through to get the pendant."
    "Eso no funcionó. Dejo caer la cesta dentro de la puerta, y hurgo para coger el colgante."

# game/script_marion.rpy:481
translate Spanish ch2m_03_25f3e740:

    # "Then I haul the basket of wet linens back to the lines, where I spot Marion's favorite cow, Fiona, weaving her hefty frame through the hanging laundry."
    "Luego arrastro el cesto de ropa mojada hasta los tendederos, donde veo a Fiona, la vaca favorita de Marion, entre la ropa colgada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:482
translate Spanish ch2m_03_463f22d7:

    # "Oh, Marion. She must give her cows free reign. No wonder they like her so much!"
    "Oh, Marion. Debe dar rienda suelta a sus vacas. No me extraña que les guste tanto ella!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:483
translate Spanish ch2m_03_46697030:

    # "It's a good thing it's just laundry and not a china shop. Fiona's horns get caught on the sheets... and it gives me another idea."
    "Menos mal que es sólo lavandería y no una tienda de baratijas. Los cuernos de Fiona se enganchan en las sábanas... y me da otra idea."

# game/script_marion.rpy:484
translate Spanish ch2m_03_f17ff8a7:

    # "I set the basket down, and pretend to start clipping the fabric to the lines."
    "Dejo la cesta en el suelo y hago como que empiezo a recortar la tela en las líneas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:486
translate Spanish ch2m_03_0b58d78e:

    # "Clandestinely, I slip the pendant around Fiona's long, curving horn. I can't wait to see Marion's face when Fiona clomps over."
    "A escondidas, deslizo el colgante alrededor del largo y curvado cuerno de Fiona. Me muero de ganas de ver la cara de Marion cuando Fiona se acerque. Dejo la cesta en el suelo y finjo que empiezo a enganchar la tela a las líneas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:488
translate Spanish ch2m_03_b8bacdb5:

    # "That ends up being a bigger mistake."
    "Eso termina siendo un grave error."

# game/script_marion.rpy:504
translate Spanish ch2m_03_08aff24f:

    # m "Malcolm, can you help me reach the top? Grace tied the line too high for me. That imp!"
    m "Malcolm, ¿puedes ayudarme a llegar arriba? Grace ató el cabo demasiado alto para mí. Esa diablilla!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:505
translate Spanish ch2m_03_09eecfb5:

    # c "Here, let me get that for you."
    c "claro, déjame que lo tome por ti"

# game/script_marion.rpy:519
translate Spanish ch2m_03_54032903:

    # "I stand behind Marion, grabbing hold of the clothespin and fabric. Our bodies press into each other and I get a tickle on my chin when it brushes against her hair."
    "Me coloco detrás de Marion, agarrando la pinza de la ropa y la tela. Nuestros cuerpos se aprietan y siento un cosquilleo en la barbilla al rozar su pelo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:534
translate Spanish ch2m_03_64a48593:

    # "My mind goes to mush... until I see Fiona ambling back to join the herd. The light catches the pendant, and I panic about how to get it back now."
    "Mi mente se vuelve un torbellino... hasta que veo a Fiona volver a reunirse con la manada. La luz capta el colgante y me asusto pensando cómo recuperarlo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:559
translate Spanish ch2m_03_98cf6b15:

    # m "Thank you."
    m "Gracias."

# game/script_marion.rpy:560
translate Spanish ch2m_03_6e2fb3f1:

    # c "Any time... uh, I'll just continue over here then, eh?"
    c "En cualquier caso... eh, seguiré por aquí entonces, eh?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:569
translate Spanish ch2m_03_da7e3e50:

    # "I pin and clip, keeping one eye each on Marion and Fiona. The heifer has rejoined her shaggy compatriots, and is recognizable only for the shiny object on her head."
    "Sujeto con alfileres y pinzas a Marion y Fiona. La vaquilla se ha reunido con sus peludos compatriotas y sólo se la reconoce por el objeto brillante que lleva en la cabeza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:570
translate Spanish ch2m_03_66da9354:

    # "My hands wrinkle and chap from handling the damp cloth for so long. Finally, my savior comes in the form of Marion's little rascal of a sister. Grace shouts from the window."
    "Mis manos se arrugan y se agrietan de tanto manipular el paño húmedo. Por fin llega mi salvadora, la hermana pequeña de Marion. Grace grita desde la ventana."

# game/script_marion.rpy:571
translate Spanish ch2m_03_8380e0ed:

    # g "Marion! Your bilberries are boiling over!"
    g "¡Marion! ¡Tus arándanos están hirviendo!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:573
translate Spanish ch2m_03_5095cbd4:

    # m "What? Grace! Take them off the fire!"
    m "¿Qué? Grace! ¡Quítalos del fuego!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:575
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a93371d1:

    # m "Oh... I'll be right back."
    m "Oh... Ahora vuelvo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:602
translate Spanish ch2m_03_2b644569:

    # "By the time Marion races inside, I'm squishing my way through a herd of two dozen cattle, shoving ribs and rumps around until I get to Fiona."
    "Para cuando Marion entra corriendo, yo ya me estoy abriendo paso entre un rebaño de dos docenas de cabezas de ganado, empujando costillas y lomos hasta llegar a Fiona."

# game/script_marion.rpy:619
translate Spanish ch2m_03_fcbd4cda:

    # "I take the pendant off her horn, thanking her for her efforts. Of course, I get nothing but a hearty huff in response."
    "Le quito el colgante del cuerno y le agradezco su esfuerzo. Por supuesto, no obtengo más que un gruñido como respuesta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:641
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_20e37f58:

    # "I'm back at my post by the clothesline when Marion returns, looking frustrated."
    "Vuelvo a mi puesto junto al tendedero cuando Marion regresa, con cara de frustración."

# game/script_marion.rpy:642
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_cff50b41:

    # m "That girl, I swear! Why can't she get anything right? Now all I have is a pot of burned bilberries and blue stains on the floor."
    m "¡Esa chica, lo juro! ¿Por qué no puede hacer nada bien? Ahora todo lo que tengo es una olla de arándanos quemados y manchas azules en el suelo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:643
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_2cc81738:

    # "I'm hot and sweaty from pushing around heifers, and Marion is red with anger from dealing with her sister."
    "Estoy acalorado y sudoroso de tanto empujar vaquillas, y Marion está roja de rabia por lidiar con su hermana."

# game/script_marion.rpy:644
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_7482ae37:

    # "A new, blessedly simpler idea presents itself."
    "Se presenta una nueva idea, benditamente más sencilla."

# game/script_marion.rpy:645
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_4a601c17:

    # c "Hey, Marion... how 'bout a hug?"
    c "Oye, Marion... ¿qué tal un abrazo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:647
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_c3dbf7c9:

    # "It catches her off guard, but I can see the enmity quickly disappear."
    "La pilla desprevenida, pero veo que la enemistad desaparece rápidamente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:649
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_a8b50a54:

    # m "What? Oh! Of course! I could really use one."
    m "¿Cómo? ¡Oh! ¡Por supuesto! Me vendría muy bien uno."

# game/script_marion.rpy:668
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_aca6e99e:

    # "We embrace. Her hugs are tender and sincere, like her soul, and I'm thrilled to finally have the gift placed where it should be."
    "Nos abrazamos. Sus abrazos son tiernos y sinceros, como su alma, y me emociona que por fin el regalo esté donde debe estar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:670
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_2aa18c67:

    # "I let my hand linger under the charm, now hanging from her neck."
    "Dejo que mi mano permanezca bajo el colgante que ahora cuelga de su cuello."

# game/script_marion.rpy:689
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_6380866d:

    # m "Oh, my! What? What is this?"
    m "¡Oh, mi! ¿Qué es esto? ¿Qué es esto?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:695
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_aad70b3d:

    # "She fingers the necklace, causing it to jingle delicately."
    "Toca el collar con los dedos, haciéndolo tintinear delicadamente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:696
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_989cf38c:

    # c "It's just a small gift."
    c "Es sólo un pequeño regalo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:697
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_c57cbf46:

    # m "Oh, Malcolm! You didn't need to do that!"
    m "¡Oh, Malcolm! No necesitabas hacer eso!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:698
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_74bcad91:

    # "Marion's already red face blushes even more deeply."
    "El rostro ya enrojecido de Marion se sonroja aún más."

# game/script_marion.rpy:700
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_397f2ec2:

    # m "Seeing you is a big enough present."
    m "Verte ya es un regalo bastante grande."

# game/script_marion.rpy:701
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_b22494e4:

    # c "Likewise! But I found something at the market this morning that reminded me too much of you to pass up. It's a token of my appreciation."
    c "¡Igualmente! Pero encontré algo en el mercado esta mañana que me recordó demasiado a ti como para dejarlo pasar. Es una muestra de mi agradecimiento."

# game/script_marion.rpy:703
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_3e90973a:

    # "She lights up brighter than the midmorning sun."
    "Se ilumina más que el sol de media mañana."

# game/script_marion.rpy:704
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_22e5c4c7:

    # m "Oh, Malcolm! It's absolutely beautiful! How thoughtful!"
    m "¡Oh, Malcolm! ¡Es absolutamente hermoso! ¡Qué considerado!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:705
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_b4b3861a:

    # c "I know how attached you are to your herd, especially—"
    c "Sé lo apegado que estás a tu rebaño, especialmente—"

# game/script_marion.rpy:707
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_ffbc2797:

    # m "Ha ha! Fiona?"
    m "Ha ha! Fiona?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:708
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_47f3185b:

    # c "That's the one!"
    c "¡Esa es!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:709
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_bfef3969:

    # "I glance over at my failed partner-in-crime, but she just stands there, a thin string of drool falling from her bottom lip."
    "Miro a mi fracasada compañera de fechorías, pero ella se queda ahí de pie, con un hilo de baba cayéndole del labio inferior."

# game/script_marion.rpy:711
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_168b3e69:

    # m "I'll cherish this, Malcolm. It's adorable and sweet."
    m "Guardaré esto, Malcolm. Es adorable y dulce."

# game/script_marion.rpy:713
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_623dc9a8:

    # "She pauses and looks into my eyes."
    "Hace una pausa y me mira a los ojos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:714
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_df3a0bca:

    # m "Just like you."
    m "Igual que tú."

# game/script_marion.rpy:716
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_55ebb859:

    # c "And you."
    c "Y tú."

# game/script_marion.rpy:717
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_a2d0f7f5:

    # "The wind starts blowing across the linens. I long to reach out to her and hold her close."
    "El viento empieza a soplar sobre las sábanas. Deseo alcanzarla y estrecharla contra mí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:726
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_a1b8779b:

    # "The fates are on my side as Marion takes a step closer to me, placing a hand on my arm, and pressing her chest against mine."
    "El destino está de mi lado cuando Marion se acerca a mí, me pone una mano en el brazo y aprieta su pecho contra el mío."

# game/script_marion.rpy:727
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_6ca554cb:

    # "I inhale, mostly from shock, as she gets up on her tiptoes, and kisses me on the cheek."
    "Respiro, sobre todo del susto, cuando se pone de puntillas y me besa en la mejilla."

# game/script_marion.rpy:732
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_83ef817e:

    # "It's too much for me to let the moment pass, so I wrap a hand around the back of her head, keeping her up on her toes. I kiss her softly on her lips."
    "Es demasiado para mí como para dejar pasar el momento, así que le rodeo la nuca con una mano, manteniéndola de puntillas. La beso suavemente en los labios."

# game/script_marion.rpy:733
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_7e6dffdf:

    # "She tastes of cinnamon and treacle. So sweet and intoxicating. I don't want to let her go, but inch by inch she drops back to the earth and our lips part."
    "Sabe a canela y melaza. Tan dulce y embriagadora. No quiero dejarla ir, pero poco a poco vuelve a caer a la tierra y nuestros labios se separan."

# game/script_marion.rpy:740
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_913a1330:

    # m "I... I don't know what to say."
    m "I... no sé qué decir."

# game/script_marion.rpy:741
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_2d49f3db:

    # c "I don't think I do, either."
    c "Creo que yo tampoco."

# game/script_marion.rpy:743
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_8f413397:

    # "We stare at each other until we both start laughing."
    "Nos miramos fijamente hasta que ambos nos echamos a reír."

# game/script_marion.rpy:744
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_377efcd1:

    # c "I've been wanting to do that for quite some time, Marion."
    c "Llevo tiempo queriendo hacer eso, Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:746
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_291ca6e3:

    # m "Thank you greatly for taking the initiative! Oh, no... I sound like an old lady! Malcolm, thank you, thank you! You are amazing."
    m "Muchas gracias por tomar la iniciativa! Oh, no... Sueno como una anciana! Malcolm, gracias, gracias! Eres increíble."

# game/script_marion.rpy:747
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_da9fbb51:

    # c "I hope you know I sincerely feel the same way about you. I... I think—"
    c "Espero que sepas que sinceramente siento lo mismo por ti. I... creo—"

# game/script_marion.rpy:749
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_6bc2fe22:

    # m "Oooof! My back!"
    m "¡Oooof! ¡Mi espalda!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:753
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_b658140a:

    # "Marion reaches to her lower back, and looks embarrassed."
    "Marion se lleva la mano a la parte baja de la espalda y parece avergonzada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:754
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_15e47501:

    # m "I'm so sorry, Malcolm. I felt a twinge. A bit painful."
    m "Lo siento mucho, Malcolm. Sentí una punzada. Un poco dolorosa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:755
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_05d93d6f:

    # "I almost ask if she wants me to rub it, but bite my tongue. What a forward thing to even think!"
    "Casi le pregunto si quiere que se lo frote, pero me muerdo la lengua. ¡Qué atrevimiento ni siquiera pensarlo!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:756
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_df872415:

    # c "Want me to look at it?"
    c "¿Quieres que eche un vistazo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:758
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_5a89c994:

    # m "No, no, I'll be fine. It's these blasted high clotheslines Grace hung... I've been straining all morning, reaching for them."
    m "No, no, estaré bien. Son estos malditos tendederos altos que Grace colgó... He estado esforzándome toda la mañana, alcanzándolos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:760
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_3e6da607:

    # m "Between that and my itchy head, you'd think I was ready to fall apart!"
    m "Entre eso y los picores en la cabeza, cualquiera diría que estoy a punto de desmoronarme!."

# game/script_marion.rpy:761
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_49fcd906:

    # c "Itchy head, too? What luck."
    c "También te pica la cabeza? Qué suerte."

# game/script_marion.rpy:763
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_cc2209e4:

    # m "It's bound to be the new soap I'm using. Strong stuff! But I'm always afraid of bedbugs getting in the house. Especially with whatever Jessie brings home from the pub."
    m "Seguro que es el nuevo jabón que estoy usando. ¡Es muy fuerte! Pero siempre tengo miedo de que entren chinches en casa. Especialmente con lo que Jessie trae a casa de la taberna."

# game/script_marion.rpy:765
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_956f5b68:

    # m "A fine group of fleabags she hangs around, I always say. Oh... I suppose I don't have to worry about that anymore, do I?"
    m "Siempre digo que se junta con un buen grupo de vagabundos. Supongo que ya no tengo que preocuparme por eso, ¿verdad?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:767
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_dcf57257:

    # m "Look at me pratter on! I'm so nervous... oh! I shouldn't say that."
    m "¡Mírame! Estoy tan nerviosa... ¡Oh! No debería decir eso."

# game/script_marion.rpy:768
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_ffbb1f2f:

    # "Marion is talking at a fast clip. Our hearts must both be beating at a frantic pace."
    "Marion habla a toda velocidad. Nuestros corazones deben de latir a un ritmo frenético."

# game/script_marion.rpy:770
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_bc20cb7a:

    # m "Say, Malcolm. Are you going to the church picnic tomorrow? It's nothing big, just the congregation getting together for a good time. Should be a bonny day for it."
    m "Dime, Malcolm. ¿Vas a ir al picnic de la iglesia mañana? No es nada grande, sólo la congregación reuniéndose para pasar un buen rato. Debería ser un buen día para ello."

# game/script_marion.rpy:771
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_f60b4f8c:

    # "Is that tomorrow, already? In my head, I weigh Gran's none-too-subtle hint against my most recent church experience."
    "Es el día de mañana? En mi cabeza, comparo la insinuación no demasiado sutil de la abuela con mi experiencia más reciente en la iglesia."

# game/script_marion.rpy:775
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_ab9bef19:

    # c "As a matter of fact, yes."
    c "De hecho, sí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:777
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_f0bd5cf0:

    # m "Oh, wonderful! If you wouldn't mind accompanying me, I would really enjoy that. Don't worry about food, I'll be bringing lots."
    m "¡Maravilloso! Si no te importa acompañarme, me encantaría. No te preocupes por la comida, llevaré mucha."

# game/script_marion.rpy:778
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_ea758862:

    # m "And thank you for..."
    m "Y gracias por..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:780
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_2b33711d:

    # c "I guess I hadn't really thought about it."
    c "Supongo que no había pensado en ello."

# game/script_marion.rpy:782
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_1c4c952c:

    # m "Grace won't show her face in a crowd, and I'd hate to go alone. I mean, I'd really like to go... if you're going."
    m "Grace no mostrará su cara en una multitud, y odiaría ir sola. Quiero decir, realmente me gustaría ir... si tú vas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:783
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_36d28436:

    # "Well, I certainly do want to spend time with Marion. Just being around her is excitement enough at this point."
    "Bueno, ciertamente quiero pasar tiempo con Marion. Sólo estar cerca de ella es suficiente emoción en este momento."

# game/script_marion.rpy:784
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_d5e93f35:

    # "She looks at me with puppy eyes, disarming me completely. I just can't say no to those."
    "Me mira con ojos de cachorrito, desarmándome por completo. No puedo decir que no a eso."

# game/script_marion.rpy:785
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_8bd76cdb:

    # c "Then, yes. Yes, I would love to join you."
    c "Entonces, sí. Sí, me encantaría unirme a ti."

# game/script_marion.rpy:787
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_3dae17c4:

    # m "Wonderful! And thank you for..."
    m "¡Maravilloso! Y gracias por..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:790
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_dd4d1641:

    # "She blushes again from ear to ear."
    "Vuelve a sonrojarse de oreja a oreja."

# game/script_marion.rpy:792
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_4657fd76:

    # m "Thank you for the cowbell. I will treasure it... and you."
    m "Gracias por el cencerro. Lo guardaré como un tesoro... y a ti."

# game/script_marion.rpy:793
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_1fad971f:

    # "I beam, and vow that next time I'll make sure to earn her affection through actions, not simply tokens."
    "Sonrío y juro que la próxima vez me aseguraré de ganarme su afecto con acciones y no con simples muestras."

# game/script_marion.rpy:794
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_5fc04449:

    # c "Marion you are a dear and a love. I can't wait to see you again for the picnic. We'll make it a grand time!"
    c "Marion eres un cielo y un amor. No puedo esperar a verte de nuevo para el picnic. ¡Lo pasaremos en grande!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:796
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_c75467ad:

    # m "That we shall."
    m "Eso haremos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:797
translate Spanish ch2m_03_a_5dcbdec8:

    # "I consider kissing her again, but believe us both to be still reeling in surprise from the first. Instead, I bid my farewell and float all the way home."
    "Considero la posibilidad de volver a besarla, pero creo que ambos estamos aún conmocionados por la sorpresa de la primera vez. En lugar de eso, me despido y vuelvo flotando a casa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:823
translate Spanish ch2m_04_1af55b34:

    # "Picnic day. The weather is indeed shaping up to be lovely, just as Marion predicted. She must have a sixth sense about such things."
    "Día de picnic. El tiempo se presenta espléndido, tal y como predijo Marion. Debe tener un sexto sentido para estas cosas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:824
translate Spanish ch2m_04_d68cc1a7:

    # "Hazel steps lightly as we approach the home of my day's companion. I've decided I'm actually looking forward to the picnic, and not just because of the company."
    "Hazel da unos pasos ligeros mientras nos acercamos a la casa de mi acompañante del día. He decidido que me apetece mucho el picnic, y no solo por la compañía."

# game/script_marion.rpy:825
translate Spanish ch2m_04_9ec0379a:

    # "The church has always been a part of our family's lives. Sure, the sermons may have grown a bit more forceful, but the message still aims to be positive."
    "La iglesia siempre ha formado parte de la vida de nuestra familia. Es cierto que los sermones se han vuelto un poco más enérgicos, pero el mensaje sigue siendo positivo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:826
translate Spanish ch2m_04_635ba703:

    # "In such a small village, we need to stick together, to be there for one another. Ach-na-Creige's parish offers that space for community and acceptance."
    "En un pueblo tan pequeño, necesitamos permanecer unidos, estar ahí los unos para los otros. La parroquia de Ach-na-Creige ofrece ese espacio de comunidad y aceptación."

# game/script_marion.rpy:827
translate Spanish ch2m_04_b01b3f16:

    # "...That, and I was hoping to be able to kiss Marion again."
    "...Eso, y que esperaba poder volver a besar a Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:828
translate Spanish ch2m_04_931ccb23:

    # "I laugh aloud. Religion be damned, I was pining for her in a very unholy manner."
    "Me río en voz alta. Maldita sea la religión, estaba suspirando por ella de una manera muy poco santa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:832
translate Spanish ch2m_04_0530e7be:

    # "My levity has clearly disturbed Hazel, who slows to a stop before the walkway to Marion's house. I go ahead and dismount."
    "Mi frivolidad ha molestado claramente a Hazel, que se detiene ante la pasarela que lleva a la casa de Marion. Me adelanto y me desmonto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:833
translate Spanish ch2m_04_f4f5bc9e:

    # c "Oh, don't be a humbug. You're invited to the picnic, too! In fact, I do believe Gran packed some extra carrots just for you. Want an appetizer?"
    c "No seas tonta. Tú también estás invitada al picnic. De hecho, creo que la abuela ha traído más zanahorias para ti. Quieres un aperitivo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:835
translate Spanish ch2m_04_02fe20e7:

    # "Hazel's ears perk up, and she gladly takes the treat I offer her."
    "Hazel levanta las orejas y acepta encantada la golosina que le ofrezco."

# game/script_marion.rpy:836
translate Spanish ch2m_04_b5672638:

    # "Hopefully the menu for us humans is equally appetizing. If the only option this year is Balgair's beer-battered haggis balls, may God have mercy on us all."
    "Esperemos que el menú para los humanos sea igual de apetitoso. Si la única opción este año son las bolas de haggis rebozadas en cerveza de Balgair, que Dios se apiade de todos nosotros."

# game/script_marion.rpy:842
translate Spanish ch2m_04_565fa419:

    # "My mouth waters as I walk up to the door, wondering what recipes our chef and savior, Marion, might have in store for us today."
    "Se me hace la boca agua cuando me acerco a la puerta, preguntándome qué recetas nos tendrá preparadas hoy nuestra chef y salvadora, Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:852
translate Spanish ch2m_04_b3bb83df:

    # c "Oh! Good morning, Grace. I'm here to collect Marion for—"
    c "Buenos días, Grace. Vengo a recoger a Marion para—"

# game/script_marion.rpy:854
translate Spanish ch2m_04_c6e41cb4:

    # g "For the picnic. Och aye, I've heard {i}all{/i} about it. Marion's been preoccupied about... the picnic, all morning."
    g "Para el picnic. Och aye, he oído {i}todo{/i} al respecto. Marion ha estado preocupada por... el picnic, toda la mañana."

# game/script_marion.rpy:855
translate Spanish ch2m_04_ef458aef:

    # c "So much excitement over a church event?"
    c "¿Tanta emoción por un evento de la iglesia?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:857
translate Spanish ch2m_04_b2888730:

    # "Grace is not the easiest person to read, but her expression seems strained. It's like she is trying to suppress a laugh."
    "Grace no es la persona más fácil de leer, pero su expresión parece tensa. Es como si intentara reprimir una carcajada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:858
translate Spanish ch2m_04_9870ac33:

    # g "Less the event, and more the company. She's still getting ready."
    g "Menos el evento y más la compañía. Todavía se está preparando."

# game/script_marion.rpy:859
translate Spanish ch2m_04_4759f37b:

    # "I blush. Goodness. I hope Marion isn't getting overly flustered about this. She's not treating this little village get-together like a proper date, is she?"
    "Me sonrojo. Cielo santo. Espero que Marion no esté demasiado nerviosa por esto. No está tratando esta pequeña reunión de pueblo como una cita apropiada, ¿verdad?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:860
translate Spanish ch2m_04_1884fe1f:

    # "If so, Grace must think seeing her sister mooning over a boy is a real riot. Should I be nervous, too? The consternation must show on my face."
    "De ser así, Grace debe pensar que ver a su hermana acariciando a un chico es un verdadero alboroto. ¿Debería estar nerviosa yo también? La consternación debe mostrarse en mi cara."

# game/script_marion.rpy:862
translate Spanish ch2m_04_b0dbe68d:

    # g "Don't fret. I'm sure you two will have a ball."
    g "No te preocupes. Estoy segura de que lo van a pasar muy bien."

# game/script_marion.rpy:866
translate Spanish ch2m_04_818f50fe:

    # m "I'm here! I'm ready!"
    m "¡Ya estoy aquí! ¡Ya estoy aquí!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:867
translate Spanish ch2m_04_a9c43a01:

    # "Marion's face is flushed, and her kerchief lays loose and askew atop her head. She's looking charming as ever."
    "Marion tiene la cara sonrojada y el pañuelo suelto sobre la cabeza. Está tan encantadora como siempre."

# game/script_marion.rpy:868
translate Spanish ch2m_04_5c752184:

    # "My heart races, and I still can't fathom her wanting to spend time with me. I notice the silver cowbell dangling from the thin chain around her neck."
    "Se me acelera el corazón y sigo sin entender que quiera pasar tiempo conmigo. Me fijo en el cencerro de plata que cuelga de la fina cadena de su cuello."

# game/script_marion.rpy:869
translate Spanish ch2m_04_01b1f8c6:

    # c "You look lovely, Marion. As always."
    c "Estás preciosa, Marion. Como siempre."

# game/script_marion.rpy:871
translate Spanish ch2m_04_d75aea24:

    # m "Oh! T-thank you."
    m "Oh, G-gracias!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:872
translate Spanish ch2m_04_7e661e89:

    # "She's fidgeting so much I worry she might keel over."
    "Está tan inquieta que me preocupa que pueda desplomarse."

# game/script_marion.rpy:874
translate Spanish ch2m_04_5037c494:

    # g "Finally ready, sis'? That must have been quite the process. I was worried you might need more help."
    g "¿Finalmente lista, hermanita? Debe haber sido todo un reto. Me preocupaba que necesitaras más ayuda."

# game/script_marion.rpy:876
translate Spanish ch2m_04_1b56681a:

    # "Marion shoots a glare at her little sister. The style hardly looks elaborate—in fact, I'm not sure Marion's wardrobe {i}ever{/i} changes... Then again, I'm no expert on how a woman prepares for an outing."
    "Marion lanza una mirada fulminante a su hermana pequeña. El estilo apenas parece elaborado; de hecho, no estoy seguro de que el vestuario de Marion {i}nunca{/i} cambie... Pero no soy una experto en cómo se prepara una mujer para salir."

# game/script_marion.rpy:877
translate Spanish ch2m_04_6be59b27:

    # "Some female mysteries, Gran tells me, men are never meant to understand."
    "Algunos misterios femeninos, me dice la abuela, los hombres nunca están destinados a entenderlos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:879
translate Spanish ch2m_04_45fad1d0:

    # m "Yes, thank you, Grace. We'll be heading out now. I'll be back later this afternoon."
    m "Sí, gracias, Grace. Nos iremos ahora. Volveré esta tarde."

# game/script_marion.rpy:881
translate Spanish ch2m_04_0599a93e:

    # g "Don't forget your basket."
    g "No olvides tu cesta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:882
translate Spanish ch2m_04_34aae018:

    # m "Yes, of course. Thank you again, Grace."
    m "Sí, por supuesto. Gracias de nuevo, Grace."

# game/script_marion.rpy:888
translate Spanish ch2m_04_d4257c10:

    # "Marion bends over to pick up the basket, adjusting her loose kerchief as she stands. I reach out to take the basket from her."
    "Marion se inclina para recoger la cesta y se ajusta el pañuelo suelto mientras se levanta. Alargo la mano para cogerle la cesta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:889
translate Spanish ch2m_04_c39ba46e:

    # c "Here, let me take that. Anything good in there?"
    c "Aquí, déjame tomar eso. ¿Hay algo bueno ahí?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:893
translate Spanish ch2m_04_a4bef9d8:

    # m "Er—Thank you, Malcolm. And you'll just have to wait and see."
    m "Eh-Gracias, Malcolm. Y tendrás que esperar y ver."

# game/script_marion.rpy:894
translate Spanish ch2m_04_d98b2bf4:

    # "The thank-you is a curt one. I'm startled by how irritable Marion appears to be... but I can't blame her. I have a sneaking suspicion being left alone with Grace can have that effect on people."
    "El agradecimiento es cortante. Me sorprende lo irritable que parece estar Marion... pero no puedo culparla. Tengo la ligera sospecha de que quedarse a solas con Grace puede tener ese efecto en la gente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:895
translate Spanish ch2m_04_b5b6831e:

    # "Plus if Marion is as nervous as Grace suggests, that's bound to contribute. I've got a case of the butterflies, myself."
    "Además, si Marion está tan nerviosa como sugiere Grace, eso contribuirá. Yo también tengo un caso de mariposas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:897
translate Spanish ch2m_04_eb570d6a:

    # m "We should really be going."
    m "Deberíamos irnos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:898
translate Spanish ch2m_04_2d7cbd02:

    # c "Of course. Care to join me atop Hazel?"
    c "Por supuesto. ¿Te importaría unirte a mí encima de Hazel?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:899
translate Spanish ch2m_04_ad3e127c:

    # "I hope I'm not being too forward, but I would love to ride double with Marion... if Hazel will let us. It's as if Marion reads my thoughts."
    "Espero no ser demasiado atrevida, pero me encantaría montar en doble con Marion... si Hazel nos deja. Es como si Marion leyera mis pensamientos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:901
translate Spanish ch2m_04_374911f6:

    # m "If she'll have me."
    m "Si me acepta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:902
translate Spanish ch2m_04_99fe6d3b:

    # c "Of course! After you, then. Our chariot awaits."
    c "¡Claro que sí! Después de ti, entonces. Nuestra carroza espera."

# game/script_marion.rpy:904
translate Spanish ch2m_04_77a8c907:

    # g "Have a good time, you two."
    g "Pásenlo bien, ustedes dos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:913
translate Spanish ch2m_04_e6b86b2a:

    # "Marion is quiet as we ride atop Hazel to the appointed hillside just outside the village."
    "Marion está tranquila mientras cabalgamos sobre Hazel hasta la ladera señalada a las afueras del pueblo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:914
translate Spanish ch2m_04_0bbaa82a:

    # "We talk about the weather and what to expect at the picnic, but the energy between us feels more nervous and strained than romantic."
    "Hablamos del tiempo y de lo que nos espera en el picnic, pero la energía entre nosotros es más nerviosa y tensa que romántica."

# game/script_marion.rpy:915
translate Spanish ch2m_04_d4243132:

    # "Needless to say, today isn't going according to how I had imagined it would."
    "No hace falta decir que hoy no va como había imaginado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:917
translate Spanish ch2m_04_967d5caf:

    # "Ever the reliable mode of transport, Hazel spots a patch of bluebells along the path and insists on veering off to munch on them. Of course."
    "Hazel, siempre tan fiable como medio de transporte, ve un parche de campanillas en el camino e insiste en desviarse para comerlas. Por supuesto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:925
translate Spanish ch2m_04_8704e045:

    # "Embarrassed and helpless, I dismount and help Marion do the same. She looks off into the distance absently, as I will Hazel to quickly finish her snack."
    "Avergonzado e indefenso, desmonto y ayudo a Marion a hacer lo mismo. Ella mira a lo lejos distraídamente, mientras le digo a Hazel que termine rápidamente su merienda."

# game/script_marion.rpy:926
translate Spanish ch2m_04_24ebaefc:

    # "Hm. Perhaps Marion and I are both acknowledging the shift in our relationship, and don't know where we will take it. I raise the subject."
    "Hm. Tal vez Marion y yo estemos reconociendo el cambio en nuestra relación y no sepamos hacia dónde lo llevaremos. Planteo el tema."

# game/script_marion.rpy:927
translate Spanish ch2m_04_3d1f39ed:

    # c "You know... I'm excited to spend the day with you, Marion. I've really been looking forward to it since you asked me to go to the picnic."
    c "Sabes... Estoy emocionado de pasar el día contigo, Marion. Lo he estado esperando desde que me pediste ir al picnic."

# game/script_marion.rpy:942
translate Spanish ch2m_04_a9e67638:

    # "This finally coaxes a relaxed smile from her. She fiddles with the ends of her kerchief, and looks up at me."
    "Esto le arranca por fin una sonrisa relajada. Juguetea con los extremos de su pañuelo y me mira."

# game/script_marion.rpy:943
translate Spanish ch2m_04_56cee9c1:

    # m "I'm excited, too. I'm so sorry if I haven't been myself. I... I'm just nervous."
    m "Yo también estoy emocionada. Lo siento mucho si no he sido yo misma. Yo... Sólo estoy nerviosa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:944
translate Spanish ch2m_04_46ceb589:

    # c "Me too. The butterflies inside my belly feel as though they're multiplying at a rapid clip."
    c "A mí también. Siento como si las mariposas en mi estomago se multiplicaran a gran velocidad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:946
translate Spanish ch2m_04_bf88be3e:

    # m "I've been thinking about you nonstop. It's been a welcome distraction from worrying about Jessie, but..."
    m "He estado pensando en ti sin parar. Ha sido una distracción bienvenida para dejar de preocuparme por Jessie, pero..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:947
translate Spanish ch2m_04_03a09d48:

    # c "You feel guilty?"
    c "Te sientes culpable?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:949
translate Spanish ch2m_04_ed73a9e0:

    # "She pauses, appearing to weigh my words."
    "Hace una pausa, parece sopesar mis palabras."

# game/script_marion.rpy:951
translate Spanish ch2m_04_36be6a7f:

    # m "Well. I suppose that's part of it."
    m "Bien. Supongo que eso es parte de ello."

# game/script_marion.rpy:953
translate Spanish ch2m_04_53f5ebe5:

    # "Marion stops and places her hand around mine. My breath quickens."
    "Marion se detiene y coloca su mano alrededor de la mía. Mi respiración se acelera."

# game/script_marion.rpy:954
translate Spanish ch2m_04_74ece74e:

    # m "But I also feel relieved. I don't know what I would do without you around. I just... don't know."
    m "Pero también me siento aliviada. No sé qué haría sin ti cerca. Yo simplemente... no lo sé."

# game/script_marion.rpy:956
translate Spanish ch2m_04_d80832c4:

    # m "Thank you for helping me put things back together when they just keep seeming to fall apart."
    m "Gracias por ayudarme a recomponer las cosas cuando parecen desmoronarse."

# game/script_marion.rpy:958
translate Spanish ch2m_04_3bb3f477:

    # m "It's... it's been harder than you know. But you make me feel like everything will turn out all right. You're just what I needed right now."
    m "Es que... ha sido más difícil de lo que crees. Pero me haces sentir que todo saldrá bien. Eres justo lo que necesitaba ahora mismo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:959
translate Spanish ch2m_04_a7c7c577:

    # "I squeeze her hand tight, not quite comprehending that I am holding hands with a childhood friend, who has turned into such a gorgeous woman."
    "Aprieto su mano con fuerza, sin comprender del todo que estoy cogido de la mano de una amiga de la infancia, que se ha convertido en una mujer tan hermosa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:960
translate Spanish ch2m_04_354a160b:

    # "A woman who shares a connection to me in this fashion. It's overwhelming in its simplicity and profoundness."
    "Una mujer que comparte una conexión conmigo de esta manera. Es abrumador por su sencillez y profundidad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:962
translate Spanish ch2m_04_7d147f1f:

    # c "I think I can empathize. Having you come back into my life... in such a..."
    c "Creo que puedo sentir empatía. Que hayas regresado a mi vida... en tal..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:963
translate Spanish ch2m_04_9fb5164d:

    # "What on earth is the word?"
    "¿Cuál es la palabra?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:965
translate Spanish ch2m_04_59e12ded:

    # m "A special way?"
    m "¿Una forma especial?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:966
translate Spanish ch2m_04_e31bf91b:

    # c "Yes. And at such a fortuitous time. Just remember that... well, routine is good for a weary soul."
    c "Sí. Y en un momento tan fortuito. Sólo recuerda que... bueno, la rutina es buena para un alma cansada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:967
translate Spanish ch2m_04_4185216d:

    # c "It's helped me substantially since coming back home. That, and being with you."
    c "Me ha ayudado sustancialmente desde que volví a casa. Eso, y estar contigo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:975
translate Spanish ch2m_04_53e1b00b:

    # "Marion blushes, and opens her mouth to speak—but a squeak comes out, and she jumps well-nigh a foot into the air."
    "Marion se sonroja y abre la boca para hablar, pero le sale un chillido y salta casi un palmo en el aire."

# game/script_marion.rpy:983
translate Spanish ch2m_04_bc5bf757:

    # "My horse, having apparently finished her leafy greens, had decided to snuffle the folds of Marion's green skirt next. I turn beet red."
    "Mi caballo, que al parecer había terminado sus hojas verdes, había decidido husmear en los pliegues de la falda verde de Marion. Me pongo rojo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:984
translate Spanish ch2m_04_3c9213a8:

    # c "{i}Hazel!{/i} That's no way to treat a lady!"
    c "{i}Hazel!{/i} Esa no es forma de tratar a una dama!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:990
translate Spanish ch2m_04_c5c47e5f:

    # "Marion looks absolutely rattled as she pats down her skirt back into place. It breaks my heart."
    "Marion parece absolutamente aturdida mientras se vuelve a poner la falda en su sitio. Me rompe el corazón."

# game/script_marion.rpy:991
translate Spanish ch2m_04_b96e61c5:

    # c "I-I'm so sorry. She has a mind of her own."
    c "Lo-lo siento mucho. Ella tiene mente propia."

# game/script_marion.rpy:993
translate Spanish ch2m_04_39cd9bc6:

    # m "It's all right! It's all right. Let's just... can we get a moove on?"
    m "¡Todo está bien! Todo está bien. Vamos... ¿podemos seguir adelante?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1003
translate Spanish ch2m_04_c8bd8ded:

    # "Marion's eyes go wide as she slurs the last word. I nod, helping her back upon the horse. It's tough, though, as she has gone almost completely limp."
    "Los ojos de Marion se abren como platos mientras balbucea la última palabra. Asiento, ayudándola a subir al caballo. Es difícil, sin embargo, ya que se ha quedado casi completamente flácida."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1004
translate Spanish ch2m_04_51ef77b1:

    # "The jitteriness, the blank looks, the shutting down... I've seen it all before. It's as if she's been {i}shell shocked.{/i}"
    "El nerviosismo, las miradas en blanco, el cierre... Lo he visto todo antes. Es como si ella hubiera estado {i}conmocionada.{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1005
translate Spanish ch2m_04_1e791e70:

    # "Jessie's leaving must have hit her even harder than I had realized."
    "
La partida de Jessie debió haberla golpeado aún más fuerte de lo que me había dado cuenta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1006
translate Spanish ch2m_04_2de52375:

    # c "Are you sure you want to go, today? We can stay home, get some rest... perhaps we've both been pushing ourselves too hard."
    c "¿Estás segura de que quieres ir hoy? Podemos quedarnos en casa, descansar un poco... quizás ambos nos hemos estado esforzando demasiado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1007
translate Spanish ch2m_04_e612037c:

    # m "..."
    m "..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1008
translate Spanish ch2m_04_cb59cd19:

    # m "No, I'll manage. Like you say, it's best to get back into routine. Everything will be fine."
    m "No, me las arreglaré. Como dices, lo mejor es volver a la rutina. Todo estará bien."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1009
translate Spanish ch2m_04_09675d49:

    # "My determined Marion smiles weakly. But who is she trying to convince? Me, or herself?"
    "
Mi decidida Marion sonríe débilmente. ¿Pero a quién intenta convencer? ¿A mi o ella misma?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1034
translate Spanish ch2m_05_01cf0145:

    # "Any sense of calm restored by Hazel's gentle rocking is shattered as we ride into the picnic spot outside of town."
    "Cualquier sensación de calma restaurada por el suave balanceo de Hazel se hace añicos cuando nos dirigimos al lugar de picnic en las afueras de la ciudad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1035
translate Spanish ch2m_05_2f5dc0e2:

    # "The hillside is teeming with activity. Quilts are draped across it resembling an even larger patchwork, but hardly anyone sits."
    "La ladera rebosa actividad. Los manteles se extienden por toda la colina, como si fuera un gran mosaico, pero casi nadie se sienta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1036
translate Spanish ch2m_05_8eeed2c0:

    # "The congregation seems so much smaller when it sits quietly inside the confines of the church."
    "La congregación parece mucho más pequeña cuando se sienta tranquilamente dentro de los confines de la iglesia."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1037
translate Spanish ch2m_05_1eb11d43:

    # "Cakes are being laid out on a long table, lemonade is being stirred in large carved glass punch bowls."
    "En una larga mesa se colocan tartas y se sirve limonada en grandes poncheras de cristal tallado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1038
translate Spanish ch2m_05_746e714a:

    # "Clusters of adults group together, chatting. Children chase each other with an unending supply of energy. Were Marion and I ever like that?"
    "Grupos de adultos se agrupan, charlando. Los niños se persiguen unos a otros con una energía inagotable. ¿Alguna vez fuimos así Marion y yo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1039
translate Spanish ch2m_05_30ac4a48:

    # "A foppish man on a penny-farthing tries to entertain the little ones, but he would have just as much luck holding the attention of a pack of caffeinated Yorkies."
    "Un hombre elegante montado en un carruaje intenta entretener a los más pequeños, pero tendría la misma suerte manteniendo la atención de una manada de yorkshire con cafeína."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1045
translate Spanish ch2m_05_fde46752:

    # "Wait. Is that... Wondrous Walter? The circus man from God knows how many years ago? I slide off Hazel and offer my hand to help Marion down."
    "Espera. ¿Es ese... ¿Wondrous Walter? ¿El hombre del circo de Dios sabe cuántos años atrás? Me deslizo fuera de Hazel y ofrezco mi mano para ayudar a Marion a bajar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1046
translate Spanish ch2m_05_54ef864e:

    # c "Marion, you remember when the circus came to town when we were wee kids? D'ye think that's—"
    c "Marion, ¿recuerdas cuando el circo vino a la ciudad cuando éramos niños? ¿Crees que es—"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1049
translate Spanish ch2m_05_09fe5ab2:

    # "She is taking in the scene with obvious distress. I've never seen her so nervous in a crowd."
    "Está asimilando la escena con evidente angustia. Nunca la había visto tan nerviosa entre la multitud."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1050
translate Spanish ch2m_05_3599e572:

    # c "Er, Marion? All's well?"
    c "¿Eh, Marion? ¿Todo bien?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1052
translate Spanish ch2m_05_dce75c5b:

    # "She swallows."
    "Ella traga saliva."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1053
translate Spanish ch2m_05_89554b4c:

    # m "Yes. Do you have the basket? Let's add it to the others."
    m "Sí. Tienes la cesta? Vamos a añadirlo a los demás."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1066
translate Spanish ch2m_05_e7359a6f:

    # "After I hitch Hazel up to a fencepost, we weave in and around the revelers to the table, where Marion opens the picnic basket."
    "Después de enganchar a Hazel a un poste de la valla, nos movemos entre los invitados hasta la mesa, donde Marion abre la cesta de picnic."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1067
translate Spanish ch2m_05_4b57a89e:

    # c "Ah! Are those some of your homemade cheeses, Marion?"
    c "¡Ah! ¿Esos son algunos de tus quesos caseros, Marion?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1074
translate Spanish ch2m_05_8847b664:

    # "She finally seems to relax again, and gives me a conspiratorial smile."
    "Por fin parece relajarse de nuevo y me dedica una sonrisa de complicidad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1075
translate Spanish ch2m_05_38b52b7c:

    # m "You remember? Yes, but I only share them on special occasions. Don't tell the cheesemonger!"
    m "¿Te acuerdas? Sí, pero sólo los comparto en ocasiones especiales. ¡No se lo digas al quesero!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1076
translate Spanish ch2m_05_bccc4661:

    # c "Not a word."
    c "Ni una palabra."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1079
translate Spanish ch2m_05_7f7babdc:

    # "Cheeses and fresh loaves of bread are added to the piles of other delicious looking foods. I set out the spice cake Gran sent me with, as well."
    "Los quesos y las barras de pan fresco se añaden a los montones de otros alimentos de aspecto delicioso. También he colocado la tarta de especias que me envió abue."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1080
translate Spanish ch2m_05_40bdd91d:

    # "It's a good looking spread this year—although I can smell Balgair's haggis balls from here."
    "Este año tiene buena pinta, aunque desde aquí puedo oler las bolas de haggis de Balgair."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1081
translate Spanish ch2m_05_94578010:

    # "I make sure to stay well away from those, even though Balgair assures me time and again that they'll put hair on my chest. And one foot in my grave, no doubt."
    "Me aseguro de mantenerme alejado de ellos, aunque Balgair me asegura una y otra vez que me pondrán los pelos de punta. Y un pie en mi tumba, sin duda."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1082
translate Spanish ch2m_05_8217b720:

    # "Being back in her element seems to have restored some of Marion's confidence. We mingle a bit with the other churchgoers around the table."
    "Estar de nuevo en su elemento parece haber devuelto a Marion parte de su confianza. Nos mezclamos un poco con los otros fieles alrededor de la mesa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1083
translate Spanish ch2m_05_48df8e61:

    # "Most of them are still unfamiliar or unmemorable to me, and I hesitate to speak too much about myself. I'm not eager to discuss my homecoming with strangers anymore."
    "La mayoría de ellos me siguen resultando desconocidos o poco memorables, y dudo en hablar demasiado de mí. Ya no me apetece hablar de mi vuelta a casa con desconocidos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1084
translate Spanish ch2m_05_122a3f56:

    # "Their words wash over me as my eyes wander over the crowds. It looks like just about the whole of Ach-na-Creige turned out for the picnic this fine day."
    "Sus palabras me inundan mientras mis ojos recorren la multitud. Parece que casi todo Ach-na-Creige ha acudido al picnic de hoy."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1090
translate Spanish ch2m_05_301c3482:

    # "I spot Effie, wandering shyly over by the dessert table, and Murdoch the milliner, flirting with the Whist club members."
    "Veo a Effie, paseándose tímidamente junto a la mesa de postres, y a Murdoch, el sombrerero, coqueteando con los miembros del club de Whist."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1091
translate Spanish ch2m_05_57908d29:

    # "Then, {i}I{/i} am spotted. Pastor Ted beelines toward our group and I feel my insides stiffen. I'm not ready to face another impromptu sermon."
    "Entonces, {i}Yo{/i} soy visto. El pastor Ted se dirige hacia nuestro grupo y siento que se me agarrotan las tripas. No estoy listo para enfrentar otro sermón improvisado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1095
translate Spanish ch2m_05_fe00ff02:

    # "I slink away from the conversing group, focusing my attentions on filling a napkin with hors d'oeuvres."
    "Me alejo sigilosamente del grupo de conversación, centrando mi atención en llenar una servilleta con entremeses."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1102
translate Spanish ch2m_05_c7a98c11:

    # a "Oh, Malcolm!"
    a "Oh, Malcolm!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1103
translate Spanish ch2m_05_25ef048d:

    # "So this is what quarry feels like when it's been flushed out into a trap."
    "Así es como se siente la cantera cuando ha sido arrojada a una trampa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1104
translate Spanish ch2m_05_cff3aae7:

    # c "Alana. Glad you made it."
    c "Alana. Me alegro de que lo consiguieras."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1106
translate Spanish ch2m_05_5641affa:

    # a "Likewise. I'm happy to see you out on such a bonny day. Truly."
    a "Lo mismo digo. Me alegra verte fuera en un día tan bonito. De verdad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1107
translate Spanish ch2m_05_6d8631ec:

    # "Her face softens into what seems like genuine concern."
    "Su rostro se suaviza en lo que parece genuina preocupación."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1109
translate Spanish ch2m_05_197b6725:

    # a "I know how hard it can be to show yourself in public so soon after living through extraordinary times. Difficult times, when the wounds are still fresh."
    a "Sé lo duro que puede ser mostrarse en público tan pronto después de haber vivido tiempos extraordinarios. Tiempos difíciles, cuando las heridas aún están frescas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1110
translate Spanish ch2m_05_038f6ee8:

    # c "Well, I'm happy to say I've had help. Most here have made me feel quite welcomed."
    c "Me alegra decir que he recibido ayuda. La mayoría aquí me han hecho sentir muy bienvenido."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1111
translate Spanish ch2m_05_cb4f0d35:

    # "I don't intend to sound accusatory, but perhaps she senses my concern, anyway."
    "No pretendo sonar acusador, pero quizá ella perciba mi preocupación."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1113
translate Spanish ch2m_05_b3c6cabd:

    # a "I'm glad, Malcolm, and for my part, I am sorry. I wish I had been able to offer you a more pleasant reception that first night."
    a "Me alegro, Malcolm, y por mi parte, lo siento. Ojalá hubiera podido ofrecerte un recibimiento más agradable aquella primera noche."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1114
translate Spanish ch2m_05_888a7e18:

    # "Her apology comes as a surprise. Alana is showing her human side again, it would seem."
    "Su disculpa es una sorpresa. Parece que Alana vuelve a mostrar su lado humano."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1118
translate Spanish ch2m_05_2d1f4539:

    # "My tenseness eases, and I don't have the heart to hold it against her."
    "Mi tensión disminuye y no tengo valor para reprochárselo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1119
translate Spanish ch2m_05_0bd91b9e:

    # c "Don't fret. It's enough to know that I am welcomed among old friends and acquaintances."
    c "No te preocupes. Basta saber que soy bienvenido entre viejos amigos y conocidos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1121
translate Spanish ch2m_05_021dedce:

    # a "And family too, I hope. How has your grandmother been? Is she here today?"
    a "Y la familia también, espero. ¿Cómo ha estado tu abuela? ¿Está hoy aquí?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1122
translate Spanish ch2m_05_7fd44a5c:

    # c "She would have loved to come, but Sunday service is her only outing for the week. Anything more does tire her greatly, these days."
    c "Le hubiera encantado venir, pero el servicio dominical es su única salida durante la semana. Cualquier cosa más la cansa mucho estos días."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1123
translate Spanish ch2m_05_f783f9ce:

    # c "Thank you for asking, though. I'll give her your best. Or you can tell her yourself, next Sunday."
    c "Gracias por preguntar. Le daré tus saludos. O puedes decírselo tú mismo, el próximo domingo"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1125
translate Spanish ch2m_05_931724e2:

    # a "Oh, I don't make it to the church in town very often. I just came today to help look after the children."
    a "No voy muy a menudo a la iglesia del pueblo. Sólo vine hoy para ayudar a cuidar a los niños."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1127
translate Spanish ch2m_05_49ae87f7:

    # c "I appreciate your concern, but I'm still confused as to what prompted it."
    c "Le agradezco su preocupación, pero sigo sin saber qué la motivó."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1129
translate Spanish ch2m_05_1d8b1aa6:

    # a "And for that, I'm sorry as well. But I'm afraid there's not much more I can say."
    a "Y por eso, yo también lo siento. Pero me temo que no hay mucho más que pueda decir."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1130
translate Spanish ch2m_05_51a06b16:

    # "And back to her mysterious side, she withdraws. Come to think of it, I don't even remember seeing her in the pews previously."
    "Y volviendo a su lado misterioso, se retira. Ahora que lo pienso, ni siquiera recuerdo haberla visto antes en los bancos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1131
translate Spanish ch2m_05_ca8adfef:

    # c "I see. So... what brings you to the church picnic today? Are you here as part of the congregation, or...?"
    c "Ya veo. Entonces... ¿qué te trae hoy al picnic de la iglesia? ¿Estás aquí como parte de la congregación, o...?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1133
translate Spanish ch2m_05_af3167bb:

    # a "I offered to help look after the children."
    a "Me ofrecí a ayudar a cuidar a los niños."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1143
translate Spanish ch2m_05_3cdb5348:

    # "One look toward poor \"Wondrous Walter\" shows just what a hopeless task that is. The kids swarm around his penny-farthing like angry Sopwiths about a Zeppelin."
    "Una mirada al pobre \"Wondrous Walter\" muestra lo inútil que es esa tarea. Los niños se arremolinan en torno a su bicicleta como Sopwiths enfadados por un Zeppelin."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1144
translate Spanish ch2m_05_0bd5d5d9:

    # "They duck and dive perilously close to his machine. It's only a matter of time before someone is shot down."
    "Se agachan y se lanzan peligrosamente cerca de su máquina. Es sólo cuestión de tiempo que alguien sea derribado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1147
translate Spanish ch2m_05_c78bd89c:

    # a "Children!"
    a "Niños!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1156
translate Spanish ch2m_05_769597d1:

    # "Alana's call isn't loud, but the kids seem to hear it nonetheless. At once, they become quiet and snap to attention. My back straightens as I instinctively do the same."
    "La llamada de Alana no es muy fuerte, pero los niños parecen oírla. Enseguida se callan y vuelven a prestar atención. Mi espalda se endereza y yo hago lo mismo instintivamente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1158
translate Spanish ch2m_05_1446f0a8:

    # a "Behave."
    a "Compórtense."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1160
translate Spanish ch2m_05_d9febc7c:

    # "And like that, the children abort their mission, buzzing off to find new quarry. Alana seems to have powers that would make any schoolmarm jealous."
    "Y así, los niños abortan su misión y salen zumbando en busca de una nueva presa. Alana parece tener poderes que pondrían celosa a cualquier maestra."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1161
translate Spanish ch2m_05_35923a42:

    # c "Impressive. Still putting your schoolhouse skills to good use?"
    c "Impresionante. ¿Sigues haciendo buen uso de tus habilidades en la escuela?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1163
translate Spanish ch2m_05_4b82f986:

    # a "Aye. And this class is a fair share more obedient than your own."
    a "Sí. Y esta clase es bastante más obediente que la tuya."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1164
translate Spanish ch2m_05_4d6447f3:

    # "Hmph. A bit of healthy disobedience never hurt anyone... except for the occasional ruler to the backside. Nonetheless, I choose to take it as a compliment."
    "Hmph. Un poco de sana desobediencia nunca hace daño a nadie... excepto por la regla ocasional en el trasero. Sin embargo, elijo tomarlo como un cumplido."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1165
translate Spanish ch2m_05_2531bf05:

    # c "Your students? Still teaching the youth of Ach-na-Creige, then?"
    c "¿Tus alumnos? ¿Sigues enseñando a la juventud de Ach-na-Creige, entonces?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1167
translate Spanish ch2m_05_4b0df312:

    # a "You didn't think you'd driven me into retirement, did you? No, I'll keep teaching this town's little troublemakers as long as I have to."
    a "No pensarías que me habías llevado a la jubilación, ¿verdad? No, seguiré enseñando a los pequeños alborotadores de este pueblo mientras sea necesario."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1169
translate Spanish ch2m_05_e2c24a33:

    # "I can see the moment Alana's face drops. Marion has come up beside me, to offer me a cold ginger tonic."
    "Puedo ver el momento en que la cara de Alana se desencaja. Marion se ha acercado a mi lado para ofrecerme un tónico de jengibre frío."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1172
translate Spanish ch2m_05_6467d0da:

    # m "Miss Alana! How are you? You look lovely today."
    m "¡Señorita Alana! ¿Cómo está? Hoy estás preciosa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1173
translate Spanish ch2m_05_23ac0152:

    # a "Thank you, Marion."
    a "Gracias, Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1174
translate Spanish ch2m_05_2e7e21e6:

    # "While Alana's still smiling, there's an icy tone to her voice. She looks back and forth between Marion and me."
    "Aunque Alana sigue sonriendo, su voz tiene un tono gélido. Nos mira a Marion y a mí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1175
translate Spanish ch2m_05_bf3ccaed:

    # "I can tell she's displeased to see the two of us in such close proximity after voicing her warnings to me not long back."
    "Me doy cuenta de que le disgusta vernos tan cerca después de haberme advertido hace poco."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1177
translate Spanish ch2m_05_e55ac09b:

    # a "So, you two are... here together?"
    a "Entonces, ¿ustedes dos están... aquí juntos?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1178
translate Spanish ch2m_05_386c9e91:

    # "Marion is quick to save the situation, obviously as uncomfortable as I am, though most likely unaware that Alana's question is more of an accusation."
    "Marion se apresura a salvar la situación, obviamente tan incómoda como yo, aunque lo más probable es que ignore que la pregunta de Alana es más bien una acusación."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1180
translate Spanish ch2m_05_50c823f3:

    # m "Malcolm was kind enough to bring his horse by, so I didn't have to lug my large basket all this way."
    m "Malcolm tuvo la amabilidad de traer su caballo, así que no tuve que cargar mi canasta grande hasta aquí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1182
translate Spanish ch2m_05_f26ad090:

    # a "Don't you have your own horse?"
    a "¿No tienes tu propio caballo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1183
translate Spanish ch2m_05_081a0a18:

    # "Curt and aggressive as ever. I nearly choke on my ginger tonic."
    "Brusco y agresivo como siempre. Casi me ahogo con mi tónico de jengibre."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1184
translate Spanish ch2m_05_890b5879:

    # c "She does, yes. I... uh, thought it best not to aggravate her horse further. It's been injured of late."
    c "Ella sí, sí. Yo... uh, pensé que sería mejor no irritar más a su caballo. Últimamente ha resultado herido."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1186
translate Spanish ch2m_05_ec346513:

    # "I'm sure I turned red at the lie, though when I look to Marion, she seemed undisturbed by my tall tale."
    "Estoy seguro de que me sonrojé por la mentira, aunque cuando miro a Marion, ella no parecía perturbada por mi cuento."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1188
translate Spanish ch2m_05_2eff2244:

    # a "What's wrong with it?"
    a "¿Qué tiene de malo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1189
translate Spanish ch2m_05_689664ed:

    # "It asks too many questions, I want to say."
    "Hace demasiadas preguntas, quiero decir."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1191
translate Spanish ch2m_05_aef82278:

    # m "I believe it's a stress injury. Overcompensating on one side. With rest, he'll be fine."
    m "Creo que es una lesión por estrés. Sobrecompensación en un lado. Con descanso, estará bien."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1192
translate Spanish ch2m_05_072ca2c0:

    # "Marion looks to me with big eyes, as if to confirm our story. I'm not sure why she's covering for my lie, but I certainly appreciate it."
    "Marion me mira con ojos grandes, como si quisiera confirmar nuestra historia. No estoy seguro de por qué encubre mi mentira, pero desde luego se lo agradezco."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1193
translate Spanish ch2m_05_ea12d3ed:

    # c "Aye. The poor horse still has the gumption, just not the drive."
    c "Sí. El pobre caballo aún tiene agallas, pero no el empuje."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1201
translate Spanish ch2m_05_602f0017:

    # b "Ahoy, good friends and neighbors!"
    b "¡Ah, buenos amigos y vecinos!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1202
translate Spanish ch2m_05_61ed0dce:

    # "As heavenly as Moses parting the Red Sea, Balgair barges into our social huddle, plate in hand. He presents it with great enthusiasm."
    "Tan celestial como Moisés partiendo el Mar Rojo, Balgair irrumpe en nuestra charla social, plato en mano. Lo presenta con gran entusiasmo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1204
translate Spanish ch2m_05_7e233057:

    # b "Miss Alana, I don't believe you've had one of my beer-battered haggis balls, yet!"
    b "Sr. Alana, creo que aún no ha probado una de mis bolas de haggis a la cerveza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1207
translate Spanish ch2m_05_475c9175:

    # "Alana's expression goes from skeptical to horrified, instantly. I believe he may have distracted her attention fully."
    "La expresión de Alana pasa de escéptica a horrorizada, al instante. Creo que puede haber distraído su atención por completo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1209
translate Spanish ch2m_05_19d69fa6:

    # a "Ah, the children seem to be unleashing a colony of ants upon the desserts. Please excuse me."
    a "Ah, los niños parecen estar desatando una colonia de hormigas sobre los postres. Por favor, disculpadme."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1215
translate Spanish ch2m_05_de0881f6:

    # "Alana makes her escape, without bidding anyone a fair day. Balgair watches after her, grinning."
    "Alana escapa sin desear a nadie un buen día. Balgair la sigue con una sonrisa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1225
translate Spanish ch2m_05_76a85f15:

    # c "I daresay we owe you."
    c "Me atrevería a decir que estamos en deuda contigo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1227
translate Spanish ch2m_05_979a1f4e:

    # b "Eh?"
    b "Eh?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1228
translate Spanish ch2m_05_c0a6ef5f:

    # c "For saving us, just then."
    c "Por salvarnos, justo entonces."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1235
translate Spanish ch2m_05_5dda5117:

    # b "Ah, lad, mah pleasure, though not mah intent. Just trying to see that these don't go to waste like last year. And the year before. And the year 'afore that."
    b "Ah, muchacho, es un placer, aunque no es mi intención. Sólo intento que no se desperdicien como el año pasado. Y el año anterior. Y el año anterior a ese."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1236
translate Spanish ch2m_05_22d3652a:

    # "It's very clearly eating at him. The plate is still full, and my nose wrinkles at the scent. I look to Marion."
    "Está claro que se lo está comiendo. El plato sigue lleno y mi nariz se arruga ante el olor. Miro a Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1238
translate Spanish ch2m_05_d8acb95b:

    # m "My stomach has been very delicate of late, but thank you, Balgair."
    m "Mi estómago ha estado muy delicado últimamente, pero gracias, Balgair."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1249
translate Spanish ch2m_05_ae8985d5:

    # b "That leaves you, my boy! Well?"
    b "¡Eso te deja a ti, muchacho! ¿Y bien?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1255
translate Spanish ch2m_05_feddf415:

    # "I take a ball in my hand, rolling its greasy surface a bit between my fingers. Ugh."
    "Cojo una bola con la mano, haciendo rodar un poco su grasienta superficie entre los dedos. Uf."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1257
translate Spanish ch2m_05_1682b9e3:

    # b "That's it! Eat up!"
    b "¡Eso es! ¡Come!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1258
translate Spanish ch2m_05_9dfa7156:

    # "The wind kicks up, and it calls to mind the sound of a trench whistle. In one swift motion, I pop the ball whole into my mouth. Gagging, I swallow."
    "El viento se levanta y me recuerda el sonido de un silbato de trinchera. Con un movimiento rápido, me meto la pelota entera en la boca. Trago con arcadas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1261
translate Spanish ch2m_05_bfe222a6:

    # "My, if the whole of a garbage heap was compressed into a palm-sized ball, battered, and fried... it would still taste better than Balgair's balls."
    "Vaya, si todo un montón de basura se comprimiera en una bola del tamaño de la palma de la mano, se rebozara y se friera... seguiría sabiendo mejor que las bolas de Balgair."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1263
translate Spanish ch2m_05_3832a2a9:

    # b "Attaboy! A pair of those would make a true Scot out of even an Englishman."
    b "¡Bravo! Un par de esos convertirían a un verdadero escocés incluso en un inglés."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1266
translate Spanish ch2m_05_7366dc8e:

    # c "Sorry, I'm... tryin' to watch my weight."
    c "Lo siento, estoy... intentando vigilar mi peso."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1268
translate Spanish ch2m_05_24fe275b:

    # b "Are ye sure m'boy? They're my grandpappy's recipe!"
    b "¿Estás seguro, muchacho? ¡Son la receta de mi abuelo!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1269
translate Spanish ch2m_05_4cbd2d36:

    # c "No, but thank you."
    c "No, pero gracias."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1271
translate Spanish ch2m_05_09ea56d5:

    # b "Ah, well... more for me!"
    b "Ah, bueno... ¡más para mí!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1274
translate Spanish ch2m_05_23edb6ad:

    # "He takes three whole balls, wads them into his mouth, and nearly swallows them whole. I feel queasy."
    "Toma tres bolas enteras, se las mete en la boca y casi se las traga enteras. Me mareo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1275
translate Spanish ch2m_05_5b1163d3:

    # c "Would you excuse me a moment?"
    c "Me disculpa un momento?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1284
translate Spanish ch2m_05_e9847eb7:

    # "I shuffle away from the table—and the offending plate—to get some fresh air, lest I start retching."
    "Me alejo de la mesa -y del plato- para respirar aire fresco, no sea que me den arcadas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1285
translate Spanish ch2m_05_d6795e0d:

    # "The feeling passes quickly enough, but I linger, enjoying the break from the crowds. A moment later, Marion joins me."
    "La sensación pasa con rapidez, pero me quedo, disfrutando de la pausa entre la multitud. Un momento después, Marion se une a mí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1292
translate Spanish ch2m_05_2d85290c:

    # m "You're a brave fellow, Mr. Campbell!"
    m "¡Es usted un tipo valiente, Sr. Campbell!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1293
translate Spanish ch2m_05_f6dd0088:

    # c "My own delicate stomach will repay me later."
    c "Mi delicado estómago me lo pagará más tarde."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1297
translate Spanish ch2m_05_44ae4792:

    # m "Everything well?"
    m "Todo bien?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1298
translate Spanish ch2m_05_ccc5c712:

    # c "Better than if I had eaten one of Balgair's haggis balls, for certain."
    c "Mejor que si me hubiera comido una de las bolas de haggis de Balgair, seguro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1301
translate Spanish ch2m_05_6e817e84:

    # "Marion laughs. She seems much less jittery now, but she still fidgets with her head covering and her skirt."
    "Marion se ríe. Parece mucho menos nerviosa ahora, pero todavía juguetea con su gorro y su falda."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1302
translate Spanish ch2m_05_bc8a0c58:

    # c "How are you holding up, now?"
    c "Cómo lo llevas ahora?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1304
translate Spanish ch2m_05_bc2fe20e:

    # m "A bit better, I suppose. It definitely has helped take my mind off... things."
    m "Un poco mejor, supongo. Definitivamente me ha ayudado a olvidarme de... cosas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1305
translate Spanish ch2m_05_4820ea1d:

    # c "Good! Good. And, your horse—he {i}is{/i} all right, isn't he?"
    c "¡Bien! Bien. Y tu caballo está bien, ¿no?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1307
translate Spanish ch2m_05_610131fc:

    # "She laughs again, shaking her head."
    "Se ríe de nuevo, sacudiendo la cabeza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1308
translate Spanish ch2m_05_cc9b81e8:

    # m "Of course! I know how... odd... Alana can be. It looked like you needed help, so I followed your lead."
    m "¡Claro! Sé lo... rara... Alana puede ser. Parecía que necesitabas ayuda, así que te seguí la corriente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1309
translate Spanish ch2m_05_f0ffa1a8:

    # c "I guess I should thank you... thank you for enabling my lies."
    c "Supongo que debería darte las gracias... gracias por permitir mis mentiras."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1311
translate Spanish ch2m_05_46b3b8da:

    # m "Hey now. I can't be a perfect role model for you rascals {i}all{/i} the time."
    m "hey ahora, No puedo ser un modelo perfecto para ustedes {i}todo{/i} el tiempo, bribones"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1313
translate Spanish ch2m_05_e12cbdcd:

    # "We trade conspiratorial winks, and I reach out to take her hand in mine—when a little scamp screeches to a halt in between us."
    "Intercambiamos guiños de complicidad y alargo la mano para coger la mía, cuando un pequeño bribón se detiene entre nosotros."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1317
translate Spanish ch2m_05_3e847dcf:

    # m "Oh! Hello Florrie. Take care where you're hastening to, now."
    m "¡Oh! Hola Florrie. Ten cuidado a donde te diriges."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1319
translate Spanish ch2m_05_c182eb5d:

    # "The child nods vigorously. I'm amazed how Marion seems to know everyone in town, even down to the wee ones."
    "El niño asiente enérgicamente. Me sorprende cómo Marion parece conocer a todo el mundo en el pueblo, incluso a los más pequeños."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1321
translate Spanish ch2m_05_74cc91cc:

    # f "Hullo Miss Marion an' Mister... not-Marion. Wan' sum space keck?"
    f "Hola Srta. Marion y Sr... no-Marion. Quieren un pastel espacial?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1322
translate Spanish ch2m_05_91c53eae:

    # "Space cake? For a moment I wonder if H.G. Wells contributed a dessert to the picnic."
    "¿Pastel espacial? Por un momento me pregunto si H.G. Wells contribuyó con un postre al picnic."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1324
translate Spanish ch2m_05_2a7dc360:

    # "Then Florrie produces a frosted wad of dessert from her pocket, and I recognize—barely—the remains of Gran's spice cake."
    "Entonces Florrie saca del bolsillo un fajo de postre escarchado, y reconozco -apenas- los restos de la tarta de especias de la abuela."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1326
translate Spanish ch2m_05_34a1839e:

    # m "Ooooh... thank you?"
    m "Ooooh... ¿gracias?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1328
translate Spanish ch2m_05_d3809ab9:

    # "Marion and I exchange a glance as she takes the lint-covered gift. Florrie smiles, and says something unintelligible to adult ears."
    "Marion y yo intercambiamos una mirada mientras ella coge el regalo cubierto de pelusa. Florrie sonríe y dice algo ininteligible para los oídos adultos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1329
translate Spanish ch2m_05_4be64fd6:

    # c "Heh. Gran will be thrilled to know her dessert was such a hit with the kids."
    c "Je. La abuela estará encantada de saber que su postre fue un éxito con los niños."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1331
translate Spanish ch2m_05_9e0635ce:

    # m "I, um, will save this for later, Florrie. Dessert comes {i}after{/i} the... the..."
    m "Dejaré esto para más tarde, Florrie. El postre viene {i}después{/i} del... el..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1336
translate Spanish ch2m_05_d606c6b2:

    # m "Oh! OH, NO!"
    m "Oh! OH, NO!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1337
translate Spanish ch2m_05_6a853f68:

    # "That's not lint on the frosting. Little black dots begin to crawl indiscriminately from the cake to Marion's hand. So Alana wasn't kidding about the ants, after all..."
    "Eso no son pelusas en el glaseado. Pequeños puntos negros comienzan a arrastrarse indiscriminadamente desde la tarta hasta la mano de Marion. Así que Alana no estaba bromeando sobre las hormigas, después de todo..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1347
translate Spanish ch2m_05_3709bd20:

    # "Marion sends the glob flying, and dances a wild jig that would give even her flapper sister a run for her money."
    "Marion hace volar la tarta y baila una danza salvaje que le daría incluso a su hermana flapper una oportunidad por su dinero."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1348
translate Spanish ch2m_05_c9c95ede:

    # m "Get off me, get off me, {i}waaaaaah!{/i}"
    m "¡Quítate de mí, quítate de mí, {i}waaaaaah!{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1368
translate Spanish ch2m_05_83e53353:

    # "...What in the world?"
    "... ¿Qué diablos?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1369
translate Spanish ch2m_05_a0f688a6:

    # c "Marion, what is—?"
    c "Marion, ¿qué es...?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1380
translate Spanish ch2m_05_6644ffc6:

    # "She dives over the wall and down the hillside, speeding away from the picnic as fast as the wind will take her."
    "Se lanza sobre la pared y baja por la ladera, alejándose del picnic tan rápido como el viento se lo permite."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1381
translate Spanish ch2m_05_9e5ed4ef:

    # "I rub my eyes, not sure I believe what I see."
    "Me froto los ojos, no estoy seguro de creer lo que veo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1384
translate Spanish ch2m_05_eb7111b2:

    # f "Miss Marion look funny. Hey, Mister, can I haf tail too?"
    f "La señorita Marion se ve graciosa. Oye, señor, ¿puedo tener cola también?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1391
translate Spanish ch2m_05_e2566841:

    # c "Don't be ridiculous, lass. Marion doesn't have a tail."
    c "No seas ridícula, muchacha. Marion no tiene cola."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1403
translate Spanish ch2m_05_1de6efc3:

    # "Although that's certainly what it looked like. I glance left and right."
    "Aunque ciertamente eso es lo que parecía. Miro de izquierda y derecha."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1404
translate Spanish ch2m_05_5b5ed37e:

    # "The elderly women of the Whist club are still deep in conversation. Murdoch seems to have given up on them and is now intent on sampling every hors d'oeuvre."
    "Las ancianas del club de Whist todavía están enfrascadas en una conversación. Murdoch parece haber renunciado a ellos y ahora tiene la intención de probar cada entremés."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1405
translate Spanish ch2m_05_0a912266:

    # "Everyone else is further up the hill. No one but the child and I seem to have witnessed the scene."
    "Todos los demás están más arriba de la colina. Nadie más que el niño y yo parece haber presenciado la escena."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1406
translate Spanish ch2m_05_9e49231f:

    # c "Why don't you go back and play with your friends. Malcolm needs to have a talk with Miss Marion."
    c "¿Por qué no vuelves y juegas con tus amigos? Malcolm necesita hablar con la señorita Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1407
translate Spanish ch2m_05_b7338cae:

    # "I hop the wall and give chase."
    "Salto la pared y lo persigo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1434
translate Spanish ch2m_06_42187cbf:

    # c "Marion! Please, wait for me!"
    c "¡Marión! ¡Por favor, espérame!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1435
translate Spanish ch2m_06_dc31be2e:

    # "She tears down the path away from town, desperately tugging at her kerchief and skirt. A tuft of hair at her hem refuses to be contained, and it swings back and forth."
    "Se aleja del pueblo tirando desesperadamente de su pañuelo y su falda. Un mechón de pelo en el dobladillo se niega a contenerse y se balancea de un lado a otro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1436
translate Spanish ch2m_06_d94766dc:

    # "It's difficult to keep pace, but I finally catch up as she ducks behind a small berm. She struggles to catch her breath."
    "Es difícil mantener el ritmo, pero finalmente la alcanzo cuando se agacha detrás de una pequeña berma. Se esfuerza por recuperar el aliento."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1441
translate Spanish ch2m_06_01a93953:

    # c "Marion, I—"
    c "Marion, yo..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1443
translate Spanish ch2m_06_7d8397bd:

    # m "I have to show you something. Please, please, {i}please{/i} don't run away!"
    m "Tengo que enseñarte algo. ¡Por favor, por favor, no huyas!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1444
translate Spanish ch2m_06_62d0071b:

    # c "You're worrying me. I don't want you to run off, either!"
    c "Me estás preocupando. ¡Yo tampoco quiero que huyas!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1445
translate Spanish ch2m_06_ba9cfa4c:

    # "Marion is panting as she slowly and deliberately lifts the loose kerchief she's been playing with all day."
    "Marion jadea mientras levanta lenta y deliberadamente el pañuelo suelto con el que ha estado jugando todo el día."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1451
translate Spanish ch2m_06_d472b1bc:

    # "Then I see them."
    "Entonces los veo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1452
translate Spanish ch2m_06_8475e721:

    # c "Horns?"
    c "¿Cuernos?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1454
translate Spanish ch2m_06_5edb22b6:

    # m "{i}And ears!{/i}"
    m "{i}¡Y orejas!{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1455
translate Spanish ch2m_06_7b51754b:

    # "Gone are Marion's petite human ears. Right before my eyes sit two fuzzy brown cow-shaped ears jutting from the sides of her head."
    "Las pequeñas orejas humanas de Marion han desaparecido. Ante mis ojos se alzan dos peludas orejas marrones con forma de vaca que sobresalen de los lados de su cabeza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1457
translate Spanish ch2m_06_48bfa05e:

    # "Nubby horns sit in between the ears, just like a common shorthorn heifer. All I can do is laugh out loud."
    "Los cuernos nudosos se asientan entre las orejas, igual que una vaquilla shorthorn común. Lo único que puedo hacer es reírme a carcajadas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1458
translate Spanish ch2m_06_98a5ec88:

    # c "Oh, Marion! It's lovely. But, why the costume?"
    c "¡Oh, Marion! Es precioso. Pero, ¿por qué el disfraz?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1460
translate Spanish ch2m_06_3f21e352:

    # m "It's not a costume!"
    m "¡No es un disfraz!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1478
translate Spanish ch2m_06_df139e3f:

    # "She is near tears as she grabs my hand, and has me feel at her new ears."
    "Está a punto de llorar cuando me agarra la mano y me hace tocar sus nuevas orejas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1479
translate Spanish ch2m_06_cd722734:

    # c "They're so soft!"
    c "Son tan suaves!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1480
translate Spanish ch2m_06_5ce3693d:

    # m "They're {i}cow's ears,{/i} Malcolm!"
    m "¡Son {i}orejas de vaca,{/i} Malcolm!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1483
translate Spanish ch2m_06_d4fd413f:

    # "I'm petting her head when she pulls at her skirt. A swishing, thick bovine tail falls out."
    "Le acaricio la cabeza cuando se tira de la falda. Se le cae un grueso rabo bovino."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1484
translate Spanish ch2m_06_56248904:

    # m "I have a {i}tail!{/i}"
    m "¡Tengo una {i}cola!{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1485
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a79a19ef:

    # "She is trying to use a low voice, but she is still shouting."
    "Intenta hablar en voz baja, pero sigue gritando."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1486
translate Spanish ch2m_06_e01ef08b:

    # c "You... do? You sure do."
    c "¿Tú... sí? Claro que sí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1487
translate Spanish ch2m_06_5f960a1a:

    # m "That's all you can say?!"
    m "¡¿Eso es todo lo que puedes decir?!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1488
translate Spanish ch2m_06_71661eed:

    # "I'm quite taken aback. I'm not entirely sure what to make of this."
    "Estoy bastante sorprendido. No sé muy bien qué pensar de esto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1494
translate Spanish ch2m_06_2b2a9e6f:

    # m "I-I don't know when or how it happened. I woke up like this."
    m "No sé cuándo ni cómo ocurrió. Me desperté así."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1495
translate Spanish ch2m_06_62457877:

    # c "Does it hurt?"
    c "Te duele?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1497
translate Spanish ch2m_06_2e1ccd22:

    # m "No. Not a bit. It all feels... very natural. Like it's always been there. But... why did this {i}happen?{/i}"
    m "No. Ni un poco. Todo se siente... muy natural. Como si siempre hubiera estado ahí. Pero... ¿por qué sucedió {i}esto?{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1502
translate Spanish ch2m_06_09dd63cc:

    # butterfly_effect "{image=butterflysprite}" nointeract
    butterfly_effect "{image=butterflysprite}" nointeract

# game/script_marion.rpy:1505
translate Spanish ch2m_06_ab093036:

    # c "It's certainly odd."
    c "Es ciertamente extraño."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1507
translate Spanish ch2m_06_5c95cfb9:

    # m "Odd?? It's insane! I've become a cow!"
    m "¿Extraño? ¡Es una locura! ¡Me he convertido en una vaca!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1508
translate Spanish ch2m_06_b412d171:

    # c "Well, only parts of you."
    c "Bueno, sólo partes de ti."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1510
translate Spanish ch2m_06_073113f5:

    # m "Oh, don't joke about this! What will I do?"
    m "¡No bromees con esto! ¿Qué voy a hacer?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1511
translate Spanish ch2m_06_bbe7b163:

    # c "Here. Take my hand. I'll lead you home, and we'll think of something. Somehow."
    c "Aqui. Toma mi mano. Te llevaré a casa, y pensaremos en algo. De alguna manera."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1514
translate Spanish ch2m_06_5700710d:

    # c "I've no idea."
    c "No tengo ni idea."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1515
translate Spanish ch2m_06_f284eb2d:

    # "It's quite shocking, even a bit dreadful. My mind can't help but return to that horribly vivid nightmare, which... I wonder, could it now be playing out before our eyes?"
    "Es bastante chocante, incluso un poco espantoso. Mi mente no puede evitar volver a esa pesadilla horriblemente vívida, que... Me pregunto, ¿podría estar desarrollándose ahora ante nuestros ojos?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1516
translate Spanish ch2m_06_2fe5a3d3:

    # "I want to be able to reassure Marion, but find myself doing the opposite."
    "Quiero ser capaz de tranquilizar a Marion, pero me encuentro haciendo lo contrario."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1517
translate Spanish ch2m_06_53d7a36e:

    # c "I just don't know... I'm not entirely sure I can deal with this."
    c "No sé... No estoy del todo seguro de poder lidiar con esto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1519
translate Spanish ch2m_06_aeeed5bd:

    # m "Not now. Not today. Not... ever?"
    m "Ahora no. Hoy no. No... ¿nunca?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1521
translate Spanish ch2m_06_2a2788fa:

    # "Marion's face drops, but she must be feeling the same way."
    "A Marion se le cae la cara de vergüenza, pero debe de sentir lo mismo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1523
translate Spanish ch2m_06_9a000a61:

    # m "I shouldn't have shown you."
    m "No debería habértelo enseñado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1524
translate Spanish ch2m_06_d4c765e9:

    # c "No, please don't say that. Don't ever be ashamed or embarrassed. You'll..."
    c "No, por favor, no digas eso. Nunca te sientas avergonzada o apenada. Tu..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1526
translate Spanish ch2m_06_fb60a1ea:

    # m "Be fine? Get better? Everything sounds like a hopeful lie."
    m "¿Estar bien? ¿Mejorar? Todo suena a mentira esperanzadora."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1528
translate Spanish ch2m_06_f7e3d5e3:

    # "Marion tears up, and I regret having been overly honest in her time of need. There's no taking my words back. She's hurt, and I am the one that hurt her."
    "A Marion se le saltan las lágrimas y me arrepiento de haber sido demasiado sincero en su momento de necesidad. No puedo retirar mis palabras. Está herida, y soy yo quien le ha hecho daño."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1529
translate Spanish ch2m_06_203ddfc5:

    # c "Come. We should probably get you home right away."
    c "Ven. Probablemente deberíamos llevarte a casa de inmediato."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1532
translate Spanish ch2m_06_7b0dbb2b:

    # "I almost don't dare admit that I actually think it's adorable. Almost. I really can't help myself."
    "Casi no me atrevo a admitir que me parece adorable. Casi. Realmente no puedo evitarlo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1533
translate Spanish ch2m_06_b1e3aac1:

    # c "It's... well, it's cute!"
    c "Es... bueno, ¡es lindo!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1535
translate Spanish ch2m_06_8797186d:

    # m "You don't really think that! ...Do you?"
    m "¡Realmente no piensas eso! ...¿verdad?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1536
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a1155cd8:

    # c "I do. I just... let's get you home. We'll figure this out together. There must be an explanation."
    c "Sí, quiero. Yo sólo... vamos a llevarte a casa. Resolveremos esto juntos. Debe haber una explicación."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1539
translate Spanish ch2m_06_740c1046:

    # "She slips her hand into mine, and I smile to myself."
    "Ella desliza su mano en la mía y yo sonrío para mis adentros."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1540
translate Spanish ch2m_06_61635df6:

    # c "At least you don't have hooves."
    c "Al menos no tienes pezuñas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1542
translate Spanish ch2m_06_45f937c7:

    # m "Oh, Malcolm! At least... not yet."
    m "¡Oh, Malcolm! Al menos... todavía no."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1543
translate Spanish ch2m_06_d00f8522:

    # "I brush back the hairs off the fuzzy little nubs on top of her head. Her anxiety is briefly interrupted by a giggle."
    "Le retiro los pelos de las pequeñas protuberancias de la parte superior de la cabeza. Una risita interrumpe brevemente su ansiedad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1545
translate Spanish ch2m_06_e6b51c68:

    # m "That tickles. Oh, stop... you're being silly. This is serious!"
    m "Eso hace cosquillas. Oh, para... estás siendo tonto. ¡Esto es serio!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1546
translate Spanish ch2m_06_9087c000:

    # "I don't mean to make light of the situation, but it seems important to lighten the mood. Any excuse to tug at her tail, really. It swishes back and forth playfully."
    "No quiero quitarle importancia a la situación, pero me parece importante aligerar el ambiente. Cualquier excusa es buena para tirar de su cola. Se balancea de un lado a otro juguetonamente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1548
translate Spanish ch2m_06_ee87d548:

    # m "Malcolm!"
    m "Malcolm!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1549
translate Spanish ch2m_06_7233a2d3:

    # c "All right, let's go. We probably shouldn't be seen."
    c "Muy bien, vámonos. Probablemente no deberían vernos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1558
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_ee44b9aa:

    # "A rustling noise announces that we have a visitor. Marion instinctively jumps behind me."
    "Un susurro anuncia que tenemos visita. Marion salta instintivamente detrás de mí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1570
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_fbca6df7:

    # "From around the berm, Hazel strolls up to us. I see that she has chewed her way through the thick rope that had tethered her to the fencepost."
    "Desde la berma, Hazel se acerca a nosotros. Veo que ha mordido la gruesa cuerda que la ataba al poste de la valla."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1571
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_46679989:

    # c "While I ought to give you a swift kick, Miss Hazel, your timing couldn't be better."
    c "Aunque debería darte una patada, Srta. Hazel, no podrías llegar en mejor momento."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1578
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_ecc1ecca:

    # "Marion tucks her new... features... away, and accepts my help mounting Hazel. We take off towards home in silence."
    "Marion aparta sus nuevos... rasgos... y acepta mi ayuda montando a Hazel. Partimos hacia casa en silencio."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1585
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_166f058d:

    # m "Malcolm, can we go a little slower? Riding with... er, my skirt is... well. It's just not very comfortable, is all."
    m "Malcolm, ¿podemos ir un poco más despacio? Montar con... er, mi falda es... bueno. No es muy cómodo, eso es todo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1586
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_ebee38b6:

    # "Nodding, I gently reign in Hazel. We take the ride nice and easy so Marion isn't further distressed."
    "Asiento con la cabeza y tranquilizo a Hazel. Nos tomamos el viaje con calma para que Marion no se angustie más."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1587
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_1d821c02:

    # "I only have to chastise Hazel a few times for going akilter and trying to eat dandelions."
    "Sólo tengo que reprender a Hazel un par de veces por volverse loca e intentar comer dientes de león."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1594
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_211ef611:

    # "As we ride, Marion places her head on my back. The tears are silent, but her sniffles give them away. I take my handkerchief out of my pocket and pass it back to her."
    "Mientras cabalgamos, Marion apoya la cabeza en mi espalda. Las lágrimas son silenciosas, pero sus mocos las delatan. Saco el pañuelo del bolsillo y se lo paso."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1595
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_98c6141c:

    # m "Thank you..."
    m "Gracias..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1596
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_3b9eb6ef:

    # "She blows her nose hard."
    "Se suena la nariz con fuerza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1597
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_d4ad6a04:

    # m "I... I'm just so sorry."
    m "Yo... Lo siento mucho."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1598
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_216c1c04:

    # c "This isn't your fault, Marion. We'll figure it out."
    c "Esto no es culpa tuya, Marion. Lo resolveremos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1621
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_c38c1ebc:

    # "Back at the farm, Grace meets us at the door. She shows no sign of surprise. Apparently she'd helped Marion conceal her new features earlier."
    "De vuelta en la granja, Grace nos recibe en la puerta. No muestra ningún signo de sorpresa. Al parecer, había ayudado antes a Marion a disimular sus nuevos rasgos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1622
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_f7930750:

    # "In the privacy of her own home, Marion finally stops trying to maintain her uncomfortable disguise—though she is far from relaxed. As usual, Grace doesn't hold back on her opinions."
    "En la intimidad de su propia casa, Marion por fin deja de intentar mantener su incómodo disfraz, aunque está lejos de estar relajada. Como de costumbre, Grace no se guarda sus opiniones."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1625
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_5bd257fa:

    # g "It's bizarre!"
    g "¡Es extraño!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1626
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_56eacb2f:

    # c "Grace, don't be rude!"
    c "¡Grace, no seas maleducada!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1628
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_4591fe16:

    # g "I can't help it, she has a tail. What would you call it? Gross?"
    g "No puedo evitarlo, tiene cola. ¿Cómo lo llamarías? ¿Asqueroso?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1630
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_c4b7833b:

    # m "It's not {i}gross!{/i} I-It's not like I smell like a cow!"
    m "¡No es {i}asqueroso!{/i} ¡No es que huela a vaca!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1631
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_a7f76f99:

    # "Marion freezes."
    "Marion se queda helada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1633
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_8cdb0011:

    # m "Or do I?"
    m "¿O sí?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1634
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_7c46c055:

    # c "Of course not. You still smell like... you."
    c "Por supuesto que no. Sigues oliendo como... tú."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1652
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_cf4f7e05:

    # "Marion immediately busies herself, boiling kettle water for us all to have tea."
    "Marion inmediatamente se pone a hervir agua en una tetera para que todos tomemos té."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1653
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_6d75203c:

    # "Ever the giver, she is still trying to keep a brave face and tend to her sister and me. That said, her brave face actually looks petrified."
    "Siempre tan generosa, sigue intentando mantener una cara valiente y atendernos a su hermana y a mí. Dicho esto, su cara de valiente en realidad parece petrificada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1674
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_ed2d7d8a:

    # "I take a seat and speculate on what could have happened."
    "Tomo asiento y especulo sobre lo que podría haber ocurrido."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1675
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_a7945697:

    # c "Perhaps it's an illness of some sort?"
    c "¿Tal vez sea una enfermedad de algún tipo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1677
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_b6af23e6:

    # m "What? Something from the cows? How horrifying!"
    m "¿De qué? ¿Algo de las vacas? ¡Qué horror!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1691
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_8c98e1a3:

    # g "She's cursed."
    g "Está maldita."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1700
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_7d7a76ef:

    # m "Grace!"
    m "Grace!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1703
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_02b1a5e0:

    # g "What? It could be possible."
    g "¿Qué? Podría ser posible."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1704
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_7deaafe6:

    # c "I don't... no, I don't think so."
    c "No... no, no lo creo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1705
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_89afdea2:

    # "Or maybe it could. Maybe it {i}is{/i} a curse. The first thought that comes to mind is my Gran's insatiable insistence that magic runs rampant through these parts."
    "O tal vez podría. Quizás sea una maldición. El primer pensamiento que me viene a la cabeza es la insaciable insistencia de mi abuela en que la magia campa a sus anchas por estos lares."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1706
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_58dfb569:

    # "It's folklore. Old wives' tales. But why do the rumors persist? Is there any grain of truth?"
    "Es folclore. Cuentos de viejas. Pero, ¿por qué persisten los rumores? ¿Hay algo de verdad?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1707
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_192a2102:

    # "Marion readjusts her skirt, and her tail swings above the cotton."
    "Marion se reajusta la falda y su cola se balancea por encima del algodón."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1709
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_c5ba9676:

    # m "Malcolm, can you help me take this pendant off?"
    m "Malcolm, ¿puedes ayudarme a quitarme este colgante?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1730
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_aad3342a:

    # "I unclasp the cowbell necklace, and slide it into my palm. Looking at the charm, I flash back to Effie's suggestion that I get it. She even paid for it. Why would she do that?"
    "Desabrocho el collar del cencerro y lo deslizo en la palma de la mano. Miro el colgante y recuerdo la sugerencia de Effie de que me lo comprara. Incluso me lo pagó. ¿Por qué lo haría?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1731
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_559931af:

    # m "Thank you, Malcolm. Even the back of my neck feels uncomfortable."
    m "Gracias, Malcolm. Incluso mi nuca se siente incómoda."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1732
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_39b5244d:

    # "She rubs her hands together and whispers."
    "Se frota las manos y susurra."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1733
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_d5b90330:

    # m "{size=22}...and my fingers are starting to go numb.{/size}"
    m "{size=22}...y mis dedos están empezando a entumecerse.{/size}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1734
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_17030105:

    # c "Here, let me look."
    c "Déjame ver."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1735
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_7fd912d4:

    # "My encounter with Alana also crosses my mind. She repeatedly told me how the girls should be avoided at all costs. Was this why?"
    "También se me pasa por la cabeza mi encuentro con Alana. Me dijo repetidamente que había que evitar a toda costa a las chicas. ¿Fue por esto?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1738
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_b1841fda:

    # "As I run my fingertips gently along Marion's neck and shoulders, I examine her skin and see a thin film of brown hairs. It can't be fur. It simply can't."
    "Al pasar suavemente las yemas de los dedos por el cuello y los hombros de Marion, examino su piel y veo una fina película de pelos marrones. No puede ser pelo. No puede serlo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1739
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_7a827509:

    # "My skin covers with goosebumps simultaneously with Marion's. I step back."
    "Se me pone la piel de gallina al mismo tiempo que a Marion. Doy un paso atrás."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1746
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_9ecdf868:

    # c "It's fine. Your neck is fine."
    c "Está bien. Tu cuello está bien."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1747
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_0dbcaf6b:

    # "And what of that haunting nightmare? I turned into an animal. This is beyond coincidence. Maybe the curse is from Alana herself?"
    "¿Y qué hay de esa pesadilla inquietante? Me convertí en un animal. Esto va más allá de la coincidencia. ¿Tal vez la maldición es de la misma Alana?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1748
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_6bb4247d:

    # "She was so resolute about me never getting close to Marion. Are we being punished? If so, why should Marion be harmed? She's but a lamb, always."
    "She was so resolute about me never getting close to Marion. Are we being punished? If so, why should Marion be harmed? She's but a lamb, always."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1752
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_8aa08fe9:

    # "I look Marion in the eyes, and take her hands in mine."
    "Miro a Marion a los ojos y cojo sus manos entre las mías."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1753
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_c58e0fef:

    # c "Does this hurt?"
    c "¿Te duele?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1755
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_6ae0b4bd:

    # "I massage her fingers, softly at first, then harder, deeper. She shakes her head."
    "Le masajeo los dedos, primero suavemente, luego más fuerte, más profundo. Ella sacude la cabeza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1756
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_942e8e29:

    # m "I can barely feel a thing."
    m "Apenas siento nada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1763
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_b1b6e4c9:

    # "Grace starts laughing, and Marion looks again like she could faint at a pin drop."
    "Grace se echa a reír, y Marion vuelve a parecer que podría desmayarse con la caída de un alfiler."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1764
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_9a4b522e:

    # m "What is it, Grace?"
    m "¿Qué pasa, Grace?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1766
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_e4bf6016:

    # g "I was just thinking about how you'll look with an udder!"
    g "¡Estaba pensando en cómo te verías con una ubre!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1776
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_86f4a405:

    # "Marion goes white as a ghost and starts to faint. I catch her, and try to shake her awake."
    "Marion se queda blanca como un fantasma y empieza a desmayarse. La cojo e intento despertarla."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1777
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_ba2bd908:

    # c "Grace! Stop it!"
    c "¡Grace! ¡Detente!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1791
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_0d3f8624:

    # "Marion comes to, and I seat her comfortably in the chair before giving her hot tea."
    "Marion vuelve en sí y yo la siento cómodamente en la silla antes de darle un té caliente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1793
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_f411395e:

    # m "Am I going crazy? Will I lose my mind, Malcolm?"
    m "¿Me estoy volviendo loca? ¿Perderé la cabeza, Malcolm?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1794
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_93303fcb:

    # c "No, no! Of course not. We'll get to the bottom of this. I'll contact the apothecary and—"
    c "¡No, no! Por supuesto que no. Llegaremos al fondo de esto. Contactaré con el boticario y..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1796
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_6c2c8bf2:

    # m "No! No one can see me like this! No one can know about this. I'll be humiliated!"
    m "¡No! ¡Nadie puede verme así! Nadie puede saber de esto. ¡Seré humillada!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1797
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_05c699d3:

    # c "Then what else do you suggest? We need... you need help!"
    c "Entonces, ¿qué más sugieres? Necesitamos... ¡necesitas ayuda!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1800
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_64f424c8:

    # g "But who would we ask for help?"
    g "Pero ¿a quién pediríamos ayuda?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1807
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_c1e3cc04:

    # "I consider returning to town to confront Effie about a cursed pendant, but realize how insane that sounds even before muttering the option."
    "Me planteo volver al pueblo para enfrentarme a Effie por un colgante maldito, pero me doy cuenta de lo descabellado que suena eso incluso antes de murmurar la opción."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1808
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_a41390c9:

    # "Does Marion even know Effie? Even if she does, I would have to explain how I know Effie. And then I would sound like a madman accusing a young girl of witchcraft."
    "¿Conoce Marion a Effie? Incluso si la conoce, tendría que explicarle de qué conozco a Effie. Y entonces sonaría como un loco acusando a una joven de brujería."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1809
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_6f6e839f:

    # "I look back at Marion, who is obviously exhausted, slumped over, and needing sleep."
    "Vuelvo a mirar a Marion, que obviamente está agotada, desplomada y necesitada de sueño."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1813
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_c5f80195:

    # c "I could fetch Gran. Or at least tell her what's happened. Even if she doesn't know how to help, she may have heard of such a condition."
    c "Podría ir a buscar a la abuela. O al menos contarle lo que ha pasado. Incluso si ella no sabe cómo ayudar, puede haber oído hablar de tal condición."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1814
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_eab2e0e7:

    # c "She's been here forever, and Lord knows in her own silly way... she kind of believes the \"auld magicks\" still have some sway over the village."
    c "Ella ha estado aquí desde siempre, y Dios lo sabe, a su manera tonta... ella cree que las \"viejas magias\" todavía tienen cierta influencia sobre la aldea."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1815
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_ebf3c84a:

    # c "At least that's what she'd have you believe, if you listen to all her superstitions."
    c "Al menos eso es lo que te quiere hacer creer, si haces caso a todas sus supersticiones."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1818
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_405ce512:

    # g "Malcolm, I know you're trying to help. Your Gran would probably be very understanding. But let's give Marion some time alone. Maybe this... maybe it will clear up on its own."
    g "Malcolm, sé que estás tratando de ayudar. Tu abuela probablemente sería muy comprensiva. Pero démosle a Marion algo de tiempo a solas. Tal vez esto... tal vez se aclare por sí solo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1820
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_d6285997:

    # "I believe myself to be mad even thinking of asking Miss Alana for help right now. She'd blame me for this in a flash, I just know it."
    "Creo que estoy loco incluso pensando en pedir ayuda a la señorita Alana ahora mismo. Ella me culparía de esto en un instante, lo sé."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1821
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_1ae53fff:

    # "But who else is more invested in these girls? Who else is more often accused of witchcraft? Certainly she would know something of the ills affecting Marion right now."
    "¿Pero quién más se interesa por estas chicas? ¿Quién más es acusado más a menudo de brujería? Ciertamente ella sabría algo de los males que afectan a Marion en este momento."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1822
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_01052e02:

    # "But I stop myself. I don't want to upset Marion any more, and Alana's... indelicate tendencies are apt to only make things worse right now."
    "Pero me detengo. No quiero enfadar más a Marion, y las tendencias poco delicadas de Alana sólo pueden empeorar las cosas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1824
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_e72e0cbc:

    # m "Malcolm, I... I need to sleep. I can't think anymore."
    m "Malcolm, yo... Necesito dormir. No puedo pensar más."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1828
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_64fe06aa:

    # g "What about Balgair? He knows everything!"
    g "¿Y Balgair? ¡Él lo sabe todo!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1829
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_88a6b5bd:

    # c "Oddly enough, I was thinking the same thing. Even if he doesn't have a cure, he certainly has the \"medicine\" to help calm your nerves."
    c "Curiosamente, yo estaba pensando lo mismo. Aunque no tenga una cura, seguro que tiene la "medicina" que te ayuda a calmar los nervios."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1831
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_8a461618:

    # m "Oh, my heavens! No! I can't have him see me like this!"
    m "¡Oh, cielos! ¡No! ¡No puedo dejar que me vea así!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1833
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_9f8b7848:

    # g "Oh, please, Marion. He's seen Jessie shaking every inch of herself. Your floppy ears are hardly a shock to his sore eyes!"
    g "Por favor, Marion. Ha visto a Jessie sacudiendo cada centímetro de sí misma. ¡Tus orejas caídas no son un shock para sus ojos doloridos!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1834
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_624bf1ad:

    # c "Grace!"
    c "Grace!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1836
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_db7328c3:

    # g "I'm trying to make her feel better, Malcolm."
    g "Estoy tratando de hacerla sentir mejor, Malcolm."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1838
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_0745b51a:

    # m "I... I want to crawl into bed. I can't think anymore. I need sleep."
    m "Yo... Quiero meterme en la cama. No puedo pensar más. Necesito dormir."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1842
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_7b2748be:

    # g "You should probably go now. I don't think Marion is up for analysis right now. She needs some rest. Or at least a glass of something strong. I believe I do, too."
    g "Probablemente deberías irte ya. No creo que Marion esté para análisis en este momento. Necesita descansar. O al menos un vaso de algo fuerte. Creo que yo también."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1843
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_05b9d6cf:

    # "Grace points to the door, and my body involuntarily starts shaking. I knew I would have to leave, but this feels sudden."
    "Grace señala la puerta y mi cuerpo empieza a temblar involuntariamente. Sabía que tendría que irme, pero esto es repentino."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1844
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_4b5da1e5:

    # c "Marion? I don't... I don't know what's happening. I'm {i}so{/i} sorry. I'll be by later, I promise."
    c "¿Marion? No... no sé qué está pasando. Lo siento {i}mucho{/i}. Estaré más tarde, lo prometo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1845
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_d58bc866:

    # "Marion is all but deaf to my voice."
    "Marion está casi sorda a mi voz."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1846
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_b3118c3f:

    # g "Malcolm, one of us will come fetch you...."
    g "Malcolm, una de nosotras irá a buscarte...."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1849
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_2fd11da9:

    # "Grace turns to Marion, who is now curled up and weeping. My heart tightens, and I want desperately to take away her sadness."
    "Grace se vuelve hacia Marion, que ahora está acurrucada y llorando. Se me aprieta el corazón y deseo desesperadamente quitarle la tristeza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1850
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_fc5d4eab:

    # c "Thank you, Grace. Please do. As soon as possible, any time of day or night."
    c "Gracias, Grace. Por favor, hágalo. Tan pronto como sea posible, a cualquier hora del día o de la noche."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1852
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_2acf7e90:

    # "I kiss Marion atop her head, as she stifles her tears. I can't bear to see her like this."
    "Beso a Marion en la cabeza mientras ella reprime las lágrimas. No puedo soportar verla así."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1854
translate Spanish ch2m_06_a_74c46e95:

    # "Grace gives me the most sympathetic look she can muster, and I trust that Marion is at least in good hands."
    "Grace me lanza la mirada más comprensiva que puede reunir y confío en que Marion al menos esté en buenas manos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1875
translate Spanish ch2m_07_3515a33f:

    # "The front door closes gently behind me, as my head keeps spinning."
    "La puerta principal se cierra suavemente detrás de mí, mientras mi cabeza sigue dando vueltas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1876
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a8b24717:

    # "I'm too troubled by the morning's events to return home, where I know I will either take to drink, or suffer through more of Gran's gossip talk... which would also lead me to drink."
    "Estoy demasiado preocupado por los acontecimientos de la mañana como para regresar a casa, donde sé que tomaré o sufriré más los chismes de mi abue... lo que también me llevaría a beber."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1877
translate Spanish ch2m_07_8d8306c8:

    # "Instead, I hop back atop Hazel towards town to clear my head on some things... and think long and hard on others."
    "En lugar de eso, vuelvo a subir a Hazel en dirección a la ciudad para aclarar algunas cosas... y pensar largo y tendido en otras."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1882
translate Spanish ch2m_07_ac24fc85:

    # "The fresh air and chance to clear my head are much needed. The wind blows lightly, and the sun shines high. It would be a beautiful day, if only I were sharing it with Marion."
    "El aire fresco y la oportunidad de despejarme son muy necesarios. El viento sopla suave y el sol brilla en lo alto. Sería un día precioso, si lo compartiera con Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1883
translate Spanish ch2m_07_5639d4c4:

    # "I urge Hazel to quicken her pace, feel my breathing deepen, and we ride along the beaten path, unsure where the day will take us now."
    "Insto a Hazel a que acelere el paso, siento que mi respiración se hace más profunda y cabalgamos por el camino trillado, sin saber adónde nos llevará ahora el día."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1884
translate Spanish ch2m_07_da2a2500:

    # "I should head home to work on the crumbled sections of wall. Gran will be upset with me. But I just can't shake the thought of Marion with her horns and tail. I can't unsee her crying."
    "Debería irme a casa a trabajar en los trozos de pared derrumbados. La abuela se enfadará conmigo. Pero no puedo dejar de pensar en Marion con sus cuernos y su cola. No puedo dejar de verla llorar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1886
translate Spanish ch2m_07_922d7c95:

    # "But those adorable floppy ears... That cute swishing tail..."
    "Pero esas adorables orejas caídas... Esa linda cola..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1888
translate Spanish ch2m_07_6eb8afa9:

    # "Malcolm! What are you thinking?! It's not normal! She needs {i}help!{/i}"
    "¡Malcolm! ¡¿Qué estás pensando?! ¡No es normal! ¡Necesita {i}ayuda!{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1889
translate Spanish ch2m_07_448391b0:

    # "She seemed so helpless, but so... well, herself. Still enchanting and sweet. Still so grounded and rational as her whole world is changing."
    "Parecía tan indefensa, pero tan... bueno, ella misma. Sigue siendo encantadora y dulce. Sigue siendo tan sensata y racional mientras todo su mundo está cambiando."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1896
translate Spanish ch2m_07_34c7b660:

    # "Hazel carries me onward, and before I know it we are crossing the bridge back into town. The picnic has ended and a few others are filtering back into Ach-na-Creige, too."
    "Hazel me lleva en volandas y, antes de que me dé cuenta, estamos cruzando el puente de vuelta al pueblo. El picnic ha terminado y algunas otras personas también están volviendo a Ach-na-Creige."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1899
translate Spanish ch2m_07_01e062ae:

    # "Despite my best efforts to avoid a daytime swig, my resolve is wavering. Marion might not be up for a dose of the pub's remedy, but I certainly find myself in need."
    "A pesar de mis esfuerzos por evitar un trago diurno, mi determinación flaquea. Puede que a Marion no le apetezca una dosis del remedio del bar, pero a mí sí me hace falta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1900
translate Spanish ch2m_07_417101f7:

    # "When Hazel and I reach the pub, I detour myself into the quiet, musty place."
    "Cuando Hazel y yo alcanzo a ver la taberna, me desvío hacia el lugar tranquilo y mohoso."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1902
translate Spanish ch2m_07_00ff3f03:

    # "Despite my best efforts to avoid a daytime swig, my resolve is wavering. When we reach the pub, I detour myself into the quiet, musty place."
    "A pesar de mis esfuerzos por evitar un trago diurno, mi determinación flaquea. Cuando llegamos a la taberna, me desvío hacia el interior del silencioso y húmedo local."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1917
translate Spanish ch2m_07_06e562d0:

    # "It's nearly silent, with no customers, and without Jessie crooning center stage. Balgair has already returned from the picnic and is tending bar."
    "Está casi en silencio, sin clientes y sin Jessie canturreando en el centro del escenario. Balgair ya ha vuelto del picnic y está atendiendo el bar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1919
translate Spanish ch2m_07_6e961353:

    # b "Ahoy, lad! Enjoy the company this morn'?"
    b "¡Ah, muchacho! Disfrutaste de la compañía esta mañana?."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1920
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c2dd3f1e:

    # c "Was a bit crowded for me."
    c "Estaba un poco lleno para mí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1922
translate Spanish ch2m_07_1009f630:

    # b "And yer lady?"
    b "¿Y tu chica?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1923
translate Spanish ch2m_07_f75524b9:

    # c "Aye. Miss MacLeod had a bit of the vapors."
    c "Sí. La señorita MacLeod estaba un poco exaltada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1925
translate Spanish ch2m_07_f19265fa:

    # b "I see, I see. I know how women get. Timid as a mouse at times."
    b "Ya veo. Sé cómo se ponen las mujeres. Tímidas como un ratón a veces."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1926
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c243c3a2:

    # c "Or stubborn as a bull."
    c "O tercas como un toro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1928
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a9d987aa:

    # b "Oh, boy! A grumpy lady? I'll have ye know that I've seen my fair share of women that are hard to get. Even the most pigheaded can be ones worth sticking around for!"
    b "¡Vaya! ¿Una mujer gruñona? Te haré saber que he visto mi parte justa de mujeres que son difíciles de conseguir. ¡Incluso las más testarudas pueden ser aquellas por las que vale la pena quedarse!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1930
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b296a479:

    # b "Er, not to say Miss MacLeod is pigheaded. Nay, she's an angel in disguise. Forgive her a few persnickety days, Mr. Campbell. We all have our faults, even auld man Balgair here."
    b "No quiero decir que la Srta. MacLeod sea testaruda. No, es un ángel disfrazado. Perdónela por algunos días quisquillosos, Sr. Campbell. Todos tenemos nuestros defectos, incluso el viejo Balgair."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1931
translate Spanish ch2m_07_f4004f86:

    # "I laugh and agree, not knowing where I stand with Marion, either way."
    "Me río y le doy la razón, sin saber a qué atenerme con Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1943
translate Spanish ch2m_07_2d04e65d:

    # "Balgair draws me a pint, and I steal into a corner table. I down the first half in one long drink. When I finally look up, a familiar pair of eyes meets mine."
    "Balgair me sirve una pinta y me siento en una mesa de la esquina. Me tomé la primera mitad de un trago largo. Cuando finalmente levanto la vista, un par de ojos familiares se encuentran con los míos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1953
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c2d43b04:

    # e "Hello, Malcolm."
    e "Hola, Malcolm."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1956
translate Spanish ch2m_07_9bfcfd65:

    # "Effie looks as charming as ever, but today I am not so easily disarmed. Is it more than happenstance that she show up so soon after me contemplating paying her a visit?"
    "Effie parece tan encantadora como siempre, pero hoy no me desarmo tan fácilmente. ¿Es más que casualidad que aparezca tan pronto después de que yo contemple la posibilidad de hacerle una visita?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1957
translate Spanish ch2m_07_5a8a1e3e:

    # "I nod politely and try to swallow my suspicions down with another gulp of beer."
    "Asiento cortésmente e intento tragarme mis sospechas con otro trago de cerveza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1959
translate Spanish ch2m_07_429c6b88:

    # "Effie looks as charming as ever, but today I am not so easily disarmed. I nod politely and try to swallow my suspicions down with another gulp of beer."
    "Effie parece tan encantadora como siempre, pero hoy no me desarmo tan fácilmente. Asiento cortésmente e intento tragarme mis sospechas con otro trago de cerveza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1961
translate Spanish ch2m_07_91a71481:

    # e "Nice to see you here."
    e "Me alegro de verte por aquí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1962
translate Spanish ch2m_07_709a88d0:

    # c "Is it?"
    c "¿Ah, sí?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1965
translate Spanish ch2m_07_939c8641:

    # e "Mind if I join you?"
    e "Te importa si me uno a ti?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1966
translate Spanish ch2m_07_526a5dde:

    # c "I don't suppose I can say no, can I?"
    c "Supongo que no puedo decir que no, ¿verdad?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1975
translate Spanish ch2m_07_7b70da7b:

    # "She slides in next to me. Balgair piles empty pint glasses on a tray and heads to the backroom, leaving Effie and me briefly alone in the pub."
    "Se desliza a mi lado. Balgair apila los vasos de pinta vacíos en una bandeja y se dirige a la trastienda, dejándonos a Effie y a mí brevemente solos en la taberna."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1977
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b096d138:

    # e "I wouldn't say no if I were you. There's something you need to know."
    e "Yo no diría que no si fuera tú. Hay algo que debes saber."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1978
translate Spanish ch2m_07_f2b0af92:

    # "My eyebrow lifts a fraction. Effie was at the picnic today. She was there when I bought the charm. What hasn't she told me?"
    "Levanto una ceja. Effie estuvo hoy en el picnic. Estaba allí cuando compré el amuleto. ¿Qué es lo que no me ha contado?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1979
translate Spanish ch2m_07_d11ac620:

    # c "Effie, did you see anything strange today?"
    c "Effie, ¿has visto algo extraño hoy?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1981
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b33dda03:

    # "She starts to nod her head. Then I think further."
    "Empieza a asentir con la cabeza. Entonces pienso más."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1982
translate Spanish ch2m_07_4fb39639:

    # c "No. First tell me... why were you so keen on sending me off with that charm?"
    c "No. Primero dime... ¿por qué tenías tanto interés en enviarme con ese amuleto?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1984
translate Spanish ch2m_07_4e7051e7:

    # e "Charm? Oh, the trinket? The silver cowbell? 'Twas but a silly charm. I knew Marion would like it."
    e "¿Amuleto? ¿El amuleto? ¿El cencerro de plata? No era más que un tonto amuleto. Sabía que a Marion le gustaría."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1990
translate Spanish ch2m_07_e49d00da:

    # "I know I don't look convinced. Balgair comes over, rag in hand, wiping clean his burly hands."
    "Sé que no parezco convencido. Balgair se acerca, trapo en mano, limpiándose sus fornidas manos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1991
translate Spanish ch2m_07_2b77c46d:

    # b "Another round, boy?"
    b "Otra ronda, chico?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:1992
translate Spanish ch2m_07_20baf1e5:

    # "I glance at Effie."
    "Miro a Effie."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1993
translate Spanish ch2m_07_abb40e0f:

    # c "Make it two."
    c "Que sean dos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1996
translate Spanish ch2m_07_f9c8c3b9:

    # b "That's a lad! But..."
    b "Eso es un muchacho! Pero..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:1999
translate Spanish ch2m_07_cf17ee08:

    # "He bends down to whisper in my ear."
    "Se inclina para susurrarme al oído."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2001
translate Spanish ch2m_07_f9848946:

    # b "No good deed, son. No good deed..."
    b "Ninguna mala acción, hijo. Ninguna mala acción..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2003
translate Spanish ch2m_07_ce95c86b:

    # "I'm flummoxed as he strolls behind the bar until I realize that it must look odd me sitting here with another girl."
    "Me quedo perpleja mientras se pasea detrás de la barra hasta que me doy cuenta de que debo de parecer raro sentado aquí con otra chica."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2004
translate Spanish ch2m_07_27adae3d:

    # "I haven't it in me to explain the situation. The beer will help most assuredly. Then I'll be on my way."
    "No tengo fuerzas para explicar la situación. La cerveza ayudará con toda seguridad. Entonces seguiré mi camino."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2005
translate Spanish ch2m_07_3e465c0b:

    # c "Well, out with it, then. What do I \"need to know?\""
    c "Bueno, entonces déjalo. \"Qué necesito saber?\""

# game/script_marion.rpy:2013
translate Spanish ch2m_07_1d608f7a:

    # "Effie opens her mouth to speak, but pauses as Balgair returns to set the pints down on the table. I grab one, and guzzle."
    "Effie abre la boca para hablar, pero se detiene cuando Balgair vuelve a dejar las pintas sobre la mesa. Cojo una y me la bebo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2014
translate Spanish ch2m_07_da61b2d9:

    # b "Enjoy! I'm off to empty the buckets. If you need me, just holler."
    b "¡Que aproveche! Me voy a vaciar los cubos. Si me necesitas, solo grita."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2017
translate Spanish ch2m_07_6e0a4821:

    # "I slide the beer over to Effie, but she raises a hand in protest."
    "Le acerco la cerveza a Effie, pero ella levanta una mano en señal de protesta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2018
translate Spanish ch2m_07_41cfeabc:

    # e "You'll need them both."
    e "Necesitarás los dos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2019
translate Spanish ch2m_07_1ecec1f5:

    # c "Why, thank you."
    c "Vaya, gracias."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2020
translate Spanish ch2m_07_48da0393:

    # "I've already finished the second pint, and dive into the third. My head appreciates them now, even if it's bound to punish me later."
    "Ya he terminado la segunda pinta y me zambullo en la tercera. Mi cabeza lo agradece ahora, aunque luego me castigue."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2022
translate Spanish ch2m_07_4f09ad33:

    # e "Malcolm, Marion has more to think about than a trifle given to her by an admirer. Even if he is a handsome admirer."
    e "Malcolm, Marion tiene más en qué pensar que una bagatela que le regaló un admirador. Incluso si es un admirador guapo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2023
translate Spanish ch2m_07_8d9bb814:

    # c "You saw..."
    c "Tu viste..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2025
translate Spanish ch2m_07_25c54bb8:

    # e "The tail? Yes. The ears too. Dainty little things, I'll give her that."
    e "¿La cola? Sí. Las orejas también. Pequeñas cosas delicadas, lo reconozco."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2026
translate Spanish ch2m_07_669c19c5:

    # "Effie knows. And she's not surprised, either. My gut clenches, doubly cautious now of the woman next to me. Could it be true...?"
    "Effie lo sabe. Y tampoco se sorprende. Se me revuelven las tripas, doblemente cautelosa ahora con la mujer que tengo al lado. ¿Podría ser verdad...?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2027
translate Spanish ch2m_07_48273be1:

    # c "Tell me... do you know how can I help her?"
    c "Dime... ¿sabes cómo puedo ayudarla?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2029
translate Spanish ch2m_07_ba4cfe1c:

    # e "Help? Ha. No, there's nothing to help. Except in matters of the heart."
    e "¿Ayuda? Ha. No, no hay nada que ayudar. Excepto en asuntos del corazón."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2030
translate Spanish ch2m_07_70a15431:

    # "Effie's taken on quite a caustic tone."
    "Effie ha adquirido un tono bastante cáustico."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2031
translate Spanish ch2m_07_df5dfb9b:

    # c "I'd argue that's a strong matter."
    c "Yo diría que es un asunto importante."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2034
translate Spanish ch2m_07_bc2bdeef:

    # e "It is. I... I'm just not feeling myself today. You'll have to forgive me."
    e "Lo es. Yo... No me siento yo misma hoy. Tendrás que perdonarme."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2038
translate Spanish ch2m_07_e73039f4:

    # "I see a sadness in her eyes that needs appeasing. I'm three pints in, and Balgair strolls by with another."
    "Veo una tristeza en sus ojos que hay que apaciguar. Llevo tres pintas y Balgair se acerca con otra."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2039
translate Spanish ch2m_07_94c72987:

    # b "Slow down, my boy. That'll be yer last 'til I see ye walk a straight line to the bar your own self. Important conversation, eh?"
    b "Despacio, muchacho. Será la última hasta que te vea caminar en línea recta hasta el bar. Una conversación importante, ¿eh?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2040
translate Spanish ch2m_07_596c01cb:

    # c "I dare say, Balgair."
    c "Me atrevo a decir, Balgair."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2042
translate Spanish ch2m_07_83019d51:

    # e "That it is."
    e "Eso es."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2046
translate Spanish ch2m_07_9951860f:

    # "He winks at me, and casually glances at my hat on the table as he walks off. Effie reaches for it, but I yank it back and place it atop my head."
    "Me guiña un ojo y, mientras se marcha, me mira el sombrero que tengo sobre la mesa. Effie lo coge, pero yo lo retiro y me lo pongo en la cabeza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2048
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a1836358:

    # c "For... forget the hat! What in blazes have you come here for? Out with it."
    c "Para... ¡olvida el sombrero! ¿Para qué demonios has venido aquí? Sácalo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2063
translate Spanish ch2m_07_5b3985cc:

    # "Balgair whips around."
    "Balgair se da la vuelta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2064
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b08cac17:

    # b "Y'all right there, Malcolm?"
    b "¿Estás ahí, Malcolm?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2065
translate Spanish ch2m_07_7f09f05e:

    # "I'm slurring my speech, and Effie looks alarmed. She takes a deep breath and gathers herself."
    "Estoy arrastrando las palabras y Effie parece alarmada. Respira hondo y se recompone."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2079
translate Spanish ch2m_07_d6bb4164:

    # "Her outline looks faded as my vision glazes over. I sip the next pint, needing to slow my frenzied mind."
    "Su contorno parece desdibujado mientras mi vista se nubla. Doy un sorbo a la siguiente pinta, necesito ralentizar mi mente frenética."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2080
translate Spanish ch2m_07_91c34900:

    # c "Fine, Balgair. Ne'er been better!"
    c "Bien, Balgair. ¡Nunca he estado mejor!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2094
translate Spanish ch2m_07_7c96f51d:

    # "I turn to face Effie, and find my body slumping over in the seat. She continues in a hushed tone."
    "Me giro para mirar a Effie y veo que mi cuerpo se desploma en el asiento. Continúa en voz baja."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2095
translate Spanish ch2m_07_14daeec3:

    # e "I came here because {i}you{/i} wanted to understand! Listen, I don't have all the answers, but..."
    e "¡Vine aquí porque {i}tú{/i} querías entender! Escucha, no tengo todas las respuestas, pero..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2107
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b55d1cb8:

    # "She wrings her hands and rubs at her eyes under her glasses. When she looks back at me, her face takes on a distinct appearance, that of resolute composure."
    "Se retuerce las manos y se frota los ojos bajo las gafas. Cuando me devuelve la mirada, su rostro adquiere un aspecto distinto, el de una compostura resuelta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2108
translate Spanish ch2m_07_21015b7f:

    # "Something I am lacking in all capacity at the moment."
    "Algo de lo que carezco de toda capacidad en este momento."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2109
translate Spanish ch2m_07_7d07df45:

    # e "What do you know of spirits?"
    e "¿Qué sabes de los espíritus?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2110
translate Spanish ch2m_07_be328802:

    # "I lift my drink, smirking."
    "Levanto la copa y sonrío."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2112
translate Spanish ch2m_07_9959902c:

    # e "No, definitely not that type of spirit. Listen. Your friend Marion is different."
    e "No, definitivamente no es ese tipo de espíritu. Escucha. Tu amiga Marion es diferente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2113
translate Spanish ch2m_07_d6072769:

    # "I hiccup, but give pause."
    "Tengo hipo, pero hago una pausa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2114
translate Spanish ch2m_07_529fb9de:

    # c "I'll say."
    c "Ya lo creo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2116
translate Spanish ch2m_07_1e3db3a9:

    # e "She'll be fine. She {i}is{/i} fine. Marion is..."
    e "Ella estará bien. Ella {i}está{/i} bien. Marion es..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2118
translate Spanish ch2m_07_439083fb:

    # "Effie stops talking, and scratches her head. Her floppy hat wobbles back and forth."
    "Effie deja de hablar y se rasca la cabeza. Su sombrero flexible se tambalea de un lado a otro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2119
translate Spanish ch2m_07_4cf9ec44:

    # e "Marion and I may be kindred spirits."
    e "Puede que Marion y yo seamos almas gemelas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2121
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a8898941:

    # "Effie stops talking, and I start to drift off. Her words immediately make both all the sense in the world, and no sense at all."
    "Effie deja de hablar y yo empiezo a perder el sentido. Sus palabras tienen todo el sentido del mundo y a la vez ningún sentido."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2122
translate Spanish ch2m_07_66344432:

    # "Seems like everything today is a mystery. A riddle. Effie is sounding more like Alana than herself, but if she has any reasonable answers, I feel obligated to find out."
    "Parece que hoy todo es un misterio. Un acertijo. Effie está sonando más como Alana que como ella misma, pero si tiene alguna respuesta razonable, me siento obligada a averiguarla."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2124
translate Spanish ch2m_07_81eabc29:

    # c "I need more than that! {i}More!{/i}"
    c "¡Necesito más que eso! {i}¡Más!{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2128
translate Spanish ch2m_07_6f069753:

    # "Balgair rushes over."
    "Balgair se acerca corriendo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2129
translate Spanish ch2m_07_5e6260c4:

    # b "Lad, you're gonna hafta keep it down. The pastor has stopped in for a Virgin Mary. Keep it hushed or take it outside."
    b "Muchacho, vas a tener que bajar la voz. El pastor ha venido a por una Virgen María. Mantenlo en silencio o llévalo afuera."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2130
translate Spanish ch2m_07_49dcca64:

    # "Now that he mentions it, I do spy the holy man in the corner, sipping a blood red cocktail, eyeing me with concern."
    "Ahora que lo menciona, veo al santón en la esquina, bebiendo un cóctel rojo sangre, mirándome con preocupación."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2132
translate Spanish ch2m_07_4b94ef93:

    # b "You know I love ya, but the shouting's after hours behavior and you know it. Don't make me send for your Gran."
    b "Sabes que te quiero, pero los gritos son fuera de horario y lo sabes. No me hagas llamar a tu abuela."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2134
translate Spanish ch2m_07_6d76b595:

    # e "It's fine, Malcolm. Probably for the best if we continue this conversation somewhere else, anyway."
    e "Está bien, Malcolm. Probablemente sea lo mejor si continuamos esta conversación en otro lugar, de todos modos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2136
translate Spanish ch2m_07_8f1f342c:

    # "I sigh, which leads into a deep cough smelling of hops. Balgair pats my back with sympathy."
    "Suspiro, lo que me provoca una profunda tos con olor a lúpulo. Balgair me palmea la espalda con simpatía."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2137
translate Spanish ch2m_07_32457b81:

    # c "All right. I'm fine, {i}I'm fine.{/i} I'll go."
    c "Está bien. Estoy bien, {i}Estoy bien.{/i} Me iré."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2138
translate Spanish ch2m_07_ade4a858:

    # "I'm assuredly not fine. I've never been kicked out of a pub before, much less during daylight hours."
    "Seguro que no estoy bien. Nunca me habían echado de una taberna, y menos de día."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2149
translate Spanish ch2m_07_e40df5de:

    # "It's a challenge keeping steady as I get to my feet. I wobble my way to the door, and Effie follows not far behind."
    "Me resulta difícil mantenerme en pie. Me tambaleo hacia la puerta y Effie me sigue de cerca."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2156
translate Spanish ch2m_07_37e9f4a9:

    # "Outside, the sun burns my eyes. Effie has sidled up beside me."
    "Fuera, el sol me quema los ojos. Effie se ha arrimado a mi lado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2157
translate Spanish ch2m_07_31433701:

    # e "Come. Follow me."
    e "Ven. Sígueme."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2169
translate Spanish ch2m_07_13a9e616:

    # "I follow blindly, having lost track of time. We end up seated on a stone wall situated on a hill above the town. After a moment, it registers where we are."
    "Le sigo a ciegas, habiendo perdido la noción del tiempo. Acabamos sentados en un muro de piedra situado en una colina sobre el pueblo. Al cabo de un momento, me doy cuenta de dónde estamos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2170
translate Spanish ch2m_07_66bd17e0:

    # "The site of this morning's picnic, where this whole dream—nightmare?—started. Now deserted, the hillside takes on a much more peaceful character."
    "El lugar del picnic de esta mañana, donde empezó todo este sueño-pesadilla? Ahora desierta, la ladera adquiere un carácter mucho más apacible."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2178
translate Spanish ch2m_07_7139d012:

    # e "Malcolm... well, I'm not entirely sure you're prepared to hear this—"
    e "Malcolm... bueno, no estoy seguro de que estés preparado para oír esto..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2180
translate Spanish ch2m_07_4e6444df:

    # c "Just say it already! My God... keep speaking in ambiguities and I'll stand convinced you and Alana are cut from the same cloth!"
    c "¡Dilo de una vez! Dios mío... ¡sigue hablando con ambigüedades y me convenceré de que tú y Alana estáis cortados por el mismo patrón!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2182
translate Spanish ch2m_07_1a05b709:

    # e "I don't..."
    e "Yo no..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2183
translate Spanish ch2m_07_6dd605f3:

    # "Effie shakes her head and gathers herself again."
    "Effie sacude la cabeza y se recompone."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2184
translate Spanish ch2m_07_f262b5fe:

    # e "Marion looks to be different in ways that may make it impossible for you to find happiness with her."
    e "Marion parece ser diferente en aspectos que pueden hacer imposible que encuentres la felicidad con ella."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2185
translate Spanish ch2m_07_13e550a7:

    # "Instead of answers, I get relationship advice? It raises my hackles."
    "En lugar de respuestas, ¿me dan consejos sobre relaciones? Me pone de los nervios."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2186
translate Spanish ch2m_07_ae97a811:

    # "I don't remember myself getting this angry or riled in some time. I start to see that what I crave is normalcy... and a relationship that feels safe, like home once did."
    "No recuerdo haberme enfadado tanto en mucho tiempo. Empiezo a ver que lo que anhelo es normalidad... y una relación en la que me sienta seguro, como antes en casa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2187
translate Spanish ch2m_07_88bed24f:

    # "Marion feels so much like home, but so far from... I don't dare think it."
    "Marion se siente tan como estar en casa, pero tan lejos de... No me atrevo a pensarlo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2188
translate Spanish ch2m_07_e87e7167:

    # c "You don't know what you're saying. She'll be fine. She needs help, but she'll be all right. She {i}is{/i} all right. She's perfect."
    c "No sabes lo que dices. Se pondrá bien. Necesita ayuda, pero estará bien. Ella está bien. Está perfecta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2189
translate Spanish ch2m_07_71256055:

    # "As I talk, I come more to my senses. Marion {i}is{/i} perfect. She's a brilliant, shining star. Maybe just a shade unlike the rest of us."
    "A medida que hablo, vuelvo más en mí. Marion {i}es{/i}  perfecta. Es una estrella brillante. Tal vez sólo un poco diferente al resto de nosotros."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2191
translate Spanish ch2m_07_636c919c:

    # e "Time will tell, for both of you. Just know that Marion's... condition is something I understand quite well."
    e "El tiempo lo dirá, para ambos. Sólo sé que la condición de Marion es algo que entiendo bastante bien."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2193
translate Spanish ch2m_07_35d25160:

    # "Effie reaches up to her oversized hat, and adjusts the ribbon slowly. From concealed holes fall two similarly oversized, floppy ears."
    "Effie se acerca a su enorme sombrero y ajusta la cinta lentamente. De los agujeros ocultos caen dos orejas igualmente grandes y caídas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2195
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b94378da:

    # "They go erect, and she appears to have turned herself into a human-rabbit hybrid before my eyes."
    "Se ponen rectas, y ella parece haberse convertido ante mis ojos en un híbrido humano-conejo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2208
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_01b91dfd:

    # "I gasp, but don't move an inch, frozen by the sight."
    "Jadeo, pero no me muevo ni un centímetro, congelado por la visión."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2209
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_168c960f:

    # c "Effie! {i}You, too!?{/i}"
    c "Effie! {i}Tú también!?{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2210
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_44f47e62:

    # "Two animal people in one day? I whip my head around to make sure no one can see us. It makes the world spin."
    "¿Dos personas animales en un día? Giro la cabeza para asegurarme de que nadie nos ve. El mundo da vueltas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2211
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_d6c6fbe8:

    # e "This is what you needed to see."
    e "Esto es lo que necesitabas ver."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2212
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_007b6210:

    # c "Me? What about {i}Marion?{/i}"
    c "Yo? ¿Qué hay de {i}Marion?{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2214
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_14e3f683:

    # e "I don't think she'd take kindly to me."
    e "No creo que se lo tome bien conmigo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2215
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_6db33265:

    # c "But... what is going on? How did you get... ears?"
    c "Pero... ¿qué está pasando? ¿Cómo conseguiste... orejas?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2217
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_e967aa00:

    # e "Ha! You have them yourself, Malcolm! Yours are just less..."
    e "¡Ja! ¡Tú también los tienes, Malcolm! Los tuyos son menos..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2218
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_a0e0e645:

    # c "Fluffy?"
    c "¿Esponjosas?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2220
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_f1428a18:

    # e "Aye!"
    e "¡Sí!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2221
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_6abab643:

    # "These ears of hers, they are two new pieces to a puzzle. One I worry I might be solving."
    "Estas orejas suyas, son dos nuevas piezas de un rompecabezas. Uno que me preocupa que pueda estar resolviendo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2222
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_60470c05:

    # "What if this has nothing to do with curses or frivolity, and everything to do with magic? I'm taken back to childhood stories of wonder. This can't be real, though. Can it?"
    "¿Y si esto no tiene nada que ver con maldiciones o frivolidades, y todo que ver con la magia? Me retrotraigo a las historias de maravilla de mi infancia. Pero esto no puede ser real. ¿O sí?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2224
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_9525b8b5:

    # c "Is this all fae doing? Are you... magic, Effie?"
    c "¿Todo esto es obra de los fae? ¿Eres... mágica, Effie?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2226
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_4d968775:

    # e "Magic? Whyever would you ask that?"
    e "¿Magia? ¿Por qué preguntas eso?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2227
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_fe68491e:

    # c "Well.. how long have you had your lovely appendages?"
    c "Bueno... ¿cuánto hace que tienes tus adorables apéndices?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2229
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_84d1ea22:

    # e "Oh, my! As long as I can remember."
    e "¡Vaya! Desde que tengo memoria."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2230
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_4d83d522:

    # "I let that sink in. Born with rabbit ears?"
    "Dejé que lo comprenda. ¿Naciste con orejas de conejo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2231
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_bb2fac02:

    # c "And your family? They, too?"
    c "Y tu familia? ¿Ellos también?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2234
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_7374c3e3:

    # "Effie keeps her gaze on the water."
    "Effie mantiene la mirada fija en el agua."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2235
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_cb60171d:

    # e "I wouldn't know."
    e "No sabría decirte."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2236
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_6896ff86:

    # "My heart drops. I suddenly feel quite guilty for how I've been treating this poor girl. Confusion and frustration are no excuse."
    "Se me cae el alma a los pies. De repente me siento culpable por cómo he tratado a esta pobre chica. La confusión y la frustración no son excusas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2237
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_4d7844d6:

    # c "I... I'm sorry."
    c "Yo... ...lo siento."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2240
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_6e3261ac:

    # e "Malcolm, you asked if I could help Marion."
    e "Malcolm, me preguntaste si podía ayudar a Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2241
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_f79f54da:

    # "Her eyes lock onto mine, and I feel a chill run through me."
    "Sus ojos se clavan en los míos y siento un escalofrío que me recorre."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2243
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_67172b5c:

    # e "The truth is... I wouldn't know how to."
    e "La verdad es que... que no sabría cómo hacerlo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2244
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_739e53b5:

    # c "I don't believe that, Effie. This can't be a coincidence. There's something special about you... about both of you, more than your..."
    c "No me lo creo, Effie. Esto no puede ser una coincidencia. Hay algo especial en ti... en las dos, más que tu..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2245
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_92191746:

    # "I tilt my head, still mesmerized by her ears."
    "Inclino la cabeza, aún hipnotizado por sus orejas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2246
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_c8c7aad8:

    # c "You have a kind heart. One that, indeed, mirrors Marion's."
    c "Tienes un corazón bondadoso. Uno que, de hecho, refleja el de Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2247
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_a41c0890:

    # e "Thank you, Malcolm, but..."
    e "Gracias, Malcolm, pero..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2249
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_25fe12a0:

    # "Once more she looks away, and I fear I will not get any more answers. Certainly not the ones I want."
    "Una vez más aparta la mirada y me temo que no obtendré más respuestas. Desde luego, no las que yo quiero."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2250
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_5fc67ef5:

    # e "If you're asking for guidance about magic, I have little to offer but proof of its existence. My advice is, take matters into your own hands, Malcolm."
    e "Si pides orientación sobre magia, no tengo mucho que ofrecer, salvo pruebas de su existencia. Mi consejo es que tomes el asunto en tus manos, Malcolm."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2252
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_02db2e24:

    # e "Accept reality, but welcome the unexpected. Tell Marion the same. It's magic that gives us the strength to do that."
    e "Acepta la realidad, pero da la bienvenida a lo inesperado. Dile lo mismo a Marion. Es la magia la que nos da la fuerza para hacerlo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2262
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_4d263173:

    # "Effie starts to step away from me and our conversation. I want to stop her just as much as I want to see her gone."
    "Effie empieza a alejarse de mí y de nuestra conversación. Tengo tantas ganas de detenerla como de que se vaya."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2263
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_6602e020:

    # c "Wait! I..."
    c "Espera! Yo..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2264
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_01b6987a:

    # "I open my mouth in protest, but close it and choke down every complaint, fear, question."
    "Abro la boca para protestar, pero la cierro y ahogo cada queja, cada miedo, cada pregunta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2272
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_734e3ab8:

    # e "If you need me, I'll be here. But we can't avoid our fates, Malcolm. Not Marion, not you, not me."
    e "Si me necesitas, estaré aquí. Pero no podemos evitar nuestros destinos, Malcolm. Ni Marion, ni tú, ni yo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2274
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_a9a0a52d:

    # "She gives me one last smile before walking off down the path, turning only to say one thing."
    "Me dedica una última sonrisa antes de alejarse por el sendero, volviéndose sólo para decirme una cosa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2275
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_a6699869:

    # e "Whit's fur ye'll..."
    e "Lo que es para ti sucederá..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2277
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_c74213ce:

    # "As she disappears, I mutter under my breath..."
    "Mientras desaparece, murmuro en voz baja..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2278
translate Spanish ch2m_07_a_82a2bdf4:

    # c "...no go past ye."
    c "...y no te pasará desapercibido."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2283
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_0747ac36:

    # "For a brief, sober moment, I stare, entranced. Then the dam breaks, the clarity is sloshed away, and I burst into laughter."
    "Durante un breve y sobrio instante, me quedo mirando, absorto. Entonces se rompe el hielo, la claridad se desvanece y estallo en carcajadas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2284
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_e5d8a99f:

    # c "Hahaha! You, too, then!"
    c "¡Jajaja! Tú también, entonces!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2286
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_eddbf5a1:

    # "She looks a bit deflated, as if I've let her down somehow."
    "Parece un poco desanimada, como si la hubiera defraudado de alguna manera."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2287
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_c8ae77ed:

    # e "Malcolm, this is {i}real.{/i} A part of me. Apparently, it's who your friend Marion is, as well."
    e "Malcolm, esto es {i}real.{/i} Una parte de mí. Aparentemente, también es quien es tu amiga Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2288
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_f2f2cde8:

    # c "I'm drunk. I must be hallucinating... this whole day... it's... you're..."
    c "Estoy borracho. Debo estar alucinando... todo este día... es... estás..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2293
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_bfb3557a:

    # "My hands lift towards her head, but she pulls away."
    "Levanto las manos hacia su cabeza, pero ella se aparta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2295
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_8d1bad3a:

    # e "Malcolm! No matter how handsome a gentlemen, you can't just go around touching a young rabbit's ears!"
    e "¡Malcolm! ¡No importa lo guapo que sea un caballero, no puede ir por ahí tocándole las orejas a una joven coneja!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2296
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_b0f2baf7:

    # c "But they're so sweet. So... soft."
    c "Pero son tan tiernas. Tan... suaves."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2306
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_c1224b3b:

    # "Through the haze, it hits me. What if Effie is ashamed of them as Marion? How rude must I look? I stand frozen, alarmed and frightened, unsure what to do next."
    "A través de la confusión, me doy cuenta. ¿Y si Effie se avergüenza de ellas como Marion? ¿Tengo que parecer grosero? Me quedo paralizado, alarmado y asustado, sin saber qué hacer."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2308
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_2f6fc14a:

    # "...Then I remember, the whole thing is probably just an alcohol-fueled illusion."
    "...Entonces recuerdo, todo esto es probablemente sólo una ilusión alimentada por el alcohol."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2309
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_30a71260:

    # c "Real, you say? People don't turn into animals! This is preposte...prepostipous. Prerostipous. Crazy. The whole day's been crazy. Effie... you're a kind girl, one I want to trust, but this..."
    c "¿Real, dices? ¡La gente no se convierte en animales! Esto es absu. Absurd... Una locura. Todo el día ha sido una locura. Effie... eres una chica amable, en la que quiero confiar, pero esto..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2311
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_ee3b9914:

    # "As I talk, and vocalize the lunacy, I believe myself to be sobering up, coming more to my senses. Effie interrupts."
    "A medida que hablo y vocalizo la locura, creo que se me pasa la borrachera, que recobro la cordura. Effie interrumpe."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2312
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_30027bb0:

    # e "If you won't listen to me... if you don't {i}believe{/i} me, at least tell Marion that she is fine. She... will be fine. Tell her that. Not for me... for her."
    e "Si no me escuchas... si no me crees, al menos dile a Marion que está bien. Ella... estará bien. Dile eso. No por mí... por ella."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2313
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_fd6ccd0e:

    # c "Why not tell her yourself?"
    c "¿Por qué no se lo dices tú misma?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2315
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_50ad7a35:

    # e "I don't believe I would be any help."
    e "No creo que sea de ayuda."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2316
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_25dbc0fa:

    # c "Why tell me, then?"
    c "¿Por qué decírmelo, entonces?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2318
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_8b6c2b0e:

    # e "I want Marion to know she will be all right, that she is normal."
    e "Quiero que Marion sepa que estará bien, que es normal."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2319
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_f0c0f61c:

    # c "And you call these normal?"
    c "¿Y a esto lo llamas normal?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2321
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_fac87149:

    # "I trace two invisible lines up from my ears. She looks hurt, and I immediately regret it."
    "Trazo dos líneas invisibles desde mis orejas. Parece dolida, y me arrepiento de inmediato."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2322
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_75cabfd4:

    # e "She is still Marion. And... I'm still Effie."
    e "Sigue siendo Marion. Y... Yo sigo siendo Effie."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2323
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_ae7ca033:

    # c "I know, I know."
    c "Lo sé, lo sé."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2325
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_6816c97d:

    # "But in reality, I know nothing anymore. What even is reality? I pinch myself, as if in a childhood dream. I wince, and Effie takes notice."
    "Pero en realidad, ya no sé nada. ¿Qué es la realidad? Me pellizco, como en un sueño infantil. Hago una mueca de dolor y Effie se da cuenta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2326
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_0553d92c:

    # e "Are you all right?"
    e "Te encuentras bien?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2327
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_540023ba:

    # c "No. Not one bit."
    c "No. Ni un poco"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2329
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_4b7c0512:

    # e "I didn't mean to startle you so, but I thought this might happen. I'm only trying to reassure you. Please believe me."
    e "No quería asustarte así, pero pensé que esto podría pasar. Sólo intento tranquilizarte. Por favor, créeme."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2331
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_e1485a1c:

    # c "I do. Effie, I really do. I just can't comprehend all that has changed. It's a blur. All so sudden."
    c "Te creo. Effie, de verdad. Es sólo que no puedo comprender todo lo que ha cambiado. Está borroso. Todo tan repentino."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2333
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_afb573a4:

    # e "I understand. Much of my world is a haze of events, too."
    e "Lo comprendo. Gran parte de mi mundo es una neblina de acontecimientos, también."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2334
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_1824b4b0:

    # c "Every memory I have now.... I will question them all. As will Marion."
    c "Cada recuerdo que tengo ahora.... Los cuestionaré todos. Al igual que Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2336
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_fe1083a8:

    # e "It's okay to soften your focus. To look through a foggy lens. Sometimes we need a little less sharpness in our lives."
    e "Está bien suavizar el enfoque. Mirar a través de una lente empañada. A veces necesitamos un poco menos de nitidez en nuestras vidas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2337
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_954dabd2:

    # c "However do you mean? I've never craved clarity more."
    c "Sin embargo, ¿a qué te refieres? Nunca he anhelado tanto la claridad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2339
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_8120d773:

    # e "The fog makes you pay attention, makes you look for the good, for all that you want to see. And..."
    e "La niebla te hace prestar atención, te hace buscar lo bueno, todo lo que quieres ver. Y..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2344
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_482386d4:

    # "Effie takes a step back, and I fear she is leaving, all before I can ask her more."
    "Effie da un paso atrás y temo que se vaya, todo antes de que pueda preguntarle más."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2346
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_2b1b6ab2:

    # e "It dulls all the visions of what you wish not to see."
    e "Atenúa todas las visiones de lo que no deseas ver."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2353
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_67211f5c:

    # "She waves demurely, and starts to walk off."
    "Saluda con la mano y se marcha."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2354
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_5e592c67:

    # c "Effie, wait—"
    c "Effie, espera-"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2362
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_8c7acb70:

    # e "I'll find you, should you need me. But remember, no amount of whisky will wash away your fate, Malcolm. Nor Marion's, nor mine. Whit's fur ye'll..."
    e "Te encontraré, si me necesitas. Pero recuerda, ninguna cantidad de whisky borrará tu destino, Malcolm. Ni el de Marion, ni el mío. Lo que es para ti sucederá"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2364
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_c74213ce:

    # "As she disappears, I mutter under my breath..."
    "Mientras desaparece, murmuro en voz baja..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2365
translate Spanish ch2m_07_b_82a2bdf4:

    # c "...no go past ye."
    c "...y no te pasará desapercibido."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2370
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_cd1b03e2:

    # c "No. Nonono."
    c "No. Nonono."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2371
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_5896bfa1:

    # "I shake my head and the world spins."
    "Sacudo la cabeza y el mundo da vueltas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2372
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_63fe7257:

    # c "What in the... Effie, are you mocking me? Are you mocking... {i}Marion{/i}?"
    c "¿Qué demonios...? Effie, ¿te estás burlando de mí? ¿Te estás burlando de... {i}Marion{/i}?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2374
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_1424df95:

    # "The words come out as barely a squeak. Effie looks hurt, insulted."
    "Las palabras salen apenas como un chillido. Effie parece dolida, insultada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2375
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_cbe905cb:

    # e "Quite the contrary. Marion is like me... somehow."
    e "Todo lo contrario. Marion es como yo... de alguna manera."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2376
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_ffec5780:

    # "Two... animal people? {i}In one day?{/i} It can't be. I'm dizzied from the day's events, and from three... four? Well, from several pints to drink. I hesitate to trust my own eyes."
    "¿Dos... personas animales? {i}En un día?{/i} No puede ser. Estoy mareado por los eventos del día, y por tres... ¿cuatro? Bueno, de varias pintas de beber. Dudo en confiar en mis propios ojos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2379
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_a9e73c00:

    # "My hands reach of their own accord toward those rabbit ears, but she shrinks away, looking timid as the first day I saw her."
    "Mis manos se dirigen por sí solas hacia esas orejas de conejo, pero ella se aparta, con el mismo aspecto tímido que el primer día que la vi."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2389
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_21a5d564:

    # c "And... just what {i}are{/i} you?"
    c "Y... qué eres tú?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2392
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_def41997:

    # e "I am the fairy tales your grandparents told you. Or one grain of truth."
    e "Soy los cuentos de hadas que te contaban tus abuelos. O un grano de verdad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2394
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_638609a9:

    # c "Oh, really? You are a living, breathing fairy tale, eh? I guess that makes me... what? A fairy prince? A hobgoblin? Do tell."
    c "¿En serio? Eres un cuento de hadas viviente, ¿eh? Supongo que eso me convierte en... ¿qué? ¿Un príncipe de hadas? ¿Un hobgoblin? Dímelo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2395
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_c858b75b:

    # "My blood starts boiling. How dare she ridicule sweet Marion?"
    "Me hierve la sangre. ¿Cómo se atreve a ridiculizar a la dulce Marion?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2397
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_ae77d43c:

    # e "If you won't listen to me... if you don't {i}believe{/i} me, at least tell Marion that she is fine. She... will be fine. I know you will leave here and see her."
    e "Si no me escuchas... si no me crees, al menos dile a Marion que está bien. Ella... estará bien. Sé que saldrás de aquí y la verás."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2398
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_bf59bd52:

    # c "And inform her that she's stuck this way, like you told me? That we're all part of a fairy tale, now?"
    c "¿Y decirle que se ha quedado así, como me dijiste? ¿Que ahora todos somos parte de un cuento de hadas?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2400
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_6753e02a:

    # e "She deserves to know!"
    e "Merece saberlo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2401
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_014ccb9c:

    # c "What else would you have me tell her? That it will get worse?"
    c "¿Qué más quieres que le diga? ¿Que empeorará?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2403
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_7aa52e52:

    # "Effie goes silent, and won't meet my eyes."
    "Effie se calla y no me mira a los ojos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2404
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_4edaec91:

    # c "...{i}Will{/i} it get worse?"
    c "...¿{i}se{/i} pondrá peor?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2405
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_72a33094:

    # e "..."
    e "..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2407
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_9861235e:

    # e "You make it sound like a disease. I don't know what to tell you. This is who we {i}are.{/i}"
    e "Haces que suene como una enfermedad. No sé qué decirte. Esto es lo que {i}somos.{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2414
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_082f46fc:

    # c "I'm sorry. I didn't mean it like that. It's just... Marion is so scared right now."
    c "Lo siento. No quise decir eso. Es que... Marion está tan asustada ahora mismo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2415
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_a6fbec12:

    # c "The last thing she needs is someone to tell her that she's... if she is, in fact... turning into a cow."
    c "Lo último que necesita es que alguien le diga que... si es que, de hecho... se está convirtiendo en una vaca."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2416
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_baf4a12f:

    # "My voice shrivels away as I can barely believe what I am saying."
    "Se me va la voz y apenas puedo creer lo que digo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2417
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_389cccc5:

    # e "Malcolm. She is still Marion. And... I'm still Effie."
    e "Malcolm. Ella sigue siendo Marion. Y... Yo sigo siendo Effie."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2419
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_6d5469a1:

    # "It's all just too much for me to digest. My head is pounding, and the inevitable hangover hasn't even started yet."
    "Es demasiado para digerirlo. Me duele la cabeza y aún no ha empezado la inevitable resaca."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2421
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_04351d52:

    # c "She needs help, Effie. I don't know what's going on, but there's got to be a way to return her to normal."
    c "Necesita ayuda, Effie. No sé qué está pasando, pero tiene que haber una forma de devolverla a la normalidad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2424
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_082f46fc_1:

    # c "I'm sorry. I didn't mean it like that. It's just... Marion is so scared right now."
    c "Lo siento. No quise decir eso. Es que... Marion está tan asustada ahora mismo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2425
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_a6fbec12_1:

    # c "The last thing she needs is someone to tell her that she's... if she is, in fact... turning into a cow."
    c "Lo último que necesita es que alguien le diga que... si es que, de hecho... se está convirtiendo en una vaca."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2426
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_baf4a12f_1:

    # "My voice shrivels away as I can barely believe what I am saying."
    "Se me va la voz y apenas puedo creer lo que digo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2427
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_389cccc5_1:

    # e "Malcolm. She is still Marion. And... I'm still Effie."
    e "Malcolm. Ella sigue siendo Marion. Y... Yo sigo siendo Effie."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2429
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_6d5469a1_1:

    # "It's all just too much for me to digest. My head is pounding, and the inevitable hangover hasn't even started yet."
    "Es demasiado para digerirlo. Me duele la cabeza y aún no ha empezado la inevitable resaca."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2431
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_14f539a3:

    # "There's no way I'm going to bother Marion again today. Not in her state... certainly not in mine."
    "De ninguna manera voy a molestar a Marion de nuevo hoy. No en su estado... ciertamente no en el mío."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2432
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_ce1e0784:

    # c "No more. I'm sorry, but I must bid ye a fine day. I need to clear my head."
    c "No más. Lo siento, pero debo desearte un buen día. Necesito aclarar mis ideas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2433
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_887f2c73:

    # c "Effie, I do wish you well. But if you won't help... then I ask you not to meddle in Miss MacLeod's business, nor mine."
    c "Effie, te deseo lo mejor. Pero si no quieres ayudar... entonces te pido que no te metas en los asuntos de la Señorita MacLeod, ni en los míos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2435
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_3c3650d0:

    # "Her face goes stoic."
    "Su rostro se vuelve rígido."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2436
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_405e52ca:

    # e "Malcolm, I've learned to endure hardship with little to no complaint. I refuse to let myself be called a liar."
    e "Malcolm, he aprendido a soportar las dificultades sin apenas quejarme. Me niego a que me llamen mentirosa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2437
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_a59492cc:

    # e "Be on your way if you must, but once you come back to your senses, you'll want me around. On that, I'll stake a bet."
    e "Sigue tu camino si es necesario, pero una vez que vuelvas a tus cabales, me querrás cerca. Apuesto a que sí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2446
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_e5bea4ae:

    # "Effie doesn't allow me the honor of escaping the conversation first. Instead, she takes off in a huff, only turning to offer one rebuttal."
    "Effie no me permite el honor de escapar primero de la conversación. En lugar de eso, se marcha enfadada y sólo se vuelve para rebatirme."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2454
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_a6699869:

    # e "Whit's fur ye'll..."
    e "Lo que es para ti sucederá..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2456
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_97e5863d:

    # "She keeps storming off, and I mutter under my breath..."
    "Se va enfadada y yo murmuro en voz baja..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2457
translate Spanish ch2m_07_c_82a2bdf4:

    # c "...no go past ye."
    c "...y no te pasará desapercibido"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2484
translate Spanish ch2m_08_d5bd348a:

    # "In a stupor, I throw myself into my labors for nearly two days, stopping only to empty several gallon jugs of water, and my bladder."
    "Con estupor, me lanzo a mis labores durante casi dos días, parando sólo para vaciar varias garrafas de agua y mi vejiga."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2485
translate Spanish ch2m_08_e18f4b12:

    # "Gran's concern quickly becomes apparent. There's fear in her tone with which I'm not familiar. But I don't know what to tell her, so I say little at all."
    "La preocupación de abue no tarda en hacerse evidente. Hay un miedo en su tono con el que no estoy familiarizado. Pero no sé qué decirle, así que no digo nada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2486
translate Spanish ch2m_08_9b65dfcd:

    # "She leaves me alone for a time, but I can see it eats at her. While I should be placating her worry, I know I'm only making it worse."
    "Me deja en paz durante un tiempo, pero veo que le preocupa. Aunque debería aplacar su preocupación, sé que sólo la empeoraría."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2497
translate Spanish ch2m_08_9946ffd7:

    # "Eventually I hobble into the kitchen and drink another large pitcher of water. The aches within me dissipate slowly, and I see Gran's shadow by the table."
    "Finalmente, cojeo hasta la cocina y bebo otra jarra grande de agua. Los dolores dentro de mí se disipan lentamente y veo la sombra de mi Abue junto a la mesa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2498
translate Spanish ch2m_08_a4496dcd:

    # s "Are you well?"
    s "Estás bien?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2499
translate Spanish ch2m_08_c18ebd79:

    # c "Decidedly not, Gran. With apologies."
    c "Decididamente no, abue. Con mis disculpas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2501
translate Spanish ch2m_08_f3e445e8:

    # s "No need. I hate seeing you upset. My best guess was that you received a broken heart, and didn't need your old Gran meddling in your affairs."
    s "No es necesario. Odio verte molesto. Mi mejor suposición fue que recibiste un corazón roto, y no necesitabas a tu vieja abuela entrometiéndose en tus asuntos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2502
translate Spanish ch2m_08_9379ad62:

    # c "Gran, you are always welcome to meddle."
    c "Abue, siempre eres bienvenida a entrometerte."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2520
translate Spanish ch2m_08_27ec4016:

    # "I give her a huge hug, and my heart starts to feel lighter... though I still can't quiet my brain. Over some tea and toast, I ask her what's on my mind."
    "Le doy un abrazo enorme y mi corazón comienza a sentirse más ligero... aunque todavía no puedo calmar mi cerebro. Mientras tomamos un té y unas tostadas, le pregunto qué tengo en mente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2521
translate Spanish ch2m_08_83daa93c:

    # c "Gran, do you happen to know a girl in town named Effie? She's petite, a bit of a skittish sort. Brown hair, large spectacles."
    c "Abue, ¿por casualidad conoces a una chica en la ciudad llamada Effie? Es pequeña, un poco asustadiza. Pelo castaño, gafas grandes."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2523
translate Spanish ch2m_08_b657515b:

    # s "Oh, let me wrack my old brain. Brown hair? Glasses? How old?"
    s "Oh, déjame estrujar mi viejo cerebro. ¿Pelo castaño? ¿Gafas? ¿Cuántos años?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2524
translate Spanish ch2m_08_b3b206b2:

    # c "I'd say she's about my age. Maybe a tad younger? Can't say for sure."
    c "Diría que tiene más o menos mi edad. ¿Tal vez un poco más joven? No puedo asegurarlo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2526
translate Spanish ch2m_08_93272180:

    # s "No, no. It's the name that doesn't ring a bell."
    s "No, no. Es el nombre lo que no me suena."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2527
translate Spanish ch2m_08_c084b9d7:

    # s "The description sounds a bit like Maggie Tyte's oldest, Gemma, but she's anything but petite. Half the size of a bull steer, I reckon."
    s "La descripción suena un poco a Gemma, la mayor de Maggie Tyte, pero es todo menos pequeña. La mitad del tamaño de un novillo, supongo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2528
translate Spanish ch2m_08_862bdb96:

    # c "That's fine, Gran."
    c "Está bien, abue."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2530
translate Spanish ch2m_08_0ee7f0dd:

    # s "Who is she, this Effie?"
    s "Quién es, esta Effie?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2531
translate Spanish ch2m_08_ce9d9247:

    # c "Well, that's hard to say. I've bumped into her in town several times. She's social, friendly, but a bit too chatty if you ask me."
    c "Bueno, es difícil de decir. Me la he encontrado varias veces en la ciudad. Es sociable, simpática, pero demasiado charlatana, en mi opinión."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2533
translate Spanish ch2m_08_de83ce26:

    # "Gran's face drops as if realizing something."
    "La cara de la abuela cae como si se diera cuenta de algo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2534
translate Spanish ch2m_08_8c4537c5:

    # s "You don't have eyes for her, do you? Miss Marion would not take a liking to that."
    s "No tienes ojos para ella, ¿verdad? A la Señorita Marion no le gustaría."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2535
translate Spanish ch2m_08_930a3d32:

    # c "Rest assured, Effie does not have my gaze. Nor does Marion know about her. I was simply asking, Gran."
    c "Ten por seguro que Effie no tiene mi mirada. Ni Marion sabe de ella. Simplemente preguntaba, abuela."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2537
translate Spanish ch2m_08_43715d57:

    # s "You know who may know her... Balgair. Jessie would have, too, were she still here."
    s "Sabes quién puede conocerla... Balgair. Jessie también lo habría hecho, si aún estuviera aquí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2538
translate Spanish ch2m_08_37452e9d:

    # c "Mm. Well, I may ask around."
    c "Mm. Bueno, puede que pregunte por ahí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2539
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bddfd24f:

    # "I hesitate before asking the next question, thinking how to phrase it properly."
    "Dudo antes de hacer la siguiente pregunta, pensando cómo formularla adecuadamente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2541
translate Spanish ch2m_08_e3f78c5a:

    # s "...You're fiddlin' with your toast, Malcolm. What's it done to harm ye?"
    s "...estás jugueteando con tu tostada, Malcolm. ¿Qué daño te ha hecho?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2542
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bbf82068:

    # c "Oh—I'm sorry, Gran. 'Pologies to you as well, pumpernickel. I... um..."
    c "Oh... lo siento, abue. Mis disculpas también para ti, pan integral de centeno. Yo... um..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2543
translate Spanish ch2m_08_a5e8d1c4:

    # "I take a deep breath."
    "Respiro hondo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2544
translate Spanish ch2m_08_d7be981f:

    # c "Gran, do you actually {i}believe{/i} in magic? Like... magical sorts of things? I've heard you talk about it frequently, and don't know for sure if it's in jest."
    c "Abuela, ¿realmente {i}crees{/i} en la magia? ¿En... cosas mágicas? Te he oído hablar de ello con frecuencia y no sé si es en broma."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2546
translate Spanish ch2m_08_db6fbd6e:

    # s "Well, that's an odd one for the morn', but not the oddest I've heard at this hour."
    s "Bueno, es algo extraño para esta mañana, pero no el más extraño que he escuchado a esta hora."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2550
translate Spanish ch2m_08_8683d229:

    # "Gran frowns then smiles, clasping her hands together. I'm more taken aback at how forthright she is in answering than in hearing the answer itself."
    "La abuela frunce el ceño y luego sonríe, juntando las manos. Me sorprende más la franqueza con que responde que la respuesta en sí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2551
translate Spanish ch2m_08_aebcd6e2:

    # s "There's much that can't be explained, my boy. Magic? Faerie mischief? Witchcraft? It has many names, and comes in as many forms as there are stories about it."
    s "Hay muchas cosas que no se pueden explicar, muchacho. ¿Magia? ¿Maldades de hadas? ¿Brujería? Tiene muchos nombres y adopta tantas formas como historias hay sobre ella."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2552
translate Spanish ch2m_08_f90cfc8a:

    # s "I can't say for sure what I believe, but I believe in something."
    s "No puedo decir con seguridad en qué creo, pero creo en algo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2554
translate Spanish ch2m_08_b26f072f:

    # "She pauses and starts laughing out loud."
    "Hace una pausa y empieza a reírse a carcajadas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2555
translate Spanish ch2m_08_4bac88cc:

    # s "You know, I wished for a pair of faerie wings as a child! What a thing!"
    s "Sabes, yo deseaba un par de alas de hada cuando era niña! Qué cosa!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2556
translate Spanish ch2m_08_68604bad:

    # c "I can't say I blame you. Would be a treasure, no?"
    c "No puedo decir que te culpo. Sería un tesoro, ¿no?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2558
translate Spanish ch2m_08_ce3b0427:

    # "I sip my tea and watch my grandmother's eyes sparkle, beginning to understand why it cheers her so to see me happy."
    "Doy un sorbo a mi té y observo cómo brillan los ojos de mi abuela, empezando a entender por qué le alegra tanto verme feliz."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2559
translate Spanish ch2m_08_16e79e8c:

    # c "I only ask because I have... a friend..."
    c "Sólo pregunto porque tengo... un amigo..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2561
translate Spanish ch2m_08_b5e00e81:

    # s "Miss Marion?"
    s "La joven Marion?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2562
translate Spanish ch2m_08_ceb86bb2:

    # "Gran narrows her eyes."
    "La abuela entrecierra los ojos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2563
translate Spanish ch2m_08_f8338ec5:

    # c "We ought not be mad at her. She's... well, it would be a right challenge to explain, Gran."
    c "No deberíamos enfadarnos con ella. Ella es... bueno, sería todo un reto explicarlo, abue."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2565
translate Spanish ch2m_08_b98393ab:

    # s "You're asking if there's magic involved? Between a man and a woman? Aye, always!"
    s "Preguntas si hay magia de por medio? ¿Entre un hombre y una mujer? Sí, siempre!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2566
translate Spanish ch2m_08_c339cc71:

    # c "It's... something like that, I suppose."
    c "Es... algo así, supongo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2568
translate Spanish ch2m_08_75c79c68:

    # s "Who knows, Malcolm. It's like church, like the way I see my religion... just go with it."
    s "Quién sabe, Malcolm. Es como la iglesia, como la forma en que veo mi religión... sólo déjate llevar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2570
translate Spanish ch2m_08_1752c0c6:

    # s "I don't always know what to believe anymore! Is there a gentleman in the sky looking down on us? Perhaps not."
    s "Ya no siempre sé qué creer. ¿Hay un señor en el cielo mirándonos? Puede que no."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2572
translate Spanish ch2m_08_a66027bf:

    # s "But the mysteries of the world—and the heart—are often unsolvable, and best left to a greater power."
    s "Pero los misterios del mundo -y del corazón- son a menudo irresolubles, y es mejor dejarlos en manos de un poder mayor."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2573
translate Spanish ch2m_08_d880158b:

    # s "One that you and I know nothing of, but can only guess... Although it never hurts to trust in something better than ourselves."
    s "Uno del que tú y yo no sabemos nada, sólo podemos adivinar... Aunque nunca está de más confiar en algo mejor que nosotros mismos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2575
translate Spanish ch2m_08_93da388c:

    # s "The faults of man are inexplicable at times. Wanting magic, or whatever ye call it, to fix those wrongs, is quite understandable."
    s "Los defectos del hombre son a veces inexplicables. Querer que la magia, o como se llame, arregle esos males, es bastante comprensible."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2577
translate Spanish ch2m_08_9465e906:

    # c "Gran, you never fail to surprise me. I can't tell you how much that means."
    c "Abue, nunca dejas de sorprenderme. No sabes lo mucho que significa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2579
translate Spanish ch2m_08_ed125864:

    # "A knock on the door comes as Gran offers one last bit of advice."
    "Llaman a la puerta y la abuela da un último consejo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2581
translate Spanish ch2m_08_227a4f32:

    # s "Whether you call it God or a Faerie King, we all want it to solve our problems. But in my experience, it rarely will."
    s "Llámese Dios o Rey de las Hadas, todos queremos que resuelva nuestros problemas. Pero, según mi experiencia, rara vez lo hace."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2585
translate Spanish ch2m_08_34d39f2d:

    # s "Sometimes we're just on our own... and that's perfectly all right. Take matters into your own hands, Malcolm."
    s "A veces estamos solos... y eso está perfectamente bien. Toma el asunto en tus manos, Malcolm."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2593
translate Spanish ch2m_08_897f5d1e:

    # "Gran heads to the door. A few seconds later, her voice calls out to me."
    "La abuela se dirige a la puerta. Unos segundos después, su voz me llama."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2597
translate Spanish ch2m_08_19ae0913:

    # s "Malcolm! A friend is here to see you."
    s "¡Malcolm! Un amigo está aquí para verte."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2608
translate Spanish ch2m_08_fc14452c:

    # "Standing in the open threshold is Marion. Her smile is faint but visible. She shines still, brighter than any moonglow."
    "En el umbral abierto está Marion. Su sonrisa es tenue pero visible. Sigue brillando, más que cualquier resplandor de luna."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2617
translate Spanish ch2m_08_7cc1e34a:

    # "Gran walks past me, and heads to her room, whispering in my ear."
    "La abuela pasa a mi lado y se dirige a su habitación, susurrándome al oído."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2619
translate Spanish ch2m_08_cb761c81:

    # s "{size=22}Lemme know if she needs a good whomping.{/size}"
    s "{size=22}Avísame si necesita una buena paliza.{/size}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2622
translate Spanish ch2m_08_a332c375:

    # "I laugh. Even though I'm blinded by fear—and Marion's misty-eyed face—I'm comforted by Gran's humor. It's certainly what I'll need to get by."
    "Me río. Aunque estoy cegado por el miedo -y por la cara empañada de Marion-, el humor de la abuela me reconforta. Sin duda es lo que necesitaré para salir adelante."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2624
translate Spanish ch2m_08_6e6ae3fb:

    # "There Marion and I stand, face to face, a few steps apart."
    "Allí estamos Marion y yo, frente a frente, a unos pasos de distancia."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2625
translate Spanish ch2m_08_ba61915f:

    # c "Please, come in."
    c "Por favor, pasa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2626
translate Spanish ch2m_08_7859549f:

    # "My, she couldn't look more lovely. Peaceful, even."
    "No podría estar más encantadora. Incluso pacífica."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2628
translate Spanish ch2m_08_d39f2f00:

    # m "Do you... do you mind stepping outside? I don't believe your Gran wants me around."
    m "¿Te... te importaría salir? No creo que tu abuela me quiera cerca."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2629
translate Spanish ch2m_08_2ea2328d:

    # c "Oh! Yes, of course."
    c "¡Oh! Sí, claro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2634
translate Spanish ch2m_08_0de88b5e:

    # "We walk to the stone wall where we sat just days earlier. Marion's heady lilac scent fills the air around us."
    "Caminamos hasta el muro de piedra donde nos sentamos días antes. El embriagador aroma a lilas de Marion inunda el aire que nos rodea."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2642
translate Spanish ch2m_08_53dbee49:

    # "A bee lands gently on her sleeve, taking a break from its daily rounds to rest its wings. Marion looks at it wistfully."
    "Una abeja se posa suavemente en su manga, haciendo una pausa en su ronda diaria para descansar las alas. Marion la mira con nostalgia."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2643
translate Spanish ch2m_08_fe487c1f:

    # m "At least one creature is happy to see me."
    m "Al menos una criatura se alegra de verme."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2645
translate Spanish ch2m_08_c70001f0:

    # c "More than one, Marion."
    c "Más de una, Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2647
translate Spanish ch2m_08_8d96e500:

    # "I can't help myself. I take her hand in mine, and caress her open palm."
    "No puedo evitarlo. Cojo su mano entre las mías y le acaricio la palma abierta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2648
translate Spanish ch2m_08_0b78d371:

    # c "I've missed you. Oh, how I've missed you!"
    c "Te he echado de menos. ¡Cómo te he echado de menos!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2661
translate Spanish ch2m_08_0a0bc021:

    # "My urge to embrace her is met with hesitation, then enthusiasm. The bee departs for other flowers as I hold her tight, and she squeezes my body back fiercely."
    "Mi impulso de abrazarla es recibido con vacilación, luego con entusiasmo. La abeja se marcha hacia otras flores mientras la abrazo con fuerza, y ella me devuelve el abrazo con fiereza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2674
translate Spanish ch2m_08_500877aa:

    # "We lean into each other, and I kiss her cheek. She pulls back and has tears in her eyes. Tears that I vow to help stop permanently."
    "Nos abrazamos y le beso la mejilla. Se retira y tiene lágrimas en los ojos. Lágrimas que juro ayudar a detener para siempre."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2675
translate Spanish ch2m_08_2838b02b:

    # c "I never want to see you cry, Marion."
    c "No quiero verte llorar nunca, Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2680
translate Spanish ch2m_08_2089228f:

    # "Marion pulls her tail out from her waistband. She adjusts the scarf on her head, and the horns are still there. She is unchanged."
    "Marion se saca la cola de la cintura. Se ajusta el pañuelo en la cabeza y los cuernos siguen ahí. No ha cambiado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2681
translate Spanish ch2m_08_2091804d:

    # "My stomach churns thinking back on my conversation with Effie. How many ways can this scenario play out?"
    "Se me revuelve el estómago al recordar mi conversación con Effie. ¿De cuántas maneras puede desarrollarse este escenario?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2682
translate Spanish ch2m_08_9bd791e2:

    # "Fresh tears fall into her kerchief."
    "Nuevas lágrimas caen sobre su pañuelo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2684
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bdccc95f:

    # m "I've missed you too. Oh, Malcolm, I... I've been better."
    m "Yo también te he echado de menos. Oh, Malcolm, yo... He estado mejor."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2685
translate Spanish ch2m_08_2afa7a75:

    # "Her voice shakes, cracking into a small laugh."
    "Le tiembla la voz y suelta una pequeña carcajada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2687
translate Spanish ch2m_08_88248dd4:

    # m "Well—no, wait. I actually {i}feel{/i} just fine. Can you believe it? More myself, even, if that's possible."
    m "Bueno, no, espera. En realidad {i}me siento bien{/i}. ¿Puedes creerlo? Más yo misma, incluso, si eso es posible."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2688
translate Spanish ch2m_08_1d68b4c0:

    # c "Has anything... changed?"
    c "Algo ha... cambiado?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2690
translate Spanish ch2m_08_7fac5c85:

    # m "No. Grace, bless her, went to the apothecary in Strathcarron. Asked around, delicately. Did some research at the library there."
    m "No. Grace, bendita sea, fue a la botica en Strathcarron. Preguntó por ahí, delicadamente. Hizo algunas investigaciones en la biblioteca de allí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2691
translate Spanish ch2m_08_79ed3212:

    # c "...And?"
    c "...y?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2693
translate Spanish ch2m_08_d86f970c:

    # m "There's nothing. No record of this condition. No guidance on how to fix it. No help to be had."
    m "No hay nada. Ningún registro de esta condición. Ninguna orientación sobre cómo solucionarlo. No hay ayuda."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2695
translate Spanish ch2m_08_5d392fbe:

    # m "She's been measuring the horns and ears four times a day for me. They're not getting any longer, she says, but..."
    m "Me ha estado midiendo los cuernos y las orejas cuatro veces al día. No se están haciendo más largos, dice, pero..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2697
translate Spanish ch2m_08_7af5b705:

    # m "I... I still don't know what to do. But I had to come see you again."
    m "Yo... Todavía no sé qué hacer. Pero tenía que volver a verte."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2698
translate Spanish ch2m_08_0ed3b1da:

    # "My heart melts at her predicament. Despite Effie's words to the contrary, I can't help but think there must be something or someone that can help."
    "Se me encoge el corazón ante su situación. A pesar de las palabras de Effie en sentido contrario, no puedo evitar pensar que debe haber algo o alguien que pueda ayudar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2699
translate Spanish ch2m_08_2df8c093:

    # c "What if we went to the city? Glasgow, Edinburgh, London even—surely someone must know... something?"
    c "¿Y si vamos a la ciudad? Glasgow, Edimburgo, incluso Londres... seguro que alguien sabe... ¿algo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2701
translate Spanish ch2m_08_d10236df:

    # m "But how can I ever go in the public again? With a tail and floppy ears? Just think of the stares I'll get! It doesn't matter how I feel, if I'm going to be ridiculed or shunned!"
    m "Pero, ¿cómo voy a volver a ir en público? ¿Con rabo y orejas caídas? Piensa en las miradas que me echarán. No importa cómo me sienta, ¡si me van a ridiculizar o a rechazar!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2703
translate Spanish ch2m_08_f7fba7cc:

    # m "The laughing, the jabs, the whispers. What on earth will people say about me? I can't show my face in public ever again!"
    m "Las risas, las burlas, los susurros. ¿Qué diablos dirá la gente de mí? No puedo volver a mostrar mi cara en público."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2705
translate Spanish ch2m_08_0b4ca193:

    # "Marion plays gently at the little nubs on her head, and I can't take my eyes off of her. I stay positive, hoping for the best."
    "Marion juega suavemente con las pequeñas protuberancias de su cabeza y yo no puedo apartar los ojos de ella. Me mantengo positivo, esperando lo mejor."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2706
translate Spanish ch2m_08_f3639c58:

    # c "It's possible you'll change back."
    c "Es posible que vuelvas a cambiar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2708
translate Spanish ch2m_08_86ab8b07:

    # m "But when, Malcolm?"
    m "Pero cuándo, Malcolm?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2709
translate Spanish ch2m_08_d79ee174:

    # c "I don't know. But..."
    c "No lo sé. Pero..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2716
translate Spanish ch2m_08_ee2e3dad:

    # "I stroke her hair, and push a lock behind her new, softer ear."
    "Le acaricio el pelo y empujo un mechón detrás de su nueva oreja, más suave."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2717
translate Spanish ch2m_08_fb8b08c0:

    # c "What do you think about me sticking by your side? While we get through this. While you... while we adjust?"
    c "¿Qué te parece si me quedo a tu lado? Mientras superamos esto. ¿Mientras tú... mientras nos adaptamos?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2719
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bbd27f57:

    # m "...We?"
    m "...Nosotros?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2720
translate Spanish ch2m_08_04c50468:

    # "Marion has a look of disbelief, and I don't feel as though I need to reassure her further."
    "Marion pone cara de incredulidad, y no siento que tenga que tranquilizarla más."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2726
translate Spanish ch2m_08_0d068452:

    # m "I honestly think I would like that. I'd like it very much. Is that... possible?"
    m "Sinceramente, creo que me gustaría. Me gustaría mucho. ¿Es eso... posible?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2727
translate Spanish ch2m_08_0c27ded8:

    # c "There's a you. There's a me. We're an \"us!\""
    c "Hay un tú. Hay un yo. Somos un \"nosotros!\"."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2728
translate Spanish ch2m_08_c39b902f:

    # "By keeping the mood light, I'm trying to alleviate some of her stress."
    "Manteniendo el ánimo ligero, intento aliviar parte de su estrés."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2730
translate Spanish ch2m_08_1e59bfd4:

    # m "Malcolm, do you think I could show..."
    m "Malcolm, ¿crees que podría mostrar..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2731
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bff0b458:

    # "She pats her head."
    "Se da palmaditas en la cabeza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2733
translate Spanish ch2m_08_6b96d35d:

    # m "...this, to your Gran? I can tell she already knows something's amiss, and I can't bear deceiving her. She's always been so good to me."
    m "...esto, a tu abuela? Puedo decir que ella ya sabe que algo anda mal, y no puedo soportar engañarla. Siempre ha sido tan buena conmigo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2734
translate Spanish ch2m_08_2385a088:

    # c "Of course! I'm sure in all her years she's seen stranger things than this. Plus she's always got a piece of advice, whether it's needed or not!"
    c "¡Claro que sí! Seguro que en todos sus años ha visto cosas más raras que esta. Además, siempre tiene un consejo, ¡se necesite o no!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2736
translate Spanish ch2m_08_1941e3fe:

    # m "Like... drink less milk?"
    m "Como... beber menos leche?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2737
translate Spanish ch2m_08_8cf0664e:

    # "Marion smiles weakly. I laugh and reassure her."
    "Marion sonríe débilmente. Me río y la tranquilizo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2738
translate Spanish ch2m_08_2f43914d:

    # c "Believe it or not, sometimes her wisdom is even wise. Stay right here, I'll get her."
    c "Lo creas o no, a veces su sabiduría es incluso sabia. Quédate aquí, voy a buscarla."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2748
translate Spanish ch2m_08_2a2d37e2:

    # "I walk back to the house, where it is strangely quiet. Had Gran gone to bed? I swing the door open and hear a yelp."
    "Vuelvo a la casa, que está extrañamente silenciosa. ¿Se habrá acostado la abuela? Abro la puerta y oigo un aullido."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2749
translate Spanish ch2m_08_1fa1e3d5:

    # s "Ouch! Malcolm!"
    s "Ouch! Malcolm!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2750
translate Spanish ch2m_08_e02b47b6:

    # "Gran is caught between the door and wall."
    "La abuela está atrapada entre la puerta y la pared."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2751
translate Spanish ch2m_08_071a4c45:

    # c "Oh, no! Are you all right? I'm so sorry."
    c "¡Oh, no! ¿Estás bien? Lo siento mucho."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2758
translate Spanish ch2m_08_2c850616:

    # s "I'm fine... and I wasn't snooping, I tell ye!"
    s "Estoy bien... ¡y no estaba fisgoneando, te lo digo yo!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2759
translate Spanish ch2m_08_ec5a2ebb:

    # "A likely story. I roll my eyes."
    "Una historia probable. Pongo los ojos en blanco."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2760
translate Spanish ch2m_08_f3b2662b:

    # c "Come with me. Marion and I need a bit of your good advice."
    c "Ven conmigo. Marion y yo necesitamos un poco de tu buen consejo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2762
translate Spanish ch2m_08_4a649d54:

    # s "Aye, now {i}that's{/i} what I'm here for."
    s "Sí, ahora {i}eso{/i} es por lo que estoy aquí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2780
translate Spanish ch2m_08_6c460aae:

    # "I bring Gran to the stone wall, where Marion is sitting and fidgeting with her skirt. When Marion stands to receive Gran, Gran is a bit reluctant to greet her."
    "Llevo a la abuela hasta el muro de piedra, donde Marion está sentada jugueteando con su falda. Cuando Marion se levanta para recibir a la abuela, ésta se muestra un poco reacia a saludarla."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2781
translate Spanish ch2m_08_4d48d406:

    # s "Hello, Marion."
    s "Hola, Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2782
translate Spanish ch2m_08_913d0751:

    # "Gran sounds stern and off-putting, an unusual tone to hear from such a normally genial woman. I'm now worried that Marion's reveal may upset her."
    "Abue suena severa y desagradable, un tono inusual en una mujer tan amable. Ahora me preocupa que la revelación de Marion pueda molestarla."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2783
translate Spanish ch2m_08_1ee4a453:

    # m "Hello, Mrs. Campbell."
    m "Hola, Sra. Campbell."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2785
translate Spanish ch2m_08_75e5ea5e:

    # "Gran relaxes."
    "Abue se relaja."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2786
translate Spanish ch2m_08_1e8aebb0:

    # s "Always Agnes, dear. No need for formalities here... even under the circumstances."
    s "Siempre Agnes, querida. No hay necesidad de formalidades aquí... incluso dadas las circunstancias."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2788
translate Spanish ch2m_08_6da29fdc:

    # m "Wh... what circumstances?"
    m "Qu... qué circunstancias?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2789
translate Spanish ch2m_08_32cf5c35:

    # "Marion looks to me for an answer."
    "Marion me mira en busca de una respuesta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2790
translate Spanish ch2m_08_9cb005ba:

    # c "Marion, my Gran here believes you have left me heartbroken. Perhaps we can set her straight on the matter."
    c "Marion, mi abuela cree que me has dejado con el corazón roto. Tal vez podamos aclararle el asunto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2792
translate Spanish ch2m_08_53527905:

    # m "Oh... oh, my. My apologies, Agnes. I... didn't mean... I would never hurt Malcolm. Not intentionally. He's much too dear to my heart."
    m "Oh... oh, Dios. Mis disculpas, Agnes. Yo... no quise decir... Nunca lastimaría a Malcolm. No intencionalmente. Él es demasiado querido para mi corazón."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2793
translate Spanish ch2m_08_269c3f0a:

    # "Just hearing those words make my heart beat faster, and the plea must have softened Gran's heart, as well."
    "Sólo con oír esas palabras se me acelera el corazón, y la súplica debe de haber ablandado también el de la abuela."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2795
translate Spanish ch2m_08_386617e1:

    # s "Oh! Miss Marion! You're a love, aren't you? Come here to Agnes!"
    s "¡Oh! ¡Señorita Marion! Eres un amor, ¿verdad? ¡Ven aquí con Agnes!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2802
translate Spanish ch2m_08_aaf55cba:

    # "Gran pulls Marion in close, a bit too fast. Marion holds onto Gran for dear life as she is smothered in affection."
    "Abue se acerca a Marion demasiado rápido. Marion se aferra a la abuela con todas sus fuerzas, asfixiada por el afecto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2803
translate Spanish ch2m_08_c9dfe088:

    # "Unfortunately, Marion's kerchief goes askew, and Gran reaches for it as she releases Marion."
    "Desgraciadamente, el pañuelo de Marion se tuerce y la abuela lo coge al soltar a Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2806
translate Spanish ch2m_08_0e021d67:

    # s "Oh... my... goodness... gracious..."
    s "Oh... mi... Dios... misericordioso..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2807
translate Spanish ch2m_08_4b616920:

    # "Marion tries to put the kerchief back on, but it's too late. The horns and cow ears are out in the open."
    "Marion intenta volver a ponerse el pañuelo, pero es demasiado tarde. Los cuernos y las orejas de vaca están al descubierto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2814
translate Spanish ch2m_08_19fb4b58:

    # s "A bit early for the Heifer Parade, don't you think?"
    s "Un poco pronto para el desfile de vaquillas, ¿no crees?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2815
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bf4587ca:

    # "I intervene."
    "Intervengo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2816
translate Spanish ch2m_08_4944f1ff:

    # c "Herein lies the need for your customary good counsel, Gran. It seems as though Marion has sprouted a new set of..."
    c "Aquí yace la necesidad de tu acostumbrado buen consejo, abuela. Parece que a Marion le ha salido un nuevo par de..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2818
translate Spanish ch2m_08_65eadd97:

    # s "Fashionable headwear."
    s "Sombreros a la moda."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2820
translate Spanish ch2m_08_96d6e7b3:

    # m "That's one way to put it."
    m "Es una forma de decirlo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2822
translate Spanish ch2m_08_810ec1be:

    # s "Oh, Marion. When did this happen? Are you feeling all right?"
    s "Oh, Marion. ¿Cuándo ocurrió esto? ¿Te encuentras bien?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2823
translate Spanish ch2m_08_11c87be5:

    # "Gran and Marion go through a similar conversation to the one shared with Grace and myself just days before. From it, very little is decided."
    "La abuela y Marion mantienen una conversación similar a la que compartimos Grace y yo días antes. De ella se decide muy poco."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2825
translate Spanish ch2m_08_40d37285:

    # s "I dare not share any of the fairy stories {i}my{/i} grandmother used to tell me. For every happy ending there is a sinister one."
    s "No me atrevo a compartir ninguno de los cuentos de hadas que me contaba mi abuela. Por cada final feliz hay uno siniestro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2826
translate Spanish ch2m_08_4d23c91f:

    # c "Yes, let's steer clear of that."
    c "Sí, alejémonos de eso."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2827
translate Spanish ch2m_08_85f7b2bb:

    # "I chuckle at my own pun, but see no one else is laughing."
    "Me río de mi propio juego de palabras, pero veo que nadie más se ríe."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2829
translate Spanish ch2m_08_b7227af4:

    # m "Are there no hints, no auld wives' tales that indicate what this could be? It's certainly not something you catch from the herd, or the whole town would have caught it by now!"
    m "¿No hay ninguna pista, ningún cuento de viejas que indique lo que podría ser? Desde luego, no es algo que se coja del rebaño, ¡o ya se habría contagiado todo el pueblo!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2831
translate Spanish ch2m_08_aac63eef:

    # s "Give me a minute. Let me think."
    s "Dame un minuto. Déjame pensar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2833
translate Spanish ch2m_08_f6983609:

    # "Gran gets up and goes inside. She returns carrying a large tome."
    "La abuela se levanta y entra. Vuelve con un gran libro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2847
translate Spanish ch2m_08_ff5830e9:

    # s "Let's consult Baird's!"
    s "¡Consultemos a Baird's!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2848
translate Spanish ch2m_08_82624246:

    # "The florid script upon the cover reads, \"Baird's Unabridged Compendium of Faerie Lore: Rhymes, Myths and Legends of Scotch Tradition.\""
    "La florida letra de la portada reza: \"Compendio Inédito de Tradiciones Fantásticas de Baird: Rimas, Mitos y Leyendas de la Tradición Escocesa.\""

# game/script_marion.rpy:2849
translate Spanish ch2m_08_9eef9b03:

    # c "Gran, where did you get this?"
    c "Abuela, ¿de dónde has sacado esto?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2850
translate Spanish ch2m_08_7318087c:

    # s "Every child grew up with Baird's! It's what got us all to sleep at night, and gave us the willies and shivers."
    s "Todos los niños crecieron con Baird's. Es lo que nos hacía dormir por las noches y nos daba escalofríos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2851
translate Spanish ch2m_08_3d0610bd:

    # s "I saved you the horror, and read you the jolly faerie tales. Now let's put it to good use, or at least try. Start scouring."
    s "Te he ahorrado el horror y te he leído los alegres cuentos de hadas. Ahora vamos a darle un buen uso, o al menos intentarlo. Empieza a buscar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2861
translate Spanish ch2m_08_729d9230:

    # "The old binding crackles in protest as we flip and skim pages furiously."
    "La vieja encuadernación cruje en señal de protesta mientras pasamos y hojeamos páginas furiosamente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2862
translate Spanish ch2m_08_afefcdd8:

    # m "Wait! What's a changeling?"
    m "¡Espera! ¿Qué es un cambiante?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2864
translate Spanish ch2m_08_a135638c:

    # c "A child surreptitiously exchanged for another? No. That wouldn't make sense. You're hardly a child."
    c "¿Un niño intercambiado a escondidas por otro? No. Eso no tendría sentido. Difícilmente eres un niño."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2865
translate Spanish ch2m_08_544e8e65:

    # m "You're right. Keep reading."
    m "Tienes razón. Sigue leyendo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2875
translate Spanish ch2m_08_985000a8:

    # s "There y'are! Púca—"
    s "¡Ahí están! Púca-"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2876
translate Spanish ch2m_08_5f587a76:

    # c "Pook-what?"
    c "¿Pook-qué?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2877
translate Spanish ch2m_08_1065d160:

    # s "Animal spirits, my dear. \"Oft have traits of a domestic animal, such as ears or tail...\" my, so many tales here."
    s "Espíritus animales, querida. \"A menudo tienen rasgos de un animal doméstico, como orejas o cola...\" Vaya, cuántos cuentos aquí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2878
translate Spanish ch2m_08_613a45d5:

    # m "What does it say?"
    m "¿Qué es lo que dice?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2879
translate Spanish ch2m_08_743ca05a:

    # s "Well... they seem to run the gamut from helpful to hurtful. They can bear good luck, or portend great misfortune. Hm. This one here seems to be a trickster..."
    s "Bueno... parece que van de lo útil a lo perjudicial. Pueden traer buena suerte o presagiar grandes desgracias. Hm. Este de aquí parece ser un estafador..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2880
translate Spanish ch2m_08_128b6be1:

    # m "A trickster...? C-could this really be a curse, then?"
    m "¿Un estafador...? ¿Podría ser esto realmente una maldición, entonces?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2881
translate Spanish ch2m_08_5de51a4e:

    # "My stomach drops as my mind flashes back to Effie's ears. Is {i}she{/i} a púca? Has she been tricking us all along?"
    "Se me revuelve el estómago cuando pienso en las orejas de Effie. ¿Es una púca? ¿Nos ha estado engañando todo el tiempo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2882
translate Spanish ch2m_08_116da640:

    # s "Who's to say? I'd ask Baird, were he still with us. But, more often than not, there's a grain of truth to ancient wisdom. At least I hope so, lest I be out of a job!"
    s "¿Quién sabe? Le preguntaría a Baird, si aún estuviera con nosotros. Pero, más a menudo que no, hay un grano de verdad en la sabiduría antigua. Al menos eso espero, ¡no sea que me quede sin trabajo!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2883
translate Spanish ch2m_08_1c643575:

    # "Agnes squints at the tiny text."
    "Agnes entrecierra los ojos al leer el texto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2884
translate Spanish ch2m_08_b1cdb210:

    # s "Hm... this tale is about a púca who helped a farmer mill his crop. And this one befriended a man, but no one believed him because the púca was invisible. Thrown in the madhouse, he was."
    s "Hm... este cuento trata de un púca que ayudó a un granjero a moler su cosecha. Y éste se hizo amigo de un hombre, pero nadie le creyó porque el púca era invisible. Lo arrojaron al manicomio."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2885
translate Spanish ch2m_08_ab363a42:

    # m "That's horrible!"
    m "Eso es horrible!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2886
translate Spanish ch2m_08_9731826b:

    # s "That's nothing, lass. {i}This{/i} one, oh my... this púca lured unsuspecting men off the road to {i}devour{/i} them! Hah! Oh, these faerie tales..."
    s "Eso no es nada, muchacha. {i}Este{/i}, oh mi... ¡este púca atrajo a hombres desprevenidos fuera del camino para {i}devorarlos{/i}! ¡Ja! Oh, estos cuentos de hadas..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2887
translate Spanish ch2m_08_be5a2c96:

    # "Marion's face goes quite pale. This exercise is exacerbating her fears instead of containing them."
    "Marion palidece. Este ejercicio está exacerbando sus temores en lugar de contenerlos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2888
translate Spanish ch2m_08_23c36afa:

    # s "Ahem. Let's close the book for now. There are no reasonable answers. It's getting late for me, anyway."
    s "Ejem. Cerremos el libro por ahora. No hay respuestas razonables. Se está haciendo tarde para mí, de todos modos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2898
translate Spanish ch2m_08_4816303b:

    # "The three of us close up the book, and Gran kisses Marion on the head."
    "Los tres cerramos el libro y la abuela besa a Marion en la cabeza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2899
translate Spanish ch2m_08_69410d75:

    # s "You'll be fine, good girl. If the faeries made ye this way, it's for a reason. Ours is not to reason why..."
    s "Estarás bien, buena chica. Si los hados os hicieron así, es por algo. La nuestra no es para razonar por qué..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2902
translate Spanish ch2m_08_8301940b:

    # "We bid our goodnights to Gran, but as she heads back toward the house, a thought pops into my mind. Something left unaddressed."
    "Nos despedimos de la abuela, pero mientras se dirige de nuevo a la casa, me viene un pensamiento a la cabeza. Algo que había quedado pendiente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2903
translate Spanish ch2m_08_0a866d6c:

    # c "Gran, uh... if you could, please don't... um..."
    c "Abuela, uh... si pudieras, por favor no... um..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2906
translate Spanish ch2m_08_9a6f4d3f:

    # s "Gossip in the pews?"
    s "Cotilleos en los banquillos?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2909
translate Spanish ch2m_08_b0a5606c:

    # s "Don't worry, I should be able to keep it a secret. Robina's boys and Murdoch's flirting will keep us all entertained for the time being."
    s "No te preocupes, debería ser capaz de mantenerlo en secreto. Los chicos de Robina y el coqueteo de Murdoch nos mantendrán entretenidos por el momento."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2911
translate Spanish ch2m_08_79939687:

    # s "Marion, my darling. You are loved. You are protected. Someone, or something, is watching o'er you... as are we. May your dreams let you rest easy tonight."
    s "Marion, querida. Eres amada. Estás protegida. Alguien, o algo, vela por ti... como nosotros. Que tus sueños te dejen descansar tranquila esta noche."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2916
translate Spanish ch2m_08_0657501b:

    # "Once Gran closes the door, we are left with just the humming of insects and chirping of birds. The quiet is welcome."
    "Una vez que la abuela cierra la puerta, nos quedamos sólo con el zumbido de los insectos y el piar de los pájaros. La tranquilidad es bienvenida."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2917
translate Spanish ch2m_08_ecd3de24:

    # c "Would you be up for a walk?"
    c "¿Te apetece dar un paseo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2919
translate Spanish ch2m_08_664379ca:

    # m "Yes, please."
    m "Sí, por favor."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2926
translate Spanish ch2m_08_b9d5d9fe:

    # "We wander in the late spring warmth, and the air is refreshing. As we pause at the overlook, I take ahold of Marion's hand, and press it to my heart."
    "Paseamos bajo el calor primaveral y el aire es refrescante. Cuando nos detenemos en el mirador, cojo la mano de Marion y la estrecho contra mi corazón."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2929
translate Spanish ch2m_08_0790ee8e:

    # "She looks calm."
    "Parece tranquila."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2930
translate Spanish ch2m_08_23b31db7:

    # m "I don't want to get my hopes up, but Grace keeps trying to convince me it will get better. Or at least, that it won't get any worse."
    m "No quiero hacerme ilusiones, pero Grace sigue intentando convencerme de que todo mejorará. O al menos, de que no empeorará."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2931
translate Spanish ch2m_08_fca4ec12:

    # c "Sisterly intuition? I wouldn't discount it. We're already well into uncharted territory... there are flimsier things on which to base our faith."
    c "¿Intuición de hermanas? Yo no la descartaría. Ya estamos en territorio desconocido... hay cosas más endebles en las que basar nuestra fe."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2933
translate Spanish ch2m_08_0d54df26:

    # m "I guess, but... I'm so nervous. About everything. I've lost my sister, and a great deal of income. And what have I gained? A tail?"
    m "Supongo, pero... Estoy tan nerviosa. Por todo. He perdido a mi hermana, y una gran cantidad de ingresos. ¿Y qué he ganado? ¿Una cola?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2938
translate Spanish ch2m_08_748c7c7f:

    # c "And a boyfriend."
    c "Y un novio."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2940
translate Spanish ch2m_08_a92fa81e:

    # "Her face lights up."
    "Su rostro se ilumina."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2941
translate Spanish ch2m_08_b4b1b481:

    # m "Really?"
    m "En serio?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2942
translate Spanish ch2m_08_68c10266:

    # c "Yes, I hope so."
    c "Sí, eso espero."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2944
translate Spanish ch2m_08_29972307:

    # m "A boyfriend. I never thought I would hear that word in my life! A boyfriend and a tail. I guess I'll take it!"
    m "Un novio. ¡Nunca pensé que oiría esa palabra en mi vida! Un novio y una cola. Supongo que lo aceptaré!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2945
translate Spanish ch2m_08_7ec005fa:

    # c "So, you'll be my girlfriend?"
    c "Entonces, serás mi novia?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2947
translate Spanish ch2m_08_2e569aa9:

    # m "Of course, Malcolm! It would be an honor."
    m "Por supuesto, Malcolm! Sería un honor."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2949
translate Spanish ch2m_08_900bba2a:

    # c "And a confidant."
    c "Y un confidente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2951
translate Spanish ch2m_08_8b30f6ab:

    # "She smiles sympathetically."
    "Sonríe con simpatía."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2954
translate Spanish ch2m_08_0d52b9ba:

    # m "This has been the most insane week of my life. I don't know how you'll be able to put up with me. But if you're really willing, I'll be by your side."
    m "Esta ha sido la semana más loca de mi vida. No sé cómo serás capaz de aguantarme. Pero si de verdad estás dispuesto, estaré a tu lado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2955
translate Spanish ch2m_08_d5bc6434:

    # "We fall back into conversation, keeping it light, like our demeanors. It's amazing she is able to stay so down to Earth."
    "Volvemos a la conversación, manteniéndola ligera, como nuestros comportamientos. Es increíble que sea capaz de mantener los pies en la tierra."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2962
translate Spanish ch2m_08_e11cefa0:

    # "Behind her skirt, I see a little wiggling. Her tail moves to and fro, and the movement is at once hilarious, adorable, and utterly confusing."
    "Detrás de su falda, veo un pequeño contoneo. Su cola se mueve de un lado a otro, y el movimiento es a la vez hilarante, adorable y absolutamente confuso."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2963
translate Spanish ch2m_08_ec1280e6:

    # "Does it mean she is happy? If so, if I had a tail, it would be wagging too."
    "Significa que está contenta? Si es así, si yo tuviera cola, también la movería."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2964
translate Spanish ch2m_08_1d996e99:

    # c "Marion... my heart leapt when you came to the door earlier. I knew I'd see you again, but I didn't know when."
    c "Marion... mi corazón saltó cuando llegaste a la puerta antes. Sabía que volvería a verte, pero no sabía cuándo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2966
translate Spanish ch2m_08_6541b1bb:

    # m "I'm sorry. I didn't mean to keep you waiting, I just... I'm as nervous about... {i}us{/i}... as I am about..."
    m "Lo siento. No quise hacerte esperar, es sólo que... Estoy tan nerviosa por... {i}nosotros{/i}... como lo estoy por..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2967
translate Spanish ch2m_08_ec46fb21:

    # "She taps her head."
    "Se da golpecitos en la cabeza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2969
translate Spanish ch2m_08_6572d4fc:

    # m "...well, you know."
    m "...bueno, ya sabes."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2977
translate Spanish ch2m_08_1b379da9:

    # "I plant a kiss on her forehead. My hand goes to her ears, and I'm still taken aback when I feel felt-like fur instead of skin."
    "Le planto un beso en la frente. Llevo la mano a sus orejas y me sorprendo al notar que, en lugar de piel, tiene pelo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2978
translate Spanish ch2m_08_9d0b3953:

    # "...?"
    "...?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2979
translate Spanish ch2m_08_b46e4b45:

    # "Her ears are much longer than the last time. I can tell by touch alone. And that means the measurements Grace has been taking..."
    "Sus orejas son mucho más largas que la última vez. Puedo decirlo sólo con el tacto. Y eso significa que las medidas que Grace ha estado tomando..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2980
translate Spanish ch2m_08_e034a5f7:

    # "Oh, no. Has Grace been fibbing to her sister? Is Marion... still changing?"
    "Oh, no. ¿Grace ha estado mintiendo a su hermana? ¿Está Marion... todavía cambiando?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:2981
translate Spanish ch2m_08_23e0c40b:

    # c "Marion..."
    c "Marion..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2983
translate Spanish ch2m_08_8a0ec403:

    # "I... I'm too emotional to fully digest the notion, right now. The sun is getting low on the horizon. I need rest, as must she."
    "Yo.. estoy demasiado emocional para digerir plenamente la noción, en este momento. El sol está bajando en el horizonte. Necesito descansar, al igual que ella."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2984
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bc9ac528:

    # c "Marion, let me walk you home. Both of us should be readying for a good night's sleep."
    c "Marion, déjame acompañarte a casa. Ambos deberíamos prepararnos para una buena noche de sueño."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2985
translate Spanish ch2m_08_1558e386:

    # "Marion loops her fingers into mine, and places my hand against her chest."
    "Marion entrelaza sus dedos con los míos y coloca mi mano contra su pecho."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2987
translate Spanish ch2m_08_1b155e3c:

    # m "I don't want to be forward, but... I don't want to be alone tonight."
    m "No quiero ser atrevida, pero... No quiero estar sola esta noche."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2988
translate Spanish ch2m_08_ef2e5037:

    # "Her golden eyes reflect the setting sun, framed by thick, long lashes. I can feel her heartbeat, steady and resolute."
    "Sus ojos dorados reflejan el sol poniente, enmarcados por espesas y largas pestañas. Siento los latidos de su corazón, firmes y decididos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2989
translate Spanish ch2m_08_4a8cd86a:

    # "I take a deep breath and respond."
    "Respiro hondo y respondo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:2990
translate Spanish ch2m_08_82d07371:

    # c "All right. Come with me."
    c "De acuerdo. Ven conmigo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3000
translate Spanish ch2m_08_fcc02840:

    # "Back home, Gran's ubiquitous snores come as a relief. The sun has already dipped behind the mountains. I quietly lead my ladyfriend into my room, where I light two beeswax candles."
    "De vuelta a casa, los ronquidos omnipresentes de la abuela son un alivio. El sol ya se ha ocultado tras las montañas. Conduzco en silencio a mi novia a mi habitación, donde enciendo dos velas de cera de abeja."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3008
translate Spanish ch2m_08_1f53ba5a:

    # "Marion and I curl up in my bed, under my childhood quilts and blankets, surrounded by everything that reminds me of my youth."
    "Marion y yo nos acurrucamos en mi cama, bajo los cobertores y mantas de mi infancia, rodeados de todo lo que me recuerda a mi juventud."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3009
translate Spanish ch2m_08_b28ee75c:

    # "The peeling wallpaper, chipped paint, even the hairline crack that runs from the door threshold to the ceiling."
    "El papel pintado descascarillado, la pintura desconchada, incluso la pequeña grieta que va desde el umbral de la puerta hasta el techo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3010
translate Spanish ch2m_08_679f2e57:

    # "I never thought I would be lying here, cuddled chest to chest with the eldest MacLeod girl. Especially not under such... unusual circumstances."
    "Nunca pensé que estaría acostado aquí, abrazado pecho a pecho con la mayor de las chicas MacLeod. Especialmente no bajo tan... inusuales circunstancias."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3011
translate Spanish ch2m_08_4d41b1fe:

    # "My head presses into her soft hair, carefully nestled between two nubby horns. Horns! Inconceivable!"
    "Mi cabeza se aprieta contra su suave pelo, cuidadosamente acurrucado entre dos cuernos nudosos. ¡Cuernos! ¡Inconcebibles!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3012
translate Spanish ch2m_08_cee7007c:

    # "For the first time, I try to imagine what Marion must be going through, what it must feel like. Her life and body completely changed."
    "Por primera vez, intento imaginar por lo que debe estar pasando Marion, lo que debe sentir. Su vida y su cuerpo han cambiado por completo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3013
translate Spanish ch2m_08_6c6db7b4:

    # "My mind conjures up flashbacks of the haunting dream I had when I turned into a stag."
    "Mi mente evoca recuerdos del inquietante sueño que tuve cuando me convertí en ciervo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3014
translate Spanish ch2m_08_6979927a:

    # "The sensation of my hands and fingers being slowly cloven together. The pain of antlers piercing my skull as they emerged."
    "La sensación de que mis manos y dedos se entrelazaban lentamente. El dolor de las astas perforando mi cráneo cuando emergían."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3015
translate Spanish ch2m_08_2839ea0a:

    # "I think of Marion's adorable ears, and how odd it must have been to discover them. Did she feel them grow, when they first transformed?"
    "Pienso en las adorables orejas de Marion y en lo extraño que debió de ser descubrirlas. ¿Las sintió crecer, cuando se transformaron por primera vez?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3016
translate Spanish ch2m_08_521d1be9:

    # "My stomach churns, and I shudder, but then cautiously relax back into the thought. Maybe it feels good, like a powerful stretch in the evening after plowing the fields."
    "Se me revuelve el estómago y me estremezco, pero luego me relajo cautelosamente. Tal vez me siente bien, como un estiramiento poderoso al atardecer después de arar los campos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3017
translate Spanish ch2m_08_0ab1cc8f:

    # "Is it painful? Is it natural? Why am I too nervous just to ask her?"
    "¿Es doloroso? ¿Es natural? ¿Por qué estoy tan nervioso como para preguntarle?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3018
translate Spanish ch2m_08_c68c234b:

    # "I ease into the questions as delicately as possible."
    "Le planteo las preguntas con la mayor delicadeza posible."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3019
translate Spanish ch2m_08_c0a6bc29:

    # c "Marion, I've had another thought on my mind. I'm... well, I've been worried that I might change, as well."
    c "Marion, he tenido otro pensamiento en mi mente. Yo... bueno, me ha preocupado que yo también pueda cambiar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3021
translate Spanish ch2m_08_0b8a6548:

    # m "I have the same fears, Malcolm. But I want us to be able to moove forward."
    m "Tengo los mismos temores, Malcolm. Pero quiero que podamooos avanzar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3022
translate Spanish ch2m_08_a54e9c27:

    # "Did she hiccup? Or...?"
    "¿Tuvo hipo? ¿O...?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3023
translate Spanish ch2m_08_5037deb9:

    # c "I do, too, Marion. I just... I never had reason to mention it, but I had a vivid dream upon returning home. In it, well... I transformed, too. Into a stag."
    c "Yo también, Marion. Yo sólo... Nunca tuve motivos para mencionarlo, pero tuve un sueño vívido al volver a casa. En él, bueno... Yo también me transformé. En un ciervo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3024
translate Spanish ch2m_08_af55d1a4:

    # c "I know I can't compare a mere dream to what's happened to you, but the sensations, the pain, the intensity are all so {i}lucid{/i} in my mind."
    c "Sé que no puedo comparar un mero sueño con lo que te ha pasado, pero las sensaciones, el dolor, la intensidad son tan {i}lúcidos{/i} en mi mente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3025
translate Spanish ch2m_08_55113459:

    # "Marion snuggles in closer to me, and kisses my lips. I let her mouth linger on mine. I don't believe she is quieting me. She is reassuring me."
    "Marion se acurruca más cerca de mí y me besa los labios. Dejo que su boca se quede en la mía. No creo que me esté haciendo callar. Me está tranquilizando."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3026
translate Spanish ch2m_08_5c4cae64:

    # "When she smiles at me, I see the pink on the tip of her nose gets rosier, darker. Maybe it's just the light, but I truly don't think so."
    "Cuando me sonríe, veo que el rosa de la punta de su nariz se vuelve más rosado, más oscuro. Tal vez sea sólo la luz, pero realmente no lo creo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3027
translate Spanish ch2m_08_b8fcd3ff:

    # "Her changes are continuing, and I'm at a loss for how to tell her."
    "Sus cambios continúan y no sé cómo decírselo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3028
translate Spanish ch2m_08_1e80be5b:

    # m "You'll be fine, Malcolm. You have to be. To keep me sane. You don't show any symptoms, do you?"
    m "Estarás bien, Malcolm. Tienes que estarlo. Para mantenerme cuerda. No muestras ningún síntoma, ¿verdad?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3029
translate Spanish ch2m_08_df4e0732:

    # c "No, no. Nothing I've seen."
    c "No, no. No he visto nada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3030
translate Spanish ch2m_08_3bcd81e2:

    # "Marion yawns."
    "Marion bosteza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3031
translate Spanish ch2m_08_c4e810e3:

    # m "Oh, my. I'm much more sleepy than I thought. Malcolm, thank you for being by my side today."
    m "Vaya. Tengo mucho más sueño del que pensaba. Malcolm, gracias por estar a mi lado hoy."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3032
translate Spanish ch2m_08_b65b894c:

    # c "And always, Marion. Sleep well."
    c "Y siempre, Marion. Que duermas bien."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3033
translate Spanish ch2m_08_d5a29e45:

    # "Marion flutters her eyes closed, and presses her head onto my shoulder as I roll back, allowing us both more room to sleep."
    "Marion cierra los ojos y apoya la cabeza en mi hombro mientras yo me echo hacia atrás, dejándonos a los dos más espacio para dormir."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3046
translate Spanish ch2m_08_ab65de11:

    # "As she drifts off, I watch her tail inch out from under the quilt. Ever so slowly, it flops against the bedframe, and extends further down to the floor."
    "Mientras se queda dormida, veo cómo su cola sale de debajo del cubrecama. Lentamente, se deja caer contra el armazón de la cama y se extiende hasta el suelo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3047
translate Spanish ch2m_08_df503438:

    # "Had it {i}grown,{/i} or simply slipped out? The tip brushes along the hardwood, and particles of dust float into the air."
    "¿Había {i}crecido,{/i} o simplemente se había escapado? La punta roza la madera dura y las partículas de polvo flotan en el aire."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3048
translate Spanish ch2m_08_24e5734b:

    # "I don't know which is more disturbing: how my girlfriend's tail just swept against the floor, or how after all this time {i}I{/i} haven't swept my own living space, despite a fervent dedication to chores."
    "No sé qué es más inquietante: si que la cola de mi novia acabe de barrer el suelo, o que después de todo este tiempo {i}yo{/i} no haya barrido mi propio espacio vital, a pesar de una ferviente dedicación a las tareas domésticas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3049
translate Spanish ch2m_08_88a2a7f9:

    # "My brain turns itself off, due to fatigue. Here I am, enveloped in a warm blanket cocoon with my dear Marion. My girlfriend. A woman I... love? Is it too soon to think such a thing?"
    "Mi cerebro se apaga, debido a la fatiga. Aquí estoy, envuelto en un cálido capullo de manta con mi querida Marion. Mi novia. ¿Una mujer a la que... amo? ¿Es demasiado pronto para pensar tal cosa?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3050
translate Spanish ch2m_08_03fe85d9:

    # "With a puff, I blow out the candles."
    "De un soplido, apago las velas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3065
translate Spanish ch2m_08_97e144e5:

    # "I wake to the sound of the cock crowing. My eyes flutter open and spy Marion slipping her shoes back on."
    "Me despierto con el canto del gallo. Abro los ojos y veo a Marion poniéndose los zapatos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3071
translate Spanish ch2m_08_41ffb4cf:

    # m "Oh! I'm sorry... I didn't want to wake you, but I must get back home. The herd. They'll need milking, and I can't trust that Grace will get it done."
    m "¡Oh! Lo siento... No quería despertarte, pero debo volver a casa. El rebaño. Necesitarán ordeño, y no puedo confiar en que Grace lo haga."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3082
translate Spanish ch2m_08_ceb8f2c9:

    # "She leans over, kisses me, and wraps her kerchief tightly around her chin."
    "Se inclina, me besa y se envuelve la barbilla con el pañuelo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3083
translate Spanish ch2m_08_1fe96b5b:

    # m "I'll see you soon!"
    m "Nos vemos pronto!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3084
translate Spanish ch2m_08_794b199f:

    # c "Soon."
    c "Pronto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3088
translate Spanish ch2m_08_ce310a85:

    # "I roll over, but can't will myself back to sleep. I had seen the tail. It was thicker now, longer. And brown fur was trailing up her calves."
    "Me doy la vuelta, pero no consigo dormirme. Había visto la cola. Ahora era más gruesa, más larga. Y un pelaje marrón le subía por las pantorrillas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3106
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bad_7c2a03c9:

    # m "I honestly think I would like that. I'd like it very much. But... that's what I came to tell you."
    m "Sinceramente, creo que me gustaría. Me gustaría mucho. Pero... eso es lo que vine a decirte."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3113
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bad_02bb68ae:

    # m "It's just not possible. There can't be a you and me, Malcolm. Not like this."
    m "Simplemente no es posible. No puede haber un tú y yo, Malcolm. No así."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3114
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bad_5f44fe62:

    # "She shudders as she sighs heavily. My stomach drops, but I'm at once resigned to her decision."
    "Se estremece y suspira con fuerza. Se me revuelve el estómago, pero enseguida me resigno a su decisión."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3115
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bad_2e8b7054:

    # "I can't argue with her. It's all too strange and foreign an event to not admit that I'm horrified. But mostly, I'm unable to help, and that sense of helplessness is killing me just as surely as it is her."
    "No puedo discutir con ella. Es un acontecimiento demasiado extraño y ajeno como para no admitir que estoy horrorizado. Pero, sobre todo, soy incapaz de ayudar, y esa sensación de impotencia me está matando con tanta certeza como a ella."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3116
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bad_f92045a4:

    # c "But, Marion... I want us to be together."
    c "Pero, Marion... Quiero que estemos juntos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3118
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bad_947eb848:

    # m "You don't have to agree. I'm making your mind up for you."
    m "No tienes que estar de acuerdo. Estoy decidiendo por ti."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3119
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bad_37103207:

    # "Gran's words of wisdom float back into my head. The woman makes her mind up first. Then the man accepts it."
    "Las sabias palabras de Abue vuelven flotando a mi cabeza. La mujer decide primero. Luego el hombre la acepta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3120
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bad_81b64381:

    # "If Marion wasn't ready or willing to allow me into her life right now, I had to accept the consequences, or risk losing her forever, as both a friend... and possibly more."
    "Si Marion no estaba preparada o dispuesta a permitirme entrar en su vida ahora mismo, tenía que aceptar las consecuencias, o arriesgarme a perderla para siempre, como amiga... y posiblemente como algo más."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3121
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bad_98b8eb4b:

    # c "But.. I..."
    c "Pero... yo..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3122
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bad_5f5b4f61:

    # "My voice catches, and it hits me that I'm fighting back a torrent of tears. I don't want to lose her. Ever."
    "Se me entrecorta la voz y me doy cuenta de que estoy conteniendo un torrente de lágrimas. No quiero perderla. Jamás."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3123
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bad_9786d31b:

    # c "I don't want this... us... to end. Marion, please. There must be a way to fix this."
    c "No quiero que esto... nosotros... termine. Marion, por favor. Debe haber una manera de arreglar esto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3125
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bad_1ed1efc1:

    # "Marion shakes her head."
    "Marion niega con la cabeza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3126
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bad_dddda258:

    # m "Even if there is, I don't want to burden you. You're only recently home. You need to acclimate, find your life again."
    m "Incluso si lo hay, no quiero agobiarte. Hace poco que estás en casa. Necesitas aclimatarte, encontrar tu vida de nuevo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3127
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bad_2186e8a9:

    # "I want to say more, but I'm shaken to the core. Her life is now as shattered as mine."
    "Quiero decir más, pero estoy conmocionada hasta la médula. Su vida está ahora tan destrozada como la mía."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3128
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bad_f525fbe0:

    # "Once again, everything I know of my world has turned on its head, and I'm frozen in trying to respond."
    "Una vez más, todo lo que conozco de mi mundo se ha vuelto del revés, y me quedo helado al intentar responder."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3130
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bad_1645dc81:

    # m "Malcolm, we'll talk again. I'm sure of it. Please, don't worry. I feel fine. I'm going to look for help. Just know..."
    m "Malcolm, volveremos a hablar. Estoy seguro de ello. Por favor, no te preocupes. Me siento bien. Voy a buscar ayuda. Sólo debes saber..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3131
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bad_01a93953:

    # c "Marion, I—"
    c "Marion, yo..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3133
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bad_5f8f7c40:

    # m "I love you, Malcolm."
    m "Te amo, Malcolm."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3135
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bad_526f9915:

    # c "I love you, too, Marion."
    c "Yo también te amo, Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3136
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bad_cb66be27:

    # "As we both say the words, the tears fall. We don't try to stop them, and I brush back her hair while wiping her eyes dry with my handkerchief."
    "Mientras ambos pronunciamos las palabras, caen las lágrimas. No intentamos detenerlas, y le echo el pelo hacia atrás mientras le seco los ojos con mi pañuelo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3137
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bad_75edf176:

    # c "You'll get through this. If you need anything, at all... ever, Marion, know that I am here."
    c "Lo superarás. Si necesitas algo, lo que sea... alguna vez, Marion, que sepas que estoy aquí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3145
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bad_f4f852d3:

    # "Marion stands to leave, and I hold her tight against my chest. The pounding of our hearts beat in unison."
    "Marion se levanta para marcharse y yo la estrecho contra mi pecho. Los latidos de nuestros corazones laten al unísono."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3153
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bad_c63001bd:

    # "While I can't bear to let her go, she decides when to loosely drop her arms, and push me away."
    "Aunque no soporto dejarla marchar, ella decide cuándo soltar los brazos y apartarme."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3154
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bad_b4d6fd89:

    # "As she leaves, she looks at me, smiling."
    "Cuando se va, me mira sonriendo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3155
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bad_d23be2ad:

    # m "I am here, too... always."
    m "Yo también estoy aquí... siempre."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3163
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bad_b5d8b5a3:

    # "I long to take her in my arms once more, and kiss her hard. Instead, I let her go, back down the path towards her home. Her exile."
    "Ansío tomarla en mis brazos una vez más y besarla con fuerza. En lugar de eso, la dejo ir, de vuelta por el camino hacia su hogar. Su exilio."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3164
translate Spanish ch2m_08_bad_171d4169:

    # "Her hair blows in the breeze, and she does not look back."
    "Su pelo se agita con la brisa y no mira hacia atrás."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3184
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_fd2b8419:

    # "For weeks and months after that day, I write down everything I want to say to her."
    "Durante semanas y meses después de ese día, escribo todo lo que quiero decirle."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3185
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_2da1b775:

    # "Long letters about how much she means to me, how much I want her back, and how much I miss her."
    "Largas cartas sobre lo mucho que significa para mí, lo mucho que quiero que vuelva y lo mucho que la echo de menos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3186
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_664d8725:

    # "But I never give her the letters. I never say the words I want to say to her."
    "Pero nunca le doy las cartas. Nunca le digo las palabras que quiero decirle."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3187
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_1d80f060:

    # "The more that time passes, the more I distance myself from her, and try to forget."
    "Cuanto más pasa el tiempo, más me distancio de ella e intento olvidar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3188
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_9cf54018:

    # "Gran cries more often than I do these days. I find her weeping alone at night by the fire, and I assure her that this is for the best."
    "La abuela llora más a menudo que yo estos días. La encuentro llorando sola por la noche junto al fuego, y le aseguro que es lo mejor."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3189
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_9eef8ef0:

    # "Marion changed her mind. We aren't meant to be together."
    "Marion ha cambiado de opinión. No estamos destinados a estar juntos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3190
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_d251f22c:

    # "I imagine it will take her much longer to recover from my heartbreak."
    "Imagino que tardará mucho más en recuperarse de mi ruptura."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3191
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_89e9ea52:

    # "Marion's father, Owen, returns home in one month, Gran informs at dinnertime one night."
    "El padre de Marion, Owen, vuelve a casa dentro de un mes, me informa Abue una noche a la hora de cenar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3192
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_170aac8a:

    # "She tells me the congregation will be throwing a homecoming party for him, and I ought to attend. Marion should be there; perhaps we can reconnect, Gran says."
    "Me dice que la congregación le hará una fiesta de bienvenida y que debería asistir. Marion debería estar allí; tal vez podamos reconectar, dice Gran."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3193
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_23a166da:

    # "The party comes and goes, and neither of us attend. Gran later tells me that Owen didn't show either."
    "La fiesta va y viene, y ninguno de los dos asistimos. La abuela me dice más tarde que Owen tampoco fue."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3194
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_ae3742ad:

    # "Apparently there is much happening at the MacLeod homestead, and that wartime servitude has taken a toll on Mr. MacLeod's temperament."
    "Al parecer, están ocurriendo muchas cosas en la granja de los MacLeod, y la servidumbre de la guerra ha hecho estragos en el temperamento del Sr. MacLeod."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3195
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_fe1717c8:

    # "I relate, but I worry even more for Marion's safety. Is he treating her well? Is she being ostracized?"
    "Me identifico, pero me preocupa aún más la seguridad de Marion. ¿La está tratando bien? ¿Está siendo condenada al ostracismo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3196
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_6d3f8829:

    # "The fear comes to a head one evening, and I find myself venturing over to the neighboring farm."
    "El miedo llega a su punto álgido una noche, y me encuentro aventurándome en la granja vecina."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3197
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_be436ddf:

    # "I find Marion among the cows, a bucket of feed in her hands. Subconsciously, I am relieved to see fingers instead of hooves. Perhaps she's all right. Better, even."
    "Encuentro a Marion entre las vacas, con un cubo de pienso en las manos. Inconscientemente, me alivia ver dedos en lugar de pezuñas. Quizá esté bien. Mejor, incluso."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3198
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_1ad3a6a9:

    # c "Marion. How are you?"
    c "Cómo estás, Marion?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3199
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_fca4202b:

    # "My stomach drops. None of my feelings for her have changed. I yearn to be with her."
    "Se me cae el estómago. Nada de lo que siento por ella ha cambiado. Anhelo estar con ella."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3200
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_166e5e9a:

    # m "Well, Malcolm. And you?"
    m "Bien, Malcolm. Y tú?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3201
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_d2a4bb91:

    # "She is standoffish, not making eye contact, barely looking up from her chores."
    "Se muestra distante, no establece contacto visual y apenas levanta la vista de sus quehaceres."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3202
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_a3ee354b:

    # c "I've been better. I was... just making sure you're all right. I heard you father was home."
    c "He estado mejor. Estaba... asegurándome de que estabas bien. Oí que tu padre estaba en casa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3203
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_3f78ddad:

    # m "I know why you're here, Malcolm. And yes, we're all fine. I appreciate the gesture..."
    m "Sé por qué estás aquí, Malcolm. Y sí, todos estamos bien. Aprecio el gesto..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3204
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_57ccd36c:

    # "Her voice chokes."
    "Su voz se entrecorta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3205
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_3a571ba5:

    # m "I enjoy being home... with the herd. It's relaxing. And so much of my workload has been relieved since father came home."
    m "Me gusta estar en casa... con el rebaño. Es relajante. Y gran parte de mi carga de trabajo se ha aliviado desde que padre llegó a casa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3206
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_d947d7a4:

    # "Even Grace has been guilted into helping out more... finally. She's working as a barmaid. Jessie's old job."
    "Incluso Grace ha sido obligada a ayudar más... finalmente. Está trabajando como camarera. El antiguo trabajo de Jessie."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3207
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_d01352bf:

    # c "Not singing, I hope?"
    c "No cantando, Espero?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3208
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_15c4f295:

    # "I try to lighten the mood by making a bad joke, and am relieved when Marion cracks a smile."
    "Intento aligerar el ambiente haciendo un chiste malo, y me siento aliviado cuando Marion esboza una sonrisa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3209
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_5c42ee41:

    # m "Oh, my! No!"
    m "Oh, Dios! No!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3211
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_d57168e2:

    # c "Marion—"
    c "Marion—"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3212
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_675db794:

    # m "Malcolm—"
    m "Malcolm—"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3213
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_470c68bc:

    # "Marion looks up, and my heart leaps."
    "Marion levanta la vista y mi corazón da un salto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3214
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_611a2d65:

    # c "Go ahead, please."
    c "Adelante, por favor."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3215
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_846566ed:

    # m "Malcolm... I know there's no... us, anymore. But maybe there could be a you and me?"
    m "Malcolm... Sé que ya no hay un... nosotros. ¿Pero tal vez podría haber un tú y yo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3216
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_2a6043e3:

    # c "I miss you. Every day."
    c "Te extraño. Todos los días."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3217
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_9ce43147:

    # m "I miss you too. Every second of every day."
    m "Yo también te extraño. Cada segundo de cada día."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3218
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_44af5cd1:

    # c "There can always be a you and me."
    c "Siempre puede haber un tú y un yo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3219
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_826d8fd5:

    # "We talk a while longer until the sun sets."
    "Hablamos un rato más hasta que se pone el sol."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3220
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_befacecd:

    # "Marion invites me to dinner, and I immediately flash back to those first nights of being home from war, and her invitation being a salvation from loneliness and confusion."
    "Marion me invita a cenar, e inmediatamente recuerdo aquellas primeras noches en casa tras la guerra, y su invitación como una salvación de la soledad y la confusión."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3221
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_aa667ee7:

    # "I decline the invitation this time, but promise to take her up on the offer another night, if she's willing."
    "Esta vez declino la invitación, pero prometo aceptar su oferta otra noche, si ella está dispuesta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3222
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_bc0d5c8c:

    # "Marion and I rebuild our trust and friendship in the following weeks, but she never reveals her true nature to the world."
    "Marion y yo reconstruimos nuestra confianza y amistad en las semanas siguientes, pero ella nunca revela su verdadera naturaleza al mundo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3223
translate Spanish ch2m_herd_c54fc4e4:

    # "Enough time passes that it's hardly ever spoken of again. Though her lips never reach mine again, we are forever connected to each other's hearts. For that, I am grateful."
    "Pasa el tiempo suficiente para que apenas se vuelva a hablar de ello. Aunque sus labios nunca vuelvan a alcanzar los míos, estamos conectados para siempre al corazón del otro. Por eso, le estoy agradecido."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3269
translate Spanish ch2m_09_d82cf7f4:

    # "One secret. Four confidants. Two households, acting as one. We get through the next few days as a team, losing track of time, devoting ourselves to our labors."
    "Un secreto. Cuatro confidentes. Dos hogares, actuando como uno solo. Pasamos los siguientes días como un equipo, perdiendo la noción del tiempo, dedicándonos a nuestras labores."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3275
translate Spanish ch2m_09_085d3d97:

    # "Even Grace chips in more, offering to go to market and till the garden for spring sowing."
    "Incluso Grace aporta más, ofreciéndose a ir al mercado y a labrar el huerto para la siembra de primavera."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3276
translate Spanish ch2m_09_1fe310d3:

    # "Gran makes double batches of biscuits, scones, and shortbread to pass off to the MacLeod girls, to ease their baking load. Which is not to say that Marion minds being chef."
    "La abuela hace dos tandas de bizcochos, bollos y galletas para las chicas MacLeod, para aliviar su carga de repostería. Lo que no quiere decir que a Marion le importe ser chef."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3277
translate Spanish ch2m_09_2fc84b2f:

    # "On the contrary, she seems to find great relief in cooking. We find ourselves overloaded with treats, cheeses, and vegetable stews in no time."
    "Al contrario, parece encontrar un gran alivio en la cocina. En un santiamén nos encontramos sobrecargados de golosinas, quesos y guisos de verduras."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3289
translate Spanish ch2m_09_c665dc81:

    # "Certainly a wonderful problem to tackle. I'm in the MacLeods' kitchen with the girls one sunny morning when Grace files a complaint."
    "Sin duda, un maravilloso problema que abordar. Estoy en la cocina de los MacLeod con las niñas una mañana soleada cuando Grace presenta una queja."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3291
translate Spanish ch2m_09_17bd73c7:

    # g "Goodness, Marion. Are you attracting flies?"
    g "Dios mío, Marion. Estás atrayendo moscas?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3293
translate Spanish ch2m_09_d825d01b:

    # m "{i}What?{/i} What on Earth? Why would you say that!?"
    m "{i}Qué?{/i} Qué demonios?, Por qué dices eso?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3295
translate Spanish ch2m_09_1a80836e:

    # "Marion furrows her brow, and looks humiliated. We go silent and all hear the buzzing, though. Thankfully, I'm quick to find the solution."
    "Marion frunce el ceño y parece humillada. Nos callamos y todos oímos el zumbido. Por suerte, no tardo en encontrar la solución."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3296
translate Spanish ch2m_09_d4bfa5c8:

    # c "The pies!"
    c "Las tartas!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3307
translate Spanish ch2m_09_d01ba00b:

    # "I rush to the window where two cloudberry pies are attracting flies on the open sill. After a few waves of my arms, the bugs go off to find an easier meal. I shut the window behind them."
    "Me apresuro hacia la ventana, donde dos pasteles de mora de los pantanos atraen a las moscas al alféizar abierto. Tras unos cuantos movimientos de mis brazos, los bichos se marchan en busca de una comida más fácil. Cierro la ventana tras ellos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3320
translate Spanish ch2m_09_236fc2cd:

    # m "Malcolm, you saved the day! ...Or at least dessert."
    m "Malcolm, salvaste el día! ...O al menos el postre."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3331
translate Spanish ch2m_09_6dfa7d5b:

    # "Marion hugs me, and glares at her younger sister."
    "Marion me abraza y mira a su hermana pequeña."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3332
translate Spanish ch2m_09_bdcbbe04:

    # m "Grace, don't you have laundry to finish?"
    m "Grace, no tienes ropa que lavar?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3334
translate Spanish ch2m_09_9e05f14e:

    # g "Aye, aye. But don't blame me for jumping to conclusions. I'm only looking out for you!"
    g "Sí, sí. Pero no me culpes por sacar conclusiones precipitadas. ¡Sólo te estoy cuidando!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3337
translate Spanish ch2m_09_15e512d8:

    # m "Oh, get! Or nary a slice of pie will be left for ye."
    m "¡Oh, vamos! O no quedará ni un trozo de tarta para ustedes."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3338
translate Spanish ch2m_09_333f51b9:

    # "Marion shoos me out, too, with two baskets of dirty laundry to scour alongside Grace."
    "Marion también me echa, con dos cestos de ropa sucia para fregar junto a Grace."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3351
translate Spanish ch2m_09_112fa985:

    # "Outside, it's a delight to bask in the sun, even with my hands soaked in lye water. And even if it be next to a persnickety scamp like Grace."
    "Fuera, es una delicia tomar el sol, incluso con las manos empapadas en agua con lejía. E incluso si es al lado de un bribón quisquilloso como Grace."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3352
translate Spanish ch2m_09_22537ed1:

    # "She stands beside me, surprisingly helpful, although the tide-pool scent wafting off of her is overpowering. How much time does she spend down by the loch, anyways?"
    "Está a mi lado, sorprendentemente servicial, aunque el olor a marea que desprende es abrumador. De todas formas, ¿cuánto tiempo pasa junto al lago?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3353
translate Spanish ch2m_09_b88cf15b:

    # "It seems she's a troublemaker even unintentionally. I need to ask her how she's holding up, though."
    "Parece que es una alborotadora incluso sin querer. Aunque tengo que preguntarle cómo lo lleva."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3355
translate Spanish ch2m_09_aa919ddf:

    # c "So... How are you surviving all of this..."
    c "Entonces... ¿Cómo estás sobreviviendo a todo esto..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3356
translate Spanish ch2m_09_eb30e1b2:

    # "What would I even call it? Bovine business? Tail trouble? I'm at a loss, but it doesn't even need mentioning."
    "¿Cómo lo llamaría? ¿Asunto bovino? ¿Problemas de cola? Estoy perdido, pero ni siquiera hace falta mencionarlo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3358
translate Spanish ch2m_09_aebcfdfb:

    # g "My horny sister? Quite honestly, I'm a bit jealous. I was hoping if I hung around the fish long enough maybe I'd grow fins. Alas..."
    g "¿Mi hermana cornuda? Sinceramente, estoy un poco celosa. Tenía la esperanza de que si me quedaba cerca de los peces el tiempo suficiente tal vez me crecerían aletas. Ay..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3360
translate Spanish ch2m_09_05009f51:

    # "She raises her hands and flips them back and forth."
    "Levanta las manos y las mueve de un lado a otro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3362
translate Spanish ch2m_09_4be2c7c2:

    # g "Still ten fingers and toes. That's a curse right there, I tell ya."
    g "Aún diez dedos en manos y pies. Eso es una maldición, te lo digo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3363
translate Spanish ch2m_09_de820172:

    # "Ever the sympathetic sister. I keep shoving the fabrics into the sudsy solution, rubbing them hard against the edge of the wood basin."
    "Siempre tan comprensiva. Sigo metiendo las telas en la solución jabonosa, frotándolas con fuerza contra el borde del recipiente de madera."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3365
translate Spanish ch2m_09_cde2f386:

    # g "I don't know if she's told you, but she's desperately afraid of what Father will think when he gets home. Also frets about turning into a cow proper."
    g "No sé si te lo ha contado, pero teme desesperadamente lo que pensará papá cuando llegue a casa. También teme convertirse en una vaca."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3367
translate Spanish ch2m_09_93559a50:

    # g "I try to cheer her up, make jokes about getting free milk for life. It's really been terrible at times, though. I've heard her cry herself to sleep."
    g "Intento animarla, le hago bromas sobre la leche gratis de por vida. Pero a veces ha sido terrible. La he oído llorar hasta quedarse dormida."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3368
translate Spanish ch2m_09_1359c5b3:

    # "Grace wipes her soapy hands off on her skirt, and starts wringing out her clean dish towels."
    "Grace se limpia las manos enjabonadas en la falda y empieza a escurrir los paños de cocina limpios."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3369
translate Spanish ch2m_09_9f59ca45:

    # g "These days I guess I worry about as much as she ever has. Or at least, now I understand her fears."
    g "Estos días creo que me preocupo tanto como ella lo ha hecho siempre. O al menos, ahora entiendo sus miedos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3372
translate Spanish ch2m_09_6a3c84b9:

    # g "Sometimes I'm afraid Marion will never leave the farm again, beyond your walls. And when Father returns, well... that's just bound to make everything worse."
    g "A veces temo que Marion no vuelva a salir de la granja, más allá de sus muros. Y cuando Padre regrese, bueno... eso sólo empeorará las cosas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3373
translate Spanish ch2m_09_c7756fde:

    # "I cringe, and don't raise my head. Grace might well be right."
    "Me estremezco y no levanto la cabeza. Puede que Grace tenga razón."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3375
translate Spanish ch2m_09_c4503a05:

    # g "At the same time, I've never seen her smile and laugh more. She's positively smitten with you, Malcolm."
    g "Al mismo tiempo, nunca la he visto sonreír y reír tanto. Ella está positivamente enamorada de ti, Malcolm."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3377
translate Spanish ch2m_09_c1d166eb:

    # g "I'd say your timing is terrible, though. 'Tis a shame you couldn't have returned to town after her tail goes away."
    g "Sin embargo, yo diría que tu sincronización es terrible. Es una pena que no pudieras volver a la ciudad después de que su cola se fuera."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3378
translate Spanish ch2m_09_6b9ff2de:

    # "We laugh to break the somber mood. Here we are, Marion and me, falling in love as she struggles through this bizarre... illness? Affliction? Ailment?"
    "Nos reímos para romper el ambiente sombrío. Aquí estamos, Marion y yo, enamorándonos mientras ella lucha contra esta extraña... ¿enfermedad? ¿Aflicción? ¿Padecimiento?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3379
translate Spanish ch2m_09_9b3af6b2:

    # "She still appears healthy, just... changed. Physically altered. It has to get better. Doesn't it?"
    "Aún parece saludable, sólo... cambiada. Físicamente alterada. Tiene que mejorar. ¿No es así?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3381
translate Spanish ch2m_09_d8436547:

    # "Grace looks up and admits that which I did not want confirmed."
    "Grace levanta la vista y admite lo que no quería que se confirmara."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3382
translate Spanish ch2m_09_eff251ac:

    # g "I've been lying to her about her ears and horns not getting any bigger. They grow every day. The tail, too."
    g "Le he estado mintiendo acerca de que sus orejas y cuernos no crecen. Crecen cada día. La cola también."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3383
translate Spanish ch2m_09_bd373eb2:

    # c "...I know. I've seen the growth. The fur."
    c "...lo sé. He visto el crecimiento. El pelaje."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3385
translate Spanish ch2m_09_2c2f2f28:

    # "I finally glance up and see Grace nodding and smiling, but with tears in her eyes—a sight I assume to be uncommon."
    "Por fin levanto la vista y veo a Grace asintiendo y sonriendo, pero con lágrimas en los ojos, algo que supongo poco común."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3386
translate Spanish ch2m_09_267f371c:

    # g "Ne'er say a word, but... those ears of hers shed a bit. If things keep up at this rate, I'll be sweeping even more than we did when we had a housecat."
    g "No ha dicho ni una palabra, pero... esas orejas suyas se caen un poco. Si las cosas siguen a este ritmo, voy a estar barriendo aún más de lo que hicimos cuando teníamos un gato doméstico."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3387
translate Spanish ch2m_09_eeaf6ad0:

    # "Grace dries her eyes and continues."
    "Grace se seca los ojos y continúa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3389
translate Spanish ch2m_09_3156e61f:

    # g "You know, I wanted to thank you for getting her that cowbell pendant."
    g "Sabes, quería darte las gracias por conseguirle ese colgante de cencerro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3390
translate Spanish ch2m_09_3414e5c6:

    # "My hands pause mid-scrub. Part of me still does not trust the trinket, or its purveyor."
    "Mis manos se detienen a mitad del frotado. Una parte de mí aún no confía en la baratija ni en su proveedor."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3391
translate Spanish ch2m_09_5df27ab0:

    # c "Oh! I'm just glad she likes it. Does she... still wear it?"
    c "Me alegro de que le guste. ¿Ella... todavía lo usa?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3393
translate Spanish ch2m_09_21942b81:

    # g "Yes, when you're not around. I think she wears it to keep you close. To be honest, it's been helpful when she wanders off sometimes. I can hear her in the fields from twenty ells off."
    g "Sí, cuando no estás cerca. Creo que lo lleva para mantenerte cerca. Para ser honesto, ha sido útil cuando ella se aleja a veces. Puedo oírla en los campos a veinte manzanas de distancia."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3394
translate Spanish ch2m_09_432f49d6:

    # c "Oh, my. Has she been wandering often?"
    c "Oh, vaya. ¿Ha estado vagando a menudo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3396
translate Spanish ch2m_09_a8c7613b:

    # "Grace nods again, and my heart sinks. It's not like Marion to roam the fields. Unlike her sisters, she's very structured in her daily routine."
    "Grace asiente de nuevo, y mi corazón se hunde. No es propio de Marion vagar por los campos. A diferencia de sus hermanas, ella es muy estructurada en su rutina diaria."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3397
translate Spanish ch2m_09_448a2760:

    # g "Mmmhmm. A few times a day, it seems. She's usually among the herd, though, so I don't worry. But she's skipped a couple of meals, which is definitely unlike her."
    g "Mmmhmm. Varias veces al día, parece. Aunque normalmente está entre la manada, así que no me preocupo. Pero se ha saltado un par de comidas, lo que definitivamente no es propio de ella."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3398
translate Spanish ch2m_09_2fa896d9:

    # "I don't know whether to worry or be relieved that she may be treating herself to some much deserved privacy and personal time."
    "No sé si preocuparme o sentirme aliviado de que se conceda a sí misma un merecido tiempo personal y de intimidad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3399
translate Spanish ch2m_09_a1035d6f:

    # c "Do you think she seems lonely? I've noticed it a bit. Even when we're all together, she seems distant."
    c "¿Crees que parece solitaria? Lo he notado un poco. Incluso cuando estamos todos juntos, parece distante."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3401
translate Spanish ch2m_09_dd446b57:

    # g "Of course. I imagine her thoughts are quite scattered these days. Her friends in town are starting to ask after her, too. They know she's a busy woman, but I'm not sure how long that excuse can last."
    g "Por supuesto. Imagino que sus pensamientos están bastante dispersos estos días. Sus amigos en la ciudad están empezando a preguntar por ella, también. Saben que es una mujer ocupada, pero no sé cuánto durará esa excusa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3409
translate Spanish ch2m_09_7cb11741:

    # g "I think we need to tell her to go into the village. But I suspect she'll only listen to you."
    g "Creo que tenemos que decirle que vaya al pueblo. Pero sospecho que sólo te escuchará a ti."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3414
translate Spanish ch2m_09_09dd63cc:

    # butterfly_effect "{image=butterflysprite}" nointeract
    butterfly_effect "{image=butterflysprite}" nointeract

# game/script_marion.rpy:3417
translate Spanish ch2m_09_ce0b3d24:

    # c "It's definitely a sound idea. If we all encourage her, Gran as well, I think she would try it."
    c "Definitivamente es una buena idea. Si todos la animamos, la abuela también, creo que lo intentaría."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3418
translate Spanish ch2m_09_22a207f4:

    # "Marion peeks her head out of the window."
    "Marion asoma la cabeza por la ventana."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3420
translate Spanish ch2m_09_8e8a8c2a:

    # m "I just made four pots of cranachan. I'll bring them tonight for dinner! We don't have any more jarred raspberries, so I just used extra cream and whisky!"
    m "Acabo de hacer cuatro ollas de cranachan. Los traeré esta noche para cenar. Ya no tenemos frambuesas de bote, así que he usado nata y whisky de más!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3421
translate Spanish ch2m_09_67cbbdc8:

    # c "Sounds delicious!"
    c "Suena delicioso!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3423
translate Spanish ch2m_09_4f9f15bd:

    # "I turn back to Grace."
    "Me vuelvo hacia Grace."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3424
translate Spanish ch2m_09_abcad452:

    # c "We need to get her out of here or we'll be as big as heifers..."
    c "Tenemos que sacarla de aquí o seremos tan grandes como vaquillas..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3425
translate Spanish ch2m_09_068ba168:

    # "Oh, please tell me I didn't just say that."
    "Por favor, dime que no acabo de decir eso."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3427
translate Spanish ch2m_09_3b0c5573:

    # g "Malcolm Campbell. Always a way with words."
    g "Malcolm Campbell. Siempre muy hábil con las palabras."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3428
translate Spanish ch2m_09_ffdb6b97:

    # c "Hey, now. Maybe you should be the one who convinces her to leave the house."
    c "Oye. Tal vez deberías ser tú quien la convenza de dejar la casa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3431
translate Spanish ch2m_09_f54426a6:

    # c "But... what if she's seen like this?"
    c "Pero... y si la ven así?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3433
translate Spanish ch2m_09_9d77c9e2:

    # g "So what if she is? I don't think the town has anything to fear from a perky cow-lass."
    g "Y qué si lo es? No creo que el pueblo tenga nada que temer de una alegre vaquera."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3434
translate Spanish ch2m_09_22a207f4_1:

    # "Marion peeks her head out of the window."
    "Marion asoma la cabeza por la ventana."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3436
translate Spanish ch2m_09_8e8a8c2a_1:

    # m "I just made four pots of cranachan. I'll bring them tonight for dinner! We don't have any more jarred raspberries, so I just used extra cream and whisky!"
    m "Acabo de hacer cuatro ollas de cranachan. Los traeré esta noche para cenar. Ya no tenemos frambuesas de bote, ¡así que he usado nata y whisky de más!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3437
translate Spanish ch2m_09_67cbbdc8_1:

    # c "Sounds delicious!"
    c "Suena delicioso!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3439
translate Spanish ch2m_09_4f9f15bd_1:

    # "I turn back to Grace."
    "Me vuelvo hacia Grace."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3440
translate Spanish ch2m_09_74a9cc7a:

    # c "Nothing to fear, except a wider waistband."
    c "Nada que temer, salvo una cintura más ancha."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3442
translate Spanish ch2m_09_7e741789:

    # g "I'm just saying, it'll be good for her."
    g "Sólo digo que será bueno para ella."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3443
translate Spanish ch2m_09_dcfba017:

    # "I'm not so sure it's worth it if there's a chance Marion's secret will be exposed. But I can tell there's no dissuading Grace."
    "No estoy seguro de que valga la pena si existe la posibilidad de que el secreto de Marion salga a la luz. Pero puedo decir que no hay forma de disuadir a Grace."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3444
translate Spanish ch2m_09_d5d1b7d8:

    # c "If you're so keen on it, maybe you should be the one who convinces her to leave the house."
    c "Si tanto te interesa, quizá deberías ser tú quien la convenciera de salir de casa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3447
translate Spanish ch2m_09_b9e33f51:

    # g "She never listens to me!"
    g "Nunca me escucha!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3448
translate Spanish ch2m_09_b79dafb4:

    # c "Just tell her she should stay home forever."
    c "Sólo dile que debería quedarse en casa para siempre."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3450
translate Spanish ch2m_09_39bb42d8:

    # g "But that's something I would do, not her."
    g "Pero eso es algo que haría yo, no ella."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3453
translate Spanish ch2m_09_50d51012:

    # c "Exactly. She'll hear that, and run to the Stag & Nanny faster than she's ever run before."
    c "Exactamente. Oirá eso, y correrá al Stag & Nanny más rápido que nunca."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3475
translate Spanish ch2m_09_648796ee:

    # "The MacLeod sisters join us for dinner that evening. Gran has made beef stovies to use up our leftovers. We crowd around the small table, say the Selkirk Grace, and dig in."
    "Las hermanas MacLeod nos acompañan a cenar esa noche. La abuela ha preparado estofados de ternera para aprovechar las sobras. Nos apiñamos en torno a la pequeña mesa, recitamos el Selkirk Grace y comemos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3477
translate Spanish ch2m_09_26835c33:

    # "Most of us do, anyway. Marion just shoves the food around on her plate."
    "La mayoría lo hacemos. Marion sólo empuja la comida en su plato."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3478
translate Spanish ch2m_09_144627a1:

    # c "Not much of an appetite?"
    c "No tienes mucho apetito?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3480
translate Spanish ch2m_09_0e493581:

    # "She shakes her head."
    "Menea la cabeza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3482
translate Spanish ch2m_09_52ee1f54:

    # m "I'll stick to bread and vegetables tonight. Maybe a dram of whisky for dessert. How does everyone like the greens?"
    m "Esta noche me limitaré a pan y verduras. Tal vez un trago de whisky de postre. ¿Qué les parecen las verduras?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3483
translate Spanish ch2m_09_e435d959:

    # "Marion gestures to the big bowl of dandelion greens she prepared with spring onions and some unidentifiable, and painfully acrid smelling, ingredients."
    "Marion señala el gran cuenco de hojas de diente de león que ha preparado con cebolletas y algunos ingredientes inidentificables y de olor dolorosamente acre."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3485
translate Spanish ch2m_09_9cd075d8:

    # "Grace winces as she takes a bite."
    "Grace hace una mueca de dolor al dar un mordisco."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3487
translate Spanish ch2m_09_057b536b:

    # g "Ugh! Marion. What is this?"
    g "Uf! Marion. Qué es esto?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3490
translate Spanish ch2m_09_c889c6ec:

    # m "It has bogbean fresh from the loch, and some burdock root juice that I extracted just today."
    m "Tiene bogbean fresco del loch, y un poco de jugo de raíz de bardana que extraje justo hoy."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3493
translate Spanish ch2m_09_db4ce65c:

    # c "Mm! Can't wait to try a taste!"
    c "Mm! No puedo esperar a probarlo!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3496
translate Spanish ch2m_09_3db801e2:

    # "I take a bite, and it's all I can do to keep it down. And all this time I thought Balgair's fried haggis balls might be the worst thing I would ever taste."
    "Le doy un mordisco, y es todo lo que puedo hacer para no comerlo. Y todo este tiempo pensé que las bolas de haggis fritas de Balgair serían lo peor que probaría en mi vida."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3498
translate Spanish ch2m_09_c8227e5d:

    # g "It's awful."
    g "Es horrible."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3500
translate Spanish ch2m_09_06987c29:

    # m "It's good for you! It's... supposed to be good for you. The herbology text I consulted said they're good for digestion and internal health."
    m "Es bueno para ti! Se... supone que es bueno para ti. El texto de herbología que consulté dice que son buenas para la digestión y la salud interna."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3501
translate Spanish ch2m_09_536f4064:

    # g "Where in the world did you get an herbology text?"
    g "De dónde sacaste un texto de herbología?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3503
translate Spanish ch2m_09_3e6a174e:

    # "Marion pauses and chews her greens happily. She couldn't look more smug."
    "Marion hace una pausa y mastica alegremente sus verduras. No puede estar más satisfecha."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3504
translate Spanish ch2m_09_82ecda1a:

    # m "It was {i}mother's.{/i} It was in her hope chest."
    m "Era de mi {i}madre.{/i} Estaba en su baúl de las esperanzas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3506
translate Spanish ch2m_09_fa35005a:

    # "Grace stays quiet after that."
    "Grace se queda callada después de eso."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3508
translate Spanish ch2m_09_6de70376:

    # s "I say we all eat up. Whether stovies or weeds, it's all good for our innards!"
    s "Yo digo que comamos todos. Ya sean estofados o hierbajos, ¡todo es bueno para nuestras entrañas!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3509
translate Spanish ch2m_09_96dfee7b:

    # "Gran is quick to change the subject, but it's not necessarily one that I think Marion is ready to discuss."
    "Abue se apresura a cambiar de tema, pero no creo que Marion esté dispuesta a hablar de ello."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3513
translate Spanish ch2m_09_5e218f8b:

    # s "The congregation has been asking about you, Marion. People are beginning to wonder what happened to you, and if you're all right."
    s "La congregación ha estado preguntando por ti, Marion. La gente empieza a preguntarse qué te ha pasado y si estás bien."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3514
translate Spanish ch2m_09_a2b5cb88:

    # c "People? Or the Whist club?"
    c "Gente? ¿O el club de Whist?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3516
translate Spanish ch2m_09_11d386b2:

    # s "Hush! Those are people too, Malcolm! Bite your tongue."
    s "Silencio! ¡Esos también son personas, Malcolm! Muérdete la lengua."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3519
translate Spanish ch2m_09_6e69c023:

    # m "I suppose I ought to make my big debut. I just need to make sure my kerchief is clean, and my skirt is cinched tight."
    m "Supongo que debería hacer mi gran debut. Sólo tengo que asegurarme de que mi pañuelo esté limpio y mi falda bien ceñida."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3521
translate Spanish ch2m_09_9cb8abbd:

    # "She giggles, but her voice is cracking. She fiddles with her napkin before stuffing another scoop of those dreadful greens into her mouth and chomping away."
    "Se ríe, pero se le quiebra la voz. Juguetea con la servilleta antes de meterse otra cucharada de esas horribles verduras en la boca y masticar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3524
translate Spanish ch2m_09_184094e9:

    # c "You certainly don't have to... I mean, if you're not comfortable. But I know others would love to see you... if that's something you want."
    c "Ciertamente no tienes que... ...si no te sientes cómodo. Pero sé que a otros les encantaría verte... si es algo que quieres."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3526
translate Spanish ch2m_09_8bbbc9aa:

    # c "All joking aside, Gran is right. Others would love to see you. And not just the Whist club ladies."
    c "Bromas aparte, la Abue tiene razón. A otros les encantaría verte. Y no sólo las damas del club de Whist."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3529
translate Spanish ch2m_09_d1b1cb6f:

    # "Grace speaks up in support."
    "Grace habla en su apoyo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3530
translate Spanish ch2m_09_2add1d32:

    # g "Alana has asked about you. So has Balgair. I imagine the preacher, too."
    g "Alana ha preguntado por ti. También Balgair. Imagino que el predicador también."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3531
translate Spanish ch2m_09_8c65c9b1:

    # "Grace looks to Gran on that account."
    "Grace mira a Abue en esa cuenta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3533
translate Spanish ch2m_09_ce680df9:

    # s "He certainly has."
    s "Desde luego que sí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3534
translate Spanish ch2m_09_e707c15c:

    # g "A great deal of people hope to see you..."
    g "Mucha gente espera verte..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3535
translate Spanish ch2m_09_8e10ff3c:

    # "Grace starts to lower her voice, almost to a whisper."
    "Grace empieza a bajar la voz, casi hasta un susurro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3538
translate Spanish ch2m_09_37a33742:

    # g "...to know you're doing well."
    g "...saber que te va bien."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3541
translate Spanish ch2m_09_c48eef92:

    # "Marion nods, and understands we're not trying to badger her, just encourage."
    "Marion asiente y comprende que no intentamos acosarla, sólo animarla."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3543
translate Spanish ch2m_09_da2349e1:

    # m "I know. It would be best for me to go into town, see others. It's just been... overwhelming."
    m "Lo sé. Sería mejor para mí ir a la ciudad, ver a otros. Ha sido... abrumador."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3545
translate Spanish ch2m_09_b6dfedd1:

    # g "The fear?"
    g "El miedo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3547
translate Spanish ch2m_09_8cb62253:

    # m "Yes."
    m "Si."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3549
translate Spanish ch2m_09_0ff8f833:

    # "Grace looks to me, pleadingly."
    "Grace me mira, suplicante."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3553
translate Spanish ch2m_09_8f40b5ea:

    # c "I get it, Marion. And if you don't want to go, we'll understand. But if you do, we'll make sure your secret stays safe. Don't worry one bit!"
    c "Lo entiendo, Marion. Y si no quieres ir, lo entenderemos. Pero si lo haces, nos aseguraremos de que tu secreto permanezca a salvo. No te preocupes!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3555
translate Spanish ch2m_09_648a7b5f:

    # c "That fear isn't going to go away. Well... if I let fear run my life, I never would have left the homestead ever again."
    c "Ese miedo no va a desaparecer. Bueno... si hubiera dejado que el miedo dirigiera mi vida, nunca habría dejado la granja nunca más."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3556
translate Spanish ch2m_09_c8367e12:

    # c "I'd be holed up here, alone with Gran, biding my time doing manual labor and drinking myself to sleep."
    c "Estaría aquí encerrado, solo con la abuela, pasando el tiempo haciendo trabajos manuales y bebiendo hasta dormirme."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3558
translate Spanish ch2m_09_eda1fa38:

    # "Marion gives me a compassionate glance."
    "Marion me lanza una mirada compasiva."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3559
translate Spanish ch2m_09_34e7e799:

    # c "But I took a risk. I reached out to you, for support, for friendship."
    c "Pero me arriesgué. Me acerqué a ti, por apoyo, por amistad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3560
translate Spanish ch2m_09_f646a3d4:

    # c "I think... Marion, what we're all suggesting is that you take your fear with you into town, but try to ignore it. At least for a short while."
    c "Creo que... Marion, lo que todos te sugerimos es que lleves tu miedo contigo a la ciudad, pero que trates de ignorarlo. Al menos por un corto tiempo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3564
translate Spanish ch2m_09_59b7ae91:

    # m "I know you will all protect me. Look out for me. If you all join me, I'll be happy to go."
    m "Sé que todos ustedes me protegerán. Que me cuidaréis. Si todos me acompañan, estaré feliz de ir."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3567
translate Spanish ch2m_09_b21e1c8d:

    # c "Anything you need, Marion."
    c "Lo que necesites, Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3568
translate Spanish ch2m_09_e88adee9:

    # s "Anything at all."
    s "Cualquier cosa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3569
translate Spanish ch2m_09_ad674b23:

    # g "Agreed."
    g "De acuerdo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3572
translate Spanish ch2m_09_34d738b5:

    # "Gran dons a mischievous grin."
    "La abue esboza una sonrisa pícara."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3573
translate Spanish ch2m_09_04213de5:

    # s "We'll all go to church in the morning."
    s "Iremos todos a la iglesia por la mañana."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3576
translate Spanish ch2m_09_a1fadda8:

    # g "Oh... well..."
    g "Oh... bueno..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3578
translate Spanish ch2m_09_1161ff58:

    # m "It's too late to backtrack, Grace."
    m "Es demasiado tarde para retroceder, Grace."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3580
translate Spanish ch2m_09_f4adab5c:

    # s "Get out your Sunday best, Miss Grace. Shine yer shoes. Scrub your cheeks 'til they're pink. Maybe even consider washing the seaweed outta your mane, and we can find you a jaunty single fella."
    s "Saca tus mejores ropas, Srta. Grace. Lustra tus zapatos. Frota tus mejillas hasta que estén rosadas. Tal vez incluso considere lavar las algas de su melena, y podemos encontrarle un soltero alegre."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3582
translate Spanish ch2m_09_4b18a0f7:

    # s "I hear Murdoch's nephew just lost his wife. He's a sea captain. Maybe he can get ya a houseboat! You'd love that!"
    s "He oído que el sobrino de Murdoch acaba de perder a su esposa. Es capitán de barco. ¡Quizás pueda conseguirte una casa flotante! ¡Te encantaría!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3583
translate Spanish ch2m_09_0860ad12:

    # "We all go silent, but Grace smirks."
    "Todos nos quedamos en silencio, pero Grace sonríe."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3585
translate Spanish ch2m_09_8546684d:

    # g "There's nothing I'd like more."
    g "No hay nada que me gustaría más."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3614
translate Spanish ch2m_10_beed310d:

    # "Morning arrives and Gran and I climb aboard Hazel to go over to the MacLeods. We'll all ride as a team to church. The sun has barely crept into the sky, and is hidden behind a veil of clouds."
    "Llega la mañana y la abuela y yo subimos a bordo de Hazel para ir a casa de los MacLeod. Todos cabalgaremos en equipo hasta la iglesia. El sol apenas se ha colado en el cielo y se oculta tras un velo de nubes."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3631
translate Spanish ch2m_10_e9eeaecf:

    # "Marion and Grace come out and untie their steed, Eachann. They lead him over to Hazel, to whom the stallion seems to have taken a liking."
    "Marion y Grace salen y desatan a su corcel, Eachann. Lo conducen hasta Hazel, a quien el semental parece haber cogido cariño."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3638
translate Spanish ch2m_10_98f24d28:

    # c "So... are you sure you want to go to today?"
    c "Entonces... ¿estás segura de que quieres ir hoy?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3640
translate Spanish ch2m_10_8dafc518:

    # g "Ah... If I must."
    g "Ah... Si debo hacerlo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3643
translate Spanish ch2m_10_f51e71d4:

    # "There's a pause as we all look to Grace. For all the world, you would think this trip was going to be harder on her than her sister."
    "Hay una pausa mientras todos miramos a Grace. Por todo el mundo, se podría pensar que este viaje iba a ser más duro para ella que para su hermana."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3646
translate Spanish ch2m_10_e8a49b1b:

    # "I turn my gaze back to Marion, to whom the question was directed."
    "Vuelvo la mirada hacia Marion, a quien iba dirigida la pregunta"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3649
translate Spanish ch2m_10_b08bb4e5:

    # m "Oh—yes! Absolutely. I want to hear the sermon. And to be with the congregation."
    m "¡Oh, sí! Absolutamente. Quiero escuchar el sermón. Y estar con la congregación."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3651
translate Spanish ch2m_10_ee24af1f:

    # s "And your kerchief fits properly?"
    s "Y tu pañuelo te queda bien?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3653
translate Spanish ch2m_10_2947b6a4:

    # c "Gran!"
    c "Abue!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3655
translate Spanish ch2m_10_02085880:

    # s "I want you to be worry-free, Marion."
    s "Quiero que no te preocupes, Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3657
translate Spanish ch2m_10_2e8a672f:

    # m "Well, it's large, that's for sure. But it's comfortable, and nothing slips out."
    m "Bueno, es grande, eso está claro. Pero es cómodo y no se escapa nada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3658
translate Spanish ch2m_10_adde23d6:

    # c "And... the tail?"
    c "Y... la cola?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3667
translate Spanish ch2m_10_35870d5c:

    # "Marion spins for me, and indeed, not one conspicuous part pops out. She is a marvel."
    "Marion gira hacia mí y, efectivamente, no sobresale ni una parte. Es una maravilla."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3669
translate Spanish ch2m_10_8c9be1a9:

    # m "All tucked in nicely. Malcolm, I'll be fine. No one will notice a thing! Stay calm, and I will be, too."
    m "Todo bien metido. Malcolm, estaré bien. ¡Nadie notará nada! Mantén la calma, y yo también lo estaré."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3685
translate Spanish ch2m_10_d5dbe89a:

    # "It's an awkward ride, and I'm thankful it's short. Gran has been tolerant of my flirting with Marion, but I learn that that must stay within the confines of our respective homes."
    "Es un viaje incómodo, y agradezco que sea corto. La abuela ha tolerado que flirtee con Marion, pero he aprendido que eso debe quedar dentro de los límites de nuestros respectivos hogares."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3686
translate Spanish ch2m_10_18a5fe8f:

    # s "Crivens, Malcolm! Stop making moony eyes. Marion, stop twirling your hair! There's no one to impress here. You've already got the boy snared."
    s "¡Crivens, Malcolm! Deja de hacer ojitos. ¡Marion, deja de revolverte el pelo! No hay nadie a quien impresionar aquí. Ya tienes al chico atrapado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3687
translate Spanish ch2m_10_cfcde8b4:

    # "Gran tuts away, mostly to herself. Grace is stifling her laughter by burying her face in the back of Marion's dress."
    "La abuela se ríe, sobre todo para sí misma. Grace ahoga la risa enterrando la cara en la espalda del vestido de Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3688
translate Spanish ch2m_10_9e02cc4e:

    # s "I can't be seen with the two of you if you're going to embarrass me!"
    s "No pueden verme con ustedes dos si van a avergonzarme!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3689
translate Spanish ch2m_10_be5a2e98:

    # s "I want everyone to see my grandson and his new lady love, and be happy for them... not feeling sorry that I have to deal with two frisky schoolchildren romancing away in the pews!"
    s "Quiero que todo el mundo vea a mi nieto y a su nueva novia, y se alegre por ellos... ¡no que sienta pena por tener que lidiar con dos escolares juguetones que se divierten en los bancos!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3690
translate Spanish ch2m_10_bfe52ae8:

    # "It appears that Gran's fear manifests wholly in crankiness and complaints."
    "Parece que el miedo de la abuela se manifiesta totalmente en mal humor y quejas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3691
translate Spanish ch2m_10_769a1687:

    # g "Agnes, you're as grumpy as Hazel today."
    g "Agnes, hoy estás tan gruñona como Hazel."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3692
translate Spanish ch2m_10_0e3e07ba:

    # c "I'd argue that Hazel is much more dignified."
    c "Yo diría que Hazel es mucho más digna."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3693
translate Spanish ch2m_10_f48b7bb7:

    # s "Hmph. Well, just you two keep your hands to yourselves. No handholding during prayer, and absolutely {i}no{/i} smooching in public! Not 'til the girl has a ring on her finger!"
    s "Hmph. Bueno, ustedes dos mantengan sus manos quietas. ¡No se toquen durante la oración, y absolutamente no se besuqueen en público! ¡No hasta que la chica tenga un anillo en su dedo!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3694
translate Spanish ch2m_10_99ee3159:

    # "Marion turns beet red, and nudges Eachann to trot faster. I follow suit, and Gran hollers as Hazel picks up speed."
    "Marion se pone roja y empuja a Eachann para que trote más deprisa. Yo le sigo y la abuela grita cuando Hazel acelera."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3695
translate Spanish ch2m_10_2fc86cbe:

    # s "{i}Oh!{/i} Heaven help me!"
    s "{i}Oh!{/i} ¡Que el cielo me ayude!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3719
translate Spanish ch2m_10_835c008a:

    # "The church bell rings seven times and we huddle around Marion, leading her inside like an invalid."
    "La campana de la iglesia suena siete veces y nos amontonamos alrededor de Marion, conduciéndola al interior como a una inválida."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3720
translate Spanish ch2m_10_c68e8de0:

    # "I feel bad for treating Marion so delicately. As we shuffle into the back pew, I lean over to her."
    "Me siento mal por tratar a Marion con tanta delicadeza. Mientras nos arrastramos hacia el banco de atrás, me inclino hacia ella."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3721
translate Spanish ch2m_10_9bd864aa:

    # c "I'm sorry if we're making this such a big deal. We just want you to be comfortable. Let me know if all this hovering is too much."
    c "Lo siento si estamos haciendo de esto un gran problema. Sólo queremos que estés cómoda. Hazme saber si todo este revoloteo es demasiado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3722
translate Spanish ch2m_10_e1f0ffe2:

    # m "So far, so good. I appreciate the closeness."
    m "Hasta ahora, todo bien. Aprecio la cercanía."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3723
translate Spanish ch2m_10_bff59177:

    # "She lowers her voice."
    "Ella baja la voz."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3724
translate Spanish ch2m_10_ff0f7b76:

    # m "{size=26}Especially from you... but definitely don't let your grandmother know. And don't let her see anything...{/size}"
    m "{size=26}Especialmente de ti... pero definitivamente no dejes que tu abuela lo sepa. Y no dejes que vea nada...{/size}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3725
translate Spanish ch2m_10_7f2bf6e8:

    # "I don't know what Marion means until she adjusts her big bow on her lap, letting the cloth ends fall partially across my legs."
    "No sé a qué se refiere Marion hasta que ajusta su gran moño sobre el regazo, dejando que los extremos de tela caigan parcialmente sobre mis piernas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3726
translate Spanish ch2m_10_d0068188:

    # "She slides one hand under the fabric, and surreptitiously slips her hand into mine. I give her hand a squeeze."
    "Desliza una mano bajo la tela y, subrepticiamente, desliza la mía. Le aprieto la mano."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3727
translate Spanish ch2m_10_a29b0bff:

    # c "{size=26}How {i}scandalous,{/i} Marion!{/size}"
    c "{size=26}Qué {i}escandaloso,{/i} Marion!{/size}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3728
translate Spanish ch2m_10_dd6d4803:

    # m "{size=26}Don't let the preacher see. We may be removed for indecency!{/size}"
    m "{size=26}Que no nos vea el predicador. ¡Podemos ser expulsados por indecencia!{/size}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3737
translate Spanish ch2m_10_858139d7:

    # "The pastor comes to the podium and a hush falls over the crowd. The subject of today's sermon, much to my relief, is much less contentious. In fact, it is surprisingly appropriate."
    "El pastor sube al estrado y se hace el silencio entre la multitud. El tema del sermón de hoy, para mi alivio, es mucho menos polémico. De hecho, es sorprendentemente apropiado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3738
translate Spanish ch2m_10_e34b059a:

    # "\"Love thy neighbor.\" Marion and I giggle. The irony isn't lost on us."
    "\"Ama al prójimo. (vecin@)\" Marion y yo soltamos una risita. No se nos escapa la ironía."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3739
translate Spanish ch2m_10_b68c2723:

    # "Only once during the sermon does the top of Marion's tail peek out from her waistband. I nudge her, and she softly snickers as I help her tuck it back in, with no one noticing."
    "Sólo una vez durante el sermón asoma la parte superior de la cola de Marion por la cintura. Le doy un codazo y se ríe suavemente mientras la ayudo a metérsela de nuevo, sin que nadie se dé cuenta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3740
translate Spanish ch2m_10_aeef4762:

    # "Unfortunately, her new silk kerchief is a bit too loose, and comes untied all too easily. I try every military knot I can think of, and Grace offers a hatpin, but the fabric won't hold."
    "Por desgracia, su nuevo pañuelo de seda está demasiado suelto y se desata con demasiada facilidad. Pruebo todos los nudos militares que se me ocurren y Grace me ofrece un alfiler de sombrero, pero la tela no aguanta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3746
translate Spanish ch2m_10_bc3ccc43:

    # "Finally, the sermon concludes, and I decide to check Hazel's pack for a safety pin. We stand to leave."
    "Finalmente, el sermón concluye y decido buscar un alfiler de gancho en la mochila de Hazel. Nos levantamos para irnos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3752
translate Spanish ch2m_10_bbfe0ecf:

    # b "Is that a costume, Miss Marion? You know you're a few months early for the Heifer Parade, darlin'!"
    b "¿Eso es un disfraz, señorita Marion? ¡Sabes que te has adelantado unos meses para el desfile de vaquillas, querida!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3760
translate Spanish ch2m_10_b1ab6ac3:

    # "The booming voice startles Marion, and she nearly jumps over the moon."
    "La voz atronadora sobresalta a Marion, que casi salta por encima de la luna."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3762
translate Spanish ch2m_10_de444901:

    # "She quickly tucks her ears back under the kerchief, but the cover is already blown. Luckily, Gran intervenes."
    "Rápidamente se mete las orejas bajo el pañuelo, pero la tapadera ya está descubierta. Por suerte, interviene la abuela."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3764
translate Spanish ch2m_10_99a4da9d:

    # s "Aye, Mr. Buchan. We didn't have time to get her out of it 'fore leaving so early this morn'."
    s "Sí, Sr. Buchan. No tuvimos tiempo de sacarla antes de salir tan temprano esta mañana."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3766
translate Spanish ch2m_10_1bfb2e9a:

    # s "Don't let on to others, y'hear? Miss Marion is aiming for Heifer Queen, and I don't want a soul to outshine her!"
    s "No se lo digas a los demás, ¿me oyes? ¡La Srta. Marion aspira a Reina de las Vaquillas y no quiero que nadie la eclipse!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3769
translate Spanish ch2m_10_293bd863:

    # b "That's an impossible task, Mrs. Campbell. There's no one more lovely than Miss Marion!"
    b "Es una tarea imposible, Sra. Campbell. ¡No hay nadie más encantadora que la Srta. Marion!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3773
translate Spanish ch2m_10_6a6f4aa9:

    # g "It's like I'm not standing here at all."
    g "Es como si no estuviera aquí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3776
translate Spanish ch2m_10_d683e9f0:

    # "Balgair blushes."
    "Balgair se sonroja."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3777
translate Spanish ch2m_10_088c4a48:

    # c "Congratulations, Grace. I reckon it's a mighty feat to embarrass Mr. Buchan."
    c "Felicidades, Grace. Creo que es una gran hazaña avergonzar al Sr. Buchan."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3779
translate Spanish ch2m_10_b3bb6b44:

    # b "Ahem. I assure you, you're a beauty Miss Grace. 'Tis been a long time since I've seen ya! Hardly a peep since Jessie hitched her wagon to the big city."
    b "Ejem. Le aseguro que es usted una belleza, Srta. Grace. ¡Hace mucho tiempo que no te veo! Apenas un pío desde que Jessie enganchó su vagón a la gran ciudad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3782
translate Spanish ch2m_10_4595c058:

    # g "I'm happy to stop in for a pint right now. How's about it, everyone? A post-sermon tipple?"
    g "Estoy feliz de pasar a tomar una copa ahora mismo. ¿Qué os parece a todos? ¿Una copa después del sermón?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3784
translate Spanish ch2m_10_6c31d63a:

    # "Gran's face drops."
    "A Abue se le cae la cara."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3785
translate Spanish ch2m_10_a489e81e:

    # s "Grace!"
    s "Grace!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3787
translate Spanish ch2m_10_107504e9:

    # m "Sounds good to me."
    m "Me parece bien."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3788
translate Spanish ch2m_10_5cde05ea:

    # c "Me, too."
    c "A mí también."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3790
translate Spanish ch2m_10_0e2feccf:

    # s "Well, I certainly couldn't. The Whist club is gathering at Robina's house, and Maggie Tyte insisted I join."
    s "Bueno, ciertamente no podría. El club de Whist se reúne en casa de Robina, y Maggie Tyte insistió en que me uniera."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3792
translate Spanish ch2m_10_f7b71c95:

    # s "Grace, I'll be needing someone to stay with me. I'm not sure I'll be able to see all the card suits, and I don't want Maggie cheatin' off my hand!"
    s "Grace, necesitaré que alguien se quede conmigo. No estoy segura de poder ver todos los palos de las cartas, ¡y no quiero que Maggie me haga trampas en la mano!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3795
translate Spanish ch2m_10_431ad305:

    # "Grace turns red with shock and disappointment."
    "Grace se pone roja de asombro y decepción."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3796
translate Spanish ch2m_10_d68ce2f3:

    # g "But—"
    g "Pero-"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3798
translate Spanish ch2m_10_d1eeac4e:

    # s "No buts! It's time for a few rounds of Whist and gossip!"
    s "Sin peros! Es hora de jugar al Whist y de cotillear."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3799
translate Spanish ch2m_10_1cf1a5ed:

    # "Gran lowers her voice, but we can still hear her just fine."
    "La abuela baja la voz, pero se la oye perfectamente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3801
translate Spanish ch2m_10_5fe222b9:

    # s "These two need some alone time, don'tcha think?"
    s "Estos dos necesitan algo de tiempo a solas, ¿no crees?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3804
translate Spanish ch2m_10_eb66e89b:

    # "Grace scowls."
    "Grace frunce el ceño."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3805
translate Spanish ch2m_10_02e4504f:

    # g "No, I don't. I think it's totally unbefitting conduct to allow them to go to a pub unchaperoned. I really ought to watch over them."
    g "No, no lo creo. Creo que es una conducta totalmente impropia permitirles ir a una taberna sin compañía. Realmente debería vigilarlos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3812
translate Spanish ch2m_10_95223d7a:

    # s "Hush now, Grace. You can play as a team with Gemma Tyte. She makes the finest homemade currant cordial in the highlands."
    s "Silencio, Grace. Puedes jugar en equipo con Gemma Tyte. Ella hace el mejor cordial de grosella casero en las tierras altas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3815
translate Spanish ch2m_10_2fbbee1d:

    # s "Spices it up with rum her mother stockpiled before the war. C'mon, we can't be late!"
    s "Lo condimenta con ron que su madre almacenó antes de la guerra. ¡Vamos, no podemos llegar tarde!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3822
translate Spanish ch2m_10_d102d1d5:

    # "Gran yanks Grace's arm, and the two take off. Grace's demeanor has instantly improved. She smiles and shouts over her shoulder."
    "La Abue tira del brazo de Grace y los dos despegan. El comportamiento de Grace ha mejorado al instante. Sonríe y grita por encima del hombro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3823
translate Spanish ch2m_10_1f5816fc:

    # g "Meet us back here in two hours! Mind, we might be blootered!"
    g "¡Nos vemos aquí en dos horas! ¡Cuidado, puede que estemos hinchados!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3824
translate Spanish ch2m_10_959d6772:

    # s "Don't listen to her! We shall most {i}certainly{/i} be blootered!"
    s "No la escuches! {i}Seguro{/i} que nos matarán!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3826
translate Spanish ch2m_10_68bb5abc:

    # b "Speaking of, I must be getting back to the pub."
    b "Hablando de eso, debo volver a la taberna."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3827
translate Spanish ch2m_10_ec57b47d:

    # "He turns and waves to Marion and me."
    "Se vuelve y nos saluda a Marion y a mí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3829
translate Spanish ch2m_10_6af38fbe:

    # b "Hope to see you both over there!"
    b "Espero veros a los dos por allí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3842
translate Spanish ch2m_10_9da26624:

    # "Marion waits until Grace, Gran, and Balgair have strolled far enough down the road before taking me by the wrist and pulling me behind the church."
    "Marion espera a que Grace, Gran y Balgair se hayan alejado lo suficiente antes de sujetarme por la muñeca y tirar de mí por detrás de la iglesia."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3854
translate Spanish ch2m_10_8f41343a:

    # "She looks to and fro before wrapping her arms around my neck and tugging me closer."
    "Me mira de un lado a otro antes de rodearme el cuello con los brazos y tirar de mí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3855
translate Spanish ch2m_10_65515568:

    # c "Here?"
    c "Aqui?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3856
translate Spanish ch2m_10_424fdc9a:

    # m "Yes!"
    m "Si!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3862
translate Spanish ch2m_10_833ec95e:

    # "I take the lead and plant a firm kiss on her warm, waiting lips. My body shivers from head to toe."
    "Tomo la iniciativa y planto un beso firme en sus labios cálidos y expectantes. Mi cuerpo se estremece de pies a cabeza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3864
translate Spanish ch2m_10_78fc9e15:

    # "As we part, her arms fall to my waist. I slide my hand down, stopping to rub her lower back."
    "Cuando nos separamos, sus brazos caen hasta mi cintura. Deslizo la mano hacia abajo y me detengo a frotarle la parte baja de la espalda."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3865
translate Spanish ch2m_10_f1a9a551:

    # c "I could hold you here forever."
    c "Podría abrazarte aquí para siempre."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3867
translate Spanish ch2m_10_8afcc248:

    # m "I wish we could stop time. Walk around without my silly disguise. Just you and me."
    m "Ojalá pudiéramos parar el tiempo. Caminar sin mi tonto disfraz. Solos tú y yo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3868
translate Spanish ch2m_10_eef41f58:

    # c "That sounds lovely."
    c "Eso suena encantador."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3870
translate Spanish ch2m_10_b695f57e:

    # m "Maybe one day. Just once."
    m "Tal vez un día. Sólo una vez."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3871
translate Spanish ch2m_10_788b19bf:

    # c "Maybe. I hope so."
    c "Tal vez. Eso espero."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3874
translate Spanish ch2m_10_f53b4aba:

    # m "In the meantime... is it time for a pint?"
    m "Mientras tanto... ¿es hora de una copa?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3875
translate Spanish ch2m_10_2383db47:

    # c "Marion MacLeod, are you asking me out for a drink... in the middle of the day... right after church?"
    c "Marion MacLeod, ¿me estás invitando a tomar una copa... en mitad del día... justo después de la iglesia?."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3877
translate Spanish ch2m_10_7eaff4c9:

    # m "Well, it's fine if you'd rather just go see the cheesemonger or milliner. Murdoch probably has a new stock of bycockets, should you need a feather in your cap—"
    m "Bueno, está bien si prefieres ir a ver al quesero o al sombrerero. Murdoch probablemente tiene un nuevo stock de bycockets, en caso de que necesite una pluma en su gorra-"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3879
translate Spanish ch2m_10_7149c9c4:

    # m "oh!"
    m "oh!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3883
translate Spanish ch2m_10_603e9d4b:

    # "Instead of responding, I take Marion by the hand, and we run from the church to the Stag & Nanny. Outside the door, we catch our breath."
    "En lugar de responder, cojo a Marion de la mano y salimos corriendo de la iglesia hacia el Stag & Nanny. Fuera de la puerta, recuperamos el aliento."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3891
translate Spanish ch2m_10_06fad999:

    # c "I thought it best to get you here before you change your mind."
    c "Pensé que era mejor traerte aquí antes de que cambiaras de opinión."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3893
translate Spanish ch2m_10_8793f81b:

    # m "Are you saying I'm fickle?"
    m "¿Estás diciendo que soy quisquillosa?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3894
translate Spanish ch2m_10_05c5426f:

    # c "I'm saying you're a hard worker, with little time for frivolities!"
    c "Digo que eres una gran trabajadora, con poco tiempo para frivolidades!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3896
translate Spanish ch2m_10_c33fbfaa:

    # m "This lady you're talking about sounds like a real wet blanket. Oh, why did it take getting horns and a tail for me to finally decide to take a day off?"
    m "Esta señora de la que hablas suena como una verdadera aguafiestas. Oh, por qué fue necesario que me pusieran cuernos y cola para que finalmente decidiera tomarme un día libre?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3897
translate Spanish ch2m_10_7e9e44fd:

    # "I'm stunned into silence."
    "Estoy aturdido en silencio."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3899
translate Spanish ch2m_10_52a2ab85:

    # m "Oh! What a thing to say... I meant it as a good thing, honest! Let's go in before I start saying crazier things."
    m "¡Oh! Qué cosas dices... ¡Lo dije como algo bueno, de verdad! Entremos antes de que empiece a decir cosas más locas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3900
translate Spanish ch2m_10_8ac0b767:

    # c "Do we know for sure if the beer won't lead to more impropriety?"
    c "¿Sabemos con certeza si la cerveza no dará lugar a más incorrecciones?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3902
translate Spanish ch2m_10_1b4b8bb1:

    # m "I thought that was the idea!"
    m "¡Pensaba que esa era la idea!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3932
translate Spanish ch2m_11_80ed208b:

    # b "Ahoy! Grab a seat, I'll have your pints up!"
    b "Ahoy! Tomen asiento, les traeré sus bebidas!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3933
translate Spanish ch2m_11_d6ce3bd6:

    # "As my eyes adjust to the low light, I see Balgair is all smiles. It seems my jaked behavior on the day of the picnic is water under the bridge."
    "Cuando mis ojos se adaptan a la poca luz, veo que Balgair es todo sonrisas. Parece que mi comportamiento brusco el día del picnic es agua pasada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3934
translate Spanish ch2m_11_8c41cdd3:

    # "I'm thankful. I'd just as well not have to explain to Marion my daytime drunken shenanigans with another girl."
    "Estoy agradecido. Preferiría no tener que explicarle a Marion mis travesuras diurnas de borracho con otra chica."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3946
translate Spanish ch2m_11_7243c955:

    # "We take a seat, and Balgair drops two dripping glasses in front of us."
    "Tomamos asiento y Balgair deja caer dos vasos goteantes delante de nosotros."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3958
translate Spanish ch2m_11_ab93a6fc:

    # b "Two pints fit for a king... and his consort, eh, Miss Future Heifer Queen?"
    b "Dos tragos dignos de un rey... y su consorte, ¿eh, Srta. Futura Reina Novilla?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3960
translate Spanish ch2m_11_3ffab7f6:

    # "Not one sip in and Marion seems giddy. In fact, she's seemed giddy all day."
    "Ni un sorbo y Marion parece mareada. De hecho, ha estado mareada todo el día."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3961
translate Spanish ch2m_11_3faa0dc2:

    # m "Thank you, Balgair. I hope your vote will go in my ballot box come parade day."
    m "Gracias, Balgair. Espero que tu voto vaya a mi urna el día del desfile."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3963
translate Spanish ch2m_11_35748263:

    # b "I can't think of any other place I'd like to stick my ballot—"
    b "No se me ocurre otro sitio donde meter mi papeleta..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3964
translate Spanish ch2m_11_105ab49e:

    # c "{i}All right, Balgair!{/i} Thanks for the drinks."
    c "{i}Muy bien, Balgair!{/i} Gracias por las bebidas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3967
translate Spanish ch2m_11_eda62a8d:

    # "Half a pint later, and Marion is positively tipsy. She can't hold her drink like she used to. Seems like the changes are affecting more than her outward appearance."
    "Media pinta más tarde, Marion está completamente achispada. Ya no aguanta la bebida como antes. Parece que los cambios están afectando más que su apariencia externa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3968
translate Spanish ch2m_11_aeed7f50:

    # "She leans in conspiratorially."
    "Se inclina conspiradoramente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3970
translate Spanish ch2m_11_ac93c9ef:

    # m "You know I almost accused you of giving me a cursed pendant! How silly am I?"
    m "¡Sabes que casi te acuso de darme un colgante maldito! Qué tonta soy."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3975
translate Spanish ch2m_11_a6a23eb1:

    # "If she treasures this token of our relationship as much as Grace said she does, I would hate to give her any misgivings about it. I put my own suspicions aside and reassure her."
    "Si aprecia tanto esta muestra de nuestra relación como dice Grace, no me gustaría que tuviera dudas al respecto. Dejo a un lado mis propias sospechas y la tranquilizo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3976
translate Spanish ch2m_11_69e42b87:

    # c "I don't think it's cursed, Marion... just, fortuitous."
    c "No creo que esté maldito, Marion... sólo, fortuito."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3978
translate Spanish ch2m_11_09fea045:

    # m "Always so positive!"
    m "Siempre tan positivo!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3979
translate Spanish ch2m_11_5894dcf7:

    # c "Just trying to be practical. You know, I have a good role model."
    c "Sólo intento ser práctico. Sabes, tengo un buen modelo a seguir."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3981
translate Spanish ch2m_11_1c37d473:

    # "She places her hand on mine, and looks morose for a moment."
    "Pone su mano sobre la mía y parece pensativa por un momento."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3982
translate Spanish ch2m_11_47925901:

    # m "I'll... I'll try to stay positive, too. I'm happy and healthy. I'll manage."
    m "Yo... Yo también intentaré ser positiva. Estoy feliz y saludable. Me las arreglaré."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3985
translate Spanish ch2m_11_1d48190a:

    # "...I'm still not sure I didn't."
    "...aún no estoy seguro de no haberlo hecho."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3986
translate Spanish ch2m_11_07a93188:

    # c "You know, maybe it'd be for the best if you... um... don't continue to wear it."
    c "Sabes, quizás sería mejor si... um... no continuaras usándolo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3989
translate Spanish ch2m_11_4a4b35d8:

    # m "You mean...?"
    m "¿Quieres decir...?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3991
translate Spanish ch2m_11_b7fcae17:

    # c "No! I just... well, maybe I'm being superstitious, but I have to admit the same thought crossed my mind."
    c "¡No! Yo sólo... bueno, tal vez estoy siendo supersticioso, pero tengo que admitir que el mismo pensamiento cruzó mi mente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3992
translate Spanish ch2m_11_0d50ca38:

    # c "Honestly, {i}every{/i} thought crossed my mind. Was it the water? Our food? Clothes? Witchcraft? Us?"
    c "Sinceramente {i}cada pensamiento{/i} cruzó mi mente. ¿Era el agua? ¿Nuestra comida? ¿La ropa? ¿La brujería? ¿Nosotros?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3994
translate Spanish ch2m_11_a1fe0f10:

    # m "Us? You mean... you and me?"
    m "¿Nosotros? ¿Quieres decir... tú y yo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:3995
translate Spanish ch2m_11_6ae16130:

    # c "It was just a dimwitted thought."
    c "Fue sólo un pensamiento tonto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3997
translate Spanish ch2m_11_2d84a8e1:

    # m "No, it wasn't. We both didn't know..."
    m "No, no lo era. Los dos no sabíamos..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:3998
translate Spanish ch2m_11_1c37d473_1:

    # "She places her hand on mine, and looks morose for a moment."
    "Pone su mano sobre la mía y parece pensativa por un momento."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4000
translate Spanish ch2m_11_5806c4c3:

    # m "We still don't know... but that's okay. At least for now. I'm happy and healthy. I'll manage."
    m "Todavía no lo sabemos... pero está bien. Al menos por ahora. Estoy feliz y saludable. Me las arreglaré."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4002
translate Spanish ch2m_11_f693d464:

    # c "{i}We'll{/i} manage."
    c "{i}Bueno{/i} nos las arreglaremos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4004
translate Spanish ch2m_11_ea3a1e42:

    # m "Still \"we?\""
    m "Todavía \"estamos?\""

# game/script_marion.rpy:4005
translate Spanish ch2m_11_4cff680c:

    # c "Always."
    c "Siempre."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4007
translate Spanish ch2m_11_c03c53cf:

    # "Marion picks up her glass, and downs the remaining liquid in one swallow."
    "Marion coge su vaso y se bebe el resto del líquido de un trago."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4008
translate Spanish ch2m_11_169cb6e1:

    # c "You might want to slow down, Marion. We've still got some time to kill."
    c "Deberías ir más despacio, Marion. Todavía tenemos algo de tiempo que matar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4010
translate Spanish ch2m_11_c2e01792:

    # m "I'm on vacation, Malcolm! For one. Whole. Day!"
    m "¡Estoy de vacaciones, Malcolm! Para empezar. Dia. Entero!."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4022
translate Spanish ch2m_11_b7bdcffa:

    # "Marion skips up to the bar and summons Balgair, who obliges her request for more beer."
    "Marion se acerca corriendo a la barra y llama a Balgair, que accede a su petición de más cerveza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4036
translate Spanish ch2m_11_c993a2b3:

    # "As she leans over the bar, her tail whips, lifting her skirt higher and higher."
    "Mientras se inclina sobre la barra, su cola se mueve, levantando cada vez más su falda."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4037
translate Spanish ch2m_11_02886c26:

    # "My heartbeat accelerates. Just a little further, perhaps...? Oh, crivens, Malcolm. Get a grip. I call to her."
    "Mis latidos se aceleran. Sólo un poco más, ¿quizás...? Oh, crivens, Malcolm. Contrólate. La llamo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4038
translate Spanish ch2m_11_e1f32d8e:

    # c "Uh... Marion?"
    c "Uh... Marion?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4039
translate Spanish ch2m_11_d01e1346:

    # "I make frantic motions. After a moment's confusion, my sign language registers, and she turns and covers herself."
    "Hago movimientos frenéticos. Tras un momento de confusión, mi lenguaje de signos se registra y ella se da la vuelta y se cubre."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4045
translate Spanish ch2m_11_0bfed515:

    # m "Oh! I didn't even notice. The thing has a mind of its own it seems."
    m "¡Oh! Ni siquiera me di cuenta. esta cosa tiene una mente propia parece."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4049
translate Spanish ch2m_11_63ab5964:

    # "She heads back to the bar to collect her drink. I can't help but think she actually has full control over that tail."
    "Vuelve al bar a recoger su bebida. No puedo evitar pensar que realmente tiene pleno control sobre esa cola."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4057
translate Spanish ch2m_11_bae4a088:

    # "As soon as I think that, though, she's on the ground, crouching. Her tail lifts her skirt again, exposing everything."
    "Sin embargo, tan pronto como pienso eso, ella está en el suelo, agachada. Su cola levanta de nuevo la falda, dejándolo todo al descubierto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4058
translate Spanish ch2m_11_b5f5e03e:

    # c "Marion!"
    c "Marion!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4059
translate Spanish ch2m_11_e508ecfb:

    # m "I dropped my kerchief, Malcolm!"
    m "Se me cayó el pañuelo, Malcolm!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4060
translate Spanish ch2m_11_f692b5e7:

    # "She's fumbling on the floor, and I rush over to help her."
    "Está buscando a tientas en el suelo y me apresuro a ayudarla."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4068
translate Spanish ch2m_11_49282eac:

    # "Her tail flies up again and whacks the noggin of some burly codger at the bar. He jumps up from his seat to accuse his companion of assault."
    "Su cola se eleva de nuevo y golpea la cabeza de un fornido camarero. Este se levanta de su asiento y acusa a su compañero de agresión."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4069
translate Spanish ch2m_11_58686da9:

    # "I hear shouts and commotion as Marion finally finds her treasured kerchief, and we tie it tightly around her head."
    "Oigo gritos y alboroto cuando Marion encuentra por fin su preciado pañuelo y se lo atamos con fuerza alrededor de la cabeza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4084
translate Spanish ch2m_11_4b7ef52f:

    # "The old man throws a punch at his friend, but it seems his vision is lacking, and the swing is easily dodged."
    "El anciano lanza un puñetazo a su amigo, pero parece que le falta visión y el golpe es fácilmente esquivado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4085
translate Spanish ch2m_11_f4e28d5e:

    # "Lots of grumbling ensues, and Balgair shouts to the pair."
    "A continuación, Balgair grita a la pareja."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4087
translate Spanish ch2m_11_57ce5698:

    # b "Boys, it's the Lord's day. No fights until you pay for a fourth round!"
    b "Chicos, es el día del Señor. ¡Nada de peleas hasta que paguéis un cuarto asalto!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4088
translate Spanish ch2m_11_4aa08d9f:

    # "Balgair places a hand on each of the men's shoulders, and shoves both them back onto their stools."
    "Balgair pone una mano sobre los hombros de cada uno de los hombres y los empuja de nuevo a sus asientos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4097
translate Spanish ch2m_11_82256e86:

    # c "Maybe it's best to duck out, Marion."
    c "Tal vez sea mejor escabullirse, Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4098
translate Spanish ch2m_11_8ff3cd13:

    # m "I'd say so."
    m "Yo diría que sí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4102
translate Spanish ch2m_11_55341249:

    # "As we're walking to the door, Balgair intercepts us."
    "Mientras nos dirigimos a la puerta, Balgair nos intercepta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4104
translate Spanish ch2m_11_d2e08c47:

    # b "You two... I've broken up a lot of fights in this here pub, but never one started by a wee lass. Now, hightail it out of here!"
    b "Ustedes dos... He interrumpido muchas peleas en esta taberna, pero nunca una iniciada por una jovencita. ¡Ahora, largo de aquí!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4123
translate Spanish ch2m_11_56d8a61a:

    # "We exit, giddy from nervous laughter. Marion's eyes are bright and alive. We amble back to the church, taking the long route along the water."
    "Salimos, mareados por la risa nerviosa. Los ojos de Marion están brillantes y vivos. Regresamos a la iglesia por el camino largo que bordea el agua."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4125
translate Spanish ch2m_11_913f90c4:

    # "I take her hand in mine again, this time noticing the tips of her fingernails have become chipped and grey."
    "Vuelvo a tomar su mano entre las mías, y esta vez me doy cuenta de que las puntas de sus uñas están astilladas y grises."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4126
translate Spanish ch2m_11_5be4d04b:

    # "Now isn't the time to worry. It's time to enjoy the sun, which has finally made its appearance from behind the clouds. A rainbow arches over the loch."
    "Ahora no es el momento de preocuparse. Es hora de disfrutar del sol, que por fin ha hecho su aparición tras las nubes. Un arco iris se arquea sobre el lago."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4128
translate Spanish ch2m_11_e0ee6c24:

    # "I point up."
    "Señalo hacia arriba."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4129
translate Spanish ch2m_11_43cd8deb:

    # c "You think that's for us?"
    c "Crees que es para nosotros?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4131
translate Spanish ch2m_11_e0795bc7:

    # m "I do!"
    m "Sí!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4133
translate Spanish ch2m_11_b9ee263d:

    # "She clings closer to my arm and sighs."
    "Se aferra más a mi brazo y suspira."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4134
translate Spanish ch2m_11_00d1a4cd:

    # m "I hope we can spend every day together."
    m "Espero que podamos pasar todos los días juntos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4137
translate Spanish ch2m_11_e7f9f544:

    # m "I mean... someday... maybe... I mean, if you want to!"
    m "Quiero decir... algún día... quizás... Quiero decir, si quieres!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4138
translate Spanish ch2m_11_a2c4fb37:

    # "Her timidity melts my heart."
    "Su timidez me derrite el corazón."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4139
translate Spanish ch2m_11_7dee05ba:

    # c "There's nothing I'd like more. What do you say to another picnic this week, after we've sorted the sheep into their new ranges?"
    c "No hay nada que me gustaría más. ¿Qué me dices de otro picnic esta semana, después de que hayamos clasificado a las ovejas en sus nuevos rangos?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4141
translate Spanish ch2m_11_ec0c8343:

    # m "Why wait? If I'm taking the day off, I think you should too. You deserve it!"
    m "¿Por qué esperar? Si yo me tomo el día libre, creo que tú también deberías. Te lo mereces."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4142
translate Spanish ch2m_11_549fad98:

    # c "I do?"
    c "Ah, sí?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4144
translate Spanish ch2m_11_07425488:

    # m "Absolutely. And all that drink worked up a mighty hunger in me. I'm at your disposal, Captain!"
    m "Absolutamente. Y toda esa bebida despertó un hambre poderosa en mí. ¡Estoy a su disposición, Capitán!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4145
translate Spanish ch2m_11_885842f7:

    # "She's still tipsy, I can tell, but she also makes it hard to say no. Spending the whole day with Marion, and with no chores to distract us? I can't think of anything I'd rather do."
    "Todavía está achispada, lo noto, pero también hace que sea difícil decir que no. ¿Pasar todo el día con Marion, y sin tareas que nos distraigan? No puedo pensar en nada que preferiría hacer."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4146
translate Spanish ch2m_11_e9b2fdb9:

    # "The sheep have lived off the harsh Torridon slopes for centuries. They can manage another day without us. I accept Marion's proposal, as well as the incidental promotion."
    "Las ovejas llevan siglos viviendo de las duras laderas de Torridon. Pueden arreglárselas otro día sin nosotros. Acepto la propuesta de Marion, así como la promoción incidental."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4147
translate Spanish ch2m_11_95da32e9:

    # c "Well then, let me gather up some scones and cheeses from the house when I get back. Gran made fresh gingerbread that we could share."
    c "Bueno, entonces, déjame recoger algunos bollos y quesos de la casa cuando regrese. La abuela hizo pan de jengibre fresco que podríamos compartir."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4149
translate Spanish ch2m_11_a6779556:

    # m "Yes, of course. That sounds lovely!"
    m "Sí, por supuesto. ¡Eso suena encantador!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4150
translate Spanish ch2m_11_157e0171:

    # c "Under the alders again?"
    c "¿Otra vez bajo los alisos?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4152
translate Spanish ch2m_11_3197d678:

    # m "Yes, let's!"
    m "Sí, vamos!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4170
translate Spanish ch2m_11_7988a6e8:

    # "We collect Gran and Grace back near the church. While Marion and I have spent the last while drying out, my grandmother and her new Whist chum are quite plainly pie-eyed."
    "Recogemos a la abuela y a Grace cerca de la iglesia. Mientras Marion y yo hemos pasado el último rato secándonos, mi abuela y su nuevo amigo de Whist están con los ojos como platos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4172
translate Spanish ch2m_11_9fa90a98:

    # s "Malcolm! I won twelve pence and the pocketwatch out of Robina's husband's waistcoat. The old galoot never saw me comin'! Three tricks in, and we had 'em suckered."
    s "Malcolm! Gané doce peniques y el reloj de bolsillo del chaleco del marido de Robina. ¡El viejo nunca me vio venir! Tres trucos y los teníamos engañados."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4174
translate Spanish ch2m_11_18ffc279:

    # "Gran slurs her words, and drops a shiny new pocketwatch into my palm. While I know at heart I should be discomfited by her actions, I'm relieved to see her so chipper."
    "La Abue arrastra las palabras y me deja caer un reluciente reloj de bolsillo en la palma de la mano. Aunque en el fondo sé que debería estar disgustada por sus acciones, me alivia verla tan alegre."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4175
translate Spanish ch2m_11_9b726349:

    # "Grace, meanwhile, nearly topples into my Gran's arms."
    "Grace, mientras tanto, casi cae en los brazos de mi abuela."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4177
translate Spanish ch2m_11_0aa03584:

    # g "It's true! We're a right mighty fine team, Agnes and me!"
    g "Es verdad! Agnes y yo formamos un buen equipo!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4179
translate Spanish ch2m_11_60e5c424:

    # m "And the cordial?"
    m "¿Y el cordial?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4181
translate Spanish ch2m_11_b9f6824c:

    # g "Best—"
    g "Bueno-"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4183
translate Spanish ch2m_11_4f752484:

    # "She stops to hiccup."
    "Se detiene para quitar el hipo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4185
translate Spanish ch2m_11_852f107e:

    # g "Best I ever tasted!"
    g "El mejor que he probado!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4193
translate Spanish ch2m_11_a90ed589:

    # "Marion and I manage to wrangle our cockeyed companions, and get them both atop the horses. We're halfway back to our respective homes when we start hearing snores."
    "Marion y yo conseguimos enredar a nuestros compañeros y subirlos a los caballos. Estamos a mitad de camino de vuelta a nuestras respectivas casas cuando empezamos a oír ronquidos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4194
translate Spanish ch2m_11_dad23949:

    # m "I'll get mine washed up and put to sleep. How about yours?"
    m "Voy a lavar el mío y ponerlo a dormir. ¿Y el tuyo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4200
translate Spanish ch2m_11_d9b3e01c:

    # c "Same here. Meet you at the alders, Marion."
    c "Lo mismo digo. Nos vemos en los alisos, Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4201
translate Spanish ch2m_11_adee8fa8:

    # m "I'll bring sweets."
    m "Llevaré dulces."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4202
translate Spanish ch2m_11_b744228a:

    # c "I'll bring savories."
    c "Traeré salados."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4203
translate Spanish ch2m_11_6c140868:

    # m "See you soon!"
    m "Hasta pronto!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4234
translate Spanish ch2m_12_3fafda28:

    # "Out under the hilltop grove, Marion stands laying out throws of her own. Watching her toss out the large cotton quilts, it's as if I'm seeing my future."
    "Bajo la arboleda de la colina, Marion está colocando sus propias colchas. Viéndola extender las grandes colchas de algodón, es como si viera mi futuro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4235
translate Spanish ch2m_12_1adefdf9:

    # "I could stand there and watch her lay out each blanket as if this were our home."
    "Podía quedarme allí y verla colocar cada manta como si fuera nuestra casa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4236
translate Spanish ch2m_12_6ae95adf:

    # "She is patient, endearing, and hope-filled, a delightful—and impressive—combination for a girl who has fought so bravely to maintain her personal home front."
    "Es paciente, entrañable y llena de esperanza, una combinación encantadora -e impresionante- para una chica que ha luchado tan valientemente por mantener su frente personal."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4247
translate Spanish ch2m_12_9afe68f0:

    # "As I approach, I have a vision of waking up to that smile, that heart, that body, day in and day out. Nothing has ever filled me with such an immediate sense of relief and excitement."
    "A medida que me acerco, tengo la visión de despertarme con esa sonrisa, ese corazón, ese cuerpo, día tras día. Nunca nada me había llenado de una sensación tan inmediata de alivio y emoción."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4259
translate Spanish ch2m_12_3f6b1de6:

    # m "Hello!"
    m "Hola!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4260
translate Spanish ch2m_12_df7e25e6:

    # "Marion waves after she sets down the last quilt."
    "Marion saluda con la mano después de dejar la última colcha."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4272
translate Spanish ch2m_12_537f47b9:

    # "I can't help myself. I drop my basket and run to her, picking her up by the waist, and spinning her wildly until she begins kissing me so passionately that I can't keep my legs from buckling."
    "No puedo contenerme. Dejo caer la cesta y corro hacia ella, la cojo por la cintura y la hago girar salvajemente hasta que empieza a besarme con tanta pasión que no puedo evitar que se me doblen las piernas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4276
translate Spanish ch2m_12_0c746142:

    # "We fall into the pile of quilts, her on top of me. Her legs straddle my hips, and I hope I can keep myself in proper form."
    "Caemos sobre la pila de colchas, ella encima de mí. Sus piernas se sientan a horcajadas sobre mis caderas, y espero poder mantenerme en forma."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4285
translate Spanish ch2m_12_3320e6f7:

    # "She bends down to kiss me once more, and my hand naturally goes to her head, knocking off her kerchief. When we break apart, her horns are the first thing I notice."
    "Se inclina para besarme una vez más, y mi mano se dirige naturalmente a su cabeza, quitándole el pañuelo. Cuando nos separamos, lo primero que veo son sus cuernos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4287
translate Spanish ch2m_12_19eafa24:

    # "She notices that I notice."
    "Se da cuenta de que me doy cuenta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4288
translate Spanish ch2m_12_fa291a15:

    # m "They don't bother you?"
    m "No te molestan?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4289
translate Spanish ch2m_12_34a8f6df:

    # c "No. No, they don't. Everything about you is perfect, Marion."
    c "No. No, no lo hacen. Todo en ti es perfecto, Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4290
translate Spanish ch2m_12_7fb8e37c:

    # "She feels free enough to keep the kerchief free, and has me tugging playfully on her new ears. They feel like the softest lambswool."
    "Se siente lo suficientemente libre como para dejar libre el pañuelo, y me tiene tirando juguetonamente de sus nuevas orejas. Son como la lana más suave."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4292
translate Spanish ch2m_12_78ad7da1:

    # "In between kisses and embraces, we just gaze at each other, ignoring the heat of the sunshine and the sounds of birds chirping."
    "Entre besos y abrazos, nos limitamos a mirarnos, ignorando el calor del sol y el piar de los pájaros."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4293
translate Spanish ch2m_12_9499934f:

    # c "I..."
    c "Yo..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4294
translate Spanish ch2m_12_72902880:

    # m "Yes, Malcolm?"
    m "¿Sí, Malcolm?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4301
translate Spanish ch2m_12_5c5e9c75:

    # "I clasp the nape of her neck, letting my thumb caress her soft ears again. I pull her close to me, and watch her beautiful gold eyes begin to close. Our lips touch, and my chest pounds from euphoria."
    "Le acaricio la nuca y dejo que mi pulgar vuelva a acariciar sus suaves orejas. La atraigo hacia mí y veo cómo sus preciosos ojos dorados empiezan a cerrarse. Nuestros labios se rozan y mi pecho palpita de euforia."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4302
translate Spanish ch2m_12_262e0092:

    # "My stomach growls, but I can't possibly think about food right now. She feels like heaven, as always. Her lips are so welcoming."
    "Me gruñe el estómago, pero ahora no puedo pensar en comida. Se siente como en el cielo, como siempre. Sus labios son tan acogedores."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4303
translate Spanish ch2m_12_f2e0a2a2:

    # "I brush the hair from her forehead as we continue to kiss more intensely. One hand travels down her back, stopping to lightly stroke her tail."
    "Le retiro el pelo de la frente mientras seguimos besándonos con más intensidad. Una mano baja por su espalda y se detiene para acariciarle ligeramente la cola."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4305
translate Spanish ch2m_12_6b6089a7:

    # m "Malcolm, I don't understand how you can be so gentle, so pure, so caring. So... completely accepting."
    m "Malcolm, no entiendo cómo puedes ser tan gentil, tan puro, tan cariñoso. Tan... completamente tolerante."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4306
translate Spanish ch2m_12_b633b9df:

    # c "I want to build a relationship. A bond built on a solid stone foundation. One we build together."
    c "Quiero construir una relación. Un vínculo construido sobre una base de piedra sólida. Uno que construyamos juntos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4308
translate Spanish ch2m_12_13bebeaf:

    # m "After all you've been through... you shouldn't have to..."
    m "Después de todo lo que has pasado... no deberías tener que..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4317
translate Spanish ch2m_12_eec4ee11:

    # "She closes her eyes tightly, and falls onto my chest. When she speaks again, it is with her face turned from me."
    "Cierra los ojos con fuerza y se deja caer sobre mi pecho. Cuando vuelve a hablar, lo hace dándome la espalda."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4318
translate Spanish ch2m_12_e41f51b1:

    # m "You shouldn't have to look at me like this."
    m "No deberías tener que mirarme así."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4319
translate Spanish ch2m_12_7fa45d1c:

    # "My heart drops. The burden she carries is unfair, but not insurmountable. I tell her as much."
    "Se me cae el corazón. La carga que lleva es injusta, pero no insuperable. Se lo digo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4320
translate Spanish ch2m_12_bc87b098:

    # c "Look at me, please, Marion."
    c "Mírame, por favor, Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4322
translate Spanish ch2m_12_973089ce:

    # "We lock eyes, and I make sure I am clear when I finally admit how I feel towards her."
    "Nos miramos a los ojos y me aseguro de ser claro cuando por fin admito lo que siento por ella."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4323
translate Spanish ch2m_12_24ed7f67:

    # c "I love you, Marion. You. Not just your face, your body, your brain, your heart... but {i}all{/i} of those things."
    c "Te quiero, Marion. A ti. No sólo tu cara, tu cuerpo, tu cerebro, tu corazón... sino {i}todas{/i} esas cosas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4325
translate Spanish ch2m_12_566e2c03:

    # c "Every single thing about you that I can't even name. The way you treat me... others, too. The times you give of yourself beyond what is needed. I love you. All of you, Marion."
    c "Cada cosa de ti que ni siquiera puedo nombrar. La forma en que me tratas... a los demás también. Las veces que das de ti más allá de lo necesario. Te quiero. Todo de ti, Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4327
translate Spanish ch2m_12_7210a466:

    # "{i}I love her.{/i} With three simple words, in one profound moment, every worry that's been weighing on my soul since I returned home seems to evaporate."
    "{i}La amo.{/i} Con tres simples palabras, en un momento profundo, todas las preocupaciones que han estado pesando sobre mi alma desde que volví a casa parecen evaporarse."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4329
translate Spanish ch2m_12_4cdbf6ec:

    # "Marion starts crying."
    "Marion empieza a llorar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4330
translate Spanish ch2m_12_b536dd1c:

    # m "You... love me?"
    m "Tú... me amas?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4331
translate Spanish ch2m_12_c6ed1d46:

    # c "I do. I love you."
    c "Sí. Yo te amo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4332
translate Spanish ch2m_12_ca9e05d7:

    # "Quietly, cautiously, but determined, Marion speaks up."
    "En voz baja, con cautela, pero decidida, Marion toma la palabra."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4333
translate Spanish ch2m_12_855c064e:

    # m "Malcolm... I love you, too."
    m "Malcolm... Yo también te amo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4334
translate Spanish ch2m_12_b53dcee2:

    # "I keep my hand behind her head as we kiss, this time as new people, people in love. In love with each other."
    "Mantengo mi mano detrás de su cabeza mientras nos besamos, esta vez como personas nuevas, personas enamoradas. Enamorados el uno del otro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4340
translate Spanish ch2m_12_5aaf04c8:

    # "We roll over until I rest on top of her soft and warm body. We kiss again, and my hand trails down her arm to the tidy bow right below her chest."
    "Rodamos hasta que descanso sobre su cuerpo suave y cálido. Volvemos a besarnos, y mi mano recorre su brazo hasta el prolijo moño que tiene justo debajo del pecho."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4341
translate Spanish ch2m_12_d1862799:

    # "I roll my fingers through the loops and hear her giggles."
    "Paso los dedos por los bucles y oigo sus risitas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4342
translate Spanish ch2m_12_85e3c995:

    # m "Malcolm! Watch those wandering hands."
    m "¡Malcolm! Cuidado con esas manos inquietas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4343
translate Spanish ch2m_12_c3306bfa:

    # c "Oh, I am. I'm watching you watch them."
    c "Lo estoy haciendo. Te estoy viendo mirarlas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4344
translate Spanish ch2m_12_abf68adb:

    # "I tease apart the bow until the ribbon falls open. I follow suit with the tiny silk bow dangling from the lace lining the bust of her dress. It's then I realize that the bows are nothing but decoration."
    "Separo el lazo hasta que la cinta se abre. Hago lo mismo con el pequeño lazo de seda que cuelga del encaje que cubre el busto de su vestido. Entonces me doy cuenta de que los lazos no son más que adornos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4345
translate Spanish ch2m_12_ec31db99:

    # "Marion can't stop laughing, and it fills me with both joy and arousal."
    "Marion no puede parar de reír, y eso me llena tanto de alegría como de excitación."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4346
translate Spanish ch2m_12_90fe7e2b:

    # m "The bows to nowhere."
    m "Los arcos a ninguna parte."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4347
translate Spanish ch2m_12_0ad34826:

    # c "I see that!"
    c "Ya lo veo!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4348
translate Spanish ch2m_12_4272a234:

    # "She winks."
    "Me guiña un ojo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4349
translate Spanish ch2m_12_f0ffdd9d:

    # m "The clasps are in the back."
    m "Los cierres están en la parte trasera."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4350
translate Spanish ch2m_12_759c6159:

    # "She takes my hand and guides me to the hooks and closures behind her dress."
    "Me coge de la mano y me guía hasta los ganchos y cierres de detrás de su vestido."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4351
translate Spanish ch2m_12_6b163a84:

    # c "Are... are you sure?"
    c "Estás... estás segura?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4352
translate Spanish ch2m_12_ab77d2d2:

    # "I'm not entirely sure what's happening... except I am, and I'm shocked."
    "No estoy del todo seguro de lo que está pasando... excepto de que lo estoy, y estoy conmocionado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4353
translate Spanish ch2m_12_1ea1ecc8:

    # m "Yes. Quite."
    m "Sí. Bastante."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4363
translate Spanish ch2m_12_a_77041c96:

    # "My fingertips unhook several loops and buttons behind her, and her dress starts to billow off of her from the front. It's loose, and her breasts rise and fall as her breathing gets quicker."
    "Mis dedos desabrochan varias presillas y botones detrás de ella, y su vestido empieza a ondear por delante. Le queda suelto y sus pechos suben y bajan a medida que su respiración se acelera."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4380
translate Spanish ch2m_12_a_e90adfb0:

    # "I, myself, am also nearly gasping for air. First from the physical contact... then from something very different..."
    "Yo también estoy casi jadeando. Primero por el contacto físico... luego por algo muy diferente..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4385
translate Spanish ch2m_12_a_316b142a:

    # "Marion's face changes from happiness to panic as she sees my look of concern. Her eyes get huge, as I blink faster and faster trying to unsee the changes before me."
    "a cara de Marion pasa de la felicidad al pánico al ver mi mirada de preocupación. Sus ojos se vuelven enormes, mientras yo parpadeo cada vez más deprisa intentando no ver los cambios que tengo ante mí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4386
translate Spanish ch2m_12_a_661fd504:

    # "Marion's transformations start once more, much faster and more pronounced than any time I've seen them."
    "Comienzan de nuevo las transformaciones de Marion, mucho más rápidas y pronunciadas que nunca."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4387
translate Spanish ch2m_12_a_8ee6b178:

    # c "It's... your face, Marion."
    c "Es... tu cara, Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4388
translate Spanish ch2m_12_a_b4310bce:

    # m "What! What about it? Malcolm, you're scaring me!"
    m "¡Qué! ¿Qué pasa con eso? ¡Malcolm, me estás asustando!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4393
translate Spanish ch2m_12_a_612e212b:

    # "I pull out the pocketwatch Gran had won earlier, and hold the shiny metal up to her mouth. In it, she can see her reflection, and she lets out a noise I can only describe as a bray."
    "Saco el reloj de bolsillo que la abuela había ganado antes y le acerco el brillante metal a la boca. En él se ve reflejada y suelta un sonido que sólo puedo describir como un quejido."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4394
translate Spanish ch2m_12_a_1d768e01:

    # m "No! It can't be."
    m "No! No puede ser."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4395
translate Spanish ch2m_12_a_3c2a4f6e:

    # c "Are you okay? Does it hurt?"
    c "Te encuentras bien? Te duele?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4396
translate Spanish ch2m_12_a_1763de18:

    # m "It tingles. Malcolm! Make it stop! It has to stop."
    m "Hace cosquillas. Malcolm! Haz que pare! Tiene que parar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4403
translate Spanish ch2m_12_a_86b3937b:

    # "Instead, her face contorts further. Her lips, bright and swollen from our kisses, pucker out and extend horizontally."
    "En cambio, su rostro se contorsiona aún más. Sus labios, brillantes e hinchados por nuestros besos, se fruncen y se extienden horizontalmente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4408
translate Spanish ch2m_12_a_4d403886:

    # "Her nostrils flare open, and stay that way. They huff a bit, taking in more air than normal. Small, clear whiskers break through the skin around her nose."
    "Sus fosas nasales se abren y permanecen así. Resopla un poco y aspira más aire de lo normal. Unos pequeños bigotes transparentes atraviesan la piel que rodea su nariz."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4409
translate Spanish ch2m_12_a_b2ddc820:

    # m "Ow! It stings! What do I do!?"
    m "Ay! Me pica! Qué hago!?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4410
translate Spanish ch2m_12_a_89b4d9ae:

    # c "Your cheeks!"
    c "Tus mejillas!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4418
translate Spanish ch2m_12_a_e1a4e839:

    # "Marion's ruddy complexion darkens to a pale brown, like that of fresh tanned hide. I touch her face, and the fur develops as I drag my thumb down the side of her cheek."
    "La tez rubicunda de Marion se oscurece hasta adquirir un color marrón pálido, como el de la piel recién curtida. Le toco la cara, y el pelaje se desarrolla mientras arrastro el pulgar por el costado de su mejilla."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4419
translate Spanish ch2m_12_a_ec2be08c:

    # m "Stop! It's getting worse!"
    m "Para! Está empeorando!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4437
translate Spanish ch2m_12_a_e8dee312:

    # "Marion shoves the pocketwatch away from her view, and me off of her body. She stands and clutches her own arms."
    "Marion aparta el reloj de bolsillo de su vista y a mí de su cuerpo. Se levanta y se agarra los brazos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4438
translate Spanish ch2m_12_a_953b7729:

    # "As she rubs her shoulders, her dress slips forward, nearly coming off. She fumbles holding it up as her fingers curl under, the tips becoming hard and grey."
    "Al frotarse los hombros, el vestido se le resbala y casi se le sale. Tantea para sostenerlo mientras sus dedos se enroscan bajo él y las puntas se vuelven duras y grises."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4439
translate Spanish ch2m_12_a_2ff43963:

    # m "My hands! Oh, no. I... I have to get out of here!"
    m "Mis manos! Oh, no. I... ¡Tengo que salir de aquí!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4440
translate Spanish ch2m_12_a_238a1061:

    # c "Don't leave! Please, I want to make sure you're safe."
    c "¡No te vayas! Por favor, quiero asegurarme de que estás a salvo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4441
translate Spanish ch2m_12_a_ede5122c:

    # m "I'm not! {i}I'm not safe, or well, or all right!{/i}"
    m "No lo estoy! {i}No estoy a salvo, ni bien, ni de acuerdo!{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4443
translate Spanish ch2m_12_a_041fb487:

    # "She pulls up her dress and hooks the top closed, looking down once again at her pinched, greying hands and spreading fur."
    "Se sube el vestido y lo cierra con un gancho, volviendo a mirar sus manos encanecidas y su pelaje extendido."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4445
translate Spanish ch2m_12_a_857ef609:

    # m "I have fur, Malcolm... like an animal! And... a {i}muzzle!{/i}"
    m "Tengo pelo, Malcolm... ¡como un animal! Y... un Un {i}hocico!{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4448
translate Spanish ch2m_12_a_360fdc89:

    # m "What will I do? What will {i}we{/i} do?"
    m "Qué voy a hacer? Qué voy a hacer? {i}Qué hacemos?{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4450
translate Spanish ch2m_12_a_5a86a858:

    # "I stare at her, my mouth agape, aware that the only thing I'm sure of is our uncertainty. I have no words to calm Marion, or to reassure her. They would be of no use anyway."
    "La miro fijamente, con la boca abierta, consciente de que de lo único que estoy seguro es de nuestra incertidumbre. No tengo palabras para calmar a Marion, ni para tranquilizarla. De todos modos, no servirían de nada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4451
translate Spanish ch2m_12_a_a520d445:

    # "Gone is the bliss only recently shared by our mutual declarations of love. There, under the alder trees, distress overtakes us both. I answer her with fervent honesty."
    "Atrás queda la dicha que hace poco compartíamos con nuestras mutuas declaraciones de amor. Allí, bajo los alisos, la angustia nos invade a los dos. Le respondo con ferviente sinceridad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4452
translate Spanish ch2m_12_a_60ed431d:

    # c "I don't know, Marion. I don't know."
    c "No lo sé, Marion. No lo sé."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4545
translate Spanish ch3m_01_fba89a51:

    # m "Malcolm! I'm one of... {i}them!{/i}"
    m "¡Malcolm! Soy uno de... {i}ellos!{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4564
translate Spanish ch3m_01_fd0704f9:

    # "Marion cries, in near hysterics, her mind on the herd in the field. I wrap her in my arms, and she melts into my chest, sobbing."
    "Marion llora, casi histérica, con la mente puesta en el rebaño del campo. La envuelvo en mis brazos y se derrite en mi pecho, sollozando"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4566
translate Spanish ch3m_01_d1021539:

    # c "You're not, Marion. You're absolutely not. We'll fix this. We'll figure it out."
    c "No lo eres, Marion. Absolutamente no. Arreglaremos esto. Lo resolveremos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4587
translate Spanish ch3m_01_cdbab9ca:

    # "Marion pushes me back, tears streaming down her muzzle.{w} {i}Did I really just think muzzle? What is going on?{/i}"
    "Marion me empuja hacia atrás, con lágrimas cayendo por su hocico.{w} {i}De verdad acabo de pensar hocico? ¿Qué está pasando?{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4588
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a8a6fe9e:

    # "It's then that I concede that she has every right to be hysterical. This... {i}illness? Curse?{/i} Whatever it is, it's uncalled for, and unfair to her."
    "Es entonces cuando reconozco que tiene todo el derecho a estar histérica. Esto... {i}¿Enfermedad? ¿Maldición?{/i} Sea lo que sea, está fuera de lugar y es injusto para ella."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4589
translate Spanish ch3m_01_8ce63018:

    # "Never has a more caring person been shouldered with a more insurmountable problem."
    "Nunca una persona más solidaria ha tenido que cargar con un problema más insuperable."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4590
translate Spanish ch3m_01_10bff9bb:

    # "Even to me, the outsider, her appearance, while sweet, is quite unnerving and unnatural. We both need answers."
    "Incluso para mí, la forastera, su aspecto, aunque dulce, es bastante desconcertante y antinatural. Ambos necesitamos respuestas"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4592
translate Spanish ch3m_01_0fcaca22:

    # m "You keep saying \"we'll figure it out!\" But what? It was bad before, but now... now it's very, very... it's just very bad! {i}Awful!{/i} I most certainly can't hide it anymore. I can never, ever be seen!"
    m "Sigues diciendo \"¡ya lo resolveremos!\" Pero qué? Antes era malo, pero ahora... ahora es muy, muy... es que es muy malo! {i}¡Qué horror!{/i} Ya no puedo ocultarlo. ¡Nunca, nunca me verán!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4593
translate Spanish ch3m_01_fef88c33:

    # "She looks at me expectantly, and I feel shame in my own helplessness."
    "Me mira expectante y siento vergüenza de mi propia impotencia."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4595
translate Spanish ch3m_01_955f377f:

    # m "I ate {i}bogbean,{/i} Malcolm! For what?! I still look hideous!"
    m "Me comí un {i}frijol,{/i} Malcolm! para qué?! sigo estando horrible!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4596
translate Spanish ch3m_01_0a683578:

    # c "You're not hideous, Marion! You're beautiful... you're still... you!"
    c "¡No eres horrible, Marion! Eres hermosa... sigues siendo... ¡tú!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4598
translate Spanish ch3m_01_69026215:

    # "Even as I say it, I know neither one of us believes that in its entirety. She is still Marion, somehow, internally, but... so very changed. And quite frightened."
    "Incluso mientras lo digo, sé que ninguno de los dos lo cree en su totalidad. Ella sigue siendo Marion, de alguna manera, internamente, pero... muy cambiada. Y bastante asustada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4607
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b54a8732:

    # "I take her hands in mine, stroking her fingers... if they can still be called that. They've become dark and stiff."
    "Tomo sus manos entre las mías y le acaricio los dedos... si es que aún pueden llamarse así. Se han vuelto oscuros y rígidos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4608
translate Spanish ch3m_01_6f0492c8:

    # "As I console her, I feel them shifting beneath my ministrations, becoming thicker and more rigid..."
    "Mientras la consuelo, siento cómo se mueven bajo mis caricias, se vuelven más gruesos y rígidos..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4621
translate Spanish ch3m_01_6b891ad2:

    # "...Becoming cloven hooves."
    "...convirtiéndose en pezuñas hendidas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4624
translate Spanish ch3m_01_385764af:

    # "My breath catches in my throat. It's like I'm reliving my nightmare, only with the roles reversed."
    "Se me corta la respiración. Es como si estuviera reviviendo mi pesadilla, solo que con los papeles invertidos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4625
translate Spanish ch3m_01_3b9e18e0:

    # "A shiver pierces through me like a sheer, baltic wind. Am {i}I{/i} changing Marion, the way that in the dream, she changed me?"
    "Un escalofrío me atraviesa como un viento báltico. ¿Estoy cambiando a Marion como ella me cambió a mí en el sueño?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4627
translate Spanish ch3m_01_605e49c3:

    # "No. This is no dream. I feel as helpless as she does, and I've little to offer in words of wisdom."
    "No. Esto no es un sueño. Me siento tan impotente como ella, y tengo poco que ofrecer en palabras de sabiduría."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4630
translate Spanish ch3m_01_8d008bf0:

    # m "I'm not me! You must see that! What shall we do? Go off to the apothecary and ask for a tincture for cow face? A balm to rub on a tail? It's absurd, Malcolm! It's..."
    m "¡Yo no soy yo! ¡Tienes que verlo! ¿Qué vamos a hacer? ¿Ir al boticario y pedir una tintura para la cara de vaca? ¿Un bálsamo para frotar en la cola? ¡Es absurdo, Malcolm! Es..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4639
translate Spanish ch3m_01_0a76df5b:

    # "Her eyes go wide as she looks down, seeing her hoof-hands, turning and flexing them instinctively. They move more naturally than their stiffness would suggest."
    "Sus ojos se abren de par en par cuando mira hacia abajo, viendo sus cascos-manos, girándolos y flexionándolos instintivamente. Se mueven con más naturalidad de lo que sugiere su rigidez."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4641
translate Spanish ch3m_01_ed16d753:

    # m "It's getting worse! Oh... Oh my God."
    m "¡Está empeorando! Dios mío."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4646
translate Spanish ch3m_01_7d9aceee:

    # "She inhales sharply, and looks as if she is about to admit something unforgivable."
    "Inspira bruscamente y parece a punto de admitir algo imperdonable."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4648
translate Spanish ch3m_01_125ff662:

    # m "At this rate I'm going to turn into a {i}real, live cow!{/i} Drool and all!"
    m "A este paso me voy a convertir en una {i}¡vaca de verdad!{/i} babas y todo!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4655
translate Spanish ch3m_01_442e1f40:

    # "She slumps down, in a stupor. In shock."
    "Se desploma, en estado de estupor. En estado de shock."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4657
translate Spanish ch3m_01_0623f7ec:

    # "I'm taken back to the trenches, watching helplessly as soldiers would go mad after weeks on end of filth, lack of rations, and excesses of caffeine and explosions."
    "Me transporta a las trincheras, viendo impotente cómo los soldados se volvían locos tras semanas y semanas de suciedad, falta de raciones y excesos de cafeína y explosiones."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4658
translate Spanish ch3m_01_d0b7c5c1:

    # "I need to rein Marion in, lest her sanity go too far to be retrieved."
    "Necesito refrenar a Marion, no sea que su cordura vaya demasiado lejos para ser recuperada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4659
translate Spanish ch3m_01_064416ff:

    # c "Come, take my hand. Let's stroll in the garden. Feed Eachann some oats. Anything to take our minds off... this. Even if for a moment."
    c "Ven, toma mi mano. Vamos a pasear por el jardín. Dale de comer avena a Eachann. Cualquier cosa que nos haga olvidar... esto. Aunque sea por un momento."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4662
translate Spanish ch3m_01_2473e3f9:

    # "She looks understandably skeptical when I reach for her hand... er, {i}hoof.{/i}"
    "Parece comprensiblemente escéptica cuando le tomo la mano... {i}casco.{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4663
translate Spanish ch3m_01_5b4f79f1:

    # c "Trust me."
    c "Confía en mí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4670
translate Spanish ch3m_01_0dbe644d:

    # "I help her to stand, as she still seems a bit unsteady."
    "La ayudo a levantarse, ya que todavía parece un poco inestable."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4680
translate Spanish ch3m_01_455d9db4:

    # m "O-oh!"
    m "O-oh!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4688
translate Spanish ch3m_01_0da3d1a3:

    # "She stumbles, landing back in her chair."
    "Tropieza y vuelve a caer en su silla."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4689
translate Spanish ch3m_01_65e32b2c:

    # c "Are you all right?"
    c "Te encuentras bien?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4706
translate Spanish ch3m_01_767b2473:

    # "Marion's shock turns to frustration, as she fumbles with her boots."
    "La sorpresa de Marion se convierte en frustración, mientras tantea con sus botas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4714
translate Spanish ch3m_01_2c905bf0:

    # m "I don't know... it feels like there's a rock in my shoe. But the shoe won't come off."
    m "No sé... siento como si tuviera una piedra en el zapato. Pero el zapato no se sale."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4753
translate Spanish ch3m_01_fc3de421:

    # "Figuring that fingers may be more adept than hooves to deal with shoelaces, I bend down to help. But quickly I realize that the laces are not the problem."
    "Pensando que los dedos pueden ser más hábiles que las pezuñas para manejar los cordones, me agacho para ayudar. Pero enseguida me doy cuenta de que el problema no son los cordones."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4754
translate Spanish ch3m_01_4ca1235b:

    # "Her boot is several sizes too small. Or perhaps more accurately, her {i}foot{/i} is now several sizes too big. I tug on the boot to try to pull it free."
    "Su bota es varias tallas más pequeña. O, para ser más exactos, su {i}pie{/i} es ahora varias tallas más grande. Tiro de la bota para intentar liberarla."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4763
translate Spanish ch3m_01_001eebc9:

    # m "Malcolm, be careful!"
    m "Malcolm, ten cuidado!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4776
translate Spanish ch3m_01_d6cf4cfb:

    # m "S-stop, you're tearing them!"
    m "Para, los estás rompiendo!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4777
translate Spanish ch3m_01_fd85f460:

    # c "That wasn't me!"
    c "No fui yo!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4779
translate Spanish ch3m_01_da0e4696:

    # "Marion groans, and starts twisting her ankle around... impossibly."
    "Marion gime y empieza a torcerse el tobillo... imposiblemente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4781
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b930419c:

    # m "Ooof! What are you doing? That tickles!"
    m "¡Uf! ¿Qué haces? Eso hace cosquillas!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4791
translate Spanish ch3m_01_f1319f4b:

    # "I loosen my grip, just as Marion's hooves burst through both her boots. It's like they have a vendetta against the leather—and perhaps rightly so."
    "Aflojo el agarre, justo cuando las pezuñas de Marion atraviesan sus dos botas. Es como si tuvieran una venganza contra el cuero, y quizá con razón."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4795
translate Spanish ch3m_01_3691ce1a:

    # m "No. No, no, noo..."
    m "No. No, no, noo..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4796
translate Spanish ch3m_01_147d57a1:

    # "I tear my gaze away from the spectacle and look up, expecting her to be scared or crying."
    "Aparto la mirada del espectáculo y levanto los ojos, esperando que esté asustada o llorando."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4798
translate Spanish ch3m_01_8af12af3:

    # m "Those boots were expensive!"
    m "Esas botas eran caras!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4801
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b7ffbc5c:

    # "To my surprise, she is just pouting. For the first time, she seems genuinely undaunted about a change. We both watch, mesmerized."
    "Para mi sorpresa, sólo hace pucheros. Por primera vez, parece realmente indiferente al cambio. Los dos la observamos, hipnotizados."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4809
translate Spanish ch3m_01_4bab55fe:

    # "It's a process, her feet matching her hands. Her heels lift upwards, further twisting and tearing what is left of the boots."
    "Es un proceso, sus pies coinciden con sus manos. Sus talones se elevan hacia arriba, retorciendo y desgarrando aún más lo que queda de las botas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4810
translate Spanish ch3m_01_cb6250ee:

    # "The movement settles just as tiny dew claws pop out below her ankle. Like the rest of her... they're pretty cute and dainty."
    "El movimiento se detiene justo cuando unas pequeñas garras de rocío asoman por debajo de su tobillo. Como el resto de su cuerpo... son bonitas y delicadas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4813
translate Spanish ch3m_01_3c7138da:

    # m "Is it awful?"
    m "Es horrible?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4814
translate Spanish ch3m_01_3940183f:

    # c "No... but it's quite a sight."
    c "No... pero es todo un espectáculo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4821
translate Spanish ch3m_01_52302ab2:

    # "She stretches her leg so we can both see clearly."
    "Estira la pierna para que ambos podamos ver con claridad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4822
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b54ff44e:

    # "The tattered remains of her footwear slough off of... what can no longer be called a foot. The walls of her new hooves seem thick and sturdy."
    "Los andrajosos restos de su calzado se desprenden de... lo que ya no puede llamarse pie. Las paredes de sus nuevos cascos parecen gruesas y resistentes."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4825
translate Spanish ch3m_01_ff0771be:

    # "Marion laughs."
    "Marion ríe."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4827
translate Spanish ch3m_01_bac27047:

    # m "Well... I'll never have to wear shoes again! A quick rinse and I'll be good to go."
    m "Bueno... ¡Nunca más tendré que usar zapatos! Un enjuague rápido y estaré lista."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4829
translate Spanish ch3m_01_cc7d12e3:

    # "One moment, she is terrified, the next she acts like nothing is wrong. I try to forgive her confusion. It's not like I've ever turned into a cow."
    "En un momento está aterrorizada y al siguiente actúa como si no pasara nada. Intento perdonar su confusión. Nunca me he convertido en una vaca."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4830
translate Spanish ch3m_01_485289ab:

    # c "Er... that's a positive spin!"
    c "Eh... eso es un giro positivo!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4832
translate Spanish ch3m_01_769c8203:

    # m "I have to be positive... or I'll go as mad as a March hare."
    m "Tengo que ser positiva... o me volveré loca como una liebre de marzo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4834
translate Spanish ch3m_01_193a2400:

    # "She snorts lightly as she laughs to herself. Her eye twitches."
    "Resopla ligeramente mientras se ríe para sus adentros. Le tiemblan los ojos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4835
translate Spanish ch3m_01_e8ae5e6a:

    # c "Um, Marion—"
    c "Um, Marion—"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4837
translate Spanish ch3m_01_f2af1df2:

    # m "I mean, can you picture me with long, floppy ears? Well, longer... and floppier... Haha!"
    m "Quiero decir, ¿me imaginas con orejas largas y caídas? Bueno, más largas... y flojas... ¡Jaja!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4838
translate Spanish ch3m_01_e5b04cbc:

    # "Effie comes to mind immediately, and I bite my tongue."
    "Effie me viene a la mente inmediatamente, y me muerdo la lengua."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4839
translate Spanish ch3m_01_7532719b:

    # c "Let's tackle one animal body at a time. Marion, please take a deep breath. Take several. As many as you need. I have a plan."
    c "Vamos a abordar un cuerpo animal a la vez. Marion, por favor, respira hondo. Toma varias. Tantas como necesites. Tengo un plan."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4846
translate Spanish ch3m_01_09fa1201:

    # "Her laughter subsides, replaced by a wan smile. In truth, I do not have a plan, but I don't share that. Instead, I resolve to come up with one. And fast."
    "Su risa se apaga, sustituida por una débil sonrisa. La verdad es que no tengo ningún plan, pero no se lo digo a nadie. En lugar de eso, decido pensar en uno. Y rápido."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4848
translate Spanish ch3m_01_ee879599:

    # c "Er... may I borrow your bathroom?"
    c "Eh... me prestas tu baño?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4860
translate Spanish ch3m_01_d8e52e1f:

    # m "{i}This{/i} is your plan?"
    m "¿{i}Este{/i} es tu plan?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4861
translate Spanish ch3m_01_2704b7c1:

    # c "I didn't say it was a good one. Now, close your eyes."
    c "No dije que fuera bueno. Ahora, cierra los ojos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4868
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c73f81cf:

    # "An array of jars and canisters are spread across the counter. I select one labeled \"Lady Esther's All-Purpose, Long-Lasting Face Powder.\""
    "En el mostrador hay un montón de tarros y botes. Selecciono uno con la etiqueta \"Lady Esther's Polvos faciales multiusos de larga duración.\""

# game/script_marion.rpy:4869
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a490c835:

    # "\"Take Your Mind Off Your Nose!\" the side panel announces, \"and never worry about making up in public again.\" Well, time to test that claim to the limit."
    "\"Olvídate de tu nariz!\" anuncia el panel lateral, \"y no volver a preocuparte por liarte en público.\" Pues bien, es hora de poner a prueba esa afirmación hasta el límite."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4912
translate Spanish ch3m_01_e3bab011:

    # "I open the jar and start applying the powder puff to Marion's face. The stuff barely sticks to her fur. Am I doing it right? I'm not exactly a makeup artist."
    "Abro el tarro y empiezo a aplicar el polvo en la cara de Marion. Apenas se le pega al pelo. ¿Lo estoy haciendo bien? No soy exactamente una artista del maquillaje."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4917
translate Spanish ch3m_01_2e79a7da:

    # "A cow snout is not exactly the intended surface, either, I remind myself. I apply the product more liberally, daubing firmly to get it to adhere."
    "Me recuerdo a mí mismo que un hocico de vaca tampoco es exactamente la superficie adecuada. Aplico el producto con más generosidad, frotando con firmeza para que se adhiera."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4920
translate Spanish ch3m_01_8fa3946b:

    # "A cloud of dust billows around her face, soon filling the room. For the first time since the war, I regret not having a gas mask by my side."
    "Una nube de polvo rodea su cara y pronto llena la habitación. Por primera vez desde la guerra, lamento no tener una máscara antigás a mi lado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4925
translate Spanish ch3m_01_9bfd1cd9:

    # m "Malcolm! *cough* I can barely breathe!"
    m "¡Malcolm! *cough* Apenas puedo respirar!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4929
translate Spanish ch3m_01_2e830e97:

    # c "Nearly done, {i}mademoiselle... et voila!{/i}"
    c "Ya casi está, {i}mademoiselle... et voila!{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4935
translate Spanish ch3m_01_e612037c:

    # m "..."
    m "..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4937
translate Spanish ch3m_01_04f3afd3:

    # c "Um. *ahem* {i}Parfait!{/i} We'll wrap your head to cover the horns, tuck in that tail of yours, and no one will notice a thing!"
    c "Um. *ahem* {i}Parfait!{/i} Te envolveremos la cabeza para cubrir los cuernos, te meteremos la cola y nadie notará nada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4939
translate Spanish ch3m_01_eeff158c:

    # m "Are you sure?"
    m "Estás seguro?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4940
translate Spanish ch3m_01_78e3c805:

    # "I put on my most convincing smile... which I hope is at least a little more convincing than her disguise. If she looked like a cow before, now she looks like a ghost! {i}And{/i} a cow."
    "Pongo mi sonrisa más convincente... que espero que al menos sea un poco más convincente que su disfraz. Si antes parecía una vaca, ¡ahora parece un fantasma! {i}y{/i} una vaca."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4941
translate Spanish ch3m_01_d917a482:

    # c "Quite sure! It simply looks like you've not seen daylight for weeks!"
    c "¡Seguro! ¡Simplemente parece como si no hubieras visto la luz del día durante semanas!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4942
translate Spanish ch3m_01_bc36ed0c:

    # m "At this rate, that may well be my future."
    m "A este paso, puede que ese sea mi futuro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4943
translate Spanish ch3m_01_f3c776f2:

    # c "Oh, no, Marion. I promise you that. Never will you become a hermit. I won't allow it. The world needs your beauty."
    c "Oh, no, Marion. Te lo prometo. Nunca te convertirás en una ermitaña. No lo permitiré. El mundo necesita tu belleza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4946
translate Spanish ch3m_01_24f15321:

    # m "You're being silly!"
    m "Estás siendo tonto!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4947
translate Spanish ch3m_01_f3caa70a:

    # c "Perhaps... but it's nice to get a smile from you."
    c "Tal vez... pero es agradable recibir una sonrisa tuya."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4963
translate Spanish ch3m_01_3a935e6a:

    # "The ghost cow embraces me, leaving a large white smudge on my dark shirt. I stand to brush it off, laughing, and open the window to vent out the dust."
    "La vaca fantasma me abraza, dejando una gran mancha blanca en mi camisa oscura. Me levanto para quitármela, riendo, y abro la ventana para ventilar el polvo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4970
translate Spanish ch3m_01_cf19bfcf:

    # c "Er, Marion? Are you expecting company?"
    c "Marion? ¿Esperas compañía?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4972
translate Spanish ch3m_01_1a7db345:

    # m "No. Why?"
    m "No. Por qué?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4977
translate Spanish ch3m_01_fbd52fb2:

    # "We hear a knock. Panic sweeps back over Marion's face."
    "Oímos un golpe. El pánico vuelve a invadir el rostro de Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4978
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c7f9ae04:

    # m "Malcolm, no! Don't answer it! No one can see me like this!"
    m "Malcolm, no! No contestes! Nadie puede verme así!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4980
translate Spanish ch3m_01_5ad1b48d:

    # "She fidgets and stomps her foot. I can tell her mind is racing again."
    "Se inquieta y pisa fuerte. Me doy cuenta de que su mente vuelve a acelerarse."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4982
translate Spanish ch3m_01_94b209ea:

    # m "Wait—no! Answer the door. Make up an excuse. I'm not here! Whatever you tell them. Whoever it is... make sure they leave!"
    m "Espera, no! Abre la puerta. Inventa una excusa. No estoy aquí! Lo que sea que les digas. Sea quien sea... asegúrate de que se vayan!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4983
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c85ea06e:

    # "I nod, but look back to the window. That blouse is familiar..."
    "Asiento con la cabeza, pero vuelvo a mirar hacia la ventana. Esa blusa me resulta familiar..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4984
translate Spanish ch3m_01_2fa64989:

    # c "Marion, it's only Grace. Why would the girl knock, not just enter her own home?"
    c "Marion, es sólo Grace. ¿Por qué llamaría la chica a la puerta y no entraría en su propia casa?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:4986
translate Spanish ch3m_01_d093d539:

    # "Relief sweeps over her, relaxing her bovine features."
    "El alivio la invade, relajando sus facciones bovinas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:4988
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b70b23ae:

    # m "Oh, I... I might have locked the door. Poor girl. Do let her in!"
    m "Oh, yo... Podría haber cerrado la puerta. Pobre chica. ¡Déjala entrar!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5001
translate Spanish ch3m_01_ef608e70:

    # "I open the door for Grace, and am hit with a look of warning. I've seen it before. It's the same look she gave me when I came to pick Marion up for the picnic just days ago."
    "Le abro la puerta a Grace y recibo una mirada de advertencia. Ya la había visto antes. Es la misma mirada que me echó cuando vine a recoger a Marion para el picnic hace unos días."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5002
translate Spanish ch3m_01_31969525:

    # c "Grace! I'm sorry we locked you out. Marion is having a terrible day. Things have gotten much worse."
    c "¡Grace! Siento haberte dejado fuera. Marion está teniendo un día terrible. Las cosas han empeorado mucho."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5003
translate Spanish ch3m_01_90f9cbf3:

    # "Grace's customary smirk is nowhere in sight. I fear she's angry with me, which seems like an overreaction for our mistake."
    "La habitual sonrisa de Grace no está a la vista. Temo que esté enfadada conmigo, lo que parece una reacción exagerada por nuestro error."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5004
translate Spanish ch3m_01_95582117:

    # "Then, from behind her, another shadow falls."
    "Entonces, desde detrás de ella, cae otra sombra."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5015
translate Spanish ch3m_01_4a642c08:

    # "It moves, revealing the long blonde hair of goodwill and nightmares. Miss Alana."
    "Se mueve, revelando la larga melena rubia de la buena voluntad y las pesadillas. Srta. Alana."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5016
translate Spanish ch3m_01_39e09c04:

    # "She steps from behind Grace, fiddling with the strings on her cloak, and brushing down her wind-blown bangs. She looks almost joyful. {i}Is she smiling to herself?{/i}"
    "Sale de detrás de Grace, juguetea con las cuerdas de su capa y se peina el flequillo despeinado por el viento. Parece casi alegre. {i}Está sonriendo para sí misma?{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5017
translate Spanish ch3m_01_08a03854:

    # c "Why, hello, Miss Alana! What a lovely surprise!"
    c "¡Hola, Srta. Alana! ¡Qué encantadora sorpresa!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5019
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c52dffb3:

    # "I raise my voice to alert Marion. Turning to look for her, I spot her tiptoeing toward her bedroom. She catches my eye and shakes her head anxiously."
    "Levanto la voz para alertar a Marion. Me giro para buscarla y la veo caminando de puntillas hacia su dormitorio. Me llama la atención y mueve la cabeza con ansiedad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5020
translate Spanish ch3m_01_6d36ec22:

    # "Alana also seems understandably confused to see me. I'm unsure of how to proceed. Luckily, Grace fills in the blanks."
    "Alana también parece comprensiblemente confusa al verme. No sé cómo proceder. Por suerte, Grace llena los espacios en blanco."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5022
translate Spanish ch3m_01_89d8a41d:

    # g "Malcolm, I ran into Miss Alana on my way back from the loch. She said she'd like to pay us a visit."
    g "Malcolm, me encontré con la Srta. Alana cuando volvía del lago. Dijo que le gustaría hacernos una visita."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5024
translate Spanish ch3m_01_52005b18:

    # a "Hello... Malcolm! A surprise to me, as well."
    a "Hola... ¡Malcolm! Una sorpresa para mí también."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5029
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a8caebe8:

    # "Grace gives me an earnest apology with one second of eye contact. {i}But why couldn't she have delayed Alana? Kept her from coming?{/i}"
    "Grace me ofrece una sincera disculpa con un segundo de contacto visual. {i}¿Pero por qué no pudo retrasar a Alana? ¿Evitar que viniera?{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5030
translate Spanish ch3m_01_8b2bd799:

    # "Alana's visit is unexpected, and presumptuous. Too coincidental to simply be goodwill, part of me thinks. I scrutinize her demeanor and tone of voice."
    "La visita de Alana es inesperada y presuntuosa. Demasiada coincidencia para ser simplemente buena voluntad, piensa una parte de mí. Escudriño su comportamiento y su tono de voz."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5032
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b41ae7f7:

    # a "I apologize for disrupting your day, but I heard the whispered talk in town."
    a "Me disculpo por interrumpir su día, pero he oído el murmullo en la ciudad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5033
translate Spanish ch3m_01_efc63e27:

    # "My heart catches in my throat."
    "El corazón se me atasca en la garganta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5034
translate Spanish ch3m_01_d2c9b5f8:

    # c "Whispers? What whispers?"
    c "¿Susurros? ¿Qué susurros?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5036
translate Spanish ch3m_01_3a2c8e4b:

    # a "Jessie has left for the city, correct? I wanted to make sure everyone was doing all right, especially Marion. She must be devastated."
    a "Jessie se ha ido a la ciudad, ¿verdad? Quería asegurarme de que todos estaban bien, especialmente Marion. Debe estar devastada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5037
translate Spanish ch3m_01_3ac1385d:

    # "Ah. Jessie. My tension eases, but only a little. Alana's voice, so unmistakable, is like rancid molasses—sweet and smooth, but sour, bitter, cloying."
    "Ah. Jessie. Mi tensión disminuye, pero sólo un poco. La voz de Alana, tan inconfundible, es como melaza rancia: dulce y suave, pero agria, amarga, empalagosa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5039
translate Spanish ch3m_01_3cd88da3:

    # "She peers her head this way and that, looking for Marion, and angling to get inside the house."
    "Mueve la cabeza de un lado a otro, buscando a Marion y tratando de entrar en la casa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5041
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c0cd96fc:

    # a "What was that you were saying to Grace? Something about Marion? What's gotten worse?"
    a "¿Qué le estabas diciendo a Grace? ¿Algo sobre Marion? ¿Qué ha empeorado?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5059
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_abf219d3:

    # c "Uhhh... she's not feeling her best at the moment."
    c "Uhhh... no se siente muy bien en este momento."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5061
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_596fc82e:

    # a "Oh no! If it's not a bother. I'll just peek my head in on her?"
    a "Oh, no! Si no es molestia. ¿Le echaré un vistazo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5063
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_67f02d54:

    # g "No!"
    g "No!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5065
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_419d5750:

    # a "What?"
    a "¿Cómo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5067
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_8a0dca30:

    # g "I mean... uh... no need. She might be contagious. We wouldn't want you getting ill."
    g "Quiero decir... eh... no es necesario. Podría ser contagiosa. No querríamos que te enfermaras."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5068
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_b3dbc7fa:

    # "I imagine cow horns sprouting from Alana's head. Not exactly what she'd expect from a charitable visit."
    "Imagino cuernos de vaca brotando de la cabeza de Alana. No es exactamente lo que ella esperaría de una visita de caridad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5069
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_421cbef2:

    # "Then again, maybe that's just what she deserves for meddling."
    "Por otra parte, tal vez eso es justo lo que se merece por entrometerse."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5071
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_1e8f5393:

    # a "Is she very sick? Maybe I can help."
    a "Está muy enferma? Tal vez pueda ayudar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5072
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_995aef9c:

    # "Now I picture her doing incantations over Marion's sleeping body, and sprinkling her head with dried flower petals and herbs. Honestly, at this point, could it hurt?"
    "Ahora me la imagino haciendo conjuros sobre el cuerpo dormido de Marion y rociándole la cabeza con pétalos de flores secas y hierbas. Honestamente, en este punto, ¿podría hacer daño?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5073
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_de8618e5:

    # c "Help? How so?"
    c "¿Ayuda? ¿En qué sentido?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5075
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_8b3b65ee:

    # "Alana crosses her arms, challenging me."
    "Alana cruza los brazos, desafiándome."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5076
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_4847eee7:

    # a "Well, may I come in, or not?"
    a "Bueno, ¿puedo entrar o no?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5078
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_762fde0f:

    # "Grace rolls her eyes."
    "Grace pone los ojos en blanco."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5079
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_a995142d:

    # g "Follow me."
    g "Sígueme"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5104
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_87fcc201:

    # "The two women push me out of the way into the living space. Marion, thankfully, is nowhere to be found."
    "Las dos mujeres me empujan hacia la sala de estar. Marion, por suerte, no aparece por ninguna parte."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5105
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_978508dc:

    # "Alana heads to the bedroom, and I hold my breath while Grace chases after her. It's too late. Alana opens the door to Marion's room."
    "Alana se dirige al dormitorio y yo contengo la respiración mientras Grace la persigue. Es demasiado tarde. Alana abre la puerta de la habitación de Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5106
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_0fa84210:

    # "I start to feel terrible for not being able to protect Marion. I whisper hurriedly to Grace."
    "Empiezo a sentirme fatal por no haber podido proteger a Marion. Susurro apresuradamente a Grace."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5119
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_f4054e16:

    # c "Why would you bring Alana here? What if Marion had answered the door? She'd have been downright humiliated!"
    c "¿Por qué trajiste a Alana aquí? ¿Y si Marion hubiera respondido a la puerta? ¡Habría sido francamente humillada!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5120
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_c6417385:

    # g "Malcolm! Hush! I knew she never would have answered the door. If she saw me through the window, she'd have seen Alana, as well. It would have been her decision."
    g "¡Malcolm! ¡Silencio! Sabía que nunca habría contestado a la puerta. Si me hubiera visto por la ventana, también habría visto a Alana. Habría sido su decisión."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5121
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_724975da:

    # c "Alana would break through a window to find her!"
    c "¡Alana rompería una ventana para encontrarla!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5123
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_fecc65ab:

    # g "I was thinking on my feet!"
    g "¡Pensaba con los pies en la tierra!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5124
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_5fe3998d:

    # c "Then you need new feet!"
    c "Entonces necesitas pies nuevos!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5126
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_f35c6ecc:

    # g "Give me a break!"
    g "Dame un respiro!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5128
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_f934e022:

    # "Footsteps sound behind us."
    "Suenan pasos detrás de nosotros."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5129
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_db8bb420:

    # a "Marion? Where are you?"
    a "Marion? Dónde estás?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5137
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_e1ecb8c9:

    # "Alana steps back out of the bedroom, alone."
    "Alana vuelve a salir del dormitorio, sola."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5138
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_9a62f111:

    # a "She's not in there."
    a "No está ahí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5147
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_a8665d92:

    # "It's then that I catch Grace's eye, which guides me to the back window. From below the heavy curtain, I see the swish of a tail."
    "Es entonces cuando capto la mirada de Grace, que me guía hacia la ventana trasera. Desde debajo de la pesada cortina, veo el aleteo de una cola."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5148
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_ab4dca52:

    # "Marion's hiding! Why? This is nonsense."
    "¡Marion se esconde! ¿Por qué? Esto no tiene sentido."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5150
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_276533c4:

    # a "This is nonsense!"
    a "Esto no tiene sentido!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5151
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_c8e7cd1f:

    # c "{size=22}{i}I agree.{/i}{/size}"
    c "{size=22}{i}Estoy de acuerdo.{/i}{/size}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5153
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_3f8cc735:

    # a "Where could she have gone?"
    a "Adónde habrá ido?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5160
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_172f083f:

    # "Alana walks closer to the back of the house, to look out the window."
    "Alana se acerca a la parte trasera de la casa, para mirar por la ventana."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5163
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_09046bfb:

    # g "Miss Alana!"
    g "Srta. Alana!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5168
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_67327bc8:

    # a "Yes, dear?"
    a "Sí, querida?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5170
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_861e25b4:

    # g "Uhh... oh... um..."
    g "Uhh... oh... um..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5176
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_df86ae90:

    # "Grace is distracted by her sister sneaking out from under the curtain, making her way to the kitchen table, and ducking underneath. Oh, for heaven's sake!"
    "Grace se distrae cuando su hermana sale a hurtadillas de debajo de la cortina, se dirige a la mesa de la cocina y se agacha. ¡Oh, por el amor de Dios!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5178
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_60d0b951:

    # "Grace looks to me for guidance."
    "Grace me busca para que la guíe."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5179
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_428ab9c2:

    # c "Er. Marion may have taken off for a walk?"
    c "Eh. Marion puede haberse ido a dar un paseo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5181
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_7867153c:

    # a "Wouldn't she have left... through the front door?"
    a "No se habría ido... por la puerta principal?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5224
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_ce8254b3:

    # "Alana goes back towards the door, knocking into a kitchen chair as she moves. A short yelp comes from under the table."
    "Alana vuelve hacia la puerta y choca con una silla de la cocina. Un pequeño aullido sale de debajo de la mesa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5235
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_612011b3:

    # a "What was that?"
    a "Qué ha sido eso?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5236
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_71951a55:

    # c "Oh, nothing! We have mice."
    c "Oh, nada! Tenemos ratones."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5239
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_e9035993:

    # g "Very loud, mice."
    g "Muy ruidoso, ratones."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5256
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_feebf18b:

    # c "Ahem. Well, it does look as though Marion has ducked out. There's no telling when she'll be back."
    c "Ejem. Bueno, parece que Marion se ha escabullido. No se sabe cuándo volverá."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5258
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_4af5d8f0:

    # a "I certainly don't mind waiting. I'm sure she'd be happy to have another shoulder to lean on when she returns."
    a "Desde luego, no me importa esperar. Seguro que le alegrará tener otro hombro en el que apoyarse cuando vuelva."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5262
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_0aaa9f7e:

    # "I want desperately to be frustrated or impatient with Alana's actions. But... I'm not."
    "Quiero desesperadamente estar frustrado o impaciente con las acciones de Alana. Pero... no lo estoy."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5263
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_4d637881:

    # "She wants to be a rock for Marion, in the very same way I do. I believe her to be nosy, but also just... maybe she is kind, after all. Possibly even sincere."
    "Quiere ser una roca para Marion, de la misma manera que yo. Creo que es entrometida, pero también... tal vez es amable, después de todo. Posiblemente incluso sincera."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5264
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_41277c4c:

    # "I can't picture a scenario in which Alana would punish or shame Marion for deeds out of the poor girl's control. Who knows... given her penchant for the weird, perhaps Alana can fix it, even."
    "No puedo imaginarme un escenario en el que Alana castigara o avergonzara a Marion por hechos fuera del control de la pobre chica. Quién sabe... dada su afición por lo raro, quizá Alana pueda arreglarlo, incluso."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5265
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_57baccde:

    # "I'm stuck not knowing what to do. I want her to speak to Marion, but I also want to respect Marion's wishes, should she want privacy."
    "Estoy atascado sin saber qué hacer. Quiero que hable con Marion, pero también quiero respetar los deseos de Marion, en caso de que quiera privacidad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5266
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_797a45c5:

    # "...Most of all, I want this awkwardness to end."
    "...Sobre todo, quiero que esta incomodidad termine."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5270
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_daa1f19a:

    # g "Oh... of course! Please stay."
    g "Oh... ¡Por supuesto! Por favor, quédate."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5272
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_297d93f3:

    # c "What?"
    c "Cómo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5274
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_716f04da:

    # a "Why, thank you."
    a "Vaya, gracias."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5275
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_88656303:

    # "I give Grace a questioning look. She nods, as if formulating a plan."
    "Miro a Grace interrogante. Ella asiente, como si estuviera formulando un plan."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5277
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_2f5038ac:

    # g "Yes, I'll make us all tea. We can catch up."
    g "Sí, prepararé té para todos. Podemos ponernos al día."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5296
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_fce71ef9:

    # "Confused and frozen, I join Alana at the table."
    "Confuso y helado, me uno a Alana en la mesa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5297
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_d8ce9df8:

    # "Behind her, Grace has the cabinet door open, and is furiously whispering to her sister. It sounds as though she's talking to herself, which, oddly, doesn't seem to affect Alana at all."
    "Detrás de ella, Grace tiene la puerta del armario abierta y susurra furiosamente a su hermana. Parece como si hablara consigo misma, lo que, curiosamente, no parece afectar en absoluto a Alana."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5300
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_cb0a794d:

    # a "On second thought..."
    a "Pensándolo bien..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5301
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_8ffcd261:

    # "Oh, thank God. Please leave."
    "Gracias a Dios. Váyase, por favor."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5306
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_59a09540:

    # a "Let me help with tea!"
    a "Déjame ayudarte con el té!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5311
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_b1c2bb4f:

    # g "No need!"
    g "No es necesario!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5315
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_89bbc0c3:

    # "Grace slams the cupboard door shut. I swear I hear a muffled cry from Marion."
    "Grace cierra de golpe la puerta del armario. Juro que oigo un grito ahogado de Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5317
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_58cfaf7a:

    # a "Oh, but I should. Idle hands, as they say..."
    a "Oh, pero debería. Manos ociosas, como dicen..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5319
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_19fd2e3a:

    # "\"...Are the Devil's tools.\" I sit there in a state of panic, unsure of how to escape this situation."
    "\"...son las herramientas del Diablo.\" Me siento allí en un estado de pánico, inseguro de cómo escapar de esta situación."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5321
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_72fb11aa:

    # a "Where do you keep your teacups, Grace?"
    a "Dónde guardas tus tazas de té, Grace?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5330
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_76cf3804:

    # g "No! Not in there!"
    g "No! Ahí dentro no!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5338
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_6acf36da:

    # "A scream echoes through the small space."
    "Un grito resuena en el pequeño espacio."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5346
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_8ff07a3d:

    # "Like a prank gone horribly wrong, Alana opens the cupboard holding a petite cow girl, all curled up in a ball of shame."
    "Como si se tratara de una broma que ha salido terriblemente mal, Alana abre el armario en el que hay una pequeña vaca, hecha un ovillo de vergüenza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5347
translate Spanish ch3m_01_a_8b4c26a9:

    # m "Hello, Miss Alana. How... are you?"
    m "Hola, Srta. Alana. Cómo... estás?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5359
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_5acd3821:

    # c "Marion hasn't... uh... been herself lately."
    c "Marion no ha... eh... sido ella misma últimamente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5361
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_6c0371f7:

    # a "Really? How so? Perhaps I can help."
    a "De verdad? Cómo es eso? Tal vez pueda ayudar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5363
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_9f89b7a0:

    # "Grace mutters softly."
    "Grace murmura en voz baja."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5364
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_c0d8f06f:

    # g "{size=20}Can you get rid of tails?{/size}"
    g "{size=20}Puede deshacerse de la cola?{/size}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5368
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_1a6bdc6f:

    # a "What's that?"
    a "Qué es eso?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5369
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_8dd53563:

    # c "Would you like a swig of ale?"
    c "Quieres un trago de cerveza?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5371
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_2b80ddd2:

    # a "Ale? What's wrong with you, Malcolm? It's so early in the day!"
    a "Ale? ¿Qué te pasa, Malcolm? ¡Es tan temprano!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5373
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_c7e58e77:

    # "Grace rolls her eyes at me. Admittedly, that wasn't one of my better covers."
    "Grace pone los ojos en blanco. Admito que no fue una de mis mejores portadas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5375
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_f287bc47:

    # g "Malcolm just enjoys his drink. Here, I'll join you."
    g "Malcolm sólo disfruta de tu bebida. Toma, te acompaño."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5376
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_96c62d26:

    # "Grace pushes me aside, and leads Alana in by the arm."
    "Grace me empuja a un lado y lleva a Alana del brazo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5435
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_0b695993:

    # "While Alana sits and Grace prepares tea, I whisper aggressively at the youngest MacLeod, rattling pots and teacups so Alana can't hear."
    "Mientras Alana se sienta y Grace prepara el té, susurro agresivamente a la menor de los MacLeod, haciendo sonar ollas y tazas de té para que Alana no oiga."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5436
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_b78e1c12:

    # c "Why is she here, Grace?"
    c "Por qué está aquí, Grace?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5438
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_d2fc9e06:

    # g "She latched onto me... like a swamp leech!"
    g "Se aferró a mí... ¡como una sanguijuela de pantano!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5439
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_b466f480:

    # c "So peel her off!"
    c "quítatela de encima!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5441
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_6aa65102:

    # g "With what?"
    g "Con qué?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5442
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_1d9fbd51:

    # c "Your grubby seaweed-covered hands, Grace!"
    c "Tus sucias manos cubiertas de algas, Grace!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5460
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_96c66e44:

    # "As I pour four rounds of cider, I turn around and smile at Alana, who smiles curtly back. It's then that I spy a new piece of furniture in the corner of the room."
    "Mientras sirvo cuatro rondas de sidra, me doy la vuelta y sonrío a Alana, que me devuelve la sonrisa. Es entonces cuando veo un mueble nuevo en un rincón de la habitación."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5478
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_88f76124:

    # "Oh, Marion, what were you thinking? Coatracks don't have {i}cow's tails!{/i}"
    "Oh, Marion, ¿en qué estabas pensando? Los percheros no tienen {i}cola de vaca!{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5480
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_524701f6:

    # "I expect Alana to spot the anomaly right away, but by fate or circumstance, she seems oblivious. Marion stays still as a statue, and doesn't make a peep."
    "Esperaba que Alana se diera cuenta enseguida de la anomalía, pero por cosas del destino o de las circunstancias, parece no darse cuenta. Marion se queda quieta como una estatua y no dice ni pío."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5499
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_a4807593:

    # "Alana stands abruptly."
    "Alana se levanta bruscamente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5500
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_8b231b6d:

    # a "Do you two need assistance? I'm handy in the kitchen."
    a "¿Necesitáis ayuda? Soy hábil en la cocina."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5502
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_9bd8141f:

    # g "We're fine!"
    g "Todo bien!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5536
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_39ed1ac9:

    # "Alana begins to meander around the small home, picking up knick knacks, and wiping her gloved hand along to tables, checking for dust."
    "Alana empieza a deambular por la pequeña casa, recogiendo chucherías y pasando la mano enguantada por las mesas, comprobando que no haya polvo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5537
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_ae8306fd:

    # a "Marion keeps a very clean home."
    a "Marion mantiene una casa muy limpia."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5538
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_cb71b65a:

    # "I turn and steal a peek at Marion the coat rack, who, through the jackets, I can see is smiling to herself."
    "Me giro y echo un vistazo a Marion, la del perchero, que, a través de las chaquetas, veo que sonríe para sus adentros."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5552
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_e84f5fa4:

    # a "Oh! Oh, my! But look at all this fur!"
    a "¡Oh! ¡Oh, Dios! ¡Pero mira todo este pelaje!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5553
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_81153279:

    # "Marion's smile drops. A large huff escapes her nostrils, blowing off a great deal of her face powder. She looks like a bull ready to charge."
    "Marion pierde la sonrisa. Un gran resoplido se escapa de sus fosas nasales, soplando gran parte de su polvo facial. Parece un toro dispuesto a embestir."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5560
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_14524bf2:

    # g "It's from our cat."
    g "Es de nuestro gato."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5562
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_8a240b60:

    # a "You have a cat?"
    a "Tienes un gato?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5564
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_4f788dd2:

    # g "Sometimes. She... uh... comes and goes."
    g "A veces. Ella... eh... va y viene."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5566
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_51b67bf3:

    # a "Well, a bit more sweeping may be in order."
    a "Bueno, puede que haga falta barrer un poco más."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5574
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_8ba7a70c:

    # "Alana continues around the room, picking up vases to check for water stains, and moving around framed pictures."
    "Alana sigue recorriendo la habitación, cogiendo jarrones para comprobar si hay manchas de agua y moviendo los cuadros enmarcados."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5575
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_4a1e4643:

    # "The \"coatrack\" follows closely behind. Under all the jackets, Marion shuffles as slowly as a tank rolling into battle. No one picks on a MacLeod woman's housekeeping skills."
    "El \"perchero\" le sigue de cerca. Bajo todas las chaquetas, Marion se mueve tan lentamente como un tanque rodando hacia la batalla. Nadie se mete con las habilidades domésticas de una mujer MacLeod."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5578
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_2338a704:

    # a "I notice a few of your pitchers are chipped. You may want to replace those."
    a "Veo que algunas de sus jarras están astilladas. Es posible que desee reemplazar esos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5597
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_94b0619c:

    # "Marion creeps closer to Alana, keeping mum, dropping the coats, and balling her fists."
    "Marion se acerca sigilosamente a Alana, guardando silencio, dejando caer los abrigos y cerrando los puños."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5599
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_ab25ad07:

    # g "Uh... those belonged to Mother, Miss Alana. I don't believe any market replacements would be better."
    g "Uh... esos pertenecían a mi madre, la Srta. Alana. No creo que ningún reemplazo del mercado sea mejor."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5600
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_412cfe0a:

    # a "Yes, but unsightly goods make for an unsightly home."
    a "Sí, pero los enseres antiestéticos hacen una casa antiestética."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5614
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_7cec95c3:

    # "Marion buckles down, head forward as if ready to charge."
    "Marion se abrocha el cinturón, con la cabeza hacia delante como si estuviera lista para cargar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5615
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_b6dee725:

    # "The teakettle whistles."
    "La tetera silba."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5617
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_43800f22:

    # "Grace screams."
    "Grace grita."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5618
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_b52df4b5:

    # g "Marion, no!"
    g "Marion, no!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5622
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_34ebb4c3:

    # "Alana whips around just in time to come face-to-face with a very angered, horned woman."
    "Alana se da la vuelta justo a tiempo para encontrarse cara a cara con una mujer cornuda y muy enfadada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5623
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_651a4974:

    # "I take the kettle off the stove."
    "Saco la tetera del fuego."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5624
translate Spanish ch3m_01_b_d0476c6b:

    # c "Ladies! How about some tea?"
    c "Señoritas! Qué tal un poco de té?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5635
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_48234d74:

    # c "She... uh went shopping in town."
    c "Ella... fue de compras a la ciudad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5637
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_2c73df50:

    # g "Yes... yes, we were low on so many things."
    g "Sí... sí, teníamos pocas cosas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5639
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_40848df2:

    # a "Really? I was just there. I didn't notice her."
    a "¿De verdad? Sólo estaba allí. No me fijé en ella."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5640
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_e24e1119:

    # c "Oh? Poor timing, I suppose. She's awfully quiet, you know. You may have crossed paths and never known."
    c "¿Oh? Mal momento, supongo. Es terriblemente callada, sabes. Puede que os hayáis cruzado y nunca lo hayáis sabido."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5642
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_71cc7688:

    # a "Unlikely. It's a very small space."
    a "Poco probable. Es un espacio muy pequeño."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5643
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_3103c7a4:

    # "Well, this was going to be a great visit."
    "Bueno, esta iba a ser una gran visita."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5645
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_9e0a81eb:

    # a "Do you mind if I sneak in and use your lavvy?"
    a "¿Te importa si me cuelo y uso tu lavabo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5646
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_096ba8a5:

    # "Yes, I do mind."
    "Sí, me importa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5649
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_20ff241f:

    # g "Of course not! Go right ahead."
    g "Claro que no! Adelante."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5659
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_44d4151e:

    # "As Alana barges in and disappears behind the bathroom door, I shoot Grace a sharp whisper."
    "Cuando Alana irrumpe y desaparece detrás de la puerta del baño, le lanzo a Grace un agudo susurro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5661
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_41bc1937:

    # c "Grace! {i}What were you thinking? Bringing her here?{/i} Marion will die if anyone sees her!"
    c "Grace! {i}¿En qué estabas pensando? ¿Traerla aquí?{/i} ¡Marion morirá si alguien la ve!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5663
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_e6fdfd4f:

    # g "Shut up, Malcolm! I tried! Have you ever talked to this woman? Lying to her is like lying to the bailiff! She'll suss you out faster than any truth serum!"
    g "¡Cállate, Malcolm! ¡Lo intenté! ¿Has hablado alguna vez con esta mujer? ¡Mentirle a ella es como mentirle al alguacil! ¡Te descubrirá más rápido que cualquier suero de la verdad!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5664
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_8f054ad1:

    # c "You're just a bad liar!"
    c "Eres una mal mentirosa!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5666
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_dc0f5447:

    # g "I'm not!"
    g "No lo soy!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5667
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_4b4e936c:

    # c "Are to!"
    c "También!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5668
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_bb1fca04:

    # "I stop when I realize it is turning into a schoolroom argument. If Alana caught us in such behavior, would she appreciate the irony? Or would she discipline us the way she always did?"
    "Me detengo cuando me doy cuenta de que se está convirtiendo en una discusión de clase. Si Alana nos pillara en semejante comportamiento, ¿apreciaría la ironía? ¿O nos disciplinaría como siempre ha hecho?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5669
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_2fd9aee5:

    # "I picture Marion curled up in bed, just waiting for us to get Alana out of here. Seems it's up to me to make that happen."
    "Me imagino a Marion acurrucada en la cama, esperando a que saquemos a Alana de aquí. Parece que depende de mí que eso suceda."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5670
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_468c3db8:

    # c "You watch. I'll have her out of here faster than a whip crack."
    c "Tú mira. La sacaré de aquí más rápido que el chasquido de un látigo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5672
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_05658c2e:

    # "Grace shakes her head."
    "Grace sacude la cabeza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5675
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_61306a86:

    # g "Good luck."
    g "Suerte."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5682
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_699ebf10:

    # "Alana comes out of the bathroom, and I have never been more determined to lie to anyone in my entire life."
    "Alana sale del baño y nunca he estado más decidido a mentir a nadie en toda mi vida."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5683
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_7726acc0:

    # a "Thank you. Now, shall I make us some tea while we wait?"
    a "Gracias, gracias. Ahora, nos preparo un té mientras esperamos?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5685
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_213552f4:

    # g "We're out of tea."
    g "Nos quedamos sin té."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5686
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_4691bc89:

    # "Dammit. Grace is ahead of me."
    "Maldita sea. Grace está delante de mí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5687
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_f945afb7:

    # c "Yes, out of biscuits, as well."
    c "Sí, también sin galletas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5688
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_6f6bd318:

    # "I glare at Grace."
    "Miro fijamente a Grace."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5690
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_4ce94d83:

    # a "But there's a tin of shortbread on the counter."
    a "Pero hay una lata de galletas en el mostrador."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5692
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_e6805341:

    # "Grace snorts. I'm already losing."
    "Grace resopla. Ya estoy perdiendo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5693
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_9e077356:

    # c "Those are Hazel's biscuits. We... uh... leave them in there for safe keeping."
    c "Esas son las galletas de Hazel. Nosotros... eh... las dejamos ahí para guardarlas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5695
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_7b443120:

    # a "Why do you keep Hazel's treats at the girls' home?"
    a "¿Por qué guardas las golosinas de Hazel en casa de las chicas?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5696
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_5e05145e:

    # c "I visit often."
    c "Las visito a menudo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5699
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_7d4d0282:

    # a "Enough that you leave treats here?"
    a "¿Lo suficiente como para dejar golosinas aquí?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5701
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_59c77043:

    # g "We give them to our horse, Eachann, as well, Miss Alana."
    g "También se las damos a nuestro caballo, Eachann, Srta. Alana."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5702
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_ccfddafe:

    # "Grace smiles at me, smugly, and any begrudging gratitude toward her vanishes."
    "Grace me sonríe, con suficiencia, y cualquier rencorosa gratitud hacia ella se desvanece."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5704
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_779896c7:

    # a "Oh, that's a pity. Marion left her shopping basket behind."
    a "Qué pena. Marion se dejó la cesta de la compra."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5705
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_e10a6733:

    # "I turn back to Alana, and follow her eyes. Indeed, the wicker basket is still sitting by the front door."
    "Me vuelvo hacia Alana y sigo su mirada. Efectivamente, la cesta de mimbre sigue junto a la puerta principal."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5706
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_baec7c20:

    # c "I've seen her shop without it many a time."
    c "La he visto comprar sin él muchas veces."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5708
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_306376f0:

    # g "That's right. She uses Eachann's saddle bags most times."
    g "Así es. Ella usa las bolsas de la silla de montar de Eachann la mayoría de las veces."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5710
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_be9fd4e9:

    # a "But Eachann is in the stable. He whinnied as we walked by. Don't you remember, Grace? 'Twas only minutes past."
    a "Pero Eachann está en el establo. Relinchó cuando pasamos. ¿No lo recuerdas, Grace? Sólo pasaron unos minutos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5712
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_2f850a34:

    # "Grace freezes. Lying our way out of this is going to be an Olympic-level event."
    "Grace se congela. Mentir para salir de esta va a ser un evento de nivel olímpico."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5713
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_f42c369d:

    # "Now's my chance to shine."
    "Ahora es mi oportunidad de brillar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5714
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_675bfd55:

    # c "You know Marion. She loves the exercise."
    c "Ya conoces a Marion. Le encanta el ejercicio."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5716
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_04629e2d:

    # a "How will she carry it all? You said you needed so much!"
    a "¿Cómo va a cargar con todo? ¡Dijiste que necesitabas tanto!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5717
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_02c7ca60:

    # "My confidence is rapidly evaporating. I look back to Grace."
    "Mi confianza se evapora rápidamente. Miro hacia Grace."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5719
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_f311968d:

    # g "Uh... well... we're a mite bit low on funds. She wouldn't be able to get too very much."
    g "Uh... bueno... estamos un poco bajos de fondos. No podría conseguir mucho."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5721
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_1c7ed5d0:

    # a "That's an awfully long trip for just a few items."
    a "Es un viaje terriblemente largo para unos pocos artículos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5723
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_ca166d26:

    # g "Marion can't go a day without tea."
    g "Marion no puede pasar un día sin té."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5725
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_b9ceed99:

    # a "Couldn't you have brought her some, Malcolm? Your Gran must keep extra on hand for guests."
    a "¿No podías haberle traído un poco, Malcolm? Tu abuela debe tener más a mano para los invitados."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5727
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_bc619eed:

    # "Grace rolls her eyes so hard, I fully expect them to lodge in the back of her head."
    "Grace pone tanto los ojos en blanco que espero que se le claven en la nuca."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5728
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_9cf7c4f6:

    # "Alana is not giving up. Now it's obvious our tales are being unwoven, one lie at a time."
    "Alana no se rinde. Ahora es obvio que nuestros cuentos están siendo destejidos, una mentira a la vez."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5730
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_02650889:

    # c "I don't believe we drink the same brand, Miss Alana."
    c "No creo que bebamos la misma marca, Srta. Alana."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5732
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_35342478:

    # a "I wouldn't have thought Marion to be so choosy."
    a "No habría pensado que Marion fuera tan exigente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5733
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_f6ba2c73:

    # "Alana's inquisition tries my patience, and I find myself taking offense that she would have so little trust in us... even if she's completely right to do so."
    "La inquisición de Alana pone a prueba mi paciencia y me ofende que confíe tan poco en nosotros, aunque tenga toda la razón."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5735
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_0a2b190b:

    # c "Do you think we're {i}lying{/i} to you, Miss Alana?"
    c "¿Crees que somos {i}mentimos?{/i} a usted, Srta. Alana?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5740
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_210c06eb:

    # a "Yes."
    a "Sí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5744
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_fdde2a98:

    # g "Wow."
    g "Wow."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5745
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_0e2e829c:

    # "Grace looks mightily impressed."
    "Grace parece muy impresionada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5747
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_49836926:

    # a "That's what honesty sounds like, Grace."
    a "Así es como suena la honestidad, Grace."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5748
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_7757ae95:

    # "I feel myself blush."
    "Siento que me sonrojo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5750
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_0abdbdb4:

    # a "I've never lied in my life. You two could take a lesson from that."
    a "Nunca he mentido en mi vida. Ustedes dos podrían tomar una lección de eso."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5753
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_dd192ca6:

    # a "Now then. Why are you lying?"
    a "Ahora bien. Por qué mienten?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5756
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_70729f56:

    # g "We're hiding Marion from you."
    g "Te estamos ocultando a Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5757
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_53a26a1d:

    # "Boy, she caved fast."
    "Chico, cedió rápido."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5758
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_ff4f4ca8:

    # c "Marion wishes not to be seen today, Miss Alana. With apologies."
    c "Marion no desea ser vista hoy, Srta. Alana. Con mis disculpas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5760
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_9d44254a:

    # a "Now, why wouldn't you just say that?"
    a "¿Por qué no lo dijiste?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5761
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_3e3046c7:

    # c "We thought you would continue to ask questions as to her well-being."
    c "Pensamos que seguirías preguntando por su bienestar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5763
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_6532ceb0:

    # a "You're absolutely right, I would. Is she ill?"
    a "Tienes toda la razón, lo haría. ¿Está enferma?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5765
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_05f1d918:

    # g "Not... exactly."
    g "No... exactamente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5767
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_a9a56918:

    # a "Honesty, Grace. Please."
    a "Honestidad, Grace. Por favor."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5768
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_6961426f:

    # c "Her... appearance has changed."
    c "Su... apariencia ha cambiado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5770
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_73e49fda:

    # "Alana appears to stop breathing momentarily."
    "Alana parece dejar de respirar momentáneamente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5772
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_65ee7342:

    # a "Let me see her. Now."
    a "Déjame verla. Ahora."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5782
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_0d7cad1c:

    # "Grace and I are saved from having to continue the conversation. The bedroom door opens, and Marion makes her way out. She has removed the powdery makeup, and looks fresh-faced."
    "Grace y yo nos ahorramos tener que continuar la conversación. La puerta de la habitación se abre y Marion sale. Se ha quitado el maquillaje empolvado y luce un rostro fresco."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5785
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_c105368b:

    # "She makes no effort to disguise herself. Her tail swishes. Her horns are held high."
    "No hace ningún esfuerzo por disimular. Mueve la cola. Lleva los cuernos en alto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5786
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_2634aeb4:

    # "A cheerful smile fills her face."
    "Una alegre sonrisa llena su rostro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5787
translate Spanish ch3m_01_c_d05034ef:

    # m "Hello, Miss Alana. How nice to see you today!"
    m "Hola, Srta. Alana. ¡Qué bueno verte hoy!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5799
translate Spanish ch3m_01_d_e9ec8320:

    # "A silence stretches between us as I weigh my options. Marion is relying on me to protect her secret, I remind myself. But each scenario that plays out in my head is less savory than the last."
    "Se hace el silencio entre nosotros mientras sopeso mis opciones. Marion confía en mí para proteger su secreto, me recuerdo. Pero cada escenario que se me pasa por la cabeza es menos sabroso que el anterior."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5800
translate Spanish ch3m_01_d_96f7ec92:

    # "I don't see any way to prevent Alana from finding out the truth of the situation, short of telling a brazen lie. And perhaps it's the old school discipline kicking in, but I can't bring myself to lie to her."
    "No veo ninguna manera de evitar que Alana descubra la verdad de la situación, a menos que le mienta descaradamente. Tal vez sea la disciplina de la vieja escuela, pero no me atrevo a mentirle."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5804
translate Spanish ch3m_01_d_d4d307d1:

    # c "Her... condition. There's something you need to know about Marion."
    c "Su... condición. Hay algo que necesitas saber sobre Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5807
translate Spanish ch3m_01_d_b086d4c5:

    # "Alana narrows her eyes at me, and I can't help but shrink back. I call over my shoulder."
    "Alana me estrecha los ojos y no puedo evitar encogerme. La llamo por encima del hombro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5808
translate Spanish ch3m_01_d_ce6523be:

    # c "Marion... forgive me. Grace has brought along company. Miss Alana is here, as well."
    c "Marion... perdóname. Grace ha traído compañía. La Srta. Alana también está aquí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5810
translate Spanish ch3m_01_d_29c0eba4:

    # "It pains me to betray Marion like this, but I just don't see another way; not now, with Alana on the scent. A nosy neighbor like her is bound to find out sooner or later."
    "Me duele traicionar así a Marion, pero no veo otra manera; no ahora, con Alana en la mira. Una vecina entrometida como ella se enterará tarde o temprano."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5811
translate Spanish ch3m_01_d_e7c8d746:

    # "And despite my schoolteacher's... odd behavior towards me of late, I believe Alana truly cares for the MacLeod girls. I hold my breath, desperately hoping Marion reaches the same conclusion."
    "Y a pesar del... extraño comportamiento de mi maestra hacia mí últimamente, creo que Alana realmente se preocupa por las chicas MacLeod. Contengo la respiración, esperando desesperadamente que Marion llegue a la misma conclusión."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5814
translate Spanish ch3m_01_d_e29def42:

    # m "Well... then... this is just perfect timing. Isn't it?"
    m "Bueno... entonces... este es el momento perfecto. ¿No lo es?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5815
translate Spanish ch3m_01_d_1527a8ed:

    # "Her voice cracks, and I'm suddenly very overwhelmed with the prospect of what is about to happen in this house."
    "Su voz se quiebra, y de repente me siento muy abrumado ante la perspectiva de lo que está a punto de ocurrir en esta casa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5816
translate Spanish ch3m_01_d_c209c8ee:

    # "Footsteps fall behind me. Marion stops short of making herself visible."
    "Los pasos caen detrás de mí. Marion se detiene antes de hacerse visible."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5817
translate Spanish ch3m_01_d_0162fa9b:

    # m "Malcolm... I'm... I'm not ready. Buy me time. Please."
    m "Malcolm... Yo... no estoy lista. Consígueme tiempo. Por favor."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5818
translate Spanish ch3m_01_d_fc7aca7b:

    # "I obey, letting her slip quietly into her bedroom. A wave of my hand ushers in Grace and Alana. Here goes nothing."
    "Obedezco y la dejo entrar en silencio en su dormitorio. Un gesto de mi mano hace entrar a Grace y Alana. Aquí no pasa nada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5858
translate Spanish ch3m_02_d4faacf7:

    # "Alana takes the surprise well."
    "Alana se toma bien la sorpresa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5859
translate Spanish ch3m_02_dde6562a:

    # a "I was very sorry to hear about Jessie. I wanted to make sure you girls were all right. Especially you, Marion."
    a "Lamenté mucho lo de Jessie. Quería asegurarme de que estaban bien. Especialmente tú, Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5862
translate Spanish ch3m_02_6687321e:

    # "Our old schoolteacher's voice is gentle and disarming. It almost feels as if we are back at school, awaiting the next lesson."
    "La voz de nuestra antigua maestra es suave y desarmante. Es como si estuviéramos de vuelta en la escuela, esperando la siguiente lección"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5864
translate Spanish ch3m_02_e02e7c47:

    # "Our old schoolteacher's voice is gentle and disarming. If she is angry about our deception, it does not show. It almost feels as if we are back at school, awaiting the next lesson."
    "La voz de nuestra antigua maestra es suave y desarmante. Si está enfadada por nuestro engaño, no lo demuestra. Es casi como si estuviéramos de vuelta en la escuela, esperando la siguiente lección."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5866
translate Spanish ch3m_02_a19650eb:

    # "After everything—the odd visits, the cryptic warnings, the uncomfortable probes—here, now, Alana gives off that unspoken motherly energy full of warmth and safety."
    "Después de todo -las visitas extrañas, las advertencias crípticas, los sondeos incómodos-, aquí, ahora, Alana desprende esa energía maternal tácita llena de calidez y seguridad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5867
translate Spanish ch3m_02_426ae71d:

    # "Like she is still watching over us after all those years."
    "Como si siguiera velando por nosotros después de tantos años."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5874
translate Spanish ch3m_02_da5f69bc:

    # "She gets close to Marion, and takes her hand. Marion obliges, as if in a trance."
    "Se acerca a Marion y le coge la mano. Marion la toma, como en trance."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5880
translate Spanish ch3m_02_044a0fa6:

    # "Finally, they stand looking into each other's eyes. With Marion's hand in hers, Alana slides her thumb over and along the hard ridges of Marion's former fingers."
    "Finalmente, se quedan mirándose a los ojos. Con la mano de Marion entre las suyas, Alana desliza el pulgar sobre y a lo largo de las duras crestas de los dedos anteriores de Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5881
translate Spanish ch3m_02_c2ddda7f:

    # "Marion whimpers. Alana lets her hand go. Tears stream down Marion's face, leaving white streaks where the remains of her makeup is washed away."
    "Marion gimotea. Alana le suelta la mano. Las lágrimas corren por el rostro de Marion, dejando rayas blancas donde se borran los restos de maquillaje."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5891
translate Spanish ch3m_02_0f0d9bcc:

    # "In a flash, Marion is gathered up in Alana's embrace, and lets herself collapse into her teacher's bosom. Her cries grow louder at first, then soften to sniffles."
    "En un instante, Marion se encuentra abrazada a Alana y se deja caer en el pecho de su maestra. Sus gritos se hacen más fuertes al principio y luego se suavizan hasta convertirse en mocos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5892
translate Spanish ch3m_02_35fc3b24:

    # "I try to keep my head down, as my stomach hurts seeing Marion so upset, so helpless. Every time I look up, I see Alana's kindness and Marion's sadness. Both disquiet me very deeply."
    "Intento mantener la cabeza gacha, ya que me duele el estómago al ver a Marion tan alterada, tan indefensa. Cada vez que levanto la vista, veo la bondad de Alana y la tristeza de Marion. Ambas me inquietan profundamente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5900
translate Spanish ch3m_02_97729b52:

    # "As Marion's tears subside, Alana guides her to the bathroom, becoming quite tender in tone and action. She comforts Marion in ways I've not seen since I was a young student."
    "Cuando las lágrimas de Marion se calman, Alana la guía hasta el cuarto de baño, con un tono y unos gestos muy tiernos. Consuela a Marion de un modo que no había visto desde que era una joven estudiante."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5901
translate Spanish ch3m_02_cf85931f:

    # "It could well be that Alana was the closest thing the MacLeod children ever had to a mother. And what a mother to have. A gift? A curse?"
    "Podría ser que Alana fuera lo más cercano a una madre que las hijas de MacLeod tuvieron. Y que madre tener. ¿Un don? ¿Una maldición?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5902
translate Spanish ch3m_02_3850cb09:

    # "I think of the many times over I've heard whispers of Alana's sorcery and magic. Of her insistence that I avoid the MacLeod sisters, and my naivete in assuming she was acting like a mad bat."
    "Pienso en las muchas veces que he oído susurros sobre la hechicería y la magia de Alana. En su insistencia en que evitara a las hermanas MacLeod y en mi ingenuidad al suponer que actuaba como un murciélago loco."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5903
translate Spanish ch3m_02_fdefe659:

    # "That perhaps there was something to her warnings doesn't excuse her behavior. Still, I'm thankful that Alana has been nothing but kind to the lasses."
    "Que tal vez hubiera algo en sus advertencias no excusa su comportamiento. Aún así, estoy agradecido de que Alana haya sido tan amable con las chicas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5907
translate Spanish ch3m_02_40c9b115:

    # c "Well, today's been a bit radge, hasn't it?"
    c "Bueno, hoy ha sido un poco loco, ¿no?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5909
translate Spanish ch3m_02_4b340443:

    # g "..."
    g "..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5910
translate Spanish ch3m_02_7ebed99c:

    # "To say the day's had its ups and downs is an understatement."
    "Decir que el día ha tenido sus altibajos es quedarse corto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5912
translate Spanish ch3m_02_8f683ea5:

    # "Grace broods. Her sister turning into a cow, neighbors traipsing in and out of her home... I can't imagine what Grace must be going through. How her world could be more turned upside down."
    "Grace se preocupa. Su hermana convertida en vaca, vecinos entrando y saliendo de su casa... No puedo imaginar por lo que Grace debe estar pasando. Cómo su mundo podría estar más patas arriba."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5914
translate Spanish ch3m_02_727440f0:

    # c "Er... bit nippy in here, you think? Shall I light us a fire?"
    c "Eh... hace un poco de frío aquí, ¿no crees? ¿Enciendo un fuego?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5917
translate Spanish ch3m_02_31105a10:

    # g "Aye, of course. {i}Make yourself at home.{/i}"
    g "Sí, por supuesto. {i}Siéntete como en casa.{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5935
translate Spanish ch3m_02_a8215ba3:

    # "Her eye roll is so exaggerated, it's practically audible. I'm not all that cold, really, but I leap at the excuse to busy myself."
    "Su mirada es tan exagerada que prácticamente se oye. No tengo tanto frío, la verdad, pero aprovecho la excusa para entretenerme."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5951
translate Spanish ch3m_02_380bb0a8:

    # "A friendly fire is dancing in the hearth by the time the women emerge together; Marion's face clean, and Alana's arms still around her."
    "Un fuego amigo baila en la chimenea cuando las mujeres salen juntas; Marion tiene la cara limpia y Alana aún la abraza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5954
translate Spanish ch3m_02_fa21891a:

    # a "Now, then. How about some tea?"
    a "Bien. ¿Qué tal un poco de té?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5956
translate Spanish ch3m_02_d67d23a4:

    # a "Now, then. How about those drinks?"
    a "Ahora, entonces. ¿Qué tal esas bebidas?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:5970
translate Spanish ch3m_02_08cdd096:

    # "I take Marion from Alana, and hold her in my arms by the fire, pulling her close as we listen to the kettle clang, then water boil."
    "Separo a Marion de Alana y la cojo en brazos junto al fuego, tirando de ella mientras oímos el tintineo de la tetera y el agua hirviendo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5971
translate Spanish ch3m_02_263e899a:

    # "Grace sits on the other side of Marion, placing the blankets around her once again, rubbing her back gently, but staying silent."
    "Grace se sienta al otro lado de Marion, la envuelve de nuevo con las mantas y le frota suavemente la espalda, pero permanece en silencio."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5974
translate Spanish ch3m_02_fbe2dc70:

    # "The rattle of teetering cups has us all raising our heads."
    "El traqueteo de tazas tambaleantes nos hace levantar la cabeza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5983
translate Spanish ch3m_02_a0d95dd9:

    # "Alana sets down the tea tray, and gives the first cup to Marion. The scent is heady, like spices from the Far East."
    "Alana deja la bandeja de té y le da la primera taza a Marion. El aroma es embriagador, como a especias del Lejano Oriente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5985
translate Spanish ch3m_02_5fa1c753:

    # a "It's an herbal blend. It will settle you."
    a "Es una mezcla de hierbas. Te calmará."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5988
translate Spanish ch3m_02_620c8301:

    # "Marion nods and sips. A smile appears across her face. It looks so forced that it is unsettling."
    "Marion asiente y bebe un sorbo. Una sonrisa se dibuja en su rostro. Parece tan forzada que resulta inquietante."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5990
translate Spanish ch3m_02_47d2b694:

    # m "Thank you, Miss Alana. It tastes wonderful."
    m "Gracias, Srta. Alana. Sabe de maravilla."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5992
translate Spanish ch3m_02_ac49518b:

    # "Marion's voice shakes, as if fresh tears are about to pour out. Her bottom lip trembles as she swallows, and her hands shake almost uncontrollably."
    "A Marion le tiembla la voz, como si estuviera a punto de derramar nuevas lágrimas. El labio inferior le tiembla al tragar y las manos le tiemblan de forma casi incontrolable."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5994
translate Spanish ch3m_02_3c6000d4:

    # "I notice she struggles to hold the teacup upright in her hoof, so I balance the bottom in my palm as she drinks. Taking it from her to set it down once she has finished the entire cup."
    "Me doy cuenta de que le cuesta sostener la taza de té con la pezuña, así que apoyo el fondo en la palma de la mano mientras bebe. Se la quito para dejarla en el suelo cuando se ha terminado toda la taza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5996
translate Spanish ch3m_02_2b0d0031:

    # "Grace also drinks her tea quickly, and I wonder what blend Alana has brewed. I hesitate in trying it myself, though it seems to work wonders, as both sisters relax and appear more alert and focused."
    "Grace también bebe su té rápidamente y me pregunto qué mezcla habrá preparado Alana. Dudo en probarlo yo misma, aunque parece hacer maravillas, pues ambas hermanas se relajan y parecen más alerta y concentradas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:5999
translate Spanish ch3m_02_43cc0047:

    # a "Malcolm, why don't you have a taste?"
    a "Malcolm, por qué no pruebas?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6000
translate Spanish ch3m_02_81f0b727:

    # "I'm not wont to ignore my own concerns, but Alana's undying state of authority has me following her command like the well-trained soldier I am."
    "No suelo ignorar mis propias preocupaciones, pero el eterno estado de autoridad de Alana me hace seguir sus órdenes como el soldado bien entrenado que soy."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6001
translate Spanish ch3m_02_a5de3cda:

    # "I take a cautious sip, and am relieved to find it tastes like... tea. No suspicious or undue feeling sweeps over me, so I take another sip, and proceed to empty the cup."
    "Tomo un sorbo con precaución y me alivia comprobar que sabe a... té. Ningún sentimiento sospechoso o indebido se apodera de mí, así que bebo otro sorbo y vacío la taza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6002
translate Spanish ch3m_02_ee85e32c:

    # "Sometimes I wonder if the mystery surrounding Alana is her candor—her unwillingness to be anything but frank. There's no small talk with her."
    "A veces me pregunto si el misterio que rodea a Alana es su franqueza, su poca disposición a ser otra cosa que franca. Con ella no hay conversaciones triviales."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6003
translate Spanish ch3m_02_75ae6fb2:

    # "No sign of enjoying the pleasure of just... being."
    "Ni rastro de disfrutar del placer de simplemente... ser."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6005
translate Spanish ch3m_02_eb357a15:

    # "The tea leaves me feeling calm, patient, and relaxed. I don't fight it, as the tranquility is so welcome."
    "El té me deja una sensación de calma, paciencia y relajación. No me resisto, ya que la tranquilidad es muy bienvenida."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6007
translate Spanish ch3m_02_2bac1154:

    # "Alana stands as if at an invisible lectern, a stance perfected over many years of teaching, I've no doubt. If only she had all the answers, like she did in our school years."
    "Alana está de pie como ante un atril invisible, una postura perfeccionada a lo largo de muchos años de enseñanza, no me cabe duda. Ojalá tuviera todas las respuestas, como en nuestros años de escuela."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6008
translate Spanish ch3m_02_a20cefa7:

    # "..."
    "..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6009
translate Spanish ch3m_02_8e58fe62:

    # "I peer at the thoughtful eyes behind those glasses. {i}Might she?{/i}"
    "Miro los ojos pensativos detrás de esas gafas. {i}¿Podría?{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6010
translate Spanish ch3m_02_5eb5ada3:

    # "It seems my peers wonder the same thing. All at once an invisible dam breaks, releasing a torrent of questions."
    "Parece que mis compañeros se preguntan lo mismo. De repente, un dique invisible se rompe y se desata un torrente de preguntas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6014
translate Spanish ch3m_02_e16440f7:

    # m "What's wrong with me? Can you help me?"
    m "Qué me pasa? Puedes ayudarme?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6015
translate Spanish ch3m_02_d6076f23:

    # g "What is it? Can you change her back? Make her a human again?"
    g "Qué pasa? Puedes volver a cambiarla? Hacerla humana de nuevo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6016
translate Spanish ch3m_02_aba96387:

    # m "Am I safe?"
    m "Estoy segura?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6017
translate Spanish ch3m_02_459309dc:

    # g "When will it go away?"
    g "Cuándo desaparecerá?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6018
translate Spanish ch3m_02_0474ac24:

    # "I join in."
    "Me uno."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6019
translate Spanish ch3m_02_a75509e5:

    # c "How will she live like this?"
    c "Cómo va a vivir así?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6020
translate Spanish ch3m_02_4f2c002e:

    # c "Can... whatever this is... can it be reversed?"
    c "¿Puede... lo que sea esto... puede revertirse?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6022
translate Spanish ch3m_02_ae198933:

    # m "Alana, can you save me? Please, {i}please{/i} tell me you can save me."
    m "Alana, ¿puedes salvarme? Por favor, {i}por favor{/i} dime que puedes salvarme."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6029
translate Spanish ch3m_02_b41a03af:

    # "We go silent, and hear only the faint ticking of the clock on the wall."
    "Nos quedamos en silencio y sólo oímos el débil tic-tac del reloj de pared."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6032
translate Spanish ch3m_02_c548a63c:

    # "Alana looks to me and adjusts her glasses before she replies."
    "Alana me mira y se ajusta las gafas antes de responder."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6033
translate Spanish ch3m_02_1b2113e2:

    # a "I will try my best to answer all of your questions. But... I don't know everything."
    a "Haré todo lo posible por responder a todas sus preguntas. Pero... no lo sé todo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6035
translate Spanish ch3m_02_20f9805a:

    # m "You've seen this before... haven't you?"
    m "Ya has visto esto antes... verdad?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6037
translate Spanish ch3m_02_0010d39d:

    # a "First, I have a question. Marion, when did all of this begin?"
    a "Primero, tengo una pregunta. Marion, ¿cuándo empezó todo esto?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6039
translate Spanish ch3m_02_2cb90099:

    # m "Just a few weeks ago, I think. I noticed it first in my back, then..."
    m "Hace unas semanas, creo. Lo noté primero en mi espalda, luego..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6041
translate Spanish ch3m_02_131e631e:

    # "Marion points to the horns. Alana seems less shocked than disappointed."
    "Marion señala los cuernos. Alana parece menos sorprendida que decepcionada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6043
translate Spanish ch3m_02_9e153f80:

    # a "Yes, I see."
    a "Sí, ya veo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6044
translate Spanish ch3m_02_16f8d730:

    # "Alana folds her hands, taking on a tone I've not heard since days of chalkboards and arithmetic: authoritative but friendly, as if she's the expert, and we're to instinctively accept it."
    "Alana cruza las manos y adopta un tono que no oía desde los tiempos de las pizarras y la aritmética: autoritario pero amistoso, como si ella fuera la experta y nosotros tuviéramos que aceptarlo instintivamente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6045
translate Spanish ch3m_02_788d7673:

    # "Can we? {i}Can I?{/i} I want to. At this point, I would feel a sense of relief if only to know this burden is finally out of our hands."
    "Podemos? {i}puedo?{/i} Lo deseo. En este momento, sentiría alivio aunque sólo fuera por saber que esta carga se nos ha ido por fin de las manos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6047
translate Spanish ch3m_02_237f3921:

    # a "I'm never quite sure how to avoid being direct and blunt, and I don't believe this is a situation in which to make an attempt. So... let me be concise and clear."
    a "Nunca sé muy bien cómo evitar ser directo y contundente, y no creo que ésta sea una situación en la que intentarlo. Así que... permítanme ser concisa y clara."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6049
translate Spanish ch3m_02_a38c1f09:

    # a "Marion, I know the question that is foremost in your mind; the one you did not ask. The answer is no. You will never become a cow. You'll never lose your mind... or your kind soul."
    a "Marion, conozco la pregunta que más te ronda por la cabeza; la que no has formulado. La respuesta es no. Nunca te convertirás en una vaca. Nunca perderás la cabeza... o tu alma bondadosa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6051
translate Spanish ch3m_02_f5de8b3a:

    # "Marion does not look relieved, only more confused."
    "Marion no parece aliviada, sino más confusa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6052
translate Spanish ch3m_02_b6e5aeb9:

    # m "How do you know that? How can you {i}possibly{/i} know that? What... what am I? What is this?"
    m "Cómo lo sabes? Cómo es posible que lo sepas? Qué... qué soy? Qué es esto?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6054
translate Spanish ch3m_02_bea72ad0:

    # "Alana stiffens, and replies in her patented fashion."
    "Alana se pone rígida y responde a su manera patentada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6056
translate Spanish ch3m_02_8e235f01:

    # a "You are special. A creature of note."
    a "Eres especial. Una criatura digna de mención."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6057
translate Spanish ch3m_02_7fba424c:

    # "I hear Grace snort."
    "Oigo a Grace resoplar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6059
translate Spanish ch3m_02_1f76b0cc:

    # g "Oh, she's a creature all right!"
    g "Oh, es una criatura sin duda!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6063
translate Spanish ch3m_02_ba2bd908:

    # c "Grace! Stop it!"
    c "Grace! ¡Basta ya!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6064
translate Spanish ch3m_02_a5c8d833:

    # "I continue, overwhelmed with impatience and frustration."
    "Continúo, abrumado por la impaciencia y la frustración."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6065
translate Spanish ch3m_02_a196e173:

    # c "Alana! That means nothing! Tell us what you may know about this. Have you seen it before?"
    c "¡Alana! ¡Eso no significa nada! Dinos lo que puedas saber sobre esto. ¿Lo habías visto antes?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6072
translate Spanish ch3m_02_e442d69a:

    # a "I have."
    a "Yo sí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6076
translate Spanish ch3m_02_9230a86f:

    # m "And I'll get better? It will go away? Right? Please tell me just that."
    m "Y me pondré mejor? ¿Se irá? ¿Verdad? Por favor, dime eso."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6080
translate Spanish ch3m_02_e651c58b:

    # a "Marion... have you heard the word \"púca\" before? Or \"changeling?\""
    a "Marion... has oído la palabra \"púca\" antes? o \"¿Cambiante?\""

# game/script_marion.rpy:6081
translate Spanish ch3m_02_5ce2bb6e:

    # "Hearing the words strike fear into my chest. The weird and gruesome stories spun in Baird's compendium... is Alana saying they are true? Marion looks shaken."
    "Oír esas palabras me infunde miedo. Las extrañas y horripilantes historias que se cuentan en el compendio de Baird... ¿está diciendo Alana que son ciertas? Marion parece estremecida."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6083
translate Spanish ch3m_02_27870dc2:

    # m "Like... in the fairy tales?"
    m "Como... en los cuentos de hadas?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6085
translate Spanish ch3m_02_3afc2649:

    # "Alana's face brightens and relaxes."
    "El rostro de Alana se ilumina y se relaja."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6086
translate Spanish ch3m_02_0ade54c2:

    # a "Yes, just like that. A human form with animal features."
    a "Sí, justo así. Una forma humana con rasgos animales."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6088
translate Spanish ch3m_02_4296109d:

    # m "Exchanged for a real child?"
    m "Cambiado por un niño de verdad?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6090
translate Spanish ch3m_02_da37ce99:

    # a "Yes. Yes, that's right."
    a "Sí. Sí, así es."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6092
translate Spanish ch3m_02_6280d06e:

    # m "Is... is that what I am?"
    m "Es... es eso lo que soy?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6094
translate Spanish ch3m_02_d9fb425a:

    # a "Yes. You are."
    a "Sí. Lo eres."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6096
translate Spanish ch3m_02_e41b7e84:

    # m "I'm not..."
    m "Yo no..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6098
translate Spanish ch3m_02_cb3247b7:

    # "Marion starts weeping again, and leans into me. I rub her shoulder."
    "Marion vuelve a llorar y se apoya en mí. Le froto el hombro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6100
translate Spanish ch3m_02_87aaf5c6:

    # m "I'm not real."
    m "No soy real."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6103
translate Spanish ch3m_02_4aefd287:

    # a "Oh, no, no, dear Marion. You are very, very true and real."
    a "Oh, no, no, querida Marion. Eres muy, muy verdadera y real."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6105
translate Spanish ch3m_02_6a5861cb:

    # "Marion's look reveals layers of fear."
    "La mirada de Marion revela capas de miedo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6106
translate Spanish ch3m_02_9984098d:

    # m "Does my father know?"
    m "Lo sabe mi padre?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6109
translate Spanish ch3m_02_13026318:

    # g "Wait. Was our mother fae? Is our family magic? {i}What will I turn into?{/i}"
    g "Espera. Nuestra madre era fae? ¿Nuestra familia es mágica? {i}En qué me convertiré?{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6111
translate Spanish ch3m_02_e546ad98:

    # "Grace leans forward, as if grasping that this may involve her, too."
    "Grace se inclina hacia delante, como si comprendiera que esto puede implicarla a ella también."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6113
translate Spanish ch3m_02_51671544:

    # a "I don't know if your father is aware. I wouldn't believe so. And, no, Grace. Your mother never possessed this gift. This is very uncommon, a near impossibility. A bit of a miracle, even."
    a "No sé si tu padre está al tanto. No lo creo. Y no, Grace. Tu madre nunca poseyó este don. Es muy poco común, casi imposible. Un milagro, incluso."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6116
translate Spanish ch3m_02_12125445:

    # m "A miracle? It's a nightmare!"
    m "Un milagro? Es una pesadilla."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6118
translate Spanish ch3m_02_c1e518b8:

    # "Alana appears unconvinced."
    "Alana parece poco convencida."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6120
translate Spanish ch3m_02_2a25494a:

    # a "Is it? Are you in pain? Uncomfortable? Are you unhappy? Or are you simply fearful?"
    a "Te duele? sientes dolor? te sientes incómoda? eres infeliz? o simplemente tienes miedo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6122
translate Spanish ch3m_02_975e423e:

    # g "Fear isn't simple, Alana."
    g "El miedo no es simple, Alana."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6124
translate Spanish ch3m_02_8eb8e1f9:

    # a "Grace, let Marion answer. I need to know."
    a "Grace, deja que Marion responda. Necesito saber."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6126
translate Spanish ch3m_02_57626391:

    # "Marion shifts under the blankets, and begins examining her hands."
    "Marion se mueve bajo las mantas y empieza a examinarse las manos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6127
translate Spanish ch3m_02_badedb97:

    # m "I have hooves for hands. Of course that frightens me."
    m "Tengo pezuñas por manos. Claro que eso me asusta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6130
translate Spanish ch3m_02_49aefb64:

    # m "But, no. No, I am not in pain."
    m "Pero, no. No, no tengo dolor."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6132
translate Spanish ch3m_02_5eaca8c4:

    # m "I'm in fear every day. Fearful that someone will see me like this, mock me, humiliate me. That fear makes me unhappy, yes."
    m "Tengo miedo todos los días. Miedo de que alguien me vea así, se burle de mí, me humille. Ese miedo me hace infeliz, sí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6134
translate Spanish ch3m_02_4279751f:

    # a "But you're comfortable, aren't you?"
    a "Pero estás cómoda, ¿no?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6136
translate Spanish ch3m_02_d9f1389e:

    # m "I don't know how... but I am. I feel like..."
    m "No sé cómo... pero lo estoy. Me siento como..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6137
translate Spanish ch3m_02_f6cbd995:

    # a "This is your true nature."
    a "Esta es tu verdadera naturaleza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6139
translate Spanish ch3m_02_a7770c88:

    # "Marion nods slowly."
    "Marion asiente lentamente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6141
translate Spanish ch3m_02_8b194480:

    # m "I've been too embarrassed to admit that."
    m "Me ha dado vergüenza admitirlo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6145
translate Spanish ch3m_02_0abbb195:

    # "My heart sinks, hearing that Marion not only has been concealing her feelings from me, but also that she... may feel better this way? How will any of us adjust?"
    "Se me hunde el corazón al oír que Marion no sólo me ha estado ocultando sus sentimientos, sino que además... puede sentirse mejor así? Cómo nos adaptaremos?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6147
translate Spanish ch3m_02_cbd818d2:

    # g "Alana, explain how you know this to be true. Am {i}I{/i} going to become a cow? What about Jessie, so far away now. She can't live like this in the city! She'll be eaten alive... quite literally!"
    g "Alana, explícame cómo sabes que esto es cierto. yo {i}tambien{/i} me voy a convertirte en una vaca? ¿Qué pasa con Jessie, tan lejos ahora. ¡No puede vivir así en la ciudad! Se la comerán viva... literalmente!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6149
translate Spanish ch3m_02_eecd46c7:

    # a "I've known for some time about Marion. I sensed changes. I can't tell you how. It's a blessing and a curse, my ability to perceive the truth."
    a "Hace tiempo que sé lo de Marion. Percibí cambios. No puedo decirte cómo. Es una bendición y una maldición, mi habilidad para percibir la verdad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6151
translate Spanish ch3m_02_7f482419:

    # a "But, no, Grace. I don't think you or Jessie have anything to worry about."
    a "Pero, no, Grace. No creo que tú o Jessie tengan nada de qué preocuparse."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6155
translate Spanish ch3m_02_4e414e2a:

    # "I want to challenge Alana as well, ask her more questions... but I still need to start digesting the answers we receive."
    "Yo también quiero retar a Alana, hacerle más preguntas... pero todavía tengo que empezar a digerir las respuestas que recibamos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6156
translate Spanish ch3m_02_9da3166c:

    # "Why do we trust her? How does it all seem so harmless, listening to her and believing her?"
    "¿Por qué confiamos en ella? ¿Cómo puede parecer todo tan inofensivo, escuchándola y creyéndole?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6158
translate Spanish ch3m_02_13218013:

    # m "So I've always been like this? This is... me?"
    m "Siempre he sido así? Esto soy... yo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6160
translate Spanish ch3m_02_98b66bdc:

    # "Marion's face drops again, and I fear that more tears are to follow."
    "El rostro de Marion vuelve a caer y me temo que le seguirán más lágrimas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6161
translate Spanish ch3m_02_7c90fcea:

    # m "This is unbelievable. I... I've been lied to my whole life. I don't... Alana, I don't know who I am!"
    m "Es increíble. Yo... me han mentido toda mi vida. Yo no... Alana, no sé quién soy!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6163
translate Spanish ch3m_02_09e519cd:

    # a "No, Marion. No one has lied to you. You are {i}you.{/i} Your life is real, as are you... and your body. Your family cares deeply for you, as do I... and Malcolm."
    a "No, Marion. Nadie te ha mentido. Tú eres {i}tú{/i} Tu vida es real, como tú... y tu cuerpo. Tu familia se preocupa profundamente por ti, al igual que yo... y Malcolm."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6164
translate Spanish ch3m_02_e09bbfd5:

    # "I think about what Alana is saying."
    "Pienso en lo que dice Alana."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6165
translate Spanish ch3m_02_40ac22c6:

    # "Her definition of truth and honesty seems not to include lies by omission, which apparently is the treatment Marion has received her entire life by this woman... her so-called protector."
    "Su definición de verdad y honestidad no parece incluir las mentiras por omisión, que aparentemente es el trato que Marion ha recibido toda su vida por parte de esta mujer... su supuesta protectora."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6168
translate Spanish ch3m_02_6eafdc18:

    # a "And here? Here is now. It is also real. Tangible. Don't lose sight of everything pure and true in your world because of change, no matter how drastic."
    a "¿Y aquí? Aquí es ahora. También es real. Tangible. No pierdas de vista todo lo puro y verdadero que hay en tu mundo por culpa de un cambio, por drástico que sea."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6170
translate Spanish ch3m_02_7cf2f191:

    # a "Just because the story of your beginning, of how you came to be, is not what you remember, do not let this knowledge impact your future. Never should our pasts define our presents."
    a "Sólo porque la historia de tus comienzos, de cómo llegaste a ser, no sea la que recuerdas, no dejes que este conocimiento afecte a tu futuro. Nuestro pasado nunca debe definir nuestro presente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6173
translate Spanish ch3m_02_18fbd085:

    # "Alana sounds as if she is trying to convince herself of the same thing. She catches Marion's eye, and directs Marion's gaze towards me."
    "Parece como si Alana intentara convencerse de lo mismo. Atrae la mirada de Marion y la dirige hacia mí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6174
translate Spanish ch3m_02_99c41eef:

    # "I blush, but hold eye contact with Marion, to assure her I am real, and here for her... always. Just as I promised."
    "Me sonrojo, pero mantengo el contacto visual con Marion, para asegurarle que soy real y que estoy aquí para ella... siempre. Tal y como prometí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6176
translate Spanish ch3m_02_3b49d214:

    # "...At the same time, I want to scream out in rage, to demand that magic is not real, and hasn't ever been. Fairy tales are stories for children. Magic has no place in our village. It never did!"
    "...Al mismo tiempo, quiero gritar de rabia, exigir que la magia no es real, y nunca lo ha sido. Los cuentos de hadas son historias para niños. La magia no tiene cabida en nuestro pueblo. Nunca lo ha tenido."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6178
translate Spanish ch3m_02_6ad82777:

    # "But as I start to open my mouth, Alana catches my eye, and holds my line of sight as she pours another cup of tea for me."
    "Pero cuando empiezo a abrir la boca, Alana me llama la atención y me mantiene a la vista mientras me sirve otra taza de té."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6179
translate Spanish ch3m_02_1b3a654a:

    # "Without saying a word, I take the cup and empty its contents down my throat. The relief sets in immediately."
    "Sin decir palabra, cojo la taza y vacío su contenido en mi garganta. El alivio me invade de inmediato."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6182
translate Spanish ch3m_02_963d97b8:

    # m "But... why? Why me? How? This isn't just defining me, it's all-encompassing. It's over every inch of my body. I just don't understand. Any of it."
    m "Pero... por qué? Por qué yo? Cómo? Esto no sólo me define, lo abarca todo. Está en cada centímetro de mi cuerpo. Simplemente no lo entiendo. Nada de esto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6184
translate Spanish ch3m_02_bd972095:

    # m "Alana, please... please just tell me more. How do you possibly know any of this? How long have you known?"
    m "Alana, por favor... por favor dime más. Cómo es posible que sepas algo de esto? Desde cuándo lo sabes?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6186
translate Spanish ch3m_02_f0a2af82:

    # a "Remember, Marion, please. The {i}why{/i} is the least important. The {i}how{/i} is too tricky to explain. The important focus is what is right in front of our eyes."
    a "Recuerda, Marion, por favor. El {i}por qué{/i} es el menos importante. El {i}cómo{/i} es demasiado complicado de explicar. Lo importante es lo que tenemos delante de los ojos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6188
translate Spanish ch3m_02_6179dc75:

    # g "And growing out from behind her."
    g "Y creciendo por detrás de ella."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6190
translate Spanish ch3m_02_ad10ce4b:

    # m "Grace, hush!"
    m "Grace, cállate!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6194
translate Spanish ch3m_02_5256ea7b:

    # "I feel locked in place. I want more tea, but I also want to be able to speak. It's a feeling short of hallucinating as I'm taken back to Effie showing me her long, soft rabbit ears."
    "Me siento encerrado en mi sitio. Quiero más té, pero también quiero poder hablar. Es una sensación cercana a la alucinación cuando Effie me enseña sus largas y suaves orejas de conejo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6195
translate Spanish ch3m_02_68238a0c:

    # "What if magic {i}is{/i} here in Ach-na-Creige, and always has been... and none of us ever recognized it, acknowledged it, or trusted in it."
    "¿Y si la magia {i}está{/i} aquí en Ach-na-Creige, y siempre lo ha sido... y ninguno de nosotros lo ha reconocido, reconocido o confiado en él."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6196
translate Spanish ch3m_02_c6e598eb:

    # "Perhaps now is our chance. For Marion's sake."
    "Quizás ahora sea nuestra oportunidad. Por el bien de Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6200
translate Spanish ch3m_02_7ec0d916:

    # m "You warned Malcolm to stay away from me. You knew! You always knew!"
    m "Le advertiste a Malcolm que se alejara de mí. Lo sabías! Siempre lo supiste!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6201
translate Spanish ch3m_02_1571d8a3:

    # "What else does Alana know? There's more she's not saying, I'm certain. Even with no assurance, no evidence, I believe the things she says to be true."
    "Qué más sabe Alana? Hay más cosas que no dice, estoy seguro. Incluso sin seguridad, sin pruebas, creo que las cosas que dice son ciertas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6202
translate Spanish ch3m_02_12cd4050:

    # "But how does she know them? What do these answers mean to her... exactly?"
    "Pero, cómo las conoce? ¿Qué significan exactamente estas respuestas para ella?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6205
translate Spanish ch3m_02_ed61c121:

    # a "This was bound to happen. It was your fate. You can't stop fate. {i}I{/i} can't stop fate."
    a "Esto tenía que pasar. Era tu destino. No puedes detener el destino. {i}No{/i} puedo detener al destino."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6208
translate Spanish ch3m_02_f5f5f474:

    # m "So I'll stay... like this? Forever?"
    m "Así que me quedaré... así? Para siempre?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6209
translate Spanish ch3m_02_8a9ec872:

    # "Alana takes a deep breath before responding."
    "Alana respira hondo antes de responder."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6212
translate Spanish ch3m_02_210c06eb:

    # a "Yes."
    a "Sí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6214
translate Spanish ch3m_02_392161d2:

    # "Marion appears more resigned than fearful at the news."
    "Marion parece más resignada que temerosa ante la noticia."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6216
translate Spanish ch3m_02_4d2d1308:

    # m "But it won't get worse...?"
    m "¿Pero no empeorará...?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6218
translate Spanish ch3m_02_338ffb68:

    # g "Don't say \"worse.\""
    g "No digas \"peor.\""

# game/script_marion.rpy:6220
translate Spanish ch3m_02_ab65683e:

    # m "Fine. No, not worse, just... more?"
    m "Bien. No, no peor, sólo... más?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6222
translate Spanish ch3m_02_6b657582:

    # a "That, I do not know. I'm sorry. I wish I had all the answers."
    a "Eso, no lo sé. Lo lamento. Ojalá tuviera todas las respuestas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6224
translate Spanish ch3m_02_7275f50c:

    # m "There's so much I still don't understand. Why is this happening now?"
    m "Hay tantas cosas que todavía no entiendo. Por qué ocurre esto ahora?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6226
translate Spanish ch3m_02_fd6c82bd:

    # a "As I said, the why is not—"
    a "Como dije, el por qué no es..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6228
translate Spanish ch3m_02_b9c10782:

    # m "Not why. Why {i}now?{/i}"
    m "No por qué. Por qué {i}ahora?{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6231
translate Spanish ch3m_02_4d76f6dd:

    # "I'm caught off guard as Alana turns to me. Her gaze lingers for a moment, and she seems to make a decision."
    "Me pilla desprevenido cuando Alana se vuelve hacia mí. Su mirada se detiene un instante y parece tomar una decisión."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6233
translate Spanish ch3m_02_eae43939:

    # a "Fae magic works in strange, often indeterminable ways, and it's not ours to understand, but to accept."
    a "La magia de los Fae funciona de formas extrañas, a menudo indeterminables, y no nos corresponde a nosotros entenderla, sino aceptarla."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6235
translate Spanish ch3m_02_b51ad0b8:

    # a "Most likely, you are now at the right age to handle your changes. They don't typically occur in childhood, when the illusion is most important."
    a "Lo más probable es que ahora estés en la edad adecuada para gestionar tus cambios. No suelen producirse en la infancia, cuando la ilusión es más importante."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6237
translate Spanish ch3m_02_37062a28:

    # "Marion snorts."
    "Marion resopla."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6238
translate Spanish ch3m_02_b1af8752:

    # m "The wonderful pleasures of adulthood."
    m "Los maravillosos placeres de la edad adulta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6240
translate Spanish ch3m_02_12928638:

    # a "Magic may be mischievous, but it also has the power for great good. Marion, you are undoubtedly a child of the fae—you should trust in your own self more than ever."
    a "La magia puede ser traviesa, pero también tiene el poder de hacer un gran bien. Marion, no cabe duda de que eres una hija de los fae, debes confiar en ti misma más que nunca."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6242
translate Spanish ch3m_02_4624b3cb:

    # "Marion's eyes get wide."
    "Marion abre mucho los ojos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6244
translate Spanish ch3m_02_5236c17f:

    # m "Do I have... special powers?"
    m "Tengo... poderes especiales?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6246
translate Spanish ch3m_02_3d8a194a:

    # g "Like can she give milk?"
    g "Puede dar leche?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6248
translate Spanish ch3m_02_624bf1ad:

    # c "Grace!"
    c "Grace!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6253
translate Spanish ch3m_02_e4bb315e:

    # "Alana stares Grace down until I truly believe Grace might cry. Alana's powers certainly have not diminished over time."
    "Alana mira fijamente a Grace hasta que creo de verdad que Grace podría llorar. Los poderes de Alana no han disminuido con el tiempo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6255
translate Spanish ch3m_02_6e2dad3a:

    # a "If I can offer you any reassurance, it is that fate makes decisions for you. Being true to yourself is the only goal in life you really ought to chase."
    a "Si puedo ofrecerte algún consuelo, es que el destino toma las decisiones por ti. Ser fiel a ti misma es el único objetivo que debes perseguir en la vida."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6257
translate Spanish ch3m_02_074fba23:

    # "Marion nods. No matter how trite, I want desperately to believe Alana is right on this single account. I've seen enough destruction to know that abhorrent goals are the ultimate roads to ruin."
    "Marion asiente. Por muy trillado que esté, quiero creer desesperadamente que Alana tiene razón en esto. He visto suficiente destrucción para saber que los objetivos aborrecibles son los caminos definitivos hacia la ruina."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6260
translate Spanish ch3m_02_0717b98c:

    # a "Now I have questions for you, Marion."
    a "Ahora tengo preguntas para ti, Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6261
translate Spanish ch3m_02_ae16db0c:

    # a "Are you sure you feel all right? No pain at all? If there is, perhaps I can help ease it."
    a "Seguro que te encuentras bien? ningún dolor? Si lo hay, tal vez pueda ayudar a aliviarlo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6262
translate Spanish ch3m_02_2674642b:

    # "I shudder to think what Alana would offer to ease pain. Something more powerful than a cup of tea, one would guess."
    "Me estremezco al pensar qué ofrecería Alana para aliviar el dolor. Algo más poderoso que una taza de té, supongo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6264
translate Spanish ch3m_02_e223943e:

    # "Marion shakes her head, but keeps it facing down."
    "Marion sacude la cabeza, pero la mantiene mirando hacia abajo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6266
translate Spanish ch3m_02_079f7870:

    # a "I am many things, but I have never been naive. I have been around long enough to have heard the rumors spread about me. Accusations of witchcraft and worse."
    a "Soy muchas cosas, pero nunca he sido ingenua. Llevo el tiempo suficiente como para haber oído los rumores que se extienden sobre mí. Acusaciones de brujería y cosas peores."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6267
translate Spanish ch3m_02_15e996ca:

    # "I feel my face redden, aware that I have believed many of these tales myself."
    "Siento que se me enrojece la cara, consciente de que yo mismo he creído muchos de esos cuentos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6269
translate Spanish ch3m_02_2032f52e:

    # a "Marion, if any of those stories of my magic powers were true, I would change you back. In one blink of an eye, I would take your hurt away."
    a "Marion, si alguna de esas historias sobre mis poderes mágicos fuera cierta, te volvería a cambiar. En un abrir y cerrar de ojos, te quitaría el dolor."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6272
translate Spanish ch3m_02_fb5aded9:

    # m "I believe you. I truly do."
    m "Te creo. De verdad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6273
translate Spanish ch3m_02_67ec7231:

    # "Marion looks Alana hard in the eye, then turns to me."
    "Marion mira a Alana fijamente a los ojos y luego se vuelve hacia mí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6275
translate Spanish ch3m_02_d8f5f485:

    # m "If I could wish for anything, I would simply wish to be accepted. To be loved for who... or what I am."
    m "Si pudiera desear algo, simplemente desearía ser aceptada. Que me quisieran por lo que soy."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6276
translate Spanish ch3m_02_53dba01a:

    # "A lump catches in my throat. This all seems so unreal, so completely unfair. So profound. The woman I love hiding in obscurity because she fears... we all fear... the judgment of others."
    "Se me hace un nudo en la garganta. Todo esto parece tan irreal, tan completamente injusto. Tan profundo. La mujer que amo escondiéndose en la oscuridad porque teme... todos tememos... el juicio de los demás."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6277
translate Spanish ch3m_02_637d7824:

    # "It's sickening. Grotesque. Moreso than any change to Marion's appearance."
    "Es repugnante. Grotesco. Más que cualquier cambio en la apariencia de Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6280
translate Spanish ch3m_02_38ef5fe3:

    # "I think back to a fellow tommy in our division, hit by shrapnel. Spared, by some miracle, but left disfigured. When he came to, his biggest fear wasn't losing his service career, or even his life."
    "Recuerdo a un compañero de nuestra división, alcanzado por la metralla. Se salvó de milagro, pero quedó desfigurado. Cuando volvió en sí, su mayor temor no era perder su carrera militar, ni siquiera su vida."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6281
translate Spanish ch3m_02_220656bf:

    # "His fear was losing respect."
    "Lo que temía era perder el respeto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6282
translate Spanish ch3m_02_89f70e79:

    # "He said he looked like a monster. That no one would ever look him in the eye, treat him like a human, love him again. I don't know what happened to him, but I've never empathized more."
    "Decía que parecía un monstruo. Que nadie volvería a mirarle a los ojos, a tratarle como a un humano, a quererle. No sé qué le pasó, pero nunca sentí más empatía."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6283
translate Spanish ch3m_02_e48db935:

    # "Marion's fear of rejection is palpable. I know there is no way of proving my devotion other than staying by her side."
    "El miedo de Marion al rechazo es evidente. Sé que no hay otra forma de demostrar mi devoción que permanecer a su lado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6284
translate Spanish ch3m_02_0819b7db:

    # "And I truly hope I am willing to do so."
    "Y espero de verdad estar dispuesto a hacerlo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6287
translate Spanish ch3m_02_3555c352:

    # a "Marion, if I were able to perform any real sorcery, I would change the opinions of others."
    a "Marion, si fuera capaz de hacer verdadera brujería, cambiaría las opiniones de los demás."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6289
translate Spanish ch3m_02_f9ef895c:

    # m "The greatest magic trick of all."
    m "El mejor truco de magia de todos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6291
translate Spanish ch3m_02_abe1bbc0:

    # a "You'll be fine, Marion. I know it."
    a "Estarás bien, Marion. Lo sé."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6293
translate Spanish ch3m_02_55ae6a6a:

    # "Marion takes another look down at where her hands used to be, tapping them together to make the unmistakable {nw}"
    "Marion vuelve a mirar hacia abajo, donde solían estar sus manos, golpeándolas entre sí para hacer el inequívoco  {nw}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6295
translate Spanish ch3m_02_e1620dd6:

    # extend "sharp clack of hooves."
    extend "ruido seco de cascos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6298
translate Spanish ch3m_02_f853e07f:

    # m "And what if... I like it?"
    m "Y qué pasaría si... Me gusta?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6302
translate Spanish ch3m_02_807c61bf:

    # "Her tone suggests there is a struggle going on within her. Will she keep fighting, or... simply let go? Suddenly, her face becomes resolute. Accusatory, even. She levels her gaze at Alana."
    "Su tono sugiere que hay una lucha dentro de ella. ¿Seguirá luchando o... simplemente se dejará llevar? De repente, su rostro se vuelve decidido. Acusatorio, incluso. Dirige su mirada hacia Alana."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6304
translate Spanish ch3m_02_90f23db3:

    # m "Is... that why you hid this from me? Because you hoped I would never find out the truth, lest I... embrace it?"
    m "Es... por eso que me ocultaste esto? ¿Porque esperabas que nunca descubriera la verdad, para que no... la aceptara?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6306
translate Spanish ch3m_02_7c47cc93:

    # "Alana's eyes get large."
    "Los ojos de Alana se abren de par en par."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6307
translate Spanish ch3m_02_3fae9ccb:

    # a "I withheld this from you because you wouldn't have believed me even if I had told you. Because I hoped the time would never come when you would find yourself in this situation."
    a "Te lo oculté porque no me habrías creído aunque te lo hubiera dicho. Porque esperaba que nunca llegara el momento en que te encontraras en esta situación."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6312
translate Spanish ch3m_02_50174e39:

    # a "But know that even if I haven't been entirely forthcoming, I have always been honest, and I have always been by your side. By {i}all{/i} of your sides."
    a "Pero que sepas que aunque no haya sido del todo sincera, siempre he sido honesta, y siempre he estado a tu lado. Por {i}todos{/i} tus lados."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6313
translate Spanish ch3m_02_a09755c4:

    # "Here I know Alana is again withholding a large piece of the truth. She made it crystal clear I was to avoid {i}all{/i} of the sisters."
    "Aquí sé que Alana está ocultando una gran parte de la verdad. Me dejó muy claro que debía evitar a {i}todas{/i} las hermanas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6314
translate Spanish ch3m_02_cd0e00dc:

    # "What had she told Grace? This was uncommon? A near impossibility? Yet now, between Marion and Effie, that's two long-eared ladies I've encountered so far."
    "¿Qué le había dicho a Grace? ¿Que esto era poco común? ¿Casi imposible? Sin embargo, ahora, entre Marion y Effie, son dos las señoras de orejas largas que he encontrado hasta ahora."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6315
translate Spanish ch3m_02_4a85e847:

    # "How many more are hiding something beneath their millinery? I stay mum, but resolve to confront Alana. What if Marion's sisters are still also at risk?"
    "Cuántas más esconden algo bajo su sombrerería? Me quedo callada, pero estoy decidida a enfrentarme a Alana. ¿Y si las hermanas de Marion también están en peligro?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6327
translate Spanish ch3m_02_f5d0b093:

    # "Picturing Jessie turning bovine in the middle of a pub in Glasgow makes my stomach churn... but also brings a smirk to my face."
    "Imaginarme a Jessie volviéndose una vaca en medio de un pub de Glasgow me revuelve el estómago... pero también me hace sonreír."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6329
translate Spanish ch3m_02_0d80cff3:

    # g "Something funny, Malcolm?"
    g "Algo gracioso, Malcolm?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6330
translate Spanish ch3m_02_71161126:

    # c "Uh, no. Quite the contrary. I was just thinking..."
    c "Uh, No. Todo lo contrario. Estaba pensando..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6333
translate Spanish ch3m_02_7a5c1899:

    # m "Yes?"
    m "Si?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6343
translate Spanish ch3m_02_917f515a:

    # c "Marion, I know you worry endlessly about what others think of you. But no matter what happens, nothing can diminish my love for you."
    c "Marion, sé que te preocupa sin parar lo que los demás piensen de ti. Pero pase lo que pase, nada podrá disminuir mi amor por ti."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6349
translate Spanish ch3m_02_47de50cf:

    # m "I... what? Malcolm, you don't have to say that."
    m "Yo... ¿Qué? Malcolm, no tienes que decir eso."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6350
translate Spanish ch3m_02_90f35060:

    # c "But, it's true. Others be damned. I know it's easier said than done, but please, hear me. I am here for you."
    c "Pero es verdad. Al diablo con los demás. Sé que es más fácil decirlo que hacerlo, pero por favor, escúchame. Estoy aquí para ti."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6352
translate Spanish ch3m_02_4ec57921:

    # g "As am I, Marion."
    g "Como yo, Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6354
translate Spanish ch3m_02_da8f3c13:

    # a "I am, too, Marion."
    a "Yo también, Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6356
translate Spanish ch3m_02_7c5f689b:

    # m "Always?"
    m "Siempre?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6357
translate Spanish ch3m_02_4cff680c:

    # c "Always."
    c "Siempre."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6369
translate Spanish ch3m_02_8196a9a6:

    # "Alana starts collecting the empty teacups."
    "Alana empieza a recoger las tazas de té vacías."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6371
translate Spanish ch3m_02_2f698736:

    # a "I recognize that this is much to hear and absorb. I should probably leave you to your thoughts, Marion."
    a "Reconozco que es mucho que escuchar y asimilar. Probablemente debería dejarte con tus pensamientos, Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6373
translate Spanish ch3m_02_2b76806c:

    # m "Yes, perhaps that is best right now."
    m "Sí, quizás sea lo mejor en este momento."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6381
translate Spanish ch3m_02_2a676151:

    # a "Find me at the schoolhouse, if you need me. Things will be all right with time. You will adapt. Others will, too. And if they don't..."
    a "Encuéntrame en la escuela, si me necesitas. Las cosas irán bien con el tiempo. Te adaptarás. Otros también lo harán. Y si no lo hacen..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6383
translate Spanish ch3m_02_2bfe3b1d:

    # "Alana waggles a stern finger."
    "Alana hace un gesto de severidad con el dedo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6385
translate Spanish ch3m_02_8e289e5b:

    # a "They'll have me to deal with!"
    a "¡Tendrán que vérselas conmigo!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6388
translate Spanish ch3m_02_36b9a794:

    # "Grace cringes and recoils in fear. None of us doubt her."
    "Grace se encoge y retrocede asustada. Ninguno de nosotros duda de ella."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6400
translate Spanish ch3m_02_dbde7f24:

    # "The youngest MacLeod goes to clean up, and Marion announces that she needs to rest. I lead Marion to bed, to tuck her in for a nap."
    "La menor de los MacLeod va a limpiar y Marion anuncia que necesita descansar. Llevo a Marion a la cama, para arroparla y que duerma una siesta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6402
translate Spanish ch3m_02_d73b3344:

    # c "Marion, if this is overwhelming, please—let any of us shoulder your burdens."
    c "Marion, si esto te resulta abrumador, por favor, deja que cualquiera de nosotros lleve tu carga."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6403
translate Spanish ch3m_02_3a5693b9:

    # c "I may not be able to sew, or cook, or probably do any number of things half as well as you, but I can always try... or tell Grace to do it!"
    c "Puede que no sepa coser, ni cocinar, ni probablemente hacer muchas cosas la mitad de bien que tú, pero siempre puedo intentarlo... ¡o decirle a Grace que lo haga!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6405
translate Spanish ch3m_02_0230da23:

    # m "Thank you, Malcolm. I'll keep that in mind."
    m "Gracias, Malcolm. Lo tendré en cuenta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6411
translate Spanish ch3m_02_9981d72f:

    # c "One kiss now, and another later. I'll return after I've done all for Gran that needs doing. In a few hours, at most."
    c "Un beso ahora, y otro después. Volveré cuando haya hecho todo lo que hay que hacer por Abue. En unas horas, como mucho."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6412
translate Spanish ch3m_02_64fbfb50:

    # "Marion doesn't move a muscle, nor look me in the eye."
    "Marion no mueve un músculo, ni me mira a los ojos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6413
translate Spanish ch3m_02_dc4ecd01:

    # "I fret momentarily that all of this new information will strain our relationship, but I know there's no changing reality, and I can't dwell too long on those fears."
    "Me preocupa momentáneamente que toda esta nueva información ponga a prueba nuestra relación, pero sé que la realidad no puede cambiar y no puedo pensar demasiado en esos temores."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6415
translate Spanish ch3m_02_049456d0:

    # c "Rest well. I'll see you soon."
    c "Descansa bien. Nos vemos pronto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6432
translate Spanish ch3m_02_177623d1:

    # "As I go to leave, I decide to pull Grace aside. She beats me to it."
    "Cuando me voy, decido apartar a Grace. Ella se me adelanta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6434
translate Spanish ch3m_02_bf82645b:

    # g "In case you're worried, I've no plans to return to the loch today. My priorities lie only with my sister."
    g "En caso de que estés preocupado, no tengo planes de volver al lago hoy. Mis prioridades están sólo con mi hermana."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6436
translate Spanish ch3m_02_ba97ca87:

    # g "I can't make a stew or roast, but hopefully biscuits and jam will make for a hearty enough meal this evening."
    g "No puedo hacer un estofado o un asado, pero espero que las galletas y la mermelada sean una comida suficientemente generosa esta noche."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6437
translate Spanish ch3m_02_738da3e7:

    # c "How about if I pick up a pint of clotted cream to have with?"
    c "¿Y si cojo medio litro de nata espesa para acompañar?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6440
translate Spanish ch3m_02_f83803bc:

    # g "Please."
    g "Por favor."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6442
translate Spanish ch3m_02_968cde1a:

    # "Knowing that Grace is taking care of her sister allows me to leave with some modicum of comfort. I also know biscuits and jam await, along with one more hug and kiss before bed."
    "Saber que Grace está cuidando de su hermana me permite marcharme con cierto consuelo. También sé que me esperan galletas y mermelada, además de un abrazo y un beso más antes de acostarme."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6443
translate Spanish ch3m_02_b5c2ad17:

    # "Marion may not have received the answers she wanted. But at least she's been comforted."
    "Puede que Marion no haya recibido las respuestas que quería. Pero al menos ha sido reconfortada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6444
translate Spanish ch3m_02_6cb1f4d4:

    # "More importantly, she is safe."
    "Y lo que es más importante, está a salvo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6469
translate Spanish ch3m_03_0a28c918:

    # "There's nothing more I can say or do. I begin my journey home, walking at a snail's pace."
    "No puedo decir ni hacer nada más. Comienzo mi camino a casa, caminando a paso de tortuga."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6470
translate Spanish ch3m_03_2b405f65:

    # "Outside, the fresh air is welcome. Being cooped up in a home of confusing revelations and confessions, I didn't realize I'd been holding my breath for so long."
    "Fuera, el aire fresco es bienvenido. Al estar encerrada en un hogar de confusas revelaciones y confesiones, no me había dado cuenta de que había estado aguantando la respiración durante tanto tiempo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6472
translate Spanish ch3m_03_6d6253c2:

    # "My lungs seize again when a familiar voice calls me over."
    "Mis pulmones vuelven a agarrotarse cuando una voz familiar me llama."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6473
translate Spanish ch3m_03_f4739c0b:

    # a "Malcolm!"
    a "Malcolm!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6483
translate Spanish ch3m_03_b1399194:

    # "I turn around, and much to my chagrin, Alana is walking quickly towards me. Has she been waiting out here this whole time?"
    "Me doy la vuelta y, para mi disgusto, Alana camina rápidamente hacia mí. Ha estado esperando aquí fuera todo este tiempo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6492
translate Spanish ch3m_03_00c5f416:

    # a "Please, please don't be angry with Marion. Be angry with me."
    a "Por favor, no te enfades con Marion. Enfádate conmigo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6495
translate Spanish ch3m_03_25ba3cb2:

    # "I take pause at the desperation in her eyes, the same look she gave me the night I returned home."
    "Me detengo ante la desesperación de sus ojos, la misma mirada que me dirigió la noche que volví a casa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6496
translate Spanish ch3m_03_51fd6249:

    # c "I'm not angry, Miss Alana. Confused, yes. Frightened. But not angry."
    c "No estoy enfadado, Srta. Alana. Confundido, sí. Con miedo. Pero no enfadado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6497
translate Spanish ch3m_03_2be3b56e:

    # a "I want to apologize. My behavior towards you and Marion has been abrupt and unwarranted."
    a "Quiero disculparme. Mi comportamiento contigo y con Marion ha sido brusco e injustificado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6498
translate Spanish ch3m_03_884f6aea:

    # c "And rude."
    c "Y grosera."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6500
translate Spanish ch3m_03_10d8a1c8:

    # a "Yes. I'm sorry."
    a "Sí. Lo siento."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6502
translate Spanish ch3m_03_c8060f67:

    # a "It is so apparent that you and Marion have feelings for each other. Feelings so strong that my... warnings... were not going to halt that love from growing."
    a "Es tan evidente que Marion y tú sentís algo el uno por el otro. Sentimientos tan fuertes que mis... advertencias... no iban a detener el crecimiento de ese amor."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6504
translate Spanish ch3m_03_cfa32b74:

    # a "Love is precious, and not a thing with which to be trifled."
    a "El amor es precioso y no se juega con él."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6505
translate Spanish ch3m_03_1dbd2b44:

    # c "I believe she and I were meant to be."
    c "Creo que ella y yo estamos hechos el uno para el otro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6507
translate Spanish ch3m_03_1876d708:

    # a "So it would seem. Malcolm, I deeply regret my actions, and the... well, circumstances you two are facing. But given that there is no going back, I truly wish the absolute best for you."
    a "Eso parece. Malcolm, lamento profundamente mis acciones, y las... bueno, circunstancias a las que os enfrentáis. Pero dado que no hay vuelta atrás, realmente deseo lo mejor para ustedes."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6508
translate Spanish ch3m_03_2ab6df51:

    # c "I appreciate and accept the apology. I'm thankful for your support and guidance. Over time, Marion will be, too. Somehow."
    c "Agradezco y acepto las disculpas. Estoy agradecido por su apoyo y orientación. Con el tiempo, Marion también lo estará. De alguna manera."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6509
translate Spanish ch3m_03_873155e2:

    # "Instead of the comforting response I desire, I'm given another dose of her peculiar nonsense."
    "En lugar de la respuesta reconfortante que deseo, me da otra dosis de sus peculiares tonterías."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6511
translate Spanish ch3m_03_c9bfa1e4:

    # a "Malcolm, have you spoken to anyone? About this?"
    a "Malcolm, ¿has hablado con alguien? ¿Sobre esto?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6512
translate Spanish ch3m_03_9f5d0d3b:

    # "{i}Other than you? Agnes? Effie?{/i} I carefully weigh my response."
    "{i}¿Aparte de ti? Agnes? Effie?{/i} Considera cuidadosamente mi respuesta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6513
translate Spanish ch3m_03_ee2f2131:

    # c "Nay. I don't believe so."
    c "No. No lo creo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6515
translate Spanish ch3m_03_cbf6bffb:

    # a "Think carefully on it. Think it over, then over again. Just think... I really... yes, I ought to be going. Be well, Malcolm. Think... please."
    a "Piénsalo detenidamente. Piénsalo una y otra vez. Sólo piensa... Realmente... sí, me tengo que ir. Cuídate, Malcolm. Piensa... por favor."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6516
translate Spanish ch3m_03_97d461a3:

    # c "That I will."
    c "Eso haré."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6518
translate Spanish ch3m_03_024e2a2c:

    # a "And please... give Marion time. For her sake. For your sake."
    a "Y por favor... dale tiempo a Marion. Por su bien. Por tu bien."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6519
translate Spanish ch3m_03_7f41deb2:

    # "Alana seems to have returned to a state of fervent nerves and mild paranoia."
    "Alana parece haber vuelto a un estado de fervorosos nervios y leve paranoia."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6520
translate Spanish ch3m_03_5dc090af:

    # c "The tea seems to have helped, as well. Thank you for that. Perhaps you need some more, yourself?"
    c "El té también parece haber ayudado. Gracias. ¿Quizás tú también necesites un poco más?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6522
translate Spanish ch3m_03_7d333766:

    # "She laughs softly."
    "Se ríe suavemente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6524
translate Spanish ch3m_03_46a35f3a:

    # a "I've known it to calm the nerves of the wee ones, who cling too tightly to their mothers' apron strings. If you add a dram or two of whisky, it will also improve spirits."
    a "He sabido que calma los nervios de los más pequeños, que se aferran con demasiada fuerza a los cordones del delantal de sus madres. Si le añades una o dos copitas de whisky, también mejorará el estado de ánimo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6525
translate Spanish ch3m_03_169f06b3:

    # c "I hope that's not what you give the students!"
    c "Espero que no sea eso lo que les den a los estudiantes!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6527
translate Spanish ch3m_03_f4739c0b_1:

    # a "Malcolm!"
    a "Malcolm!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6529
translate Spanish ch3m_03_bb8e4b4e:

    # a "..."
    a "..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6531
translate Spanish ch3m_03_69c9162c:

    # a "Not yet... but my patience has nearly been tested that far. You've not lived until you've been given charge of a dozen children under the age of ten."
    a "Aún no... pero mi paciencia casi se ha puesto a prueba hasta ese punto. No has vivido hasta que te han dado a cargo de una docena de niños menores de diez años."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6532
translate Spanish ch3m_03_8d5c88f0:

    # "I imagine myself alone in a field, with a dozen children. Children with tails and horns."
    "Me imagino solo en un campo, con una docena de niños. Niños con rabos y cuernos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6533
translate Spanish ch3m_03_380c1645:

    # "At a later time, I must ask Alana if she thinks I'm at any risk for developing fluffy ears."
    "Más adelante le preguntaré a Alana si cree que corro algún riesgo de desarrollar orejas peludas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6534
translate Spanish ch3m_03_f93103eb:

    # "Speaking of fluffy ears..."
    "Hablando de orejas esponjosas..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6535
translate Spanish ch3m_03_0a60c6db:

    # c "Do you know of any other villagers in town with this... condition?"
    c "Sabes de algún otro aldeano en el pueblo con esta... condición?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6537
translate Spanish ch3m_03_61d81d2d:

    # a "Any other fae? I can't say if I do."
    a "Algún otro fae? No puedo decir si los tengo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6540
translate Spanish ch3m_03_76f1320e:

    # "It's double talk. Meaningless. Does she, and she won't say? Or does she not? Perhaps she, herself, doesn't know the answer. Alana squints, as if reaching deeper into my thoughts."
    "Es doble discurso. Sin sentido. ¿Lo hace, y no lo dice? ¿O no? Tal vez ni ella misma sepa la respuesta. Alana entrecierra los ojos, como si metiera la mano en mis pensamientos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6542
translate Spanish ch3m_03_65a41c46:

    # a "Why? Have you seen something? Someone?"
    a "¿Por qué? ¿Has visto algo? ¿A alguien?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6552
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_7afc421f:

    # "I want desperately to ask about Effie. Who is she? Does Alana know her?"
    "Quiero preguntar desesperadamente por Effie. ¿Quién es? ¿La conoce Alana?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6553
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_d1770bdb:

    # c "Alana, do you know a girl in town..."
    c "Alana, ¿conoces a una chica en la ciudad..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6554
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_48df6007:

    # "I stop. I can't use her name. What a betrayal of trust that would be, talking behind her back to strangers. This isn't the Whist Club; this is Miss Alana."
    "Me detengo. No puedo decir su nombre. Qué traición a la confianza sería hablar a sus espaldas con extraños. Esto no es el Club de Whist; es la Srta. Alana."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6555
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_be2a5919:

    # "Certainly not the woman to share personal stories with, unless you want her to start meddling immediately. It was bad enough that I asked Gran about Effie."
    "Ciertamente no es la mujer con la que compartir historias personales, a menos que quieras que empiece a entrometerse inmediatamente. Ya era bastante malo que le preguntara a la abuela por Effie."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6556
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_0cab951d:

    # "If the whole village started gossiping about her, it would probably drive her right out of town."
    "Si todo el pueblo empezara a cotillear sobre ella, probablemente la echarían del pueblo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6558
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_ac9b29be:

    # a "Who?"
    a "A quién?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6559
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_1e1b6b95:

    # c "I... uh... can't think of her name. It's slipped my mind. Though I've seen her at market several times. My age. Younger, perhaps? Very jumpy, but very sweet. She's usually in a big floppy hat."
    c "Yo... eh... no puedo pensar en su nombre. Se me ha olvidado. Aunque la he visto en el mercado varias veces. Mi edad. ¿Más joven, quizás? Muy nerviosa, pero muy dulce. Suele llevar un gran sombrero flexible."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6561
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_8c1fdd4a:

    # a "A floppy hat? Why, that describes nobody."
    a "¿Un sombrero flexible? Eso no describe a nadie."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6562
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_30dfc5b8:

    # c "You're right. She has glasses, short brown hair."
    c "Tiene razón. Tiene gafas, pelo castaño corto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6564
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_a8c6a385:

    # a "Gemma Tyte? Maggie's oldest? She's such a lovely young girl."
    a "¿Gemma Tyte? ¿La mayor de Maggie? Es una chica encantadora."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6565
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_7e7ae8eb:

    # c "Oh... uh... no. Different girl."
    c "Oh... uh... no. Chica diferente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6567
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_0a06b734:

    # a "I may know most of the town, Malcolm, but certainly not all. What is it you need to know about her?"
    a "Puede que conozca la mayor parte del pueblo, Malcolm, pero desde luego no todo. ¿Qué es lo que necesitas saber sobre ella?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6568
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_a793782c:

    # "What do I need to know? If Alana has seen a girl with bunny ears? What would the point be? That Alana would track her down, set her straight."
    "¿Qué necesito saber? ¿Si Alana ha visto a una chica con orejas de conejo? ¿Qué sentido tendría? Que Alana la localizaría, la pondría en su sitio."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6569
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_8adb4dc8:

    # "Effie seemed quite confident and content with herself. If it's real, there's no concern, is there? If Effie was lying, why make Alana distraught?"
    "Effie parecía bastante segura y contenta consigo misma. Si es real, no hay preocupación, ¿verdad? Si Effie mentía, ¿por qué angustiar a Alana?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6571
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_2a29e6c3:

    # a "Come now, spit it out, Malcolm."
    a "Vamos, escúpelo, Malcolm."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6572
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_5e2f612d:

    # c "Could it be... well... would anyone else..."
    c "Podría ser... bueno... ¿alguien más..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6574
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_707eea60:

    # a "Does she have {i}animal features?{/i}"
    a "¿Tiene {i}¿características animales?{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6575
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_13251290:

    # c "Maybe."
    c "Tal vez."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6577
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_7357e0ab:

    # a "Honesty, Malcolm!"
    a "¡Sinceridad, Malcolm!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6579
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_26eefe0a:

    # c "Yes."
    c "Sí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6581
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_90f2652b:

    # a "How do you know?"
    a "¿Cómo lo sabes?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6582
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_a20d4a68:

    # c "Maybe she showed me. Maybe."
    c "Tal vez ella me mostró. Tal vez."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6584
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_306922d7:

    # "Alana's eyes get huge."
    "Los ojos de Alana se agrandan."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6585
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_f883310e:

    # a "What type of features did you {i}maybe{/i} see?"
    a "¿Qué tipo de características {i}tal vez{/i} viste?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6586
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_2411ee30:

    # "Quite suddenly, I believe I have stepped into a troublesome, muddied bog of potential lies. I need to withdraw myself from this conversation."
    "De repente, creo que me he metido en un pantano turbio y problemático de posibles mentiras. Necesito retirarme de esta conversación."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6587
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_fae0c85b:

    # c "I shouldn't have said anything. Really. I believe she may have seen Marion without her disguise. I think the girl was pulling my leg. I guess, I'm just asking if..."
    c "No debería haber dicho nada. De verdad. Creo que pudo haber visto a Marion sin su disfraz. Creo que la chica me estaba tomando el pelo. Supongo, sólo pregunto si..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6588
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_ace55644:

    # "I've confused myself, even. What am I asking? What more do I need to know?"
    "Incluso me he confundido. ¿Qué estoy preguntando? ¿Qué más necesito saber?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6590
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_a509ed29:

    # a "...If there are more changelings in town? Malcolm, I don't know."
    a "...si hay más cambiantes en la ciudad? Malcolm, no lo sé."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6592
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_70c65b66:

    # a "I try to protect those I can, but, as I've said, I am not the mystic others wish I was. I'm the crazy woman who lives alone, and tries to help others who want my help."
    a "Intento proteger a los que puedo, pero, como ya he dicho, no soy la mística que otros desearían que fuera. Soy la loca que vive sola e intenta ayudar a otros que quieren mi ayuda."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6594
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_5fee7dbb:

    # a "If you see this girl again, and she needs counsel, please let her know I welcome her with open arms. Otherwise, it's best to mind our own business...{w} maybe."
    a "Si vuelves a ver a esta chica y necesita consejo, por favor, hazle saber que la recibo con los brazos abiertos. De lo contrario, es mejor que nos metamos en nuestros propios asuntos...{w} tal vez."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6597
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_9312a476:

    # "She winks, and I have to smile."
    "Me guiña un ojo y tengo que sonreír."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6598
translate Spanish ch3m_03_a_664e278f:

    # c "I only mentioned it because..."
    c "Sólo lo mencioné porque..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6602
translate Spanish ch3m_03_b_1d2e7a5b:

    # "I won't betray Effie's trust. She may not know Alana, nor ever want to reveal her secret."
    "No traicionaré la confianza de Effie. Puede que no conozca a Alana, ni quiera revelar nunca su secreto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6603
translate Spanish ch3m_03_b_ce9000af:

    # c "No... no. I just..."
    c "No... no. Yo sólo..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6610
translate Spanish ch3m_03_c_8318a670:

    # "Alana places a hand on my shoulder, sending a jolt of electricity through me. I ignore the sensation, and continue."
    "Alana me pone una mano en el hombro, lo que me produce una descarga eléctrica. Ignoro la sensación y continúo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6611
translate Spanish ch3m_03_c_8ef28c12:

    # a "Tell me, please."
    a "Dime, por favor."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6613
translate Spanish ch3m_03_c_c6055333:

    # c "I just believe I need to start looking at the world in an entirely new light. A new view. Once again."
    c "Sólo creo que necesito empezar a mirar el mundo bajo una luz completamente nueva. Una nueva visión. Una vez más."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6617
translate Spanish ch3m_03_c_4271ff7d:

    # a "No. Not true, Malcolm. You only need to use the eyes you've always used. They're simply open wider now. You see what others can't... or won't. You are as blessed as Marion. Perhaps moreso."
    a "No. No es cierto, Malcolm. Sólo necesitas usar los ojos que siempre has usado. Simplemente ahora están más abiertos. Ves lo que otros no pueden... o no quieren. Estás tan bendecido como Marion. Tal vez más."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6618
translate Spanish ch3m_03_c_be946ed6:

    # c "How is that?"
    c "¿Cómo es eso?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6620
translate Spanish ch3m_03_c_7cfa0e59:

    # a "Her eyes are open because this is who she is. She has never had a choice. Your eyes are open because you want them to be."
    a "Tiene los ojos abiertos porque ella es así. Nunca ha tenido elección. Tus ojos están abiertos porque tú quieres que lo estén."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6622
translate Spanish ch3m_03_c_acfe1d18:

    # a "Think of that power you have, Malcolm. The power of choice. Of acceptance. Of willingness to accept others the way they are. To love them, despite what others see as faults."
    a "Piensa en el poder que tienes, Malcolm. El poder de elegir. De aceptación. De la voluntad de aceptar a los demás tal como son. De amarlos, a pesar de lo que otros ven como defectos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6623
translate Spanish ch3m_03_c_04b5d147:

    # c "I believe you put too much credit towards me. I simply fell in love with a woman whose heart is much purer than mine."
    c "Creo que me das demasiado crédito. Simplemente me enamoré de una mujer cuyo corazón es mucho más puro que el mío."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6625
translate Spanish ch3m_03_c_d8ee6d73:

    # "Alana tears up as I speak."
    "Alana llora mientras hablo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6626
translate Spanish ch3m_03_c_ce337f32:

    # a "Malcolm, your heart can never be given enough credit. Comfort her. Love her. Please. For me. For her. For you."
    a "Malcolm, nunca se le dará suficiente crédito a tu corazón. Consuélala. Ámala. Por favor. Por mi. Por ella. Por ti."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6636
translate Spanish ch3m_03_c_c93cbb58:

    # c "I will surely try, Miss Alana."
    c "Sin duda lo intentaré, Srta. Alana."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6665
translate Spanish ch3m_04_6fd4d48e:

    # "I didn't expect to find myself here again, today."
    "No esperaba encontrarme aquí de nuevo, hoy."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6678
translate Spanish ch3m_04_62f768a7:

    # b "My boy! I didn't expect to find you here again, today!"
    b "Mi niño! No esperaba encontrarte aquí de nuevo!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6679
translate Spanish ch3m_04_860847aa:

    # c "While chores call... the taste of barley and malt speaks louder."
    c "Mientras las tareas llaman... el sabor de la cebada y la malta habla más alto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6684
translate Spanish ch3m_04_e5a7fd5d:

    # "I feel guilty detouring to the Stag & Nanny, but I'm in need of stiff drink."
    "Me siento culpable por desviarme al Stag & Nanny, pero necesito un trago fuerte."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6690
translate Spanish ch3m_04_a3be6f6b:

    # "A fresh pint slides towards me. Balgair, always the consummate professional."
    "Una pinta fresca se desliza hacia mí. Balgair, siempre el profesional consumado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6692
translate Spanish ch3m_04_88e75b4c:

    # b "Where's the little lass? Oh... oh no, lad. That face is written with a thousand stories. Care to tell me one or two? Or dare ye save it for the bottom of yer glass?"
    b "Dónde está la muchachita? Oh... oh no, muchacho. Esa cara está escrita con mil historias. ¿Te importaría contarme una o dos? ¿O te atreves a guardarla para el fondo de tu vaso?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6693
translate Spanish ch3m_04_1f67a293:

    # "Never has his husky voice resonated so deeply inside me. I don't know if I'm tired of talking and listening, or want to keep rehashing this insanity to try and make sense of it."
    "Nunca su voz ronca había resonado tan profundamente en mi interior. No sé si estoy cansada de hablar y escuchar, o si quiero seguir repitiendo esta locura para tratar de encontrarle sentido."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6695
translate Spanish ch3m_04_64465f0e:

    # c "Balgair, have you ever been in love?"
    c "Balgair, alguna vez has estado enamorado?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6697
translate Spanish ch3m_04_c1230aa2:

    # "The thick forearm I see behind my glass starts to swing this way and that with the rag, sending wet, hoppy droplets onto my head."
    "El grueso antebrazo que veo detrás de mi vaso empieza a balancearse de un lado a otro con el trapo, lanzando gotas húmedas y lupuladas sobre mi cabeza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6698
translate Spanish ch3m_04_1a999c5f:

    # b "I see! Not beatin' around the bush today, are ya, lad? Thought ye might be here to see if auld Balgair is surviving without his number one showgirl on the stage."
    b "¡Ya veo! No te andas con rodeos hoy, ¿verdad, muchacho? Pensé que estarías aquí para ver si el viejo Balgair sobrevive sin su corista número uno en el escenario."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6699
translate Spanish ch3m_04_fdbc99f3:

    # "He's not wrong. Jessie's absence leaves a palpable void. The darkness surrounding the piano is ominous even in daylight."
    "No se equivoca. La ausencia de Jessie deja un vacío palpable. La oscuridad que rodea el piano es ominosa incluso a la luz del día."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6700
translate Spanish ch3m_04_943bd68a:

    # "I can't imagine how she would react to her sister's transformation. She always wanted excitement, didn't she? Well, can't top a sister with a genuine fur coat!"
    "No puedo imaginar cómo reaccionaría ante la transformación de su hermana. Siempre quiso emociones, ¿verdad? Bueno, ¡no se puede superar a una hermana con un auténtico abrigo de piel!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6702
translate Spanish ch3m_04_4c720b4d:

    # c "Yes, well... I mean... I want to know that you're all right, of course!"
    c "Sí, bueno... Quiero decir... Quiero saber que estás bien, ¡por supuesto!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6704
translate Spanish ch3m_04_1c407967:

    # b "Bah! You're not after my well-being. You're after Balgair's tales o' woe! Those're the stories that'll give ya even more bags under yer eyes! Well..."
    b "¡Bah! No buscas mi bienestar. ¡Buscas las historias de Balgair! ¡Esas son las historias que te darán aún más ojeras! Bueno..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6706
translate Spanish ch3m_04_b347d0d7:

    # "Balgair sets down the towel, and leans across the oak bar until he's got me locked in his sights."
    "Balgair deja la toalla y se inclina sobre la barra de roble hasta que me tiene en su punto de mira."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6707
translate Spanish ch3m_04_d0331fc5:

    # b "I could tell you a love story or two."
    b "Podría contarte una o dos historias de amor."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6708
translate Spanish ch3m_04_8aae2cca:

    # "Ever the storyteller. I knew I could count on him to take over the talking reins."
    "Siempre contando historias. Sabía que podía contar con él para tomar las riendas de la conversación."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6710
translate Spanish ch3m_04_02b6a532:

    # b "But if ye want a simple answer? Aye. I've had my heart stolen. I have."
    b "Pero si quieres una respuesta sencilla? Sí. Me han robado el corazón. Me lo han robado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6711
translate Spanish ch3m_04_db0ee951:

    # c "Tell me. Why aren't you still with her?"
    c "Dímelo. Por qué no sigues con ella?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6713
translate Spanish ch3m_04_e85fbf77:

    # b "Dark tales, lad. Probably not for ya to hear in yer current state."
    b "Cuentos oscuros, muchacho. Probablemente no para que las escuches en tu estado actual."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6714
translate Spanish ch3m_04_022961f0:

    # c "Then tell me about when it was good."
    c "Entonces háblame de cuando era bueno."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6716
translate Spanish ch3m_04_559525f1:

    # b "You need your spirits lifted?"
    b "Necesitas que te levanten el ánimo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6721
translate Spanish ch3m_04_09290179:

    # "I lift my glass to the sky, and Balgair pours me a fresh pint... and a double shot of whisky."
    "Levanto mi vaso al cielo, y Balgair me sirve una pinta fresca... y un trago doble de whisky."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6723
translate Spanish ch3m_04_477be4b0:

    # b "That I can do. Let me tell you a story of love."
    b "Que puedo hacer. Déjame contarte una historia de amor."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6724
translate Spanish ch3m_04_09c01569:

    # "He downs half a pint of his own before starting."
    "Se bebe media pinta antes de empezar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6726
translate Spanish ch3m_04_c58e2d14:

    # b "I'll try to keep it short, but I've been known to spin a long yarn."
    b "Intentaré ser breve, pero se me da bien hilar largo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6728
translate Spanish ch3m_04_ffab3473:

    # b "My true love? My only love, I dare say. That fool woman! That evil, conniving, manipulative woman..."
    b "Mi verdadero amor? Mi único amor, me atrevería a decir. ¡Esa mujer tonta! Esa malvada, confabuladora, manipuladora mujer..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6729
translate Spanish ch3m_04_87b2cf36:

    # "I don't think I want to hear what I'm about to hear."
    "No creo que quiera oír lo que estoy a punto de oír."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6731
translate Spanish ch3m_04_d12151cb:

    # b "She won my heart over by being the kindest, gentlest soul a bull-headed man like me could ever meet."
    b "Se ganó mi corazón por ser el alma más amable y gentil que un cabeza hueca como yo pudiera conocer."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6732
translate Spanish ch3m_04_ae8d467e:

    # "I laugh out loud, and Balgair joins in."
    "Me río a carcajadas y Balgair también."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6734
translate Spanish ch3m_04_bb1eada1:

    # b "I kid ye not, Malcolm! 'Twas the sweetest lass a man ever laid eyes upon. Not the most traditionally beautiful, but looks don't matter much in affairs of the heart."
    b "No bromeo, Malcolm! Era la chica más dulce sobre la que un hombre haya posado sus ojos. No la más bella tradicionalmente, pero las apariencias no importan mucho en los asuntos del corazón."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6735
translate Spanish ch3m_04_18bb07a4:

    # "I start to interrupt. That can hardly be true. But maybe he's right."
    "Empiezo a interrumpir. No puede ser verdad. Pero quizá tenga razón."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6736
translate Spanish ch3m_04_3ed4448f:

    # "Your eyes see everyone you meet, but your heart only falls for another heart, no matter the appearance."
    "Tus ojos ven a todos los que conoces, pero tu corazón sólo se enamora de otro corazón, sin importar la apariencia."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6737
translate Spanish ch3m_04_88181fb5:

    # c "'Tis all happenstance, isn't it? Meeting the woman of your dreams?"
    c "Todo es casualidad, ¿verdad? ¿Conocer a la mujer de tus sueños?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6738
translate Spanish ch3m_04_23d0701e:

    # "Or her telling you as much. I chuckle, remembering how Gran assured me that Marion was fully in charge of my affairs of the heart."
    "O que ella te lo diga. Me río entre dientes, recordando cómo la abuela me aseguraba que Marion se ocupaba totalmente de mis asuntos del corazón."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6739
translate Spanish ch3m_04_0cf2d8c0:

    # "Luckily, Marion let me know that I was to fall for her. A well and good plan, all around."
    "Por suerte, Marion me hizo saber que debía enamorarme de ella. Un buen plan, en general."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6741
translate Spanish ch3m_04_9d3e943a:

    # b "Aye. But let me tell you, falling for a woman like that puts your whole world into perspective."
    b "Aye. Pero déjame decirte, enamorarse de una mujer así pone todo tu mundo en perspectiva."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6742
translate Spanish ch3m_04_6f4a940c:

    # c "It makes you a better man, eh?"
    c "Te hace un hombre mejor, ¿eh?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6744
translate Spanish ch3m_04_5cb4d8a6:

    # "Balgair polishes off his beer, shaking his head."
    "Balgair da un trago a su cerveza y sacude la cabeza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6746
translate Spanish ch3m_04_cb7f1498:

    # b "That's what it should've done, my boy. Alas. Balgair has always been more stubborn than smart. My greatest lament is not being a better man for that one woman."
    b "Eso es lo que debería haber hecho, muchacho. Ay. Balgair siempre ha sido más terco que inteligente. Mi mayor lamento es no haber sido mejor hombre para esa única mujer."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6747
translate Spanish ch3m_04_fe27edf1:

    # "I nod along, realizing that with Marion, all I have to be is present. Kind, caring, a shoulder to lean on. Despite all of her physical changes, her heart will never be anything less than perfect."
    "Asiento con la cabeza, dándome cuenta de que con Marion sólo tengo que estar presente. Amable, cariñosa, un hombro en el que apoyarme. A pesar de todos sus cambios físicos, su corazón nunca será menos que perfecto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6749
translate Spanish ch3m_04_29584c82:

    # b "The pain of rejection? That, Malcolm, is temporary. The pain of regret? It lasts a lifetime."
    b "El dolor del rechazo? Eso Malcolm, es temporal. El dolor del arrepentimiento? Dura toda la vida."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6758
translate Spanish ch3m_04_a5777020:

    # "He looks off for a moment, and I almost think I see a small tear in his eye. He pounds the bar, then looks squarely back at me."
    "Desvía la mirada un momento y casi me parece ver una pequeña lágrima en sus ojos. Golpea la barra y vuelve a mirarme fijamente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6759
translate Spanish ch3m_04_6b8e4cf5:

    # b "Pain is temporary. Love is forever."
    b "El dolor es temporal. El amor es para siempre."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6761
translate Spanish ch3m_04_7e08e3fc:

    # b "Once you find that woman to love, make sure you do it. Give her more love than you yourself even believe you deserve. If you get even half back in return, you're way ahead. Believe you, me."
    b "Una vez que encuentres a esa mujer a la que amar, asegúrate de hacerlo. Dale más amor del que tú mismo crees merecer. Si recibes aunque sea la mitad a cambio, estás muy adelantado. Créeme."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6763
translate Spanish ch3m_04_2798e766:

    # "It feels like a talk with my Gran, what with all the sentimental advice. But Balgair's story couldn't ring more true. Here, I have not just the greatest woman, but the greatest woman for me."
    "Parece una charla con mi Abue, con todos los consejos sentimentales. Pero la historia de Balgair no podría sonar más verdadera. Aquí no sólo tengo a la mejor mujer, sino a la mejor mujer para mí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6765
translate Spanish ch3m_04_9ac4a13a:

    # b "It's not her beauty, or whether she can drive a herd, or cook a hearty meal for burly fellas like us. It's whether or not that lass will love you forever. Through thick and thin."
    b "No se trata de su belleza, ni de si puede conducir un rebaño o cocinar una buena comida para tipos fornidos como nosotros. Es si esa chica te amará para siempre. En las buenas y en las malas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6766
translate Spanish ch3m_04_38927d35:

    # c "Through the good times and the bad. That's what they say, aye?"
    c "En las buenas y en las malas. Eso es lo que dicen, ¿no?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6767
translate Spanish ch3m_04_e8f676a9:

    # "Horns and all."
    "Con cuernos y todo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6769
translate Spanish ch3m_04_992dc9e8:

    # b "I just wasn't strong enough to make it through the rougher patches. Can y'imagine?"
    b "No era lo suficientemente fuerte para superar los momentos más difíciles. Te lo imaginas?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6771
translate Spanish ch3m_04_bb2a0c68:

    # "Balgair stands proud and flexes his arm. A few catcalls are heard, and he waves."
    "Balgair se alza orgulloso y flexiona el brazo. Se oyen algunos abucheos y saluda con la mano."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6772
translate Spanish ch3m_04_b41d7b75:

    # b "Your good man, Balgair, here? Not strong enough?"
    b "Tu buen hombre, Balgair, aquí? No es lo suficientemente fuerte?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6773
translate Spanish ch3m_04_e4abbd80:

    # c "That is a tall tale, sir."
    c "Eso es un cuento chino, señor."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6776
translate Spanish ch3m_04_491dfa3b:

    # b "I only wish it weren't true."
    b "Ojalá no fuera cierto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6777
translate Spanish ch3m_04_7659b9af:

    # "He gathers his towel and glass, pointing towards the men whistling at him."
    "Recoge su toalla y su vaso, señalando a los hombres que le silban."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6779
translate Spanish ch3m_04_f0df2ecb:

    # b "I'm here to earn a living. Best set to it. Malcolm, follow your heart. 'Tis the only advice I have."
    b "Estoy aquí para ganarme la vida. Mejor ponte a ello. Malcolm, sigue a tu corazón. Es el único consejo que tengo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6784
translate Spanish ch3m_04_e98eb688:

    # "And so I am left behind, alone at the bar, as Balgair gets back to socializing with the other locals."
    "Así que me quedo atrás, solo en el bar, mientras Balgair vuelve a socializar con los demás lugareños."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6786
translate Spanish ch3m_04_36e4b350:

    # "It's only but a minute that I waste ruminating. I'm ready to return to the woman I love. I only hope she still loves me, too."
    "Es sólo un minuto que pierdo rumiando. Estoy listo para volver con la mujer que amo. Sólo espero que ella también me siga amando."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6800
translate Spanish ch3m_04_ce74d24c:

    # "I rise to leave, and run into that mess of blonde hair yet again."
    "Me levanto para irme, y me tropiezo de nuevo con ese lío de pelo rubio."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6810
translate Spanish ch3m_04_711f6194:

    # a "...Malcolm?"
    a "...Malcolm?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6811
translate Spanish ch3m_04_be334e0c:

    # c "Alana?! Are you {i}following me?{/i}"
    c "Alana?! tu me estas {i}siguiendo?{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6812
translate Spanish ch3m_04_8b94280e:

    # "My inhibitions have been washed away, and I prepare to tell Alana my mind."
    "Mis inhibiciones han desaparecido y me dispongo a decirle a Alana lo que pienso."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6814
translate Spanish ch3m_04_4f6d4736:

    # a "Hardly. I came to see Balgair."
    a "Apenas. Vine a ver a Balgair."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6815
translate Spanish ch3m_04_e9722aa0:

    # c "I— {w} Wait.{w} Balgair?"
    c "{w} Espera.{w} Balgair?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6821
translate Spanish ch3m_04_a718eed2:

    # b "What's all this about? Malcolm, is this woman giving you a hard time?"
    b "¿Qué es todo esto Malcolm?, ¿esta mujer te está haciendo pasar un mal rato?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6823
translate Spanish ch3m_04_ec97af56:

    # a "I dare say! Balgair, you're the man I've come to hassle. There's quite an empty void up under those stage lights."
    a "¡Me atrevo a decirlo! Balgair, eres el hombre al que he venido a molestar. Hay un gran vacío bajo las luces del escenario."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6825
translate Spanish ch3m_04_f539b8d1:

    # "He and I exchange baffled looks."
    "Él y yo intercambiamos miradas de desconcierto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6827
translate Spanish ch3m_04_c746ac1f:

    # b "Aye, just so. What of it?"
    b "Sí, así es. Y qué?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6829
translate Spanish ch3m_04_ab861581:

    # "She takes a breath, then gives us a look I've never seen from her before."
    "Respira hondo y nos lanza una mirada que nunca antes había visto en ella."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6832
translate Spanish ch3m_04_30935308:

    # a "I'm offering my services."
    a "Estoy ofreciendo mis servicios."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6833
translate Spanish ch3m_04_1bd7e183:

    # "My jaw nearly drops to the floor. What has gotten into her? I start to wonder if Marion's transformation has made Alana transform as well."
    "Casi se me cae la mandíbula al suelo. ¿Qué le ha pasado? Empiezo a preguntarme si la transformación de Marion ha hecho que Alana también se transforme."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6835
translate Spanish ch3m_04_3628661d:

    # b "Are you offering to become the pub's new {i}chanteuse,{/i} my dear?"
    b "¿Te ofreces a convertirte en la nueva {i}chanteuse,{/i} querida?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6837
translate Spanish ch3m_04_209f8db8:

    # a "Singing? No, never! However..."
    a "¿Cantando? No, nunca. Sin embargo..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6838
translate Spanish ch3m_04_33a1aefa:

    # "I'm thoroughly enjoying this conversation now, and anticipate quite the proposal."
    "Estoy disfrutando mucho de esta conversación ahora y anticipo bastante la propuesta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6841
translate Spanish ch3m_04_75225adb:

    # a "Do you keep spare bagpipes here anywhere?"
    a "Guardan gaitas de repuesto en algún sitio?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6843
translate Spanish ch3m_04_63caa33d:

    # b "Come, now! No good Scotsman is without an extra set of bagpipes."
    b "Vamos! Ningún buen escocés carece de un juego extra de gaitas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6847
translate Spanish ch3m_04_c622d9eb:

    # "He ducks behind the counter, and hauls out a heap of tartan and hand-carved wood pipes."
    "Se esconde detrás del mostrador y saca un montón de tartán y pipas de madera talladas a mano."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6854
translate Spanish ch3m_04_fb4e8280:

    # b "Here ya are m'lady. They may be a little out of tune, but that's nothing a few rounds of whisky won't fix!"
    b "Aquí tiene, señora. Puede que estén un poco desafinadas, ¡pero eso no es nada que unas rondas de whisky no puedan arreglar!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6855
translate Spanish ch3m_04_72b10c42:

    # a "Ah! Beautiful!"
    a "Ah! Precioso!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6875
translate Spanish ch3m_04_71eb3261:

    # "Alana straightens her gloves, and tears into a tune. The noise brings every ear in the place to attention."
    "Alana se endereza los guantes y entona una melodía. El ruido llama la atención de todos los oídos del lugar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6884
translate Spanish ch3m_04_0331645d:

    # b "Always knew she was loud and full of hot air. Eh, lad?"
    b "Siempre supe que era ruidosa y llena de aire caliente. Eh, muchacho?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6886
translate Spanish ch3m_04_43fc8339:

    # "I elbow Balgair, who smirks, and starts tapping his foot to the tune."
    "Le doy un codazo a Balgair, que sonríe y empieza a dar golpecitos con el pie al son de la melodía."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6909
translate Spanish ch3m_04_f071ad30:

    # "When she's done, she has a huge grin on her face."
    "Cuando termina, tiene una enorme sonrisa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6910
translate Spanish ch3m_04_c3edccae:

    # a "So, I'm hired?"
    a "Entonces, estoy contratada?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6911
translate Spanish ch3m_04_5e08a6ad:

    # "Balgair's face is frozen in delight and surprise."
    "El rostro de Balgair se congela de deleite y sorpresa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6912
translate Spanish ch3m_04_84e3974e:

    # b "I'll be damned, schoolmistress! An' where did you learn to do that?"
    b "Maldita sea, maestra! ¿Y dónde aprendiste a hacer eso?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6914
translate Spanish ch3m_04_03e94f70:

    # a "Balgair! You never ask a lady where she learned to play the bagpipes!"
    a "Balgair! Nunca se le pregunta a una dama dónde aprendió a tocar la gaita!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6917
translate Spanish ch3m_04_11fd576e:

    # "I'm not sure I want to know, either. I bid them both a farewell, and hurry out before I'm confronted by any new surprises. Can this day get any stranger?"
    "Tampoco estoy seguro de querer saberlo. Me despido de los dos y me apresuro a salir antes de encontrarme con nuevas sorpresas. ¿Puede este día volverse más extraño?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6919
translate Spanish ch3m_04_175909d4:

    # "...That too, I remind myself, is a question best left unanswered. I'm coming, Marion!"
    "...Eso también, me recuerdo, es una pregunta que es mejor dejar sin respuesta. ¡Ya voy, Marion!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6944
translate Spanish ch3m_05_1eaa66bb:

    # "I rush through my duties around our farm while Gran gives me looks of concern."
    "Me apresuro a realizar mis tareas en la granja mientras la abuela me mira preocupada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6948
translate Spanish ch3m_05_cecc100e:

    # s "What's the hurry, dear boy? You're going to pull a muscle if you work so furiously!"
    s "Cuál es la prisa, querido muchacho? Vas a sufrir un tirón si trabajas tan furiosamente!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6949
translate Spanish ch3m_05_5a00f467:

    # "There's no use in lying to Gran anymore, although I do spare her the details of our visit from Miss Alana."
    "Ya no sirve de nada mentirle a la abuela, aunque le ahorro los detalles de nuestra visita de la señorita Alana."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6950
translate Spanish ch3m_05_2bc2045c:

    # c "I'm to return to Marion's home this evening. She needs a bit of comforting. I thought I would bring some scones, if there are some to spare."
    c "Debo volver a casa de Marion esta tarde. Necesita un poco de consuelo. Pensé en traer algunos bollos, si hay algunos de sobra."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6952
translate Spanish ch3m_05_cefcb50b:

    # "Gran nods in approval, with a glint of joy in her eye."
    "La abuela asiente en señal de aprobación, con un brillo de alegría en los ojos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6953
translate Spanish ch3m_05_280f5d7a:

    # s "Well, then, speed up! Never leave a woman waiting!"
    s "Bueno, entonces, acelera! Nunca dejes a una mujer esperando!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:6954
translate Spanish ch3m_05_1f1977ff:

    # "I've never been happier to do as I'm told."
    "Nunca he sido tan feliz haciendo lo que me dicen."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6963
translate Spanish ch3m_05_364568b8:

    # "When I return to the MacLeod homestead, Grace advises me that I will find her sister out in the fields."
    "Cuando vuelvo a la granja de los MacLeod, Grace me dice que encontraré a su hermana en el campo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6964
translate Spanish ch3m_05_7068bc72:

    # "After how I left Marion, I'm surprised that she's in any state to return to work. But I relate to how one can find solace in routine."
    "Después de cómo me despedí de Marion, me sorprende que esté en condiciones de volver al trabajo. "

# game/script_marion.rpy:6965
translate Spanish ch3m_05_17fce2bd:

    # "The sound of mooing carries to my ears. The MacLeods' herd grazes in the vale, and I see Marion's figure a head above them. They mill around her as if she is one of their own."
    "El sonido de los mugidos llega hasta mis oídos. El rebaño de los MacLeod pasta en el valle y veo la figura de Marion una cabeza por encima de ellos. Se arremolinan a su alrededor como si fuera una de los suyos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6991
translate Spanish ch3m_05_fb602f29:

    # "As I approach, I hear her humming a tune of her own. She doesn't seem to notice me. I'm struck, once again, by her beauty."
    "Cuando me acerco, la oigo tararear una melodía. No parece fijarse en mí. Me sorprende, una vez más, su belleza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6995
translate Spanish ch3m_05_513893bb:

    # "It's not just the way she looks, or even me needing to look past her new body. She carries about her an aura that is brighter than us all."
    "No se trata sólo de su aspecto, ni siquiera de que yo tenga que mirar más allá de su nuevo cuerpo. Tiene un aura más brillante que todos nosotros."

# game/script_marion.rpy:6996
translate Spanish ch3m_05_da912212:

    # "She is the embodiment of what's left in this world that is honest, pure, and good."
    "Ella es la encarnación de lo que queda en este mundo de honesto, puro y bueno."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7010
translate Spanish ch3m_05_8acdf753:

    # "I wave, and catch her eye."
    "Saludo con la mano y capto su mirada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7011
translate Spanish ch3m_05_028ac9c0:

    # c "I hope I'm not interrupting."
    c "Espero no estar interrumpiendo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7015
translate Spanish ch3m_05_6c0d8768:

    # m "Never. I was just... pondering what's to come... what I've been told today. There's so much running at full speed through my head."
    m "Nunca. Sólo estaba... reflexionando sobre lo que vendrá... lo que me han dicho hoy. Hay tantas cosas corriendo a toda velocidad por mi cabeza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7016
translate Spanish ch3m_05_d4786050:

    # c "That's understandable."
    c "Es comprensible."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7019
translate Spanish ch3m_05_71f4263e:

    # "When I'd last left her, she seemed so distant. Now to look at her, I can see hope blooming from within."
    "La última vez que la dejé, parecía tan distante. Ahora, al mirarla, puedo ver cómo florece la esperanza en su interior."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7020
translate Spanish ch3m_05_7346b652:

    # c "You look more... at peace. I hope I'm not jumping to grand conclusions."
    c "Pareces más... en paz. Espero no estar sacando grandes conclusiones."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7027
translate Spanish ch3m_05_8e434a3a:

    # "Marion offers me her hand, which I take eagerly. Her fingers, while dark and fused, are still hers. They curl around my palm."
    "Marion me ofrece su mano, que tomo con impaciencia. Sus dedos, aunque oscuros y fundidos, siguen siendo los suyos. Se enroscan alrededor de mi palma."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7029
translate Spanish ch3m_05_e14def88:

    # m "Thank you for coming back. It's been quite a day, eh?"
    m "Gracias por volver. Ha sido un gran día, eh?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7030
translate Spanish ch3m_05_60affa10:

    # c "It certainly has."
    c "Desde luego que sí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7033
translate Spanish ch3m_05_14321539:

    # m "I... I've come to a conclusion. Something I've always heard and never believed to the extent I believe it now."
    m "Yo... he llegado a una conclusión. Algo que siempre he oído y nunca creí hasta el punto que lo creo ahora."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7035
translate Spanish ch3m_05_f75fa4d0:

    # "She looks deeply into my eyes."
    "Ella me mira profundamente a los ojos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7036
translate Spanish ch3m_05_9680a97f:

    # m "Ours is not to reason why, Malcolm."
    m "Lo nuestro no es razonar el porqué, Malcolm."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7038
translate Spanish ch3m_05_dbef5c43:

    # "Marion shrugs, and squeezes my hands."
    "Marion se encoge de hombros y me aprieta las manos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7039
translate Spanish ch3m_05_b9d782bd:

    # c "Not that saying it really stops the brain from working overtime, though, does it?"
    c "Pero decirlo no impide que el cerebro trabaje horas extras, ¿verdad?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7041
translate Spanish ch3m_05_ec6567f9:

    # m "Hah, no. But it's worth reminding myself. Besides, it keeps me sane while thinking of... other things."
    m "Hah, No. Pero vale la pena recordármelo. Además, me mantiene cuerda mientras pienso en... otras cosas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7042
translate Spanish ch3m_05_6e731ba4:

    # "I don't press for more, but Marion must sense my concern. She lowers her voice to a whisper."
    "No insisto más, pero Marion debe de notar mi preocupación. Baja la voz hasta un susurro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7044
translate Spanish ch3m_05_3c5dab59:

    # m "It's what I'm most ashamed to say."
    m "Es lo que más vergüenza me da decir."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7049
translate Spanish ch3m_05_884b0279:

    # "The breeze takes hold of our hair, and Marion's skirt. I watch her tail flow back and forth in the wind."
    "La brisa se apodera de nuestro pelo y de la falda de Marion. Veo su cola fluir de un lado a otro con el viento."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7050
translate Spanish ch3m_05_21e4eb6b:

    # "What Marion says next hits me like a punch to the gut."
    "Lo que Marion dice a continuación me golpea como un puñetazo en las tripas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7053
translate Spanish ch3m_05_2507620e:

    # m "I don't think I want to change. I mean... I don't want to change back."
    m "No creo que quiera cambiar. Quiero decir... No quiero volver a cambiar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7056
translate Spanish ch3m_05_28903b03:

    # "Not knowing how to respond, I choose only honesty."
    "Sin saber cómo responder, elijo sólo la honestidad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7058
translate Spanish ch3m_05_5e02b24a:

    # c "I wish you'd told me."
    c "Desearía que me lo hubieras dicho."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7062
translate Spanish ch3m_05_d5d98c96:

    # m "I'm telling you now. It's painful. Like admitting something horrible. I wasn't even being honest to myself. Being caught up in the fear of what people would think, or that I might end up... one of {i}them.{/i}"
    m "Te lo digo ahora. Es doloroso. Como admitir algo horrible. Ni siquiera estaba siendo honesta conmigo misma. Estaba atrapada en el miedo de lo que la gente pensaría, o que yo podría terminar ... una de {i}ellos.{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7073
translate Spanish ch3m_05_340f4af6:

    # "Fiona nuzzles Marion, apparently not taking offense."
    "Fiona acurruca a Marion, aparentemente sin ofenderse."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7077
translate Spanish ch3m_05_ac7d1318:

    # m "But after everything today—the church, the pub... outside under the alders and inside under the quilts—at the end of the day, if Alana's right... this is {i}me.{/i}"
    m "Pero después de todo lo de hoy, la iglesia, la taberna... fuera bajo los alisos y dentro bajo los edredones, al final del día, si Alana tiene razón... este soy {i}yo.{/i}."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7080
translate Spanish ch3m_05_8f896ae0:

    # c "Do you trust her?"
    c "Confías en ella?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7082
translate Spanish ch3m_05_e6a68946:

    # m "I can't say if I do, but I think...{w} no, I {i}know{/i} she's right. I can tell, deep inside. And all those worries aside... it's not so bad. Good, even."
    m "No puedo decir si la tengo, pero creo...{w} No, {i}sé que tiene razón.{/i} Lo sé, en el fondo. Y todas esas preocupaciones aparte... no es tan malo. Bueno, incluso."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7085
translate Spanish ch3m_05_6e0b53d9:

    # m "I'm still scared. I'm most worried that... you will stop loving me because of the way I look."
    m "Sigo teniendo miedo. Lo que más me preocupa es que... dejes de quererme por mi aspecto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7087
translate Spanish ch3m_05_74ef852e:

    # "Marion tilts her head up at me and smiles hopefully."
    "Marion levanta la cabeza y me sonríe esperanzada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7088
translate Spanish ch3m_05_1e915dfb:

    # m "But I can't go back. We can't go backwards."
    m "Pero no puedo volver atrás. No podemos volver atrás."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7091
translate Spanish ch3m_05_3e4dc286:

    # "The pain inside me evaporates before the warmth of her smile."
    "El dolor de mi interior se evapora ante la calidez de su sonrisa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7092
translate Spanish ch3m_05_193d1a6c:

    # "All that she's been through, and she still only wants to be seen as a good person, that which she already is. What she always has been. Perfect."
    "Por todo lo que ha pasado, y aún sólo quiere que la vean como una buena persona, lo que ya es. Lo que siempre ha sido. Perfecta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7095
translate Spanish ch3m_05_f83084c6:

    # c "Marion, I never want to go backwards. I want to be with you. All of you. Just as you are."
    c "Marion, no quiero volver atrás. Quiero estar contigo. Con todos ustedes. Tal como eres."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7098
translate Spanish ch3m_05_f0b1f93c:

    # m "I can't tell you how many times I pictured hearing you say that! Is this real? Are you real, Malcolm Campbell?"
    m "No sabes cuántas veces me he imaginado oyéndote decir eso! Esto es real? Eres real, Malcolm Campbell?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7099
translate Spanish ch3m_05_dbbdfe1a:

    # c "Oh, it's all very real, Marion. We've come back into each other's lives for reasons that... well, as you said, we ought not question. But here we are, side by side."
    c "Oh, todo es muy real, Marion. Hemos vuelto a la vida del otro por razones que... bueno, como dijiste, no deberíamos cuestionar. Pero aquí estamos, uno al lado del otro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7101
translate Spanish ch3m_05_01b76a10:

    # m "My whole world has been turned upside down today."
    m "Hoy todo mi mundo se ha puesto patas arriba."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7104
translate Spanish ch3m_05_98bb9718:

    # c "Yes... but maybe upside down is your right side up!"
    c "Sí... pero tal vez al revés sea tu lado derecho!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7106
translate Spanish ch3m_05_c2603855:

    # m "Perhaps! In fact, I've come to a decision. I... want to embrace my true nature."
    m "Quizás! De hecho, he tomado una decisión. Yo... quiero abrazar mi verdadera naturaleza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7108
translate Spanish ch3m_05_19f1ae49:

    # m "I think I like being fae, part of something magic. At least, I want to like it. If that makes sense."
    m "Creo que me gusta ser una fae, parte de algo mágico. Al menos, quiero que me guste. Si eso tiene sentido."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7109
translate Spanish ch3m_05_a4ea2d89:

    # c "Oddly enough, it does. You never know. There may be benefits to this."
    c "Por extraño que parezca, sí. Nunca se sabe. Puede haber beneficios en esto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7111
translate Spanish ch3m_05_3f3483ab:

    # m "Do you really think so?"
    m "De verdad lo crees?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7112
translate Spanish ch3m_05_cd543559:

    # "She sounds so hopeful, and for a moment I believe that maybe I can even convince myself to be excited by her changes."
    "arece tan esperanzada, y por un momento creo que incluso puedo convencerme de que me entusiasmen sus cambios."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7113
translate Spanish ch3m_05_40a7168c:

    # c "Why not? From here, your life is in your hands."
    c "Por qué no? A partir de aquí, tu vida está en tus manos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7115
translate Spanish ch3m_05_f8908636:

    # m "You mean my hooves?"
    m "Quieres decir mis pezuñas?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7116
translate Spanish ch3m_05_1df35daf:

    # "Marion lets out a genuine laugh, and my heart melts like usual."
    "Marion suelta una carcajada genuina, y mi corazón se derrite como de costumbre."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7117
translate Spanish ch3m_05_4d5aae2f:

    # c "Accept what is good, and make it better!"
    c "Acepta lo que es bueno y mejóralo!."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7119
translate Spanish ch3m_05_dca3b27e:

    # m "Take the bull by the horns?"
    m "Coger el toro por los cuernos?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7120
translate Spanish ch3m_05_6675bbf2:

    # c "Yes! Exactly! Whatever this is... you being a changeling... it's most certainly part of the village's history."
    c "¡Sí! Exactamente. Sea lo que sea... que seas un cambiante... es sin duda parte de la historia del pueblo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7122
translate Spanish ch3m_05_3b036100:

    # m "Its mysticism?"
    m "Es misticismo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7123
translate Spanish ch3m_05_63c6214f:

    # c "Yes, yes definitely."
    c "Sí, sí, definitivamente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7124
translate Spanish ch3m_05_dc746d5f:

    # "Yes, the two of us are sounding a bit delusional, but romance is intoxicating. All of a sudden we are two young people in love, instead of in turmoil. It's a feeling I never want to lose."
    "Sí, los dos estamos sonando un poco delirantes, pero el romance es embriagador. De repente somos dos jóvenes enamorados, en lugar de alborotados. Es un sentimiento que no quiero perder nunca."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7125
translate Spanish ch3m_05_6eccd4eb:

    # c "I look at you, and only see Marion, the woman I love."
    c "Te miro y sólo veo a Marion, la mujer que amo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7128
translate Spanish ch3m_05_6a3f299b:

    # m "You... still love me?"
    m "Tú... todavía me amas?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7129
translate Spanish ch3m_05_36470bd0:

    # c "Of course, Marion! Always. Forever."
    c "Por supuesto, Marion! Siempre. Para siempre."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7131
translate Spanish ch3m_05_aa24f0e7:

    # m "Malcolm, I love you, too. But.. I have one more confession..."
    m "Malcolm, yo también te amo. Pero .. Tengo una confesión más..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7132
translate Spanish ch3m_05_425b7e19:

    # "My heart stops. I don't know if I can handle any more surprises today. I steel myself for the worst."
    "Se me para el corazón. No sé si podré soportar más sorpresas hoy. Me preparo para lo peor."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7135
translate Spanish ch3m_05_270c2b21:

    # m "More of an apology, really. Do you remember when I came by the day Jessie left? And I told you that... that you couldn't save everyone?"
    m "Más bien una disculpa, en realidad. ¿Recuerdas cuando vine el día que Jessie se fue? ¿Y te dije que... que no podías salvar a todos?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7136
translate Spanish ch3m_05_ba92cbae:

    # "I do remember. It cut like a knife when she said it, though I realize it was in the heat of the moment."
    "Lo recuerdo. Me cortó como un cuchillo cuando lo dijo, aunque me doy cuenta de que fue en el calor del momento."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7138
translate Spanish ch3m_05_ac5363fa:

    # m "I truly apologize. I never should have said such a thing. Malcolm, you've completely saved me. You could never know all the good you've given this world."
    m "
Realmente me disculpo. Nunca debí haber dicho tal cosa. Malcolm, me has salvado por completo. Nunca podrás saber todo el bien que le has dado a este mundo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7139
translate Spanish ch3m_05_3556f588:

    # "My throat catches. I don't want her to see me cry, but I just can't stop the tears. Tears that have been building for hours, perhaps weeks."
    "Se me hace un nudo en la garganta. No quiero que me vea llorar, pero no puedo contener las lágrimas. Lágrimas que se han ido acumulando durante horas, quizá semanas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7140
translate Spanish ch3m_05_0b106edc:

    # c "Marion, nothing you could say would hurt me. I know you meant no harm. I feel as though there's nothing to forgive. You are so full of kindness, I don't deserve you."
    c "Marion, nada de lo que digas me hará daño. Sé que no querías hacerme daño. Siento que no hay nada que perdonar. Estás tan llena de bondad que no te merezco."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7142
translate Spanish ch3m_05_2b09906c:

    # m "I feel the same way. I never imagined being loved for all that I am."
    m "Yo siento lo mismo. Nunca imaginé ser amada por todo lo que soy."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7148
translate Spanish ch3m_05_358bc13b:

    # "She holds me tight, and leans in for a kiss."
    "Me abraza fuerte y se inclina para besarme."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7157
translate Spanish ch3m_05_fb545941:

    # "It's the first time I've kissed her mouth since her... changes."
    "Es la primera vez que beso su boca desde sus... cambios."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7158
translate Spanish ch3m_05_f16b6e65:

    # "Her top lip is broad and soft, like a hide blanket. It's not like leather, though, it's pillowy. My lips sink into hers as I glide them along the top of her open mouth."
    "Su labio superior es ancho y suave, como una manta de piel. Pero no es como el cuero, sino como una almohada. Mis labios se hunden en los suyos mientras los deslizo por la parte superior de su boca abierta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7159
translate Spanish ch3m_05_00545595:

    # "The softness to her skin makes my face feel like it is being brushed with piled cotton. As her tongue slides across mine, I sense its increase in size and length."
    "La suavidad de su piel me hace sentir como si me rozaran la cara con algodón amontonado. Cuando su lengua se desliza por la mía, noto que aumenta de tamaño y longitud."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7160
translate Spanish ch3m_05_b25a6dc5:

    # "Instead of being alarmed, it turns me on even more. Her muzzle is warm and lightly damp. She still tastes delicious, like honeysuckle."
    "En lugar de alarmarme, me excita aún más. Su hocico está caliente y ligeramente húmedo. Sigue sabiendo delicioso, a madreselva."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7179
translate Spanish ch3m_05_41118b5f:

    # "We stay connected that way, kissing and offering gentle touches, until the sun begins to dip below the horizon."
    "Permanecemos así conectados, besándonos y ofreciéndonos suaves caricias, hasta que el sol comienza a ocultarse bajo el horizonte."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7180
translate Spanish ch3m_05_1e8abc23:

    # "I offer that we go inside for dinner, but she declines, preferring to remain in the pasture. It's not unlike our first night together, which I have to remind myself was not so long ago."
    "Le propongo que entremos a cenar, pero ella se niega y prefiere quedarse en el prado. No es muy diferente de nuestra primera noche juntos, que tengo que recordarme que no fue hace tanto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7181
translate Spanish ch3m_05_94f3eab0:

    # "We stay outside for many more hours, counting the stars—and our blessings."
    "Nos quedamos fuera muchas horas más, contando las estrellas y nuestras bendiciones."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7208
translate Spanish ch3m_06_e2e5d3a9:

    # "As the days move forward, Marion seems to come to terms with her new identity. She's possessed with a renewed strength, the likes of which I'm envious, and can only hope to mirror."
    "A medida que pasan los días, Marion parece aceptar su nueva identidad. Está dotada de una fuerza renovada que envidio y de la que espero ser un reflejo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7209
translate Spanish ch3m_06_8cbdaa4c:

    # "Like it or not, Grace and I are along for the ride. We support Marion both literally and figuratively."
    "Nos guste o no, Grace y yo estamos con ella. Apoyamos a Marion en sentido literal y figurado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7210
translate Spanish ch3m_06_c50f12c6:

    # "Sometimes, she needs a lift in spirits. Other times, she needs another type of lift—to help balance on her new hooves."
    "A veces, necesita que le levanten el ánimo. Otras veces, necesita otro tipo de ayuda para mantener el equilibrio sobre sus nuevas pezuñas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7211
translate Spanish ch3m_06_26613735:

    # "The ups and downs are a wee bit more extreme than I would like. But the highs are high, and the lows do pass with time."
    "Los altibajos son un poco más extremos de lo que me gustaría. Pero los altos son altos y los bajos pasan con el tiempo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7214
translate Spanish ch3m_06_5bb9e274:

    # "Now that we're all past the initial shock, and take each day with resolve and determination, we've relaxed into a new routine."
    "Ahora que todos hemos superado el shock inicial y nos tomamos cada día con resolución y determinación, nos hemos relajado en una nueva rutina."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7215
translate Spanish ch3m_06_2be1dc79:

    # "An average day with Marion is all I could ever need. I join her at her homestead after my daily chores, staying with her well into the evening."
    "Un día normal con Marion es todo lo que necesito. Me reúno con ella en su granja después de mis tareas diarias y me quedo con ella hasta bien entrada la noche."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7216
translate Spanish ch3m_06_cf586a80:

    # "I'm relieved that she does not shy away from physical contact anymore. She welcomes more than just handholding, and showing our affection comes easily now—although we {i}have{/i} set boundaries."
    "Me alivia saber que ya no rehúye el contacto físico. No se conforma con que la cojan de la mano, y las muestras de afecto le resultan fáciles, aunque {i}tenemos{/i} que poner límites."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7217
translate Spanish ch3m_06_afbfb678:

    # "We often fall asleep in each other's arms only to wake separately, so as not to disturb Gran's sense of decorum."
    "A menudo nos dormimos abrazados para despertarnos por separado, para no alterar el decoro de la abuela."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7220
translate Spanish ch3m_06_32fc98fd:

    # "Gran gives me no grief on the nights I come back from \"the fields\" long after the sun has set. She knows where I am, and we speak nothing of it beyond shared smiles and nods."
    "La abuela no me da ninguna queja las noches que vuelvo de \"los campos\" mucho después de que se haya puesto el sol. Sabe dónde estoy y no hablamos de ello más allá de sonrisas y asentimientos compartidos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7221
translate Spanish ch3m_06_53312d71:

    # "The fact that she approves of my courtship of Marion only adds to my joy. Gran's capacity for acceptance—to look at Marion as more than some alien, bovine being—astonishes me."
    "El hecho de que apruebe mi noviazgo con Marion no hace sino aumentar mi alegría. La capacidad de aceptación de la abuela, de ver a Marion como algo más que un ser extraño y bovino, me enorgullece."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7222
translate Spanish ch3m_06_860fc23b:

    # "As for my own ability to see Marion for more than her... \"nontraditional\" appearance... that comes from a place deep within me that even I don't comprehend."
    "En cuanto a mi propia capacidad de ver a Marion por algo más que su... apariencia \"no tradicional\"... eso proviene de un lugar muy profundo dentro de mí que ni siquiera yo comprendo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7225
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a79d0c66:

    # "Gran assures me that the Campbells are men of honor, with an esteem to rival any other clan's."
    "Gran me asegura que los Campbell son hombres de honor, con una estima que rivaliza con la de cualquier otro clan."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7226
translate Spanish ch3m_06_dc1693d2:

    # "As much as I want to disagree, I believe there is a patience I possess that is unlike that of others."
    "Por mucho que quiera discrepar, creo que poseo una paciencia distinta a la de los demás."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7227
translate Spanish ch3m_06_78261e2b:

    # "Either a patience or a naivete, I do not know."
    "No sé si es paciencia o ingenuidad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7228
translate Spanish ch3m_06_d5fddecc:

    # "It may even be a link to the fae world, real or imagined... a theory my grandparents would be proud of, given their penchant for fairy tales."
    "Puede que incluso sea un vínculo con el mundo de los hados, real o imaginario... una teoría de la que mis abuelos estarían orgullosos, dada su afición a los cuentos de hadas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7229
translate Spanish ch3m_06_696cce9a:

    # "Or perhaps it's just a psychological survival tactic carried over from the trenches. Or a lingering effect of Alana's brew. Who knows!"
    "O tal vez es sólo una táctica de supervivencia psicológica heredada de las trincheras. O un efecto persistente del brebaje de Alana. ¡Quién sabe!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7231
translate Spanish ch3m_06_d7c275ef:

    # "The bottom line is I accept others as they are. I always have. There's no reason to judge another unless they give you one. And, judgement aside, Marion is beyond needing acceptance."
    "En resumen, acepto a los demás tal como son. Siempre lo he hecho. No hay razón para juzgar a otro a menos que te den alguna razón. Y, juicios aparte, Marion está más allá de necesitar aceptación."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7232
translate Spanish ch3m_06_1ac2a9be:

    # "Her heart outshines any other I've ever encountered."
    "Su corazón eclipsa a cualquier otro que haya conocido."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7234
translate Spanish ch3m_06_cc45031d:

    # "I've made mention of commitment.... marriage, even... but Marion shies away from the topic. I'm made to understand that she isn't against it, she's just not ready."
    "Incluso he mencionado el compromiso... matrimonial... pero Marion rehúye el tema. Me han hecho entender que no está en contra, sólo que no está preparada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7235
translate Spanish ch3m_06_e9e5400a:

    # "I worry she's too self-conscious to recite her vows with a tail and fur coat. I assure her that the woman I want with me forever is the one she is right now."
    "Me preocupa que sea demasiado tímida para recitar sus votos con cola y abrigo de piel. Le aseguro que la mujer que quiero conmigo para siempre es la que es ahora mismo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7236
translate Spanish ch3m_06_26018718:

    # "In fact, I can hardly abide a moment not by her side. It's a typical, chill morning when I prepare to make my way back over to the MacLeod farm. I'd only left there hours earlier."
    "De hecho, apenas puedo soportar un momento sin estar a su lado. Es una mañana típica y fría cuando me preparo para volver a la granja MacLeod. Había salido de allí horas antes."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7253
translate Spanish ch3m_06_d094c609:

    # c "But I had to be back for you, didn't I?"
    c "Pero tenía que regresar por ti, ¿no?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7255
translate Spanish ch3m_06_392d94d9:

    # "Hazel huffs a \"good morning\" at me, or perhaps something less flattering."
    "Hazel me suelta un \"buenos días\", o quizá algo menos halagador."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7256
translate Spanish ch3m_06_2d645afb:

    # c "Good morning to you too. Let's see what's on the menu, shall we?"
    c "Buenos días a ti también. Vamos a ver qué hay en el menú, ¿de acuerdo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7261
translate Spanish ch3m_06_83b48326:

    # "I pull a few dusty carrot stumps from my pockets, and she eagerly yanks them from my grasp. It distracts her just long enough to get her tack on."
    "Saco de mis bolsillos unos cuantos trozos de zanahoria polvorienta y ella me los arranca con avidez. La distraigo el tiempo suficiente para que se ponga la correa..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7262
translate Spanish ch3m_06_85aedae2:

    # "I wouldn't usually ride Hazel over to the next yard, but today is Market Day, and with Marion homebound, it's up to us to run the errands and deliver her goods."
    "Normalmente no llevaría a Hazel al patio de al lado, pero hoy es día de mercado y, con Marion confinada en casa, nos toca a nosotros hacer los recados y entregarle la mercancía."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7263
translate Spanish ch3m_06_f1279338:

    # c "Hazel, my gal, you're in for a treat today. And not just the edible kind! Once we're done loading your cart, you'll get to see all your friends next door!"
    c "Hazel, mi chica, hoy te espera una sorpresa. ¡Y no sólo del tipo comestible! Una vez que hayamos terminado de cargar tu carrito, ¡podrás ver a todos tus amigos de al lado!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7268
translate Spanish ch3m_06_0ae18f07:

    # "She swallows the last carrot whole, then huffs loudly; either at the prospect of pulling a loaded cart, or at the notion that anyone is her \"friend.\""
    "Se traga la última zanahoria entera, y luego resopla ruidosamente; ya sea ante la perspectiva de tirar de un carro cargado, o ante la idea de que alguien sea su \"amigo.\""

# game/script_marion.rpy:7270
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a20cefa7:

    # "..."
    "..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7271
translate Spanish ch3m_06_7f951638:

    # "Or perhaps she huffs at neither. She's just a horse, after all... something I keep needing to remind myself again and again."
    "O quizás no, resopla ante ninguno de las dos. No es más que un caballo, después de todo... algo que tengo que recordarme una y otra vez."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7282
translate Spanish ch3m_06_702a3fbe:

    # "I unload the last of today's market haul into the MacLeods' storehouse and step back outside. The wind is picking up, so I pull my jacket tighter around me."
    "Descargo lo que queda del mercado en el almacén de los MacLeod y salgo. El viento arrecia, así que me abrocho más la chaqueta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7284
translate Spanish ch3m_06_b2cee6b5:

    # c "A bit cold and nippy today, eh, Miss Hazel?"
    c "Un poco frío y fresco hoy, ¿eh, señorita Hazel?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7286
translate Spanish ch3m_06_96aba2ae:

    # "It occurs to me, I could be describing either the weather or my horse. I check to see that she hasn't chewed through her tether again."
    "Se me ocurre que podría estar describiendo el clima o mi caballo. Compruebo que no haya vuelto a morder su correa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7287
translate Spanish ch3m_06_f2fe1adc:

    # c "All right, lass! I'll be back shortly—I'm off to find our friends!"
    c "¡Muy bien, muchacha! Volveré enseguida. ¡Me voy a buscar a nuestras amigas!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7302
translate Spanish ch3m_06_ac3dc451:

    # "The day is still young and the sisters aren't home, presumably out doing their morning chores."
    "El día aún es joven y las hermanas no están en casa, presumiblemente haciendo sus tareas matutinas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7303
translate Spanish ch3m_06_e0ee2721:

    # "Sure enough, I find Marion in the nearby field, huddled down by Fiona, performing milking duties."
    "Efectivamente, encuentro a Marion en el campo cercano, acurrucada junto a Fiona, realizando tareas de ordeño."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7305
translate Spanish ch3m_06_246cb3fb:

    # "How must she feel about that task now, given the circumstances? It's certainly been put in a new light. Probably best not to think about it too hard."
    "¿Cómo debe sentirse ahora ante esa tarea, dadas las circunstancias? Ciertamente se ha puesto bajo una nueva luz. Probablemente sea mejor no pensar demasiado en ello."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7338
translate Spanish ch3m_06_f83b44ea:

    # "Instead, I come up behind her and tug her ears. She jumps up, and nearly topples over her bucket of milk."
    "En lugar de eso, me acerco por detrás y le doy un tirón de orejas. Se levanta de un salto y casi se cae encima de su cubo de leche."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7339
translate Spanish ch3m_06_521bb2a9:

    # m "Malcolm! You silly old goat!"
    m "Malcolm! Vieja cabra tonta!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7346
translate Spanish ch3m_06_7c3a1706:

    # "I gather her up in my arms, and plant a huge kiss on her lips."
    "La recojo en mis brazos y le planto un beso enorme en los labios."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7354
translate Spanish ch3m_06_6f6545f1:

    # c "Hey! Who are you calling old? I'm almost two whole years younger than you!"
    c "Eh! A quién llamas viejo? Soy casi dos años más joven que tú!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7356
translate Spanish ch3m_06_b3c40e28:

    # m "Oh, don't I know! You don't have to remind me. You're also not a goat... as far as I'm aware."
    m "Oh, no lo sé! No hace falta que me lo recuerdes. Tampoco eres una cabra... que yo sepa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7363
translate Spanish ch3m_06_d6a98914:

    # "She reaches behind me and yanks at my drawers."
    "Me mete la mano por detrás y me tira de los calzoncillos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7364
translate Spanish ch3m_06_5d9183af:

    # c "Oh, ho, ho! Mind your manners, Miss MacLeod! No tail yet. But you could always check for one later."
    c "Oh, ho, ho! ¡Cuida tus modales, Srta. MacLeod! No hay cola todavía. Pero siempre puedes buscar una después."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7366
translate Spanish ch3m_06_5a9a8540:

    # m "Malcolm! Get to work. I barely got any sleep last night. If you help me finish up early, maybe I can actually get to bed before midnight today."
    m "Malcolm! A trabajar. Apenas pude dormir anoche. Si me ayudas a terminar temprano, tal vez hoy pueda irme a la cama antes de medianoche."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7380
translate Spanish ch3m_06_dba7787a:

    # "As usual, I grab a stool and help her milk the cows. Fiona is still not a big fan of mine, despite my efforts to be gentle."
    "Como de costumbre, cojo un taburete y la ayudo a ordeñar las vacas. Fiona sigue sin ser una gran fan mía, a pesar de mis esfuerzos por ser amable."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7388
translate Spanish ch3m_06_cowclick_571cd872:

    # "I make a conscientious effort to calm the cow, petting her to sooth her delicate sensibilities."
    "Hago un esfuerzo consciente por calmar a la vaca, acariciándola para aliviar su delicada sensibilidad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7390
translate Spanish ch3m_06_cowclick_9f1f960f:

    # c "There, there, lass."
    c "Ahí, ahí, chica."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7392
translate Spanish ch3m_06_cowclick_65a5dca5:

    # m "It looks like you've got yourself a friend now, Malcolm."
    m "Parece que ahora tienes una amiga, Malcolm."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7394
translate Spanish ch3m_06_cowclick_339428a1:

    # m "All right, Malcolm, quit fooling around and get milkin'!"
    m "Muy bien, Malcolm, déjate de tonterías y ponte a ordeñar!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7396
translate Spanish ch3m_06_cowclick_4596e449:

    # m "Malcolm... are you all right?"
    m "Malcolm... estás bien?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7398
translate Spanish ch3m_06_cowclick_59ec8820:

    # m "Malcolm? I'm worried you're developing a cow obsession!"
    m "Malcolm? Me preocupa que estés desarrollando una obsesión por las vacas!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7418
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_74b1942d:

    # "She tosses a hoof my way, and I duck like I've been trained."
    "Me lanza una pezuña y me agacho como si me hubieran entrenado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7428
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_9f69647d:

    # m "Fiona just prefers the tender touch of a woman."
    m "Fiona simplemente prefiere el tierno toque de una mujer."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7429
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_1861804d:

    # c "Don't we all."
    c "No todos lo hacemos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7433
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_3638eece:

    # "I realize I've become completely engrossed in my efforts, and pull myself back to the task at hand."
    "Me doy cuenta de que estoy completamente absorto en mis esfuerzos y vuelvo a centrarme en la tarea que tengo entre manos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7438
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_c556604d:

    # m "I think she's taken a liking to you."
    m "Creo que le has caído bien."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7439
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_3efa06ea:

    # c "Aye, it's progress."
    c "Sí, es un progreso."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7441
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_b90d1c9d:

    # m "You certainly have a way with the ladies."
    m "Ciertamente tienes un don con las damas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7471
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_f02fe0b5:

    # "We haul the milk into the barn where Marion has constructed her own cheese-making station. A few chickens cluck by underfoot while we set up."
    "Llevamos la leche al granero, donde Marion ha construido su propia quesería. Unas cuantas gallinas cacarean bajo nuestros pies mientras nos preparamos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7484
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_694d9a58:

    # "After we skim the cream, we pour the milk into a large wooden vat. It's already nearly full to the top."
    "Después de desnatar la nata, vertemos la leche en una gran cuba de madera. Ya está casi llena hasta arriba."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7485
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_0fd0526b:

    # c "Goodness... Marion, did you get another few head of cattle?"
    c "Dios mío... Marion, conseguiste otras cabezas de ganado?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7487
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_c08f7e02:

    # m "No, this is all from the same ol' gals! They've been much more productive lately. Happier, too!"
    m "No, todo esto es de las mismas chicas de siempre! Han estado mucho más productivas últimamente. Y más felices."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7488
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_a695bdbf:

    # "They must be. I've never seen so much milk from just a few cows. The other dairy farmers in the valley would be jealous."
    "Deben de estarlo. Nunca había visto tanta leche de tan pocas vacas. Los otros granjeros del valle estarían celosos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7489
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_762f83ba:

    # c "Well, I'll be. You must have a magic touch."
    c "Bueno, lo seré. Debes tener un toque mágico."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7501
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_3c312e2c:

    # "Marion blushes as she dumps in a heap of salt and a sprinkle of rennet. We submerge some boiling water into the concoction, then step away to wait for the curds to form."
    "Marion se sonroja mientras echa un montón de sal y una pizca de cuajo. Sumergimos un poco de agua hirviendo en la mezcla y nos alejamos para esperar a que se forme la cuajada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7503
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_94eb885f:

    # m "Malcolm, do you have any interest in being completely irresponsible this morning?"
    m "Malcolm, tienes algún interés en ser completamente irresponsable esta mañana?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7504
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_a52b30ce:

    # c "Miss Marion, please do tell what that might entail, because I believe I could be convinced."
    c "Señorita Marion, por favor, dígame qué podría implicar, porque creo que podría convencerme."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7506
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_6b01b6a9:

    # m "Hmmm... how about I leave all the linens unwashed, the dishes unscrubbed, and the bed unmade?"
    m "Hmmm... qué tal si dejo toda la ropa de cama sin lavar, los platos sin fregar y la cama sin hacer?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7507
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_f5d0c5c2:

    # c "Well... the towels and plates will just get dirty again, and the bedsheets... they're likely to get rumpled tonight."
    c "Bueno... las toallas y los platos se volverán a ensuciar, y las sábanas... es probable que se arruguen esta noche."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7509
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_07ce4c3b:

    # m "Just so! In that case, the morning is ours to do as we please! Once the cheddaring's done, would you like to take a walk... somewhere quiet, somewhere private?"
    m "Eso es! En ese caso, la mañana es nuestra para hacer lo que queramos! Una vez que el queso cheddar este hecho, ¿te gustaría dar un paseo ... en algún lugar tranquilo, en algún lugar privado?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7510
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_57654c5c:

    # c "I will follow you blindly, my dear."
    c "Te seguiré ciegamente, querida."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7555
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_e0aef3f2:

    # "While we stroll the acres of grassy land, Hazel follows along for a few yards, nudging Marion, giving her very intense inhales."
    "Mientras paseamos por las hectáreas de hierba, Hazel nos sigue durante unos metros, dándole codazos a Marion e intensas inhalaciones."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7557
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_cf8f8e5d:

    # m "I think she's picking up a... {i}distinct{/i} odor, Malcolm."
    m "Creo que está percibiendo un... olor {i}distinto{/i}, Malcolm."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7558
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_3698c795:

    # c "That of lily powder and sweet cream, no doubt."
    c "La del polvo de lirio y la crema dulce, sin duda."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7560
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_cd31d684:

    # m "Oh, stop!"
    m "Oh, para!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7571
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_a3f40067:

    # "We head into a currant thicket, and Hazel tags along. I pluck a handful of berries, turning to offer them to Marion..."
    "Nos adentramos en un matorral de grosellas y Hazel nos acompaña. Arranco un puñado de bayas y me giro para ofrecérselas a Marion..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7580
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_3df758af:

    # "...But see she has already found her own patch."
    "...pero ya ha encontrado su propio trozo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7595
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_6da64c5d:

    # "We make our way to the loch's edge and sit on a rocky mount overlooking the water. The breeze is strong, and Marion's hair becomes a wave of auburn silk."
    "Nos dirigimos a la orilla del lago y nos sentamos en un monte rocoso con vistas al agua. La brisa es fuerte y el pelo de Marion se convierte en una ola de seda castaña."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7598
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_02078071:

    # "The loch surface is as whipped up as a rough sea. As turbulent as my own life had been, just months ago."
    "La superficie del lago está tan agitada como un mar embravecido. Tan turbulenta como lo había sido mi propia vida, hacía sólo unos meses."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7604
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_585ac465:

    # "I lean into the downy nook of her neck, and the sound of the winds and waves are reduced to a soft whisper."
    "Me recuesto en el suave rincón de su cuello, y el sonido de los vientos y las olas se reduce a un suave susurro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7611
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_44f16218:

    # "My eyes get watery, and it's not due to the wind."
    "Me lloran los ojos, y no es por el viento."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7612
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_8de762d9:

    # "My world was hell. Chaos. Destruction."
    "Mi mundo era un infierno. Caos. Destrucción."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7613
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_552394cf:

    # "Now, here beside Marion, it's hope-filled. More joyous than ever before."
    "Ahora, aquí al lado de Marion, está lleno de esperanza. Más alegre que nunca."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7616
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_3d6f98ab:

    # "I turn to Marion and, without speaking, give her a huge kiss. She collapses into me, and we stay connected, safe from the swirling elements around us."
    "Me vuelvo hacia Marion y, sin hablar, le doy un beso enorme. Ella se derrumba sobre mí y permanecemos conectados, a salvo de los elementos que se arremolinan a nuestro alrededor."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7620
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_7196c4d0:

    # "Our embrace fades back into stillness. A powerful tranquility has overtaken me."
    "Nuestro abrazo se desvanece en la quietud. Una poderosa tranquilidad se ha apoderado de mí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7621
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_b700fa47:

    # c "Marion, thank you for giving me my life back. I owe you {i}so{/i} much."
    c "Marion, gracias por devolverme la vida. Te debo {i}tanto{/i}."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7623
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_92dd1baf:

    # c "I love you. More than you could ever..."
    c "Te quiero. Más de lo que podrías..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7624
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_c30bbd55:

    # "A pain rises to my chest, one I cannot fight off. Tears fall."
    "Un dolor me sube al pecho, uno contra el que no puedo luchar. Caen lágrimas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7625
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_7a7017a8:

    # m "Malcolm! I—"
    m "¡Malcolm! yo-"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7626
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_c7b782e9:

    # "She sees my wet cheeks, and holds me even tighter."
    "Ve mis mejillas húmedas y me abraza aún más fuerte."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7628
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_b88a5137:

    # m "Thank you for loving me."
    m "Gracias por amarme."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7630
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_123845ad:

    # "The emotion passes nearly as fast as it hit, and I appreciate that it's opened me up... made me vulnerable, if only for her."
    "La emoción pasa casi tan rápido como golpea, y agradezco que me haya abierto... me haya hecho vulnerable, aunque sólo sea por ella."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7631
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_9d915390:

    # "Like our protected perch above the stirring waters below..."
    "Como nuestra percha protegida sobre las agitadas aguas de abajo..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7633
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_0d726e60:

    # "...Marion is my rock."
    "...Marion es mi piedra."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7647
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_bd39a151:

    # "I would have spent an eternity with Marion by the loch, if I could. Our time in that little corner of heaven is cut short, though."
    "Habría pasado una eternidad con Marion junto al lago, si hubiera podido. Sin embargo, nuestro tiempo en ese pequeño rincón del cielo se acorta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7648
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_0bf84373:

    # "There's the garden to tend. Eggs to collect. Cheese to strain. We both know we can't put off our daily responsibilities indefinitely."
    "Hay que cuidar el jardín. Huevos que recoger. Queso que colar. Ambos sabemos que no podemos aplazar indefinidamente nuestras responsabilidades diarias."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7650
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_e8b1b883:

    # "But... perhaps they can wait a moment more."
    "Pero... quizás puedan esperar un momento más."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7666
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_696c53e6:

    # "We spike our tea and pull our chairs close together to chat. Marion's as lighthearted as I remember from her tipsy outing at the pub."
    "Tomamos el té y nos sentamos a charlar. Marion está tan alegre como la recordaba de su borrachera en la taberna."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7668
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_fd993899:

    # m "...And Grace came home so blootered last night, it's a small wonder she didn't fall off ol' Eachann coming home!"
    m "...Y Grace llegó a casa tan florecida anoche, ¡que es un pequeño milagro que no se cayera del viejo Eachann volviendo a casa!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7669
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_b028af75:

    # c "Aye, well, {i}Grace{/i} is a small wonder."
    c "Sí, bueno, {i}Grace{/i} es una pequeña maravilla."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7671
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_b7989654:

    # m "That she is, that rascal!"
    m "Eso es, esa granuja!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7673
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_05e71813:

    # "Much to our surprise, Grace now spends evenings at the Stag & Nanny doing odd jobs behind the scenes—mostly on nights when the crowds are low."
    "Para nuestra sorpresa, ahora Grace pasa las tardes en el Stag & Nanny haciendo trabajillos entre bastidores, sobre todo las noches de menor afluencia."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7674
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_cf2ca84f:

    # "The coin is good... and apparently so are the benefits."
    "La moneda es buena... y aparentemente también lo son los beneficios."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7675
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_6f018c36:

    # "It's Balgair's way of helping the family financially since Jessie's departure. But why a loner like Grace accepted the job beats me."
    "Es la forma que tiene Balgair de ayudar económicamente a la familia desde la marcha de Jessie. Pero no entiendo por qué una solitaria como Grace aceptó el trabajo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7676
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_16b8bde1:

    # "Perhaps the Whist Club—with its generous helpings of Gemma Tyte's homemade rum-infused cordial—has given Grace a taste for working at such an establishment."
    "Tal vez el Whist Club con sus generosas raciones de cordial casero con infusión de ron de Gemma Tyte le haya dado a Grace el gusto de trabajar en un establecimiento así."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7679
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_47b5321c:

    # "Marion's voice drops to a whisper, even though we have the whole house to ourselves."
    "La voz de Marion se reduce a un susurro, a pesar de que tenemos toda la casa para nosotros."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7681
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_f6756c5c:

    # m "Grace got into a very bad crowd, you see. Involving her, Felix, Margaret, and a whole bottle of whisky."
    m "Grace se metió en un lío. Involucrándola a ella, Felix, Margaret, y una botella entera de whisky."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7682
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_c035df33:

    # c "Felix and Margaret? But... aren't they the only two in town who {i}don't{/i} drink?"
    c "¿Félix y Margaret? Pero... ¿no son los únicos en la ciudad {i}que no{/i} beben?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7684
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_7cf061d4:

    # m "Exactly so!"
    m "¡Exacto!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7685
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_ab6e4e4d:

    # "We both laugh. How Grace managed to down an entire bottle of whisky without passing out is beyond me. Sometimes I wonder if inside that small frame she's actually quite the heavyweight."
    "Ambos nos reímos. No entiendo cómo Grace ha podido beberse una botella entera de whisky sin desmayarse. A veces me pregunto si dentro de esa pequeña contextura es en realidad todo un peso pesado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7688
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_55c77f49:

    # "Our laughter turns into a sigh, and we sit and smile and sip our brew. All our troubles seem to melt away when we are together."
    "Nuestra risa se convierte en un suspiro, nos sentamos, sonreímos y bebemos a sorbos. Todos nuestros problemas parecen desvanecerse cuando estamos juntos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7693
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_eb00f1d8:

    # "At least, most of the time. All of a sudden, Marion's smile falters."
    "Al menos, la mayor parte del tiempo. De repente, la sonrisa de Marion titubea."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7695
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_ebc3943a:

    # m "Malcolm... do you think I've become a recluse? Like Grace was, before she took this job?"
    m "Malcolm... ¿crees que me he vuelto una ermitaña? ¿Como lo era Grace antes de tomar este trabajo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7698
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_edecaf47:

    # "It's a subject we've been avoiding mostly, but one present on both our minds."
    "Es un tema que hemos estado evitando mayormente, pero que está presente en la mente de ambos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7699
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_e8cd523b:

    # "When Marion and I are together, alone, we're a team without rival. The world we've built in private is a safe one; one where our troubles are discussed and handled with friendship and support."
    "Cuando Marion y yo estamos juntos, solos, somos un equipo sin rival. El mundo que hemos construido en privado es seguro; un mundo en el que nuestros problemas se discuten y se tratan con amistad y apoyo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7700
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_50ca8401:

    # "The world beyond the boundaries of our homesteads, though... that's a world of which we do not speak."
    "El mundo más allá de los límites de nuestros hogares, sin embargo... ese es un mundo del que no hablamos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7701
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_6b92c758:

    # "I know we're sheltered here, especially Marion. But should that imaginary wall ever be breached?"
    "Sé que estamos protegidos aquí, especialmente Marion. Pero si ese muro imaginario se rompiera alguna vez?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7702
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_3314675d:

    # "What if she went into town, or a stranger showed up on her doorstep? Would all that safety go away?"
    "¿Qué pasaría si ella fuera al pueblo o si un extraño apareciera en su puerta? ¿Se desvanecería toda esa seguridad?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7706
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_6a946d91:

    # c "No... I don't think you're a recluse. By fate and necessity, you've just found yourself a new pasture, is all."
    c "No... no creo que seas una ermitaña. Por destino y necesidad, solo has encontrado un nuevo pasto, eso es todo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7708
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_25c609ab:

    # m "A pasture? More like a paddock."
    m "¿Un pasto? Más bien un corral."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7709
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_2ae8fa51:

    # "I nod glumly. It's possibly been the hardest part of her transition, not being able to venture back out into the world for fear of her secret being discovered."
    "Asiento con desánimo. Posiblemente ha sido la parte más difícil de su transición: no poder aventurarse de nuevo al mundo por miedo a que se descubra su secreto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7710
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_e6cd5c41:

    # "She's made it clear that she misses the adventure of marketing, and the warmth of the church congregation. However, she can't exactly don a skirt and shawl like before and expect not to be noticed."
    "Ella ha dejado claro que extraña la aventura de ir al mercado y el calor de la congregación en la iglesia. Sin embargo, no puede exactamente ponerse una falda y un chal como antes y esperar pasar desapercibida."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7711
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_a25fafb0:

    # "There were already some close calls when she last went into town months ago, and that was {i}before{/i} she had a muzzle. I don't think even keen-eyed Balgair would mistake Marion's features as a costume anymore."
    "Ya hubo algunos sustos cuando fue al pueblo por última vez hace meses, y eso fue {i}antes{/i} de que tuviera un hocico. No creo que ni siquiera el perspicaz Balgair confundiera ahora sus rasgos con un disfraz."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7712
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_6bc544d1:

    # "It's difficult to say as much, though. It carries a disquieting... finality to it."
    "Aunque es difícil decirlo. Tiene una inquietante... finalidad."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7715
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_5d58d831:

    # "The uncomfortable silence stretches out. It breaks my heart to see Marion depressed, all cooped up like this."
    "El incómodo silencio se prolonga. Me parte el corazón ver a Marion deprimida, encerrada así."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7716
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_d286eba3:

    # "Maybe... there could be a way to make a short sojourn into town. After all, on a windy day like today, wearing a nice, big scarf wouldn't be out of the question."
    "Tal vez... podría haber una manera de hacer una breve excursión al pueblo. Después de todo, en un día ventoso como hoy, usar una bufanda grande no sería extraño."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7718
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_e6d40296:

    # "Yes, it could be dangerous. Perhaps even a little exciting. It would definitely be the compassionate thing to do—but is it the {i}responsible{/i} thing to do?"
    "Sí, podría ser peligroso. Tal vez incluso un poco emocionante. Definitivamente sería lo más compasivo, pero ¿es lo {i}responsable{/i}?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7723
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_09dd63cc:

    # butterfly_effect "{image=butterflysprite}" nointeract
    butterfly_effect "{image=butterflysprite}" nointeract

# game/script_marion.rpy:7731
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_a42babc6:

    # c "No... I don't think you're a recluse. I just... well, I do worry that you're missing out on a world outside these highlands. I know others miss you, same as before."
    c "No... no creo que seas una ermitaña. Solo... bueno, me preocupa que te estés perdiendo el mundo más allá de estas tierras altas. Sé que otros te extrañan, igual que antes."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7733
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_8a7cbcdc:

    # m "I know."
    m "Lo sé."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7734
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_a79d6ded:

    # "It goes unsaid, we also both know that a skirt and shawl disguise won't exactly pass muster anymore. I'm not sure even \"Lady Esther's All-Purpose, Long-Lasting Face Powder.\" is up to the task."
    "Queda implícito que ambos sabemos que un disfraz de falda y chal ya no pasaría desapercibido. Ni siquiera el \"Polvo facial multipropósito y de larga duración de Lady Esther.\" es suficiente para la tarea."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7735
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_48b6105d:

    # "Still, it had been several months since her last trip into town, and even longer since the incident at the picnic with Florrie."
    "Aun así, han pasado varios meses desde su último viaje al pueblo, y aún más desde el incidente en el picnic con Florrie."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7736
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_225f779f:

    # "I want that embarrassment to be water under the bridge. The longer Marion stays cooped up at home, I worry that she'll be less and less likely to venture back out into the world."
    "Quiero que esa vergüenza quede en el pasado. Cuanto más tiempo Marion permanezca encerrada en casa, más me preocupa que sea cada vez menos probable que se atreva a volver al mundo exterior."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7737
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_be9344cc:

    # "I know it gnaws at her, as well. She's made it clear that she misses the adventure of marketing, and the warmth of the church congregation."
    "Sé que también la inquieta. Ha dejado claro que extraña la aventura del mercado y el calor de la congregación en la iglesia."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7740
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_bb1cb048:

    # "Warmth... come to think of it, as windy as it's been today, wearing a nice, big scarf wouldn't be out of the question. If I stay by her side, like before, perhaps she'd be willing to go into town."
    "Calor... ahora que lo pienso, con lo ventoso que ha estado hoy, usar una bufanda grande no sería extraño. Si me quedo a su lado, como antes, tal vez esté dispuesta a ir al pueblo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7741
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_788dd3c8:

    # "But is it worth the risk of disrupting the safety she's built here? Is that something {i}she{/i} wants?"
    "Pero, ¿vale la pena arriesgar la seguridad que ha construido aquí? ¿Es eso algo que {i}ella{/i} quiere?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7746
translate Spanish ch3m_06_continue_09dd63cc_1:

    # butterfly_effect "{image=butterflysprite}" nointeract
    butterfly_effect "{image=butterflysprite}" nointeract

# game/script_marion.rpy:7757
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_23e0c40b:

    # c "Marion..."
    c "Marion..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7759
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_7bbb2c27:

    # "She's lost in thought. I tap her shoulder to have her turn to me."
    "Ella está perdida en sus pensamientos. Le doy un toque en el hombro para que se gire hacia mí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7760
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_1005ee26:

    # c "The bond... the one that has formed between us? It's unbreakable."
    c "El vínculo... el que se ha formado entre nosotros. Es irrompible."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7762
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_f8926538:

    # "I make sure she understands that I am being sincere."
    "Me aseguro de que entienda que estoy siendo sincero."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7763
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_da27afde:

    # c "You know, the marketplace is still up and running. It should be winding down, too; it won't be too busy."
    c "Sabes, el mercado todavía está abierto. Ya debería estar terminando, no habrá demasiada gente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7765
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_4a4b35d8:

    # m "You mean...?"
    m "¿Quieres decir...?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7766
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_a3d84d49:

    # c "Aye. Care to go for a ride into town today? I'll be right by your side. You can even pick out any hat you like for me!"
    c "Sí. ¿Te gustaría dar un paseo al pueblo hoy? Estaré a tu lado todo el tiempo. ¡Incluso puedes escoger el sombrero que quieras para mí!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7769
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_95b2b8dc:

    # "I can tell she is mulling it over, even as she shakes her head."
    "Veo que lo está considerando, incluso mientras niega con la cabeza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7771
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_458247a9:

    # m "I—I can't. Like this? No... I shouldn't."
    m "Y-Yo no puedo. ¿Así? No... no debería."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7772
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_bc5af513:

    # c "If you don't want to go, that's your decision. But despite anything that may... or may not happen in town... Marion, my opinion of you will never change. Neither will Gran's... nor Grace's, nor Alana's."
    c "Si no quieres ir, es tu decisión. Pero sin importar lo que pueda... o no pueda pasar en el pueblo, Marion, mi opinión sobre ti nunca cambiará. Tampoco la de Abue... ni la de Grace, ni la de Alana."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7773
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_437d2bc4:

    # "I wink."
    "Le guiño."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7774
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_05ce9d29:

    # c "And I would bet money that Balgair will always have your back, too."
    c "Y apostaría dinero a que Balgair siempre estará de tu lado también."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7776
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_fa1093a0:

    # "Marion cracks a smile."
    "Marion esboza una sonrisa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7777
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_4a78a39a:

    # m "That's quite a team on my side."
    m "Eso es todo un equipo de mi lado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7778
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_29897bbd:

    # c "What more could you need?"
    c "¿Qué más podrías necesitar?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7780
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_8e6b0ccd:

    # "She grins even wider."
    "Su sonrisa se ensancha aún más."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7781
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_e9341e80:

    # m "Well... I {i}could{/i} do with some more equipment and a bigger vat for cheese-making..."
    m "Bueno... {i}podría{/i} necesitar algo más de equipo y una tina más grande para hacer queso..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7784
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_77066808:

    # m "A'right! I'll do it."
    m "¡Está bien! Lo haré."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7794
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_f9ff6ccf:

    # "We ride atop Hazel's cart into town, continuing our day of irresponsibility... but not before washing the dishes, and baking some honey wheat loaves for Balgair."
    "Nos subimos a la carreta de Hazel camino al pueblo, continuando nuestro día de irresponsabilidad... pero no antes de lavar los platos y hornear unos panes de trigo y miel para Balgair."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7795
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_77d1de50:

    # "Marion's definition of \"irresponsibility\" isn't quite as carefree as my own."
    "La definición de \"irresponsabilidad\" de Marion no es tan despreocupada como la mía."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7796
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_e7099146:

    # "She wears her traditional disguise, this time including face powder, mittens and a scarf for good measure. It's an odd ensemble for summer, but not out of the question, given the wind."
    "Viste su disfraz tradicional, esta vez incluyendo polvo facial, guantes y una bufanda por precaución. Es un conjunto extraño para el verano, pero no fuera de lugar, dado el viento."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7797
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_50164eb7:

    # "It's not like our last clandestine trip to town, though. While she may be afraid of being found out, she's no longer afraid of who she {i}is{/i}."
    "No es como nuestro último viaje clandestino al pueblo. Aunque todavía tenga miedo de ser descubierta, ya no tiene miedo de quién {i}es{/i}."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7798
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_97bee750:

    # "There's an air of sober confidence about Marion, which buoys my own."
    "Hay un aire de confianza sobria en Marion, que eleva mi propio ánimo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7810
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_590c806f:

    # "Between the layers of her disguise, I can see the twinkle in her eye as we pass by familiar faces and old haunts. At the church, a few parishioners are gathered by the entrance."
    "Entre las capas de su disfraz, puedo ver el brillo en sus ojos cuando pasamos por caras familiares y viejos lugares. En la iglesia, algunos feligreses están reunidos en la entrada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7811
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_93314dab:

    # m "Oh! It must be the Women's Guild! I can see Gemma."
    m "¡Oh! Debe ser el Gremio de Mujeres. Puedo ver a Gemma."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7812
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_786bbec0:

    # c "Would you like to stop and say hello?"
    c "¿Te gustaría detenerte a saludar?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7814
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_41a60810:

    # m "No... no, let's keep going."
    m "No... no, sigamos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7815
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_854ec8ed:

    # "We move on, but my eyes linger. Seeing the group in front of the church..."
    "Seguimos adelante, pero mis ojos se quedan en el grupo frente a la iglesia..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7826
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_a2c094b0:

    # "An image of our nuptials pass through my mind. Marion holding a bouquet, me in my nicest suit, and Gran sniffling into her tissue."
    "Una imagen de nuestras nupcias pasa por mi mente. Marion sosteniendo un ramo, yo con mi mejor traje, y Abue llorando en su pañuelo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7832
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_00c9a369:

    # "Perhaps Marion nibbling on the bouquet—just a little."
    "Quizás Marion mordisqueando el ramo, solo un poco."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7837
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_9c54e2e6:

    # "I laugh. Oh, how I hope that image becomes a reality. If not soon... someday."
    "Me río. Oh, cómo espero que esa imagen se convierta en realidad. Si no pronto... algún día."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7838
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_dd8c33b0:

    # m "What's so funny?"
    m "¿De qué te ríes?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7839
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_3b0270d6:

    # c "Just picturing the looks on the parishioners' faces if they knew our little secret."
    c "Solo imaginando las caras de los feligreses si supieran nuestro pequeño secreto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7840
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_e83964b5:

    # m "'Twould be the biggest scandal in town. At least, until Balgair gets that neon sign he's been dreaming of."
    m "Sería el mayor escándalo del pueblo. Al menos, hasta que Balgair consiga el letrero de neón con el que ha soñado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7850
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_0ed175f0:

    # "I turn my head and give Marion a smile. She leans into my shoulder, and I flip the reins to get Hazel moving."
    "Giro la cabeza y sonrío a Marion. Ella se apoya en mi hombro y yo muevo las riendas para que Hazel se ponga en marcha."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7851
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_005551db:

    # "Our first stop is the Stag & Nanny, to drop off the warm bread."
    "Nuestra primera parada es el Stag & Nanny, para dejar el pan recién horneado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7865
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_e9c8d1ae:

    # c "Are you ready?"
    c "¿Estás lista?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7867
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_8f6314da:

    # m "Ready!"
    m "¡Lista!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7893
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_a27dd803:

    # "The place is, thankfully, nearly empty. With noon fast approaching, most of the marketgoers must already be on their way home."
    "El lugar está, afortunadamente, casi vacío. Con el mediodía acercándose, la mayoría de los clientes del mercado ya deben estar de camino a casa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7900
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_56bd5527:

    # b "Do m'eyes deceive me? Is that the lovely Miss Marion MacLeod?"
    b "¿Me engañan los ojos? ¿Es esa la encantadora señorita Marion MacLeod?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7914
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_89c54cea:

    # "Marion blushes, but accepts his embrace. I notice a bit of her powder left behind on his shoulder."
    "Marion se sonroja, pero acepta su abrazo. Noto un poco de su polvo facial quedado en su hombro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7916
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_60ebe9e8:

    # b "Welcome, lass! Take off those warm woolens and make yourself comfortable!"
    b "¡Bienvenida, muchacha! ¡Quítate esas lanas cálidas y ponte cómoda!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7919
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_dec9334b:

    # m "Ah, well, it's a bit blustery out, and..."
    m "Ah, bueno, está un poco ventoso afuera, y..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7930
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_8dd57892:

    # "Out of nowhere, a broom wallops the old man on the head."
    "De repente, una escoba golpea al anciano en la cabeza."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7935
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_4a8ac1c2:

    # g "Balgair! You never comment on a lady's fashion choices!"
    g "¡Balgair! ¡Nunca comentes sobre las elecciones de moda de una dama!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7958
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_5edc9a44:

    # "Grace appears, holding a broom and dustpan. She sets them aside and, to my surprise, comes over to hug her sister, as well. I hear her whisper."
    "Grace aparece, sosteniendo una escoba y un recogedor. Los deja a un lado y, para mi sorpresa, también abraza a su hermana. La escucho susurrar."

# game/script_marion.rpy:7959
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_ce7353b1:

    # g "{size=24}I'm so happy you came to visit.{/size}"
    g "{size=24}Estoy tan feliz de que hayas venido a visitarnos.{/size}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7964
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_158c0c1f:

    # b "So! What'll it be, Marion? A pint... or two?"
    b "¡Entonces! ¿qué será, Marion? ¿Una pinta... o dos?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7966
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_cc62c324:

    # m "Oh, no! I just came to deliver these loaves—"
    m "¡Oh, no! Solo vine a entregar estos panes—"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7968
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_05608b75:

    # b "You're gonna visit Balgair, and not share in a pint? Grace said you'd been under the weather, but heavens, Marion... have ye lost yer head?"
    b "¿Vas a visitar a Balgair y no compartir una pinta? Grace dijo que habías estado indispuesta, pero cielos, Marion... ¿has perdido la cabeza?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:7970
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_b8826e5f:

    # m "Well... maybe I can. Just one."
    m "Bueno... tal vez pueda. Solo una."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8000
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_510d8fe1:

    # "The four of us gather around a table and indulge in a round of fresh bread and dark ale. Marion's attempts to nibble and sip from under her shawl are... less than discreet."
    "Los cuatro nos reunimos alrededor de una mesa y disfrutamos de una ronda de pan fresco y cerveza oscura. Los intentos de Marion de mordisquear y beber desde debajo de su chal son... menos que discretos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8002
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_62e3907c:

    # b "Is everything all right, lass?"
    b "¿Está todo bien, muchacha?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8003
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_269fa051:

    # "She's turned herself away just enough to hide her munching muzzle, but I worry Balgair thinks she's giving him the cold shoulder."
    "Se ha girado lo suficiente como para ocultar su hocico mientras come, pero me preocupa que Balgair piense que lo está ignorando."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8005
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_e41906ae:

    # g "I'm sure she just doesn't want us to catch her... whatever-she-has. Isn't that right, sis'?"
    g "Estoy segura de que solo no quiere contagiarnos... lo que sea que tenga. ¿No es así, hermanita?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8011
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_a4d8a93b:

    # "A garbled \"mmhmm\" tumbles out from behind Marion's scarf, along with a few breadcrumbs. To change the subject, I ask Grace how she likes her new job."
    "Un confuso \"mmhmm\" sale de detrás de la bufanda de Marion, junto con unas migas de pan. Para cambiar de tema, le pregunto a Grace qué le parece su nuevo trabajo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8015
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_365eab95:

    # g "I can't say it's a dream... but Balgair lets me keep all the things I find on the ground. Last week I found one shilling sixpence, a brass ring, and a wooden eye!"
    g "No puedo decir que sea un sueño... pero Balgair me deja quedarme con todo lo que encuentro en el suelo. ¡La semana pasada encontré un chelín y seis peniques, un anillo de latón y un ojo de madera!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8018
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_45305052:

    # b "Aye! I couldn't keep the place tidy without you. Who would polish off the unfinished drinks?"
    b "¡Sí! No podría mantener el lugar limpio sin ti. ¿Quién terminaría las bebidas que dejan a medias?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8020
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_1802b570:

    # "We stay and chat until Balgair spots a new pair of willing listeners, then say our goodbyes."
    "Nos quedamos charlando hasta que Balgair encuentra un nuevo par de oyentes dispuestos, y luego nos despedimos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8022
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_b6e69c71:

    # b "I'll see you soon, Marion? You know the Heifer Parade is coming up fast! That costume of yours is a shoe-in."
    b "¿Te veré pronto, Marion? Sabes que el Desfile de las Vacas se acerca rápido. Ese disfraz tuyo es un éxito seguro."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8025
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_e3ab6911:

    # "He winks conspiratorially."
    "Guiña un ojo de manera cómplice."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8026
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_8630f286:

    # m "Soon, Balgair... I promise."
    m "Pronto, Balgair... te lo prometo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8042
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_db9f6601:

    # "The rest of our excursion reminds me of my first day back in town, though, my, how life has changed!"
    "El resto de nuestra excursión me recuerda mi primer día de regreso al pueblo, aunque, cielos, ¡cómo ha cambiado la vida!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8043
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_07f8e9c0:

    # "We stock up on cheesecloth and rind wax, while enjoying samples of gooseberry jam and smoked Dunlop."
    "Nos abastecemos de la tela para queso y cera para cortezas, mientras disfrutamos muestras de mermelada de grosella y queso Dunlop ahumado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8053
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_79ee2730:

    # m "Hmph. My Dunlop is much better."
    m "Hmph. Mi Dunlop es mucho mejor."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8054
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_d8e48da5:

    # c "You know, you could start your own business... build some healthy competition!"
    c "Sabes, podrías iniciar tu propio negocio... ¡crear algo de competencia saludable!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8056
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_44f23d1f:

    # "Marion laughs, but I sense her mind at work. We pick out a larger trough for skimming cream, and take it to the cart."
    "Marion ríe, pero siento que su mente está trabajando. Elegimos un abrevadero más grande para desnatado de crema y lo llevamos a la carreta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8072
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_62b924d6:

    # "Next we move on to the milliner, where I hold up my end of the bargain."
    "Luego vamos al sombrerero, donde cumplo con mi parte del trato."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8073
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_06be6497:

    # c "Your pick, Marion! What'll it be?"
    c "Tu elección, Marion. ¿Qué será?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8076
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_ae8162b4:

    # u "The lady's choice? If you're fixin' to find the best bonnet for your guidman, might I suggest the Balmoral?"
    u "¿La elección de la dama? Si busca el mejor sombrero para su buen hombre, ¿podría sugerir el Balmoral?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8078
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_f29706a4:

    # m "Oh... he's not my—"
    m "Oh... él no es mi—"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8079
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_3a8b980f:

    # c "Maybe we'll be back for a Balmoral another day, sir. For a more formal occasion."
    c "Tal vez volvamos por un Balmoral otro día, señor. Para una ocasión más formal."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8081
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_adf78614:

    # "Even under all her layers—{i}and{/i} her fur—I can tell Marion is blushing."
    "Incluso bajo todas sus capas—{i}y{/i} su piel—puedo notar que Marion está sonrojada."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8085
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_4f8de6a9:

    # m "Aha!"
    m "¡Ahá!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8086
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_05407045:

    # "She's selected a tweed touring cap for me. It's a jaunty hat, one I know I'll be happy to wear many a day. I hand Murdoch some coin, and doff my brand-new cap."
    "Ha elegido una gorra de tweed para mí. Es un sombrero alegre, que sé que me encantará llevar muchos días. Le doy a Murdoch unas monedas y me quito mi flamante gorra."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8099
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_bbad83e0:

    # m "Do you like it?"
    m "¿Te gusta?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8100
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_7359423c:

    # c "Of course. You have impeccable taste."
    c "Por supuesto. Tienes un gusto impecable."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8102
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_afd4ad04:

    # m "Excellent! Now, I don't suppose I get to pick out an accessory for you, too? Perhaps a matching cowbell charm?"
    m "¡Excelente! Supongo que también podré elegir un accesorio para ti. ¿Quizás un colgante a juego con el cencerro?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8103
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_5399e1af:

    # "My breath catches momentarily in my throat."
    "Se me corta momentáneamente la respiración."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8104
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_7d928659:

    # c "Oh, no. I think you wear it much better than I ever could."
    c "Oh, no. Creo que tú lo luces mucho mejor de lo que yo jamás podría."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8106
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_b56a1b6b:

    # "She chuckles at my joke, thankfully, while I keep an eye out for Effie, who is nowhere in sight. That girl is such an anomaly. Nothing predictable about her."
    "Ella se ríe de mi broma, afortunadamente, mientras busco a Effie con la mirada, quien no aparece por ningún lado. Esa chica es una anomalía. Nada predecible en ella."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8107
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_e14d3274:

    # "Alas... or perhaps it's for the best that we don't run into her at all. Ever. Marion seems relieved that no one else pays her much mind other than a genial greeting."
    "Ay... o tal vez es mejor que no nos la encontremos. Nunca. Marion parece aliviada de que nadie más le preste mucha atención, aparte de un saludo cordial."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8108
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_2371e80f:

    # "From the looks the stall owners give me, I get the sense they're concerned for Marion. Perhaps they think it wise not to inquire as to her rumored illness. I would agree."
    "Por las miradas que me dirigen los dueños de los puestos, tengo la sensación de que están preocupados por Marion. Tal vez piensen que es prudente no preguntar sobre su supuesta enfermedad. Estoy de acuerdo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8110
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_0d03f4a3:

    # m "One more stop, Malcolm. Then we should get going. I think Hazel's had her fill..."
    m "Una parada más, Malcolm. Luego deberíamos irnos. Creo que Hazel ya ha tenido suficiente..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8125
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_b2798bde:

    # "She points at my mare, who gnaws at her bit and lead by the hitching post."
    "Señala a mi yegua, que muerde el bocado y la correa junto al poste de amarre."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8126
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_bff0b717:

    # c "Let's grab the poor girl a treat."
    c "Vamos a conseguirle un premio a la pobre chica."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8127
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_0023f2eb:

    # "Marion selects three plump carrots, and fills a bag with anise candies for herself. We then make our way back to save Hazel."
    "Marion selecciona tres zanahorias gordas y llena una bolsa con caramelos de anís para ella misma. Luego nos dirigimos de regreso a salvar a Hazel."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8139
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_0f47ddb7:

    # m "Did you miss us?"
    m "¿Nos extrañaste?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8140
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_7d00b4bc:

    # c "As much as we've loaded up her cart? I doubt it."
    c "Con todo lo que hemos cargado en su carreta, lo dudo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8143
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_f795d74d:

    # m "Of course Hazel missed us! Just look at that sweet, bonny face!"
    m "¡Claro que Hazel nos extrañó! ¡Solo mira ese dulce y hermoso rostro!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8144
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_b531f697:

    # "That sweet, bonny face is drooling everywhere as she crushes the carrot between her jaws. I can hardly turn away from the spectacle; that is, until I hear a small voice behind us."
    "Ese dulce y hermoso rostro está babeando por todas partes mientras tritura la zanahoria entre sus mandíbulas. Apenas puedo apartar la vista del espectáculo; eso es, hasta que escucho una pequeña voz detrás de nosotros."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8151
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_830f3596:

    # f "Miss Marion! I haf a tail, jus' like you!"
    f "¡Señorita Marion! ¡Yo tengo una cola, igual que usted!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8158
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_aa8687b8:

    # "Marion gasps and stumbles into me."
    "Marion jadea y tropieza conmigo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8160
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_12ede062:

    # m "Florrie! Whatever do you mean?"
    m "¡Florrie! ¿Qué quieres decir?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8161
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_ab8c13d8:

    # f "Lookit me! I'm a lovely cow lady!"
    f "¡Míreme! ¡Soy una linda dama vaca!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8165
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_a3c0c101:

    # "The tiny girl flips a long twist of black liquorice behind her, giggles, then bites into her own candy tail."
    "La pequeña niña mueve un largo mechón de regaliz negro detrás de ella, se ríe y luego muerde su propia cola de caramelo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8166
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_040376c8:

    # f "Such a yummy tail!"
    f "¡Qué cola tan deliciosa!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8179
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_3a1fa0a1:

    # "She keeps laughing, and I am shocked at Marion's reaction. She bends down to pet young Florrie's head."
    "Sigue riendo, y estoy sorprendido por la reacción de Marion. Se inclina para acariciar la cabeza de la pequeña Florrie."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8180
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_0ed5eb2f:

    # m "You're the cutest cow in all the highlands, Florrie!"
    m "¡Eres la vaca más linda de todas las tierras altas, Florrie!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8184
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_2778e598:

    # f "No, Miss Marion. That's you!"
    f "No, señorita Marion. ¡Esa es usted!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8197
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_04102164:

    # "She hugs Marion, and takes off scurrying down the road, moo-ing."
    "Ella abraza a Marion y sale corriendo por el camino, mugiendo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8210
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_674d665a:

    # "I plant a kiss upon Marion's kerchief."
    "Planto un beso en el pañuelo de Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8211
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_4d5c4cc6:

    # c "For your bravery today... and every day!"
    c "¡Por tu valentía hoy... y todos los días!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8213
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_0e2166b8:

    # "She looks left and right, then in one swift movement..."
    "Ella mira a la izquierda y a la derecha, luego en un movimiento rápido..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8217
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_f8c64f5f:

    # "...quickly pulls down her scarf to give me a kiss in return."
    "...se baja la bufanda rápidamente para darme un beso en respuesta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8219
translate Spanish ch3m_06_a_a376271c:

    # m "For your kindness today... and every day!"
    m "¡Por tu amabilidad hoy... y todos los días!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8232
translate Spanish ch3m_06_b_9f00c49c:

    # "The question, the offer to ride to the market together, floats through my mind. I push it aside."
    "La pregunta, la oferta de ir juntos al mercado, flota en mi mente. La dejo de lado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8233
translate Spanish ch3m_06_b_a1c33377:

    # "If Marion wants to leave her own home and venture into town, she's more than capable of making that decision herself. The last thing she needs is additional meddling."
    "Si Marion quiere dejar su hogar y aventurarse en el pueblo, es más que capaz de tomar esa decisión por sí misma. Lo último que necesita es más interferencias."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8234
translate Spanish ch3m_06_b_550fd52d:

    # c "Come, now. That's a topic for another day. As much as a day off sounds enticing, there's much to be done."
    c "Vamos. Eso es tema para otro día. Por más tentador que suene un día libre, hay mucho por hacer."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8235
translate Spanish ch3m_06_b_eaf752cc:

    # "It may not be what either of us want to hear, but that doesn't make it any less true. Her resolve returns."
    "Puede que no sea lo que ninguno de los dos quiere oír, pero eso no lo hace menos cierto. Su determinación vuelve."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8237
translate Spanish ch3m_06_b_06be0528:

    # m "Is that so? I guess I'd better go feed the hens, then. You can start... hm..."
    m "¿Es así? Supongo que será mejor que vaya a alimentar a las gallinas, entonces. Tú puedes empezar... hmm..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8239
translate Spanish ch3m_06_b_15e63ed6:

    # m "How about, mucking the stalls?"
    m "¿Qué tal limpiar los establos?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8241
translate Spanish ch3m_06_b_13440844:

    # c "...I suppose I deserve that."
    c "...Supongo que me lo merezco."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8287
translate Spanish ch3m_07_584c3e02:

    # "My nose wrinkles at the scent as I plunge the pitchfork back into the straw bedding."
    "Mi nariz se arruga ante el olor mientras vuelvo a hundir la horca en la cama de paja."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8288
translate Spanish ch3m_07_f76dda84:

    # "The work isn't glamorous, but I don't feel bad about it. I {i}do{/i}, however, feel bad about the way I left the conversation with Marion. I wonder how she's taking it."
    "El trabajo no es glamoroso, pero no me siento mal por ello. {i}Aunque{/i}, me siento mal por la forma en que dejé la conversación con Marion. Me pregunto cómo lo estará tomando."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8291
translate Spanish ch3m_07_03bac036:

    # "It wasn't long ago I felt stuck in a similar rut. Hooves aside, I feel like I've been in her shoes. The bounds of the farm were nearly the bounds of my world, as well."
    "No hace mucho me sentía atrapado en una rutina similar. Pezuñas aparte, me siento como si hubiera estado en sus zapatos. Los límites de la granja eran casi los límites de mi mundo, también."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8292
translate Spanish ch3m_07_55c8bd15:

    # "It chafed, so I took the first opportunity I had to escape. To see the world. Do my part."
    "Me rozaba, así que aproveché la primera oportunidad que tuve para escapar. Para ver el mundo. Hacer mi parte."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8293
translate Spanish ch3m_07_390a2cae:

    # "...As it turns out, life stranded on a remote farm beats life mired in a trench."
    "...Resulta que la vida atrapado en una granja remota supera a la vida atrapado en una trinchera."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8294
translate Spanish ch3m_07_7efd8be4:

    # "I've grown up. Learned valuable lessons about the dangers of the world. Even if Marion doesn't have to worry about stray bullets, I know what a fear of the unknown, of things alien, can provoke."
    "He madurado. Aprendí valiosas lecciones sobre los peligros del mundo. Aunque Marion no tenga que preocuparse por balas perdidas, sé lo que puede provocar el miedo a lo desconocido, a lo ajeno."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8296
translate Spanish ch3m_07_90c1b889:

    # "Hopefully, if anyone does find out Marion's secret, the only thing it provokes is an overwhelming need to fawn over her cute muzzle."
    "Espero que, si alguien descubre el secreto de Marion, lo único que provoque sea una abrumadora necesidad de admirar su lindo hocico."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8308
translate Spanish ch3m_07_7736fa59:

    # "Eventually, Marion enters the barn with a shovel of her own to help. One look and I know all is forgiven. I only hope she's also overcome—or at least shelved—her misgivings."
    "Eventualmente, Marion entra al establo con una pala para ayudar. Una mirada y sé que todo está perdonado. Solo espero que también haya superado—o al menos dejado de lado—sus dudas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8311
translate Spanish ch3m_07_f1ba0614:

    # "At one point during the drudgery, Marion looks at me and tells me something in earnest."
    "En un momento durante la monótona tarea, Marion me mira y me dice algo en serio."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8312
translate Spanish ch3m_07_e8fa58cc:

    # m "Malcolm, I'd been having nightmares."
    m "Malcolm, he estado teniendo pesadillas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8313
translate Spanish ch3m_07_ac9e0a6b:

    # "It's a confirmation of my concerns, and something I'm all too familiar with."
    "Es una confirmación de mis preocupaciones, y algo con lo que estoy muy familiarizado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8314
translate Spanish ch3m_07_ef6d62f4:

    # c "I'm sorry. Are you all right?"
    c "Lo siento. ¿Estás bien?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8316
translate Spanish ch3m_07_0d7c81a1:

    # m "Yes. They've all but disappeared since I came to a conclusion."
    m "Sí. Casi han desaparecido desde que llegué a una conclusión."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8317
translate Spanish ch3m_07_df72d121:

    # c "What's that?"
    c "¿Cuál es?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8318
translate Spanish ch3m_07_8da2e69c:

    # "I listen for guidance. Perhaps her remedy can be mine."
    "Escucho en busca de orientación. Quizá su remedio pueda ser el mío."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8320
translate Spanish ch3m_07_cd71e073:

    # m "Everything I need is right here. Right where I am right now. I... I don't know if I will ever be able to do what I once did, but..."
    m "Todo lo que necesito está aquí. Justo donde estoy ahora. Yo... no sé si alguna vez podré hacer lo que solía hacer, pero.."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8321
translate Spanish ch3m_07_f6ef9c39:

    # c "You'll never leave home again?"
    c "¿Nunca dejarás tu hogar?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8323
translate Spanish ch3m_07_ef2d2caa:

    # "Marion looks startled."
    "Marion parece sorprendida."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8325
translate Spanish ch3m_07_f6170573:

    # m "Hearing you say it makes it feel very real."
    m "Oírte decirlo lo hace sentir muy real."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8326
translate Spanish ch3m_07_b3af1848:

    # "I wince. She's not wrong. I decide to dial back my language."
    "Hago una mueca. No está equivocada. Decido suavizar mis palabras."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8327
translate Spanish ch3m_07_e997cbeb:

    # c "Marion, don't think like that. You're just not ready yet. But you could be at any time. Any day. Never say never. You may wish to go to market, or even to the pub, next week or next year."
    c "Marion, no pienses así. Simplemente no estás lista todavía. Pero podrías estarlo en cualquier momento. Cualquier día. Nunca digas nunca. Quizás quieras ir al mercado o incluso al taberna, la próxima semana o el próximo año."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8328
translate Spanish ch3m_07_0abc2c31:

    # c "You never know."
    c "Nunca se sabe."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8330
translate Spanish ch3m_07_e21b2d1c:

    # m "Never say never, Malcolm."
    m "Nunca digas nunca, Malcolm."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8345
translate Spanish ch3m_07_69fa27c7:

    # "Marion goes to the basin, making soft clacking noises as she rinses her hooves."
    "Marion se dirige a la palangana, haciendo suaves sonidos al enjuagar sus cascos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8346
translate Spanish ch3m_07_d4909fbd:

    # m "I had fears... fears of losing my mind, losing who I am as a person. Nightmares about becoming a hermit like Grace."
    m "Tenía miedo... miedo de perder la cabeza, de perder quién soy como persona. Pesadillas sobre convertirme en una ermitaña como Grace."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8347
translate Spanish ch3m_07_65804856:

    # c "But even she's discovered a way to break free from domestic monotony, Marion."
    c "Pero incluso ella ha descubierto una forma de romper con la monotonía doméstica, Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8348
translate Spanish ch3m_07_3951409a:

    # m "I can't leave my property. I can't be discovered."
    m "No puedo salir de mi propiedad. No puedo ser descubierta."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8349
translate Spanish ch3m_07_f850f6ee:

    # c "Please don't say that. I mean... of course you can stay here until—"
    c "Por favor, no digas eso. Quiero decir... claro que puedes quedarte aquí hasta que—"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8354
translate Spanish ch3m_07_ef1af3d3:

    # m "The cows come home?"
    m "¿Hasta que las vacas vuelvan a casa?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8362
translate Spanish ch3m_07_e0a9804e:

    # "Luckily, she's only joking, and I tug at her waist to pull her closer."
    "Por suerte, sólo está bromeando, y tiro de su cintura para acercarla."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8363
translate Spanish ch3m_07_c8b70780:

    # c "What I was going to say... is that if you want to stay here, I will support you, and never leave your side... and bother you so often that you'll tire of me faster than Fiona has!"
    c "Lo que iba a decir... es que si quieres quedarte aquí, te apoyaré, y nunca me apartaré de tu lado... ¡y te molestaré tan a menudo que te cansarás de mí más rápido de lo que se ha cansado Fiona!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8365
translate Spanish ch3m_07_2f236f6b:

    # "She laughs, and gives me a genuine smile."
    "Se ríe y me da una sonrisa genuina."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8367
translate Spanish ch3m_07_c3bdadb4:

    # m "I'll share with you something Grace told me."
    m "Te compartiré algo que Grace me dijo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8369
translate Spanish ch3m_07_712f4e20:

    # m "She taught me to be aware... and know the difference between solitude and loneliness. What I have here..."
    m "Me enseñó a ser consciente... y a conocer la diferencia entre la soledad y el aislamiento. Lo que tengo aquí..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8370
translate Spanish ch3m_07_3117c200:

    # "She gestures around the barn, and the land beyond its walls."
    "Señala alrededor del establo, y hacia las tierras más allá de sus muros."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8372
translate Spanish ch3m_07_36d9cb1c:

    # m "Provides me solitude."
    m "Me proporciona aislamiento."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8379
translate Spanish ch3m_07_e23c0391:

    # "Her arms wrap around me."
    "Sus brazos se envuelven alrededor de mí."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8380
translate Spanish ch3m_07_e0be12ba:

    # m "But never loneliness, Malcolm."
    m "Pero nunca soledad, Malcolm."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8385
translate Spanish ch3m_07_3b37bbfd:

    # m "If I change my mind in the future, I shall tell you. For now, I need to keep up with taking care of myself... and you..."
    m "Si cambio de opinión en el futuro, te lo diré. Por ahora, necesito seguir cuidándome... y a ti..."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8415
translate Spanish ch3m_07_c17eeadf:

    # "She lets go of me, and walks towards the curds in the vat."
    "Me suelta y camina hacia las cuajadas en el recipiente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8416
translate Spanish ch3m_07_6a7fd4ba:

    # m "And you, my love, need to eat!"
    m "¡Y a ti, mi amor, necesitas comer!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8417
translate Spanish ch3m_07_4988d0a7:

    # "I take the hint, drop the subject, and set to my orders."
    "Tomo la indirecta, dejo el tema y me pongo manos a la obra con mis órdenes."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8429
translate Spanish ch3m_07_941f5b16:

    # "Marion feeds the blocks we'd cheddared this morning into the cheese mill as I rotate it, seemingly endlessly. Then we pour scoops of curds into molds lined with cloth."
    "Marion introduce los bloques que habíamos cheddarizado esta mañana en el molino de queso mientras yo lo hago girar, aparentemente sin cesar. Luego vertemos cucharadas de cuajada en moldes forrados con tela."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8430
translate Spanish ch3m_07_e5cfb802:

    # "She twists the cloth, but I can see her struggling with her hooves to properly tighten and squeeze the whey from the bundle."
    "Ella retuerce la tela, pero puedo verla luchando con sus pezuñas para apretar correctamente y exprimir el suero del fardo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8431
translate Spanish ch3m_07_8fb26bd3:

    # m "Och... Malcolm, I just can't do it. This has never happened."
    m "Och... Malcolm, simplemente no puedo hacerlo. Esto nunca me había pasado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8442
translate Spanish ch3m_07_a3a9dd4e:

    # "I come up behind her, as she huffs and grunts, to try to help. She nudges her elbow into my ribs."
    "Me acerco detrás de ella mientras resopla y gruñe, tratando de ayudar. Me da un codazo en las costillas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8443
translate Spanish ch3m_07_71d80954:

    # m "I... I don't want help! I want to be able to do it myself!"
    m "¡Yo... no quiero ayuda! ¡Quiero poder hacerlo yo misma!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8445
translate Spanish ch3m_07_92bc212c:

    # m "I'm... I'm so sorry. I'll figure it out."
    m "Lo... Lo siento mucho. Ya me las arreglaré."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8446
translate Spanish ch3m_07_8d3843b6:

    # c "Do you want me to assist?"
    c "¿Quieres que te ayude?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8447
translate Spanish ch3m_07_0342f94d:

    # m "Yes... please. It's too much for me right now."
    m "Sí... por favor. Es demasiado para mí ahora."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8450
translate Spanish ch3m_07_2f4f52b3:

    # "Once home, Marion is excited to try out the new cheese-making equipment. Together we heft the new vat into place beside the old one."
    "De vuelta en casa, Marion está emocionada por probar el nuevo equipo para hacer queso. Juntos levantamos el nuevo recipiente y lo colocamos junto al viejo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8454
translate Spanish ch3m_07_f79a868f:

    # m "Look, Malcolm! This new trough is so {i}big!{/i}"
    m "¡Mira, Malcolm! ¡Este nuevo recipiente es tan {i}grande{/i}!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8455
translate Spanish ch3m_07_fc2947e3:

    # "It does make the old one look tiny by comparison."
    "Hace que el viejo parezca diminuto en comparación."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8456
translate Spanish ch3m_07_dfd8f0a4:

    # c "Are you sure the ol' gals in the field will be up to the task of filling it up?"
    c "¿Estás segura de que las chicas del campo estarán a la altura de la tarea de llenarlo?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8458
translate Spanish ch3m_07_6c43d682:

    # m "Positive. I've never seen them giving so much milk!"
    m "Estoy segura. ¡Nunca las he visto dar tanta leche!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8459
translate Spanish ch3m_07_5c97b93d:

    # "Marion and the cows might be up to the challenge, but the prospect of hefting countless more buckets of milk has me daunted."
    "Marion y las vacas pueden estar listas para el desafío, pero la perspectiva de cargar incontables cubos de leche más me desanima."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8461
translate Spanish ch3m_07_f9323543:

    # m "Come on! Let's empty the curds from this vat so we can set up the new one!"
    m "¡Vamos! ¡Vaciemos la cuajada de este recipiente para que podamos instalar el nuevo!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8472
translate Spanish ch3m_07_941f5b16_1:

    # "Marion feeds the blocks we'd cheddared this morning into the cheese mill as I rotate it, seemingly endlessly. Then we pour scoops of curds into molds lined with cloth."
    "Marion introduce los bloques que habíamos cheddarizado esta mañana en el molino de queso mientras yo lo hago girar, aparentemente sin cesar. Luego vertemos cucharadas de cuajada en moldes forrados con tela."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8473
translate Spanish ch3m_07_e5cfb802_1:

    # "She twists the cloth, but I can see her struggling with her hooves to properly tighten and squeeze the whey from the bundle."
    "Ella retuerce la tela, pero puedo verla luchando con sus pezuñas para apretar correctamente y exprimir el suero del fardo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8484
translate Spanish ch3m_07_d7312c3b:

    # "I come up behind her, as she huffs and grunts."
    "Me acerco detrás de ella mientras resopla y gruñe."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8485
translate Spanish ch3m_07_658fb77b:

    # m "Hah, I... I guess I'm still getting used to these."
    m "Hah, Yo... Supongo que todavía me estoy acostumbrando a esto."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8487
translate Spanish ch3m_07_ba7c8e77:

    # "She sets down the curds, and I place my stool directly behind hers."
    "Ella deja la cuajada y yo coloco mi taburete justo detrás del suyo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8488
translate Spanish ch3m_07_337d8878:

    # "I glide my palms along her damp, bare arms, admiring the softness of her fur, and the deft movement of her strong forearms and hooves."
    "Paso mis palmas por sus brazos desnudos y húmedos, admirando la suavidad de su pelaje y el movimiento ágil de sus fuertes antebrazos y pezuñas."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8489
translate Spanish ch3m_07_1ef3f7e7:

    # c "You're stronger than me in so many ways, Marion."
    c "Eres más fuerte que yo en muchos sentidos, Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8494
translate Spanish ch3m_07_61241e48:

    # "Placing my hands near her wrists, I'm able to guide her actions."
    "Coloco mis manos cerca de sus muñecas, guiando sus movimientos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8495
translate Spanish ch3m_07_8256c300:

    # c "Does that feel okay?"
    c "Se siente bien así?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8496
translate Spanish ch3m_07_1459eaf0:

    # m "It does. It's helping."
    m "Sí. Está ayudando."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8498
translate Spanish ch3m_07_169d7b65:

    # "The curds respond to our slightest efforts. Whey slips out through the cheese cloth, between our digits, as we twist and squeeze."
    "La cuajada responde a nuestros esfuerzos más mínimos. El suero se desliza por el paño de queso, entre nuestros dedos, mientras retorcemos y exprimimos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8504
translate Spanish ch3m_07_b0528f5d:

    # "Somehow my stool slides nearer to hers, until my hips are adjacent her tail."
    "De alguna manera mi taburete se desliza más cerca del suyo, hasta que mis caderas están junto a su cola."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8505
translate Spanish ch3m_07_d734585f:

    # "It swings back and forth with the rhythm of our work."
    "Se balancea adelante y atrás con el ritmo de nuestro trabajo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8507
translate Spanish ch3m_07_1fb2e9e9:

    # "A tension is building between us that is tighter than the walls of the hickory molds."
    "Una tensión se está construyendo entre nosotros, más apretada que las paredes de los moldes de nogal."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8508
translate Spanish ch3m_07_6f979f8c:

    # "Curiously, she tilts her head back toward me, and her muzzle brushes against my face."
    "Curiosamente, inclina la cabeza hacia atrás hacia mí, y su hocico roza mi cara."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8509
translate Spanish ch3m_07_aac28309:

    # "I lean into her, kissing her snout gently, then moving down to kiss the nape of her neck. It feels so plush against my lips."
    "Me inclino hacia ella, besando suavemente su hocico, luego bajando para besar la nuca de su cuello. Se siente tan aterciopelada contra mis labios."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8511
translate Spanish ch3m_07_5ea2abde:

    # "I'm losing myself—and my inhibitions—in the moment, and I sense that Marion is too. The whey is heady and slick, splattering us with each wring of the cheesecloth."
    "Me estoy perdiendo, y mis inhibiciones también, en el momento. Siento que Marion está igual. El suero salpica y nos empapa con cada torsión de tela para queso."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8512
translate Spanish ch3m_07_31d140bb:

    # "My hands start to squeeze hers more tightly, and she lets out a low moan, less of pain than pleasure."
    "Mis manos comienzan a apretar las suyas con más fuerza, y ella deja escapar un leve gemido, más de placer que de dolor."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8514
translate Spanish ch3m_07_0a74c1a5:

    # "Marion lowers her chin, searching for my lips, and we connect."
    "Marion baja la barbilla, buscando mis labios, y nos conectamos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8515
translate Spanish ch3m_07_68eac34f:

    # "Our lips part, and our kiss becomes deeper, more passionate, with each passing breath."
    "Nuestros labios se separan, y el beso se vuelve más profundo, más apasionado, con cada respiración."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8517
translate Spanish ch3m_07_3fbb41f8:

    # "My hip is pressed so firmly to hers, now, it aches. Beneath my own tightening grip, Marion's hooves are squeezing the cheesecloth harder and harder."
    "Mi cadera está tan firmemente presionada contra la suya, ahora, que duele. Bajo mi propio agarre, las pezuñas de Marion aprietan la tela para queso cada vez más fuerte"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8527
translate Spanish ch3m_07_57170a1e:

    # "Curds tumble out of the broken cloth, spattering whey everywhere, breaking the spell between us. We both double over, laughing."
    "Las cuajadas se escapan del paño roto, salpicando suero por todas partes, rompiendo el hechizo entre nosotros. Ambos nos doblamos de la risa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8528
translate Spanish ch3m_07_b68d4a8b:

    # m "Oh, Malcolm, what a mess!"
    m "¡Oh, Malcolm, qué desastre!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8530
translate Spanish ch3m_07_bc044d5d:

    # c "Don't fret, Miss Marion. No sense crying over spilt milk!"
    c "No se preocupe, señorita Marion. No tiene sentido llorar sobre la leche derramada!"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8552
translate Spanish ch3m_07_df1e1b5e:

    # "We wash up from the cheese-making, and spend the rest of the day doing our chores in good cheer."
    "Nos lavamos después de hacer el queso, y pasamos el resto del día haciendo nuestras tareas con buen ánimo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8553
translate Spanish ch3m_07_55b837e6:

    # "I sense something changed between us, though—a new dynamic. I leave it unsaid, but... I wonder if Marion feels it too."
    "Siento que algo cambió entre nosotros, sin embargo, una nueva dinámica. No lo digo en voz alta, pero... me pregunto si Marion también lo siente."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8555
translate Spanish ch3m_07_2f517c1b:

    # "Time passes quickly and we seem to only get half the work done that we want to."
    "El tiempo pasa rápido y parece que solo logramos hacer la mitad del trabajo que queríamos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8565
translate Spanish ch3m_07_c4b717d1:

    # "Before long, the sun has dipped below the horizon, our bellies are full, and it's time to bid Marion a good evening."
    "Antes de darme cuenta, el sol se ha puesto bajo el horizonte, nuestros estómagos están llenos, y es hora darle las buenas noches a Marion."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8583
translate Spanish ch3m_07_a_8492c7ec:

    # "In her bedroom, I light some candles and pour us each a glass of cold water from the pitcher. This is our new nightly routine."
    "En su habitación, enciendo algunas velas y nos sirvo a cada uno un vaso de agua fría del cántaro. Esta es nuestra nueva rutina nocturna."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8584
translate Spanish ch3m_07_a_5654102f:

    # "Darkness permeates the room, and the scent of tallow wax surrounds me."
    "La oscuridad impregna la habitación, y el aroma de cera de sebo me rodea."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8596
translate Spanish ch3m_07_a_3f837b8b:

    # "Like an apparition, Marion emerges in her long, sheer nightgown. I have to remind myself that the vision is all too real. She curtsies shyly, and the two of us squeeze onto the small bed."
    "Como una aparición, Marion emerge con su largo camisón transparente. Tengo que recordarme que la visión es completamente real. Ella hace una reverencia tímida, y los dos nos apretamos en la pequeña cama."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8604
translate Spanish ch3m_07_a_7ec4ca12:

    # "We curl up together. We rest our heads. This time feels... different. The energy in the room has heightened. The day may have been simple, but it brought us just that much closer."
    "Nos acurrucamos juntos. Descansamos la cabeza. Esta vez parece... diferente. La energía en la habitación ha aumentado. Puede que el día haya sido sencillo, pero nos ha acercado mucho más."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8605
translate Spanish ch3m_07_a_e69559e9:

    # "I usually stay until she drifts to sleep, at which time I tiptoe out and head home."
    "Normalmente me quedo hasta que se queda dormida, momento en el que salgo de puntillas y me dirijo a casa."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8608
translate Spanish ch3m_07_a_c29d705e:

    # "As I hold her in bed, there's no part of me that wants to say goodbye to her tonight. An anxiety in me builds every time we separate."
    "Pero mientras la sostengo en la cama, no hay parte de mí que quiera decirle adiós esta noche. Una ansiedad crece en mí cada vez que nos separamos."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8609
translate Spanish ch3m_07_a_64c651cf:

    # "But I also don't want to stifle her with my presence. It {i}has{/i} been a busy day.... but every day is busy."
    "Pero tampoco quiero sofocarla con mi presencia. Ha {i}sido{/i} un día ajetreado.... pero todos los días son ajetreados."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8613
translate Spanish ch3m_07_a_1596c847:

    # "It's as if Marion senses my apprehension, or perhaps even feels it herself."
    "Es como si Marion percibiera mi inquietud, o tal vez incluso la sintiera ella misma."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8614
translate Spanish ch3m_07_a_790ed5b2:

    # "She whispers in my ear."
    "Me susurra al oído."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8615
translate Spanish ch3m_07_a_3da988b9:

    # m "It's so late, Malcolm. Why don't you just stay here tonight?"
    m "Es muy tarde, Malcolm. ¿Por qué no te quedas aquí esta noche?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8616
translate Spanish ch3m_07_a_2df86ad9:

    # "A shiver goes through me. My body goes cold like it's been tossed into an ice bath."
    "Un escalofrío recorre mi cuerpo. Siento que mi cuerpo se enfría como si me hubieran arrojado a un baño de hielo."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8617
translate Spanish ch3m_07_a_2b8c3c44:

    # "{i}Here? Tonight? With her?{/i}"
    "{i}¿Aquí? ¿Esta noche? ¿Con ella?{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8620
translate Spanish ch3m_07_a_09f95049:

    # "I'm frozen by the choice. Does she mean what I think she means? That can't be it. {i}Could it{/i}?"
    "Estoy congelado por la decisión. ¿Quiere decir lo que creo que quiere decir? No puede ser. {i}¿O sí?{/i}"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8621
translate Spanish ch3m_07_a_8e7e4806:

    # "We know how attracted we are to each other. But ever since that difficult day under the alders, I wasn't sure when—or if—she would feel comfortable enough to be that close... physically... to me again."
    "Sabemos cuánta atracción sentimos el uno por el otro. Pero desde aquel difícil día bajo los alisos, no estaba seguro de cuándo—o si—ella se sentiría lo suficientemente cómoda como para estar tan cerca... físicamente... de mí otra vez."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8622
translate Spanish ch3m_07_a_66555f84:

    # "Plus, what would that mean for {i}us?{/i} As a couple?"
    "Además, ¿qué significaría eso para {i}nosotros{/i}? ¿Como pareja?"

# game/script_marion.rpy:8623
translate Spanish ch3m_07_a_ac1d0df4:

    # "I remind myself that we've already committed to each other, even touched upon marriage, but... Marion is... so dear, so special. So different than any woman I could have ever fallen for."
    "Me recuerdo a mí mismo que ya nos hemos comprometido el uno con el otro, incluso hemos tocado el tema del matrimonio, pero... Marion es... tan querida, tan especial. Tan diferente a cualquier mujer de la que podría haberme enamorado."

# game/script_marion.rpy:8626
translate Spanish ch3m_07_a_c97a8d35:

    # m "Please don't think I'm being forward, but... I want this night to be for us, Malcolm. I love you... and..."
    m "Por favor, no pienses que estoy siendo atrevida, pero... quiero que esta noche sea para nosotros, Malcolm. Te amo... y..."

